        "CBP I-94 site for retrieving the most recent admission record.": "CBP I-94 site para sa pagkuha ng pinakabagong admission record.",
        "CMS landing page on the federal and state marketplaces. Redirected from a cciio URL.": "CMS landing page tungkol sa federal at state marketplaces. Na-redirect mula sa cciio URL.",
        "CMS page summarizing Original Medicare eligibility, including the five-year continuous residency provision for lawfully admitted permanent residents.": "CMS page na nagbubuod ng Original Medicare eligibility, kasama ang five-year continuous residency provision para sa lawfully admitted permanent residents.",
        "CMS press release on April 2026 guidance to implement statutory limits on federal Medicaid and CHIP funding for certain noncitizens, taking effect October 1, 2026, and noting the carve-out for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "CMS press release tungkol sa Abril 2026 guidance upang ipatupad ang statutory limits sa federal Medicaid at CHIP funding para sa ilang noncitizens, na epektibo sa Oktubre 1, 2026, at binabanggit ang carve-out para sa lawfully residing children at pregnant individuals.",
        "CROSS-STATE RELOCATION CHECKLIST": "CHECKLIST PARA SA PAGLIPAT SA IBANG ESTADO",
        "CUNY tuition and fee manual chapter on residency, covering nonimmigrant visa categories that may establish New York domicile and high-school-attendance provisions.": "Kabanata ng CUNY tuition and fee manual tungkol sa residency, na sumasaklaw sa mga nonimmigrant visa category na maaaring magtatag ng New York domicile at high-school-attendance provisions.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing applicant FAQ page covering documentation, SSN, and immigration-status questions.": "California Board of Registered Nursing applicant FAQ page na sumasaklaw sa dokumentasyon, SSN, at immigration-status na mga tanong.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing page on international endorsement requirements, including credentials evaluation.": "California Board of Registered Nursing page tungkol sa international endorsement requirements, kasama ang credentials evaluation.",
        "California DMV REAL ID page covering documentation for non-U.S. citizens, including how the credential expiration may track the underlying federal document.": "California DMV REAL ID page na sumasaklaw sa dokumentasyon para sa mga non-U.S. citizen, kasama ang kung paano maaaring sumunod ang credential expiration sa underlying federal document.",
        "California FTB page on part-year and nonresident filers, including a note that California does not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "California FTB page tungkol sa part-year at nonresident filers, kasama ang paalala na hindi sumusunod ang California sa federal income tax treaty exclusions.",
