        "A health plan that works at home may have limited in-network access in the destination state.": "Um plano de saúde que funciona na sua região atual pode ter acesso limitado dentro da rede no estado de destino.",
        "A household that was covered by a state-funded program in the origin state may not find an equivalent program at the destination, which can affect a move plan.": "Um domicílio que era atendido por um programa financiado pelo estado de origem pode não encontrar um programa equivalente no destino, e isso pode afetar o plano de mudança.",
        "A missed AR-11 filing can disrupt USCIS notice delivery for any pending or future case, and may create a question of status maintenance that compounds with employer and school records that also need updating.": "Deixar de enviar o AR-11 pode atrapalhar a entrega de avisos do USCIS para qualquer caso pendente ou futuro e pode criar uma dúvida sobre manutenção de situação migratória, que se soma a registros de empregador e escola que também precisam ser atualizados.",
        "A move part-way through a tax year can lead to part-year filings, multiple state filings, or unexpected withholding, and rules for non-citizens generally follow the same state framework as for citizens but documentation can differ.": "Uma mudança no meio do ano fiscal pode levar a declarações de part-year, a declarações em vários estados ou a retenção inesperada, e as regras para não cidadãos em geral seguem o mesmo arcabouço estadual aplicado a cidadãos, mas a documentação pode ser diferente.",
        "A move part-way through a tax year may produce part-year filings, multiple state filings, or unexpected withholding, and the interaction between federal nonresident alien treatment and state residency rules can change between origin and destination.": "Uma mudança no meio do ano fiscal pode gerar declarações de part-year, declarações em vários estados ou retenção inesperada, e a interação entre o tratamento federal de nonresident alien e as regras estaduais de residência pode mudar entre origem e destino.",
        "A move that triggers a fresh application in the destination state may produce a credential with a different renewal cycle than the prior state used, and timing renewal around an I-94 or visa extension can affect work, study, and travel logistics.": "Uma mudança que aciona um novo pedido no estado de destino pode gerar uma credencial com um ciclo de renovação diferente do que o estado anterior usava, e programar a renovação em torno de uma extensão do I-94 ou do visto pode afetar a logística de trabalho, estudo e viagem.",
        "A move that triggers loss of prior coverage may open a marketplace special enrollment period, and the eligibility framework for nonimmigrants can differ from Medicaid waiting-period rules. Federal rules in this area have been changing.": "Uma mudança que acione a perda da cobertura anterior pode abrir um special enrollment period no marketplace, e o arcabouço de elegibilidade para não imigrantes pode diferir das regras de período de espera do Medicaid. As regras federais nessa área têm mudado.",
        "About": "Sobre",
        "About Dreamer status": "Sobre a situação de Dreamer",
        "About green card holder status": "Sobre a situação de portador de green card",
        "About visa-holder status": "Sobre a situação de portador de visto",
        "Administrative guidance only. Not medical advice.": "Apenas orientação administrativa. Não é aconselhamento médico.",
        "Administrative requirement": "Exigência administrativa",
        "After a move that involves a new employer, payroll systems may default to withholding FICA, and a misclassification can take time to correct through the employer or via an IRS refund claim.": "Após uma mudança que envolva novo empregador, os sistemas de folha de pagamento podem aplicar a retenção de FICA por padrão, e uma classificação incorreta pode demorar a ser corrigida pelo empregador ou via pedido de restituição ao IRS.",
        "Agency rule": "Regra de órgão",
        "All": "Todos",
        "An F-1 student moving to another SEVP-certified school generally goes through a SEVIS record transfer between the current school's DSO and the new school's DSO, with a transfer release date, an initial reporting requirement at the new school, and a new Form I-20.": "Um estudante F-1 que se mude para outra escola certificada pelo SEVP em geral passa por uma transferência de registro no SEVIS entre o DSO da escola atual e o DSO da nova escola, com uma data de transfer release, uma exigência de comparecimento inicial na nova escola e um novo Formulário I-20.",
        "An interstate move during OPT or STEM OPT often coincides with an employer change, and missed reporting can affect both SEVIS standing and the running count of unemployment days, which is tracked at the federal level rather than by the destination state.": "Uma mudança entre estados durante o OPT ou o STEM OPT muitas vezes coincide com uma troca de empregador, e deixar de reportar pode afetar tanto a situação no SEVIS quanto a contagem corrente de dias de desemprego, que é acompanhada em nível federal e não pelo estado de destino.",
        "An outdated SEVIS address can interfere with notice delivery from SEVP or the program sponsor, and uncorrected records can place a SEVIS record at risk of termination, which can have downstream effects on status, work authorization, and travel.": "Um endereço desatualizado no SEVIS pode atrapalhar a entrega de avisos do SEVP ou do sponsor do programa, e registros não corrigidos podem colocar um registro SEVIS em risco de encerramento, o que pode trazer efeitos em cascata para a situação migratória, a autorização de trabalho e viagens.",
        "Apartment or landlord pet policies": "Políticas de animais do apartamento ou do locador",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements.": "Atrasos no pedido, indeferimentos ou nova coleta de digitais podem ocorrer se os documentos que você apresentar não estiverem de acordo com as regras atuais do conselho do estado de destino, especialmente ao se mudar de um estado com exigências diferentes.",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements. Boards of Nursing also vary in how they treat the Nurse Licensure Compact for non-citizen primary state of residency.": "Atrasos no pedido, indeferimentos ou nova coleta de digitais podem ocorrer se os documentos que você apresentar não estiverem de acordo com as regras atuais do conselho do estado de destino, especialmente ao se mudar de um estado com exigências diferentes. Os Boards of Nursing também variam em como tratam o Nurse Licensure Compact para a declaração de primary state of residency de não cidadão.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance and other tasks that rely on a state ID after a move.": "Chegar sem a combinação de documentos que o DMV do estado de destino espera pode atrasar a emissão da carteira e outras tarefas que dependem de um state ID após a mudança.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance, which then delays other tasks that rely on a state credential after a move, including rental, employer onboarding, and school registration.": "Chegar sem a combinação de documentos que o DMV do estado de destino espera pode atrasar a emissão da carteira, o que então atrasa outras tarefas que dependem de uma credencial estadual após a mudança, como aluguel, onboarding no empregador e matrícula escolar.",
        "Arriving without the right documents can delay your license and other tasks that depend on it.": "Chegar sem os documentos corretos pode atrasar sua carteira e outras tarefas que dependem dela.",
        "Assuming H-1B-style MSA logic for L-1 or O-1 can lead to a missed amendment when the original petition described a specific worksite or itinerary that no longer matches.": "Supor a lógica de MSA do H-1B para L-1 ou O-1 pode levar a deixar passar uma emenda quando a petição original descreveu um worksite ou itinerário específico que já não corresponde.",
        "Auto insurance": "Seguro de automóvel",
        "Auto insurance minimums and rules differ by state. Insurers may need to update your policy after a move.": "Os mínimos e as regras do seguro de automóvel diferem conforme o estado. As seguradoras podem precisar atualizar sua apólice após a mudança.",
        "Auto-detected: %@": "Detectado automaticamente: %@",
        "Awareness item": "Item de atenção",
        "Back to builder": "Voltar ao montador",
        "Back to home": "Voltar ao início",
        "Background check and fingerprinting requirements": "Exigências de verificação de antecedentes e coleta de digitais",
        "Background check or fingerprinting requirements": "Exigências de verificação de antecedentes ou coleta de digitais",
        "Based on your selected states and purpose, here are topics to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "Com base nos estados e no objetivo que você selecionou, estes são tópicos a conferir antes da mudança. Este checklist não é uma conclusão jurídica.",
        "Because the J-1 sponsor (not USCIS) controls the SEVIS record and may need Department of State approval for certain changes, a move can affect program compliance differently from H-1B or F-1 scenarios.": "Como o sponsor J-1 (e não o USCIS) controla o registro no SEVIS e pode precisar de aprovação do Department of State para certas mudanças, uma mudança pode afetar o cumprimento do programa de modo diferente dos cenários H-1B ou F-1.",
        "Beneficiary-facing CMS site on Medicare basics.": "Site do CMS voltado a beneficiários, com noções sobre Medicare.",
        "Board of nursing requirements, compact licenses, clinical placement.": "Exigências do conselho de enfermagem, licenças por compacto e estágio clínico.",
        "Boards of Nursing may have specific guidance about documentation for non-citizen applicants, including whether an SSN is required, whether an ITIN or attestation is accepted, how foreign education is evaluated, and how license endorsement works when moving from another state.": "Os Boards of Nursing podem ter orientação específica sobre documentação para candidatos não cidadãos, incluindo se um SSN é exigido, se um ITIN ou declaração é aceito, como a formação estrangeira é avaliada e como funciona o endosso de licença quando alguém se muda de outro estado.",
        "Breed or species restrictions (state, local, or housing-level)": "Restrições por raça ou espécie (em nível estadual, local ou da moradia)",
        "Build a state-to-state checklist for licenses, vehicles, housing, pets, work, school, healthcare licensure, and other rules that may change when you move.": "Monte um checklist entre estados para carteira de motorista, veículos, moradia, animais de estimação, trabalho, escola, licenciamento na área da saúde e outras regras que podem mudar quando você se muda.",
        "Build checklist": "Montar checklist",
        "Build my checklist": "Montar meu checklist",
        "Build your relocation checklist": "Monte seu checklist de mudança",
        "Builder options": "Opções do montador",
        "CBP I-94 Official Site": "Site oficial do CBP para I-94",
        "CBP I-94 site for retrieving the most recent admission record.": "Site do CBP para I-94, para obter o registro de admissão mais recente.",
        "CHECKLIST BUILDER": "MONTADOR DE CHECKLIST",
        "CMS landing page on the federal and state marketplaces. Redirected from a cciio URL.": "Página inicial do CMS sobre os marketplaces federal e estaduais. Redirecionada a partir de uma URL cciio.",
        "CMS page summarizing Original Medicare eligibility, including the five-year continuous residency provision for lawfully admitted permanent residents.": "Página do CMS resumindo a elegibilidade ao Original Medicare, incluindo a disposição de cinco anos de residência contínua para lawfully admitted permanent residents.",
        "CMS press release on April 2026 guidance to implement statutory limits on federal Medicaid and CHIP funding for certain noncitizens, taking effect October 1, 2026, and noting the carve-out for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "Press release do CMS sobre a orientação de abril de 2026 para implementar os limites legais ao financiamento federal de Medicaid e de CHIP para certos não cidadãos, com vigência a partir de 1º de outubro de 2026, e que registra a ressalva para lawfully residing children e gestantes.",
        "CPR / BLS certification": "Certificação de CPR / BLS",
        "CROSS-STATE RELOCATION CHECKLIST": "CHECKLIST DE MUDANÇA ENTRE ESTADOS",
        "CUNY tuition and fee manual chapter on residency, covering nonimmigrant visa categories that may establish New York domicile and high-school-attendance provisions.": "Capítulo do manual de mensalidades e taxas da CUNY sobre residência, cobrindo categorias de visto de não imigrante que podem estabelecer domicílio em New York e as disposições de frequência ao ensino médio.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing applicant FAQ page covering documentation, SSN, and immigration-status questions.": "Página de perguntas frequentes do candidato no California Board of Registered Nursing, cobrindo documentação, SSN e dúvidas sobre situação migratória.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing page on international endorsement requirements, including credentials evaluation.": "Página do California Board of Registered Nursing sobre exigências de endosso internacional, incluindo avaliação de credenciais.",
        "California DMV REAL ID page covering documentation for non-U.S. citizens, including how the credential expiration may track the underlying federal document.": "Página de REAL ID do DMV da California cobrindo documentação para não cidadãos dos EUA, incluindo como o vencimento da credencial pode acompanhar o documento federal subjacente.",
        "California FTB page on part-year and nonresident filers, including a note that California does not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "Página da California FTB sobre declarantes part-year e nonresident, incluindo a observação de que a California não acompanha as exclusões federais de tratado tributário sobre renda.",
        "California Franchise Tax Board page on residency, nonresidency, and part-year status for state income tax purposes.": "Página do California Franchise Tax Board sobre residência, nonresidency e situação de part-year para fins de imposto de renda estadual.",
        "Can cause inconvenience, fees, or compliance problems if ignored.": "Pode causar transtornos, taxas ou problemas de conformidade se ignorado.",
        "Categories": "Categorias",
        "Categories where rules vary substantially. Verify directly with official sources.": "Categorias em que as regras variam bastante. Confira diretamente em fontes oficiais.",
        "Check insurance networks, student health, and prescription transfer": "Confira redes de seguro, saúde estudantil e transferência de prescrições",
        "Check pet vaccination, licensing, and housing rules": "Confira regras de vacinação, licenciamento e moradia para animais",
        "Check the destination state board of nursing requirements": "Confira as exigências do conselho de enfermagem do estado de destino",
        "Check whether a destination-state license application triggers Selective Service registration": "Confira se o pedido de carteira no estado de destino aciona o registro no Selective Service",
        "Check whether moving creates a state tax filing requirement": "Confira se a mudança gera obrigação de declaração de imposto estadual",
        "Check whether your professional license transfers": "Confira se sua licença profissional é transferível",
        "Checklist builder": "Montador de checklist",
        "Choose your origin and destination state.": "Escolha seu estado de origem e de destino.",
        "Choose your origin and destination, your purpose, and the categories that apply. MoveSafe will generate a list of topics to verify before moving.": "Escolha sua origem e destino, seu objetivo e as categorias aplicáveis. O MoveSafe gerará uma lista de tópicos a conferir antes da mudança.",
        "Choose your states, purpose, and categories. MoveSafe will assemble a source-linked checklist with risk badges.": "Escolha seus estados, objetivo e categorias. O MoveSafe montará um checklist com fontes vinculadas e selos de risco.",
        "Choosing the wrong credential type at the destination-state DMV can mean reapplying later, and document expiration may shorten the validity of a REAL ID issued to non-citizens.": "Escolher o tipo de credencial errado no DMV do estado de destino pode significar refazer o pedido depois, e o vencimento do documento pode encurtar a validade de um REAL ID emitido para não cidadãos.",
        "Clears the verified state on items currently shown.": "Limpa o estado de conferido dos itens mostrados no momento.",
        "Clinical placement": "Estágio clínico",
        "Clinical sites and schools may require immunizations, drug screens, CPR/BLS, background checks, and other clearances separate from board licensure.": "Locais clínicos e escolas podem exigir imunizações, testes de drogas, CPR/BLS, verificações de antecedentes e outras liberações separadas do licenciamento do conselho.",
        "Confirm clinical placement and school onboarding requirements": "Confirme as exigências de estágio clínico e de integração escolar",
        "Confirm required documents for a destination-state license": "Confirme os documentos exigidos para a carteira no estado de destino",
        "Confirm school residency, insurance, and immunization rules": "Confirme as regras de residência, seguro e imunização da escola",
        "Confirm your auto insurance covers the destination state": "Confirme se seu seguro de automóvel cobre o estado de destino",
        "Continue my checklist": "Continuar meu checklist",
        "Continuing education requirements": "Exigências de educação continuada",
        "Continuity of coverage after a move depends on whether the destination state operates its own marketplace, which categories of non-citizens it considers, and whether state-funded coverage is offered to people who are not eligible for the federal marketplace.": "A continuidade da cobertura depois de uma mudança depende de o estado de destino operar o próprio marketplace, de quais categorias de não cidadãos ele considera e de a cobertura financiada pelo estado ser oferecida a pessoas que não são elegíveis ao marketplace federal.",
        "Could not generate checklist": "Não foi possível gerar o checklist",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page covering personal information updates.": "Página do central de ajuda do SEVIS no Study in the States do DHS sobre atualizações de informações pessoais.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on F-1 SEVIS transfer mechanics.": "Página do central de ajuda do SEVIS no Study in the States do DHS sobre a mecânica de transferência no SEVIS para F-1.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on STEM OPT.": "Página do central de ajuda do SEVIS no Study in the States do DHS sobre STEM OPT.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVP Portal help page describing OPT reporting.": "Página de ajuda do SEVP Portal no Study in the States do DHS descrevendo o reporte do OPT.",
        "DHS Study in the States blog post on the 10-day DSO reporting expectation.": "Post no blog do Study in the States do DHS sobre a expectativa de reporte ao DSO em até 10 dias.",
        "DHS Study in the States guidance for F-1 and M-1 students on reporting address changes to the designated school official within 10 days.": "Orientação do Study in the States do DHS para estudantes F-1 e M-1 sobre reportar mudanças de endereço ao designated school official em até 10 dias.",
        "DHS Study in the States post on SEVIS address-of-record.": "Post do Study in the States do DHS sobre o endereço de registro no SEVIS.",
        "DOL FLAG (Office of Foreign Labor Certification) Portal": "Portal FLAG do DOL (Office of Foreign Labor Certification)",
        "DOL FLAG portal that handles LCA and other foreign-labor filings. The dol.gov subpages returned 403 to curl with Mozilla user-agent, consistent with anti-bot behavior on a long-standing .gov domain, so this canonical FLAG portal URL is used.": "Portal FLAG do DOL que processa LCA e outros pedidos de foreign labor. As subpáginas de dol.gov retornaram 403 ao curl com user-agent Mozilla, condizente com comportamento antibot em um domínio .gov de longa data, então esta URL canônica do portal FLAG é usada.",
        "Decide your residency, eligibility, or tax status": "Decidir sua residência, elegibilidade ou situação tributária",
        "Department of Homeland Security guidance for F-1 and M-1 students, and Department of State regulations for J-1 exchange visitors, generally require reporting an address change to a designated school official (DSO) or program sponsor within 10 days so the SEVIS record can be updated.": "A orientação do Department of Homeland Security para estudantes F-1 e M-1 e os regulamentos do Department of State para exchange visitors J-1 em geral exigem reportar uma mudança de endereço a um designated school official (DSO) ou sponsor do programa em até 10 dias para que o registro SEVIS possa ser atualizado.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA categories overview.": "Visão geral das categorias do BridgeUSA do Department of State.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA landing page for the J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.": "Página inicial do BridgeUSA do Department of State para o programa J-1 Exchange Visitor.",
        "Destination state": "Estado de destino",
        "Destination state DMV / MVA": "DMV / MVA do estado de destino",
        "Destination state attorney general": "Procuradoria-geral do estado de destino",
        "Destination state board of nursing": "Board of nursing do estado de destino",
        "Destination state department of agriculture": "Departamento de agricultura do estado de destino",
        "Destination state department of health": "Departamento de saúde do estado de destino",
        "Destination state department of labor": "Departamento do trabalho do estado de destino",
        "Destination state professional licensing": "Licenciamento profissional do estado de destino",
        "Destination state tax agency": "Órgão fiscal do estado de destino",
        "Destination-state minimum coverage requirements": "Exigências de cobertura mínima do estado de destino",
        "Destination:": "Destino:",
        "Determine whether a specific act is lawful": "Determinar se um ato específico está em conformidade com a lei",
        "Different agencies may apply different residency tests. The same person can be a resident for one purpose and not another.": "Órgãos diferentes podem aplicar testes de residência diferentes. A mesma pessoa pode ser residente para um fim e não para outro.",
        "Direct users to confirm coverage with their insurer. Do not state whether coverage applies.": "Oriente os usuários a confirmar a cobertura com a seguradora. Não afirme se a cobertura se aplica.",
        "Disclaimer. %@": "Aviso legal. %@",
        "Do not assert that any group is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID rules involve both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only.": "Não afirme que um grupo é ou não elegível ao REAL ID em um estado específico. As regras do REAL ID envolvem tanto mínimos federais quanto implementação estadual, que podem mudar. Use apenas linguagem como \"confira\" e \"pode variar\".",
        "Do not assert that any specific state always uses a shortened renewal cycle for a given visa category. Frame as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não afirme que algum estado específico sempre usa um ciclo de renovação encurtado para uma determinada categoria de visto. Apresente como itens a conferir com o DMV do estado de destino. Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not assert that any visa category is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID involves both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não afirme que alguma categoria de visto é ou não elegível ao REAL ID em um estado específico. O REAL ID envolve tanto mínimos federais quanto implementação estadual, que podem mudar. Use apenas linguagem como \"confira\" e \"pode variar\" e siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not assume": "Não presuma",
        "Do not assume a USPS or DMV address update satisfies the federal AR-11 step": "Não presuma que uma atualização de endereço no USPS ou no DMV cumpre a etapa federal do AR-11",
        "Do not assume regulated items follow the same rules across state lines": "Não presuma que itens regulamentados seguem as mesmas regras entre estados",
        "Do not assume rules from your origin state apply. Rules vary across state, local, and federal jurisdictions. Verify directly with official sources.": "Não presuma que as regras do seu estado de origem se aplicam. As regras variam entre jurisdições estaduais, locais e federais. Confira diretamente em fontes oficiais.",
        "Do not characterize voter registration by non-citizens using legal-conclusion or accusatory language. Use neutral framing such as 'generally not eligible' and 'may create immigration complications'. Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney. Do not give procedural advice for any specific state.": "Não caracterize o registro eleitoral por não cidadãos com linguagem de conclusão jurídica ou de acusação. Use enquadramento neutro como \"em geral não elegível\" e \"pode criar complicações migratórias\". Direcione os leitores a consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado. Não dê orientação processual para nenhum estado específico.",
        "Do not characterize whether any visa category can establish residency in a specific state as a determination. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não caracterize como determinação se alguma categoria de visto pode estabelecer residência em um estado específico. Apresente como regras de classificação a conferir com o registrar da escola e com o órgão estadual de ensino superior. Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not determine residency. List factors to verify. Direct to the relevant agency or school.": "Não determine a residência. Liste fatores a conferir. Direcione ao órgão pertinente ou à escola.",
        "Do not determine that a household 'is' or 'is not' eligible for Medicaid. Frame as items to verify with the state Medicaid agency. Use 'may apply' and 'rules differ by jurisdiction'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não determine que um domicílio \"é\" ou \"não é\" elegível ao Medicaid. Apresente como itens a conferir com o órgão estadual de Medicaid. Use \"pode se aplicar\" e \"as regras diferem por jurisdição\". Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not list which states grant in-state tuition for DACA recipients. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency.": "Não liste quais estados concedem mensalidade in-state a beneficiários do DACA. Apresente como regras de classificação a conferir com o registrar da escola e com o órgão estadual de ensino superior.",
        "Do not provide a public-charge determination or say that using benefits 'will' or 'will not' affect immigration. Frame as 'may interact' and recommend consulting a licensed immigration attorney. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não emita determinação de public charge nem diga que usar benefícios \"vai\" ou \"não vai\" afetar a imigração. Apresente como \"pode interagir\" e recomende consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado. Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not provide medical or transport instructions for controlled substances.": "Não forneça instruções médicas ou de transporte para substâncias controladas.",
        "Do not provide tactical instructions for transporting, possessing, hiding, storing, modifying, or avoiding enforcement for regulated items.": "Não forneça instruções táticas para transportar, possuir, esconder, armazenar, modificar ou contornar a fiscalização de itens regulamentados.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to official tax agency and qualified professionals.": "Não forneça aconselhamento tributário. Direcione ao órgão tributário oficial e a profissionais qualificados.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to state tax agency or qualified tax professional.": "Não forneça aconselhamento tributário. Direcione ao órgão tributário estadual ou a um profissional tributário qualificado.",
        "Do not say a Board of Nursing in a particular state grants or refuses an applicant's NCLEX path. Use 'verify with the destination Board of Nursing'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não diga que um Board of Nursing em um estado específico concede ou recusa o caminho do NCLEX de um candidato. Use \"confira com o Board of Nursing do estado de destino\". Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not say a particular aid program 'is open to' or 'is closed to' DACA recipients or LPRs. Use 'verify with the state aid agency and the school financial-aid office'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não diga que um programa específico de auxílio \"está aberto\" ou \"está fechado\" a beneficiários do DACA ou LPRs. Use \"confira com o órgão estadual de auxílio e com o escritório de auxílio financeiro da escola\". Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not say a person 'can' or 'cannot' enroll. Use 'verify current eligibility categories with the marketplace operator' since federal rules have changed. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não diga que uma pessoa \"pode\" ou \"não pode\" se inscrever. Use \"confira as categorias atuais de elegibilidade com o operador do marketplace\", já que as regras federais mudaram. Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency for a given visa category or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não afirme como um estado específico define residência para uma determinada categoria de visto nem que alguém \"é\" residente. Apresente como \"as regras diferem por jurisdição\" e \"confira com o órgão fiscal do estado de destino\". Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não afirme como um estado específico define residência nem que alguém \"é\" residente. Apresente como \"as regras diferem por jurisdição\" e \"confira com o órgão fiscal do estado de destino\". Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license a given visa category. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não afirme que algum conselho específico licencia ou deixa de licenciar uma determinada categoria de visto. Apresente tudo como itens a conferir com o conselho do estado de destino. Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license non-citizens. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não afirme que algum conselho específico licencia ou deixa de licenciar não cidadãos. Apresente tudo como itens a conferir com o conselho do estado de destino. Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Frame as a federal requirement that 'may apply' depending on age and sex, with state implementation details to verify. Use neutral language and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não afirme que uma pessoa específica é ou não obrigada a se registrar. Apresente como uma exigência federal que \"pode se aplicar\" dependendo da idade e do sexo, com detalhes de implementação estadual a conferir. Use linguagem neutra e siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Do not state whether the user is eligible for licensure. Only identify requirements to verify.": "Não afirme se o usuário tem elegibilidade ao licenciamento. Apenas identifique exigências a conferir.",
        "Do not state which states do or do not issue licenses to a given group, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV.": "Não afirme quais estados emitem ou deixam de emitir carteiras para um determinado grupo, e não liste documentos específicos aceitos. Apresente tudo como itens a conferir com o DMV do estado de destino.",
        "Do not state which states issue or do not issue licenses to a given visa category, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Não afirme quais estados emitem ou deixam de emitir carteiras para uma determinada categoria de visto, e não liste documentos específicos aceitos. Apresente tudo como itens a conferir com o DMV do estado de destino. Siga a lista de evitar do SafeCopy.",
        "Document lists accepted by state DMVs for non-citizen license or state-ID applicants can differ from those accepted for U.S. citizens, and accepted combinations may vary by jurisdiction.": "As listas de documentos aceitas pelos DMVs estaduais para candidatos não cidadãos a carteira ou state ID podem ser diferentes das aceitas para cidadãos dos EUA, e as combinações aceitas podem variar por jurisdição.",
        "Done": "Concluído",
        "Driver's license": "Carteira de motorista",
        "Driving across one or more state lines for travel.": "Cruzar de carro a divisa de um ou mais estados em viagem.",
        "Driving with coverage that does not meet destination-state minimums can create compliance and financial problems.": "Dirigir com cobertura que não atende aos mínimos do estado de destino pode criar problemas de conformidade e financeiros.",
        "Drug screen requirements": "Exigências de teste de drogas",
        "Edit selections": "Editar seleções",
        "Emissions testing requirement": "Exigência de teste de emissões",
        "Employer policy": "Política do empregador",
        "Employment paperwork": "Documentação de emprego",
        "Endorsement requirements if already licensed": "Exigências de endosso para quem já é licenciado",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary permits, and continuing education requirements vary by state and profession.": "Endosso, reciprocidade, autorizações temporárias e exigências de educação continuada variam por estado e profissão.",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary practice, and continuing education.": "Endosso, reciprocidade, prática temporária e educação continuada.",
        "Establishing a new permanent residence in the destination state.": "Estabelecer uma nova residência permanente no estado de destino.",
        "Eviction and late-fee rules": "Regras de despejo e de multa por atraso",
        "Example checklist categories": "Categorias de exemplo do checklist",
        "Exploring options. Receive a broad overview checklist.": "Explorando opções. Receba um checklist com visão geral ampla.",
        "F-1 OPT and STEM OPT specific. Use verify with the DSO and SEVP Portal guidance. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Do not advise on a specific status outcome.": "Específico de F-1 OPT e STEM OPT. Use \"confira com o DSO e a orientação do SEVP Portal\". Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS (frases de conclusão jurídica e frases sobre escapar de sanções). Não dê parecer sobre um desfecho específico de situação migratória.",
        "F-1 specific. Frame as verify with both DSOs and reference Study in the States or ICE materials. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Específico de F-1. Apresente como conferir com os dois DSOs e remeta aos materiais do Study in the States ou do ICE. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "F-1 students on post-completion OPT or a STEM OPT extension generally use the SEVP Portal or work with their DSO to update physical and mailing address, employer information, and other personal data, typically within 10 days of a change. Unemployment-day limits during OPT continue to apply during and after a move.": "Estudantes F-1 em post-completion OPT ou em extensão STEM OPT em geral usam o SEVP Portal ou trabalham com o DSO para atualizar endereço físico e postal, informações do empregador e outros dados pessoais, normalmente em até 10 dias da alteração. Os limites de dias de desemprego durante o OPT continuam valendo durante e depois da mudança.",
        "F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q specific. Frame as items to verify with IRS guidance and the employer. Do not state that a particular worker is exempt from FICA. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Específico de F-1, J-1, M-1 e Q. Apresente como itens a conferir com a orientação do IRS e com o empregador. Não afirme que um trabalhador específico está isento do FICA. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "Factors that may affect residency for tuition, taxes, licensing, benefits.": "Fatores que podem afetar a residência para mensalidade, impostos, licenciamento e benefícios.",
        "Failing to register on time may affect eligibility for federal benefits, federal jobs, and naturalization later, even though the requirement is federal. State DMV workflows can also trigger automatic registration, which applicants should understand before applying.": "Deixar de se registrar no prazo pode afetar a elegibilidade a benefícios federais, empregos federais e à naturalização depois, ainda que a exigência seja federal. Os fluxos do DMV estadual também podem acionar registro automático, e os candidatos devem entender isso antes de se candidatar.",
        "Family move": "Mudança em família",
        "Federal HealthCare.gov guidance describes a list of immigration statuses considered lawfully present for purposes of the Affordable Care Act marketplace, which includes many common nonimmigrant categories. These categories can purchase coverage without a five-year waiting period that applies in many Medicaid contexts.": "A orientação federal do HealthCare.gov descreve uma lista de situações migratórias consideradas lawfully present para fins do marketplace da Affordable Care Act, que inclui muitas categorias comuns de não imigrante. Essas categorias podem contratar cobertura sem o período de espera de cinco anos que se aplica em muitos contextos de Medicaid.",
        "Federal Medicaid and CHIP rules generally include a five-year waiting period for many qualified non-citizens after obtaining qualified status, with several federal exceptions. States may use an option that removes the waiting period for children and pregnant people, and some states cover certain groups with state funds.": "As regras federais do Medicaid e do CHIP geralmente incluem um período de espera de cinco anos para muitos não cidadãos qualificados depois de obter a situação qualificada, com várias exceções federais. Os estados podem usar uma opção que retira o período de espera para crianças e pessoas grávidas, e alguns estados cobrem certos grupos com recursos estaduais.",
        "Federal Medicare guidance generally describes eligibility for non-citizens who are lawfully admitted for permanent residence and have lived in the United States for five continuous years. Federal Medicaid rules for most nonimmigrants are narrower than for LPRs, with state-specific options for emergency Medicaid and for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "A orientação federal do Medicare em geral descreve a elegibilidade para não cidadãos que tenham sido admitidos legalmente para residência permanente e tenham vivido nos Estados Unidos por cinco anos contínuos. As regras federais de Medicaid para a maioria dos não imigrantes são mais restritas que para LPRs, com opções específicas dos estados para emergency Medicaid e para lawfully residing children e gestantes.",
        "Federal REAL ID rules require evidence of lawful status, and many states issue a REAL ID to nonimmigrant visa holders only with an expiration date that does not extend past the I-94, the visa, or another underlying federal document. Implementation differs between states, and standard (non-REAL-ID) options may or may not be offered.": "As regras federais do REAL ID exigem comprovação de situação em conformidade com a lei, e muitos estados só emitem um REAL ID a portadores de visto de não imigrante com uma data de vencimento que não vai além do I-94, do visto ou de outro documento federal subjacente. A implementação difere entre estados, e opções padrão (não REAL ID) podem ou não ser oferecidas.",
        "Federal SNAP, TANF, and similar programs apply a waiting period to many qualified non-citizens. Some states use state funds to operate replacement or supplemental programs that cover groups not eligible for the federal program, with differing rules.": "Os programas federais SNAP, TANF e similares aplicam um período de espera a muitos não cidadãos qualificados. Alguns estados usam recursos estaduais para operar programas substitutos ou suplementares que cobrem grupos não elegíveis ao programa federal, com regras diferentes.",
        "Federal law": "Lei federal",
        "Federal law (INA section 265) generally directs non-citizens to report a change of address to USCIS within 10 days of moving, typically through Form AR-11 or the USCIS online change-of-address tool. The federal filing is separate from updating a state DMV record, an employer, a school, or the U.S. Postal Service.": "A lei federal (INA seção 265) em geral orienta não cidadãos a reportar uma mudança de endereço ao USCIS em até 10 dias após a mudança, normalmente pelo Formulário AR-11 ou pela ferramenta on-line de mudança de endereço do USCIS. O registro federal é separado da atualização do cadastro no DMV estadual, no empregador, na escola ou no U.S. Postal Service.",
        "Federal law generally requires motor vehicle offices to offer voter registration to applicants, and forms are screened for citizenship attestations. Non-citizens generally are not eligible to register for federal elections, and a registration record can later create immigration complications.": "A lei federal geralmente exige que os escritórios de veículos motorizados ofereçam registro eleitoral aos candidatos, e os formulários são triados quanto às declarações de cidadania. Não cidadãos em geral não têm elegibilidade para se registrar em eleições federais, e um registro pode criar complicações migratórias depois.",
        "Federal residency for tax purposes determines whether worldwide income is reported, which IRS forms apply, and how an interstate move's first and last year are filed at the federal level, separately from state residency rules.": "A residência federal para fins fiscais determina se a renda mundial é declarada, quais formulários do IRS se aplicam e como o primeiro e o último ano de uma mudança entre estados são declarados no nível federal, em separado das regras estaduais de residência.",
        "Federal rules govern which immigration statuses can purchase coverage and receive financial help through the Affordable Care Act marketplace, and those rules have changed. State-based marketplaces and state-funded programs add another layer that can differ between origin and destination.": "As regras federais regem quais situações migratórias podem contratar cobertura e receber ajuda financeira pelo marketplace da Affordable Care Act, e essas regras mudaram. Os marketplaces estaduais e os programas financiados pelo estado adicionam outra camada que pode diferir entre origem e destino.",
        "Federal tax authority": "Autoridade fiscal federal",
        "Federal tax authority general guidance": "Orientação geral da autoridade fiscal federal",
        "Flags risk levels so you know where to focus": "Sinaliza níveis de risco para você saber onde focar",
        "Florida Board of Governors page on residency for tuition purposes for the State University System. flbog.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Página do Florida Board of Governors sobre residência para fins de mensalidade no State University System. O flbog.edu retorna 403 a requisições que não vêm de navegador (Cloudflare); este é um falso negativo conhecido.",
        "Florida FLHSMV documentation page for nonimmigrant applicants for driver licenses and identification cards.": "Página de documentação do Florida FLHSMV para candidatos com situação de não imigrante a carteiras de motorista e cartões de identificação.",
        "Follow device language": "Seguir o idioma do dispositivo",
        "For L-1, whether the new worksite is the same qualifying U.S. office described in the petition or a different one": "Para L-1, se o novo worksite é o mesmo escritório qualificador nos EUA descrito na petição ou um diferente",
        "For L-1A, L-1B, and O-1 status, USCIS treats a move to a new worksite as a material change in some fact patterns and not others, depending on what the original petition described and whether the new location is consistent with the approved terms. The analysis follows the underlying petition, not LCA-based MSA rules.": "Para as situações L-1A, L-1B e O-1, o USCIS trata uma mudança para um novo worksite como mudança material em alguns cenários de fatos e não em outros, dependendo do que a petição original descreveu e de o novo local ser compatível com os termos aprovados. A análise segue a petição subjacente, não as regras de MSA baseadas em LCA.",
        "For O-1, whether the new venue, event, engagement, or agent arrangement falls within the approved petition scope": "Para O-1, se o novo local, evento, engagement ou arranjo de agente cai dentro do escopo da petição aprovada",
        "For federal tax purposes, a non-citizen is generally treated as a resident alien if they meet the Substantial Presence Test or hold lawful permanent resident status, with separate rules in IRS Publication 519 for exempt individuals (such as certain F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q students and scholars) whose days of presence may not count.": "Para fins fiscais federais, um não cidadão em geral é tratado como resident alien se cumprir o Substantial Presence Test ou se tiver situação de lawful permanent resident, com regras à parte na IRS Publication 519 para exempt individuals (como certos estudantes e pesquisadores F-1, J-1, M-1 e Q) cujos dias de presença podem não contar.",
        "For nursing specifically, how the destination state treats primary state of residency under the Nurse Licensure Compact for a non-citizen who declares either the country of origin or the compact state, and any credentials-evaluation requirement (for example, CGFNS) for internationally educated applicants": "Para enfermagem em particular, como o estado de destino trata o primary state of residency sob o Nurse Licensure Compact para um não cidadão que declare seja o país de origem seja o estado do compact, e qualquer exigência de avaliação de credenciais (por exemplo, CGFNS) para candidatos com formação no exterior",
        "Form AR-11 paper version posted on uscis.gov.": "Versão em papel do Formulário AR-11 publicada em uscis.gov.",
        "Frame AR-11 as a federal reporting step to verify, not a guarantee of status. Do not state that any specific status category is or is not covered without source. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing such as the i-word, the p-words, and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney for status-specific guidance.": "Apresente o AR-11 como uma etapa federal de notificação a conferir, não como garantia de situação migratória. Não afirme que uma categoria específica de situação migratória está ou não coberta sem fonte. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS (frases de conclusão jurídica e frases sobre escapar de sanções). Direcione os leitores a consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado para orientação específica à sua situação.",
        "Frame as a federal requirement that may apply, with a nonimmigrant exception that may apply based on continuous valid status. Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Apresente como uma exigência federal que pode se aplicar, com uma exceção para não imigrante que pode se aplicar com base em situação migratória válida e contínua. Não afirme que alguma pessoa específica é ou não obrigada a se registrar. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "Frame as items to verify in IRS Publication 519 and with a qualified tax preparer. Do not state a person is a dual-status filer for a particular year. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Apresente como itens a conferir na IRS Publication 519 e com um preparador de impostos qualificado. Não afirme que uma pessoa é declarante em dual status para um ano específico. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "Frame as items to verify with CMS and the destination-state Medicaid agency. Federal rules have changed and may continue to change. Do not state a person is or is not eligible. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Apresente como itens a conferir com o CMS e com o órgão estadual de Medicaid do destino. As regras federais mudaram e podem continuar mudando. Não afirme que uma pessoa é ou não elegível. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "Frame as items to verify with IRS Publication 519 and a tax preparer. Do not state a person is or is not a resident alien for federal tax purposes. Use may apply and rules differ by jurisdiction. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Apresente como itens a conferir com a IRS Publication 519 e com um preparador de impostos. Não afirme que uma pessoa é ou não resident alien para fins fiscais federais. Use \"pode se aplicar\" e \"as regras diferem por jurisdição\". Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "Frame as items to verify with the DSO or J-1 sponsor and Study in the States or ICE guidance. This item is specific to F-1, M-1, and J-1 status. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "Apresente como itens a conferir com o DSO ou o sponsor J-1 e com a orientação do Study in the States ou do ICE. Este item é específico das situações F-1, M-1 e J-1. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS (frases de conclusão jurídica e frases sobre escapar de sanções).",
        "Frame as items to verify with the current HealthCare.gov or state-based marketplace lists. Do not state any specific category is or is not on the lawfully present list, since federal rules have changed. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Apresente como itens a conferir com as listas atuais do HealthCare.gov ou dos marketplaces estaduais. Não afirme que alguma categoria específica está ou não na lista de lawfully present, já que as regras federais mudaram. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "Full disclaimer:": "Aviso legal completo:",
        "General information only. Not legal advice. Verify with official sources.": "Apenas informação geral. Não é aconselhamento jurídico. Confira em fontes oficiais.",
        "General information only. Verify with the relevant official source. Not legal advice.": "Apenas informação geral. Confira na fonte oficial pertinente. Não é aconselhamento jurídico.",
        "Generate checklist": "Gerar checklist",
        "Generated:": "Gerado em:",
        "Generates a checklist of topics to verify before moving": "Gera um checklist de tópicos a conferir antes da mudança",
        "Georgia Department of Driver Services page for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including a 30-day rule for establishing Georgia residency.": "Página do Georgia Department of Driver Services para candidatos não cidadãos dos EUA, incluindo uma regra de 30 dias para estabelecer residência na Georgia.",
        "Get a grouped checklist with risk badges and links to official sources.": "Obtenha um checklist agrupado com selos de risco e links para fontes oficiais.",
        "H-1B specific. Frame as verify with employer counsel and USCIS or DOL guidance. Do not state that an amendment is or is not required in a particular fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Específico de H-1B. Apresente como conferir com a equipe jurídica do empregador e com a orientação do USCIS ou do DOL. Não afirme que uma emenda é ou não exigida em um cenário específico de fatos. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "H-1B specific. Use verify whether MSA boundaries cover the new worksite. Do not assert that no amendment is needed in any specific fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Específico de H-1B. Use \"confira se os limites da MSA cobrem o novo worksite\". Não afirme que nenhuma emenda é necessária em algum cenário específico de fatos. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "HOW IT WORKS": "COMO FUNCIONA",
        "Health clearance documentation": "Documentação de liberação de saúde",
        "HealthCare.gov general page on immigrant coverage options.": "Página geral do HealthCare.gov sobre opções de cobertura para imigrantes.",
        "HealthCare.gov list and explanation of lawfully present categories for ACA marketplace coverage.": "Lista e explicação do HealthCare.gov sobre as categorias lawfully present para a cobertura do marketplace da ACA.",
        "HealthCare.gov page on which statuses qualify for marketplace coverage.": "Página do HealthCare.gov sobre quais situações migratórias qualificam para a cobertura do marketplace.",
        "Healthcare access / insurance": "Acesso à saúde / seguro",
        "Help avoid enforcement or recommend workarounds": "Ajudar a contornar a fiscalização ou recomendar manobras",
        "Helps tailor the checklist. None of these flags create legal conclusions.": "Ajuda a personalizar o checklist. Nenhuma dessas marcações gera conclusões jurídicas.",
        "High risk only": "Apenas alto risco",
        "High-risk categories require separate verification.": "Categorias de alto risco exigem conferência separada.",
        "High-risk categories require separate verification. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use of regulated items is lawful.": "Categorias de alto risco exigem conferência separada. O MoveSafe não determina se a posse, o transporte ou o uso de itens regulamentados está em conformidade com a lei.",
        "High-risk items to verify separately": "Itens de alto risco a conferir separadamente",
        "High-risk only": "Apenas alto risco",
        "High-risk warning. High-risk categories require separate verification.": "Aviso de alto risco. Categorias de alto risco exigem conferência separada.",
        "Highlights stale or placeholder sources": "Destaca fontes desatualizadas ou provisórias",
        "Housing / renter basics": "Moradia / noções para locatários",
        "How CHIP coverage rules in the destination state interact with the waiting period for your household": "Como as regras de cobertura do CHIP no estado de destino interagem com o período de espera para o seu domicílio",
        "How OPT or STEM OPT employment is treated for FICA while the worker remains a nonresident alien": "Como o emprego em OPT ou STEM OPT é tratado para o FICA enquanto o trabalhador continua como nonresident alien",
        "How a future change to LPR status before age 26 may affect the registration question": "Como uma futura mudança para a situação de LPR antes dos 26 anos pode afetar a questão do registro",
        "How a mid-year move between states may affect aid-application deadlines": "Como uma mudança entre estados no meio do ano pode afetar os prazos de pedido de auxílio",
        "How a move mid-coverage may affect the reasonable opportunity period for documentation": "Como uma mudança durante o período de cobertura pode afetar o reasonable opportunity period para documentação",
        "How a transfer interacts with current employment authorization, on-campus work, and any pending OPT": "Como uma transferência interage com a autorização de trabalho atual, com o trabalho on-campus e com qualquer OPT pendente",
        "How a year of arrival to or departure from the United States interacts with the test": "Como um ano de chegada aos Estados Unidos ou de saída deles interage com o teste",
        "How an in-progress extension of status (for example, an H-1B amendment or an F-1 transfer) interacts with renewing or replacing the credential": "Como uma extensão de situação migratória em andamento (por exemplo, uma emenda de H-1B ou uma transferência de F-1) interage com a renovação ou substituição da credencial",
        "How clinical-placement and background-check requirements interact with your immigration status": "Como as exigências de estágio clínico e de verificação de antecedentes interagem com a sua situação migratória",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification": "Por quanto tempo você precisa ter residência no estado de destino antes de ser considerado para a classificação in-state",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification, and whether time on a nonimmigrant visa counts": "Por quanto tempo você precisa ter residência no estado de destino antes de ser considerado para a classificação in-state, e se o tempo com visto de não imigrante conta",
        "How temporary stay is treated differently from permanent relocation": "Como a estadia temporária é tratada de forma diferente da mudança permanente",
        "How the destination state defines residency": "Como o estado de destino define residência",
        "How the destination state's DMV or other application workflows interact with Selective Service screening": "Como o DMV do estado de destino ou outros fluxos de pedidos interagem com a triagem do Selective Service",
        "How the move affects any STEM OPT Form I-983 training plan and the destination employer's E-Verify status": "Como a mudança afeta qualquer plano de treinamento STEM OPT no Formulário I-983 e a situação do E-Verify do empregador no destino",
        "How the move and any change in employer-sponsored coverage interact with marketplace special enrollment timing": "Como a mudança e qualquer alteração na cobertura patrocinada pelo empregador interagem com o cronograma do special enrollment do marketplace",
        "How the move interacts with H-4 dependent status and any pending I-485 or I-140": "Como a mudança interage com a situação de dependente H-4 e com qualquer I-485 ou I-140 pendente",
        "How to confirm a registration after applying for a license": "Como confirmar um registro após solicitar a carteira",
        "How to correct the record if a non-citizen registration was submitted in error": "Como corrigir o registro se um registro de não cidadão foi enviado por engano",
        "How to decline voter registration when offered at the DMV in that state": "Como recusar o registro eleitoral quando oferecido no DMV daquele estado",
        "How to obtain or replace a Selective Service registration record if needed for future immigration or federal-benefit filings": "Como obter ou substituir um registro do Selective Service se for necessário para futuros pedidos junto à imigração ou a benefícios federais",
        "How unemployment days are counted during a gap between employers around a move": "Como os dias de desemprego são contados em um intervalo entre empregadores em torno de uma mudança",
        "I am a nursing or healthcare student": "Sou estudante de enfermagem ou da área da saúde",
        "I am moving for school": "Estou me mudando para estudar",
        "I am moving for work": "Estou me mudando para trabalhar",
        "I have a car": "Tenho carro",
        "I hold or need a professional license": "Tenho ou preciso de uma licença profissional",
        "I may stay temporarily": "Posso ficar temporariamente",
        "I may work in the destination state": "Posso trabalhar no estado de destino",
        "I own a pet": "Tenho animal de estimação",
        "I plan to relocate permanently": "Pretendo me mudar de forma permanente",
        "I rent housing": "Alugo moradia",
        "I understand": "Eu entendo",
        "I understand that MoveSafe provides general information and source links, not legal advice.": "Entendo que o MoveSafe fornece informações gerais e links de fontes, não aconselhamento jurídico.",
        "I'm a Dreamer (DACA / similar)": "Sou Dreamer (DACA / situação similar)",
        "I'm a green card holder (LPR)": "Sou portador de green card (LPR)",
        "I'm on a nonimmigrant visa (F-1, H-1B, J-1, etc.)": "Estou com visto de não imigrante (F-1, H-1B, J-1 etc.)",
        "ICE SEVIS landing page.": "Página inicial do SEVIS no ICE.",
        "ICE SEVIS overview page for background context on F, M, and J record management.": "Página de visão geral do SEVIS no ICE, com contexto de fundo sobre a gestão de registros F, M e J.",
        "ICE Student and Exchange Visitor Program (SEVIS) Landing Page": "Página inicial do Student and Exchange Visitor Program (SEVIS) do ICE",
        "ICE page describing F-1 SEVIS transfers.": "Página do ICE descrevendo as transferências de SEVIS para F-1.",
        "IRS Publication 519 describes a dual-status tax year for non-citizens who are both a nonresident and a resident for federal tax purposes during the same year, which can apply to many arrival, departure, and adjustment-of-status fact patterns rather than interstate moves alone.": "A IRS Publication 519 descreve um ano fiscal de dual status para não cidadãos que são, no mesmo ano, tanto nonresident quanto resident para fins fiscais federais, o que pode se aplicar a muitos cenários de chegada, saída e ajuste de situação migratória, e não apenas a mudanças entre estados.",
        "IRS Publication 519 main page.": "Página principal da IRS Publication 519.",
        "IRS dual-status filer page. Final redirected URL uses the dual-status-individuals slug.": "Página do IRS para declarantes em dual status. A URL final redirecionada usa o slug dual-status-individuals.",
        "IRS general page on taxation of nonresident aliens.": "Página geral do IRS sobre a tributação de nonresident aliens.",
        "IRS guidance generally describes an exemption from FICA tax for wages paid for services performed by F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q nonresident-alien students, scholars, teachers, researchers, and trainees, when the work is part of the activity for which they were admitted and they remain nonresident aliens for federal tax purposes.": "A orientação do IRS em geral descreve uma isenção do imposto FICA para salários pagos por serviços prestados por estudantes, pesquisadores, professores e trainees nonresident aliens F-1, J-1, M-1 e Q, quando o trabalho faz parte da atividade para a qual foram admitidos e enquanto permanecerem nonresident aliens para fins fiscais federais.",
        "IRS overview page for non-citizen tax residency status.": "Página de visão geral do IRS sobre a situação fiscal de residência para não cidadãos.",
        "IRS page describing the Substantial Presence Test for federal tax residency.": "Página do IRS descrevendo o Substantial Presence Test para a residência fiscal federal.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for F, J, M, Q nonresident-alien students and scholars.": "Página do IRS sobre o tratamento do imposto FICA para estudantes e pesquisadores nonresident aliens F, J, M, Q.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for non-citizens employed in the U.S.": "Página do IRS sobre o tratamento do imposto FICA para não cidadãos empregados nos EUA.",
        "Identity and residency documents accepted by the destination state": "Documentos de identidade e residência aceitos pelo estado de destino",
        "If a credential is issued with an unexpected short term tied to a federal document, the timing of renewal can affect domestic flights, federal building access, and other tasks that may rely on a REAL ID after a move.": "Se uma credencial for emitida com um prazo curto inesperado, vinculado a um documento federal, o cronograma de renovação pode afetar voos domésticos, acesso a prédios federais e outras tarefas que podem depender de um REAL ID após a mudança.",
        "Illinois Board of Higher Education directory page on campus liaisons supporting students under state tuition-equity provisions.": "Página de diretório do Illinois Board of Higher Education sobre liaisons nos campi que apoiam estudantes sob as disposições estaduais de equidade de mensalidade.",
        "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL) page. ilsos.gov returns a 302 redirect to its own page for curl HEAD requests, which is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov domain; the URL was confirmed via the Secretary of State's own search index.": "Página do Illinois Secretary of State sobre Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL). O ilsos.gov retorna um redirecionamento 302 para a própria página em requisições HEAD do curl, o que é um falso negativo conhecido no domínio .gov de longa data; a URL foi confirmada pelo índice de busca do próprio Secretary of State.",
        "Illinois Student Assistance Commission resources page for non-U.S. citizen students including RISE Act and Alternative Application context. isac.org returns 403 to non-browser requests (anti-bot); this is a known false negative.": "Página de recursos da Illinois Student Assistance Commission para estudantes não cidadãos dos EUA, incluindo contexto do RISE Act e da Alternative Application. O isac.org retorna 403 a requisições que não vêm de navegador (antibot); este é um falso negativo conhecido.",
        "Immigration status - including Dreamer / DACA status - can significantly affect driver's licenses and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing and healthcare), in-state tuition, SSN-related requirements, and state tax filing. Rules vary by state and federal law and change frequently.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney before relying on any state-by-state summary.": "A situação migratória, incluindo a condição de Dreamer / DACA, pode afetar significativamente a carteira de motorista e o REAL ID, o licenciamento profissional (especialmente em enfermagem e saúde), a mensalidade in-state, exigências ligadas ao SSN e a declaração de impostos estaduais. As regras variam conforme o estado e a legislação federal, e mudam com frequência.\n\nO MoveSafe não substitui orientação jurídica. Considere consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de confiar em qualquer resumo estado por estado.",
        "Immunization requirements": "Exigências de imunização",
        "Important to verify": "Importante conferir",
        "Inspection requirement": "Exigência de inspeção",
        "Insurance networks, Medicaid and marketplace rules, and prescription transfer processes vary by state.": "Redes de seguro, regras de Medicaid e de marketplace e processos de transferência de prescrições variam por estado.",
        "Insurance networks, student health, prescriptions, primary care access.": "Redes de seguro, saúde estudantil, prescrições e acesso à atenção primária.",
        "J-1 specific. Frame as verify with the program sponsor and reference 22 CFR Part 62. Do not state that any specific category does or does not require sponsor pre-approval for a particular change. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Específico de J-1. Apresente como conferir com o sponsor do programa e remeta ao 22 CFR Part 62. Não afirme que alguma categoria específica exige ou deixa de exigir aprovação prévia do sponsor para uma determinada mudança. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "Jurisdiction: %@": "Jurisdição: %@",
        "Know how to respond if asked to register to vote at the DMV": "Saiba como responder se for questionado sobre se registrar para votar no DMV",
        "L-1 and O-1 specific. Frame as verify against the approved petition and consult petitioner counsel. Do not state that an amendment is or is not needed for any specific scenario. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Específico de L-1 e O-1. Apresente como conferir em relação à petição aprovada e consultar a equipe jurídica do peticionário. Não afirme que uma emenda é ou não necessária em algum cenário específico. Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS.",
        "Language": "Idioma",
        "Last verified:": "Última conferência:",
        "Last verified: %@": "Última conferência: %@",
        "Lawful permanent residents (LPRs / green card holders) can face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing - foreign credentials evaluation may apply), Medicaid and state-marketplace eligibility (the federal 5-year bar interacts with state programs), state tax filing, and how DMVs handle voter-registration prompts (LPRs are not eligible to vote in federal or most state elections).\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney for status-affecting questions and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Residentes permanentes legais (LPRs / portadores de green card) podem enfrentar variações estado a estado em documentos para carteira de motorista e REAL ID, licenciamento profissional (especialmente em enfermagem - pode ser exigida avaliação de credenciais estrangeiras), elegibilidade ao Medicaid e ao marketplace estadual (a barreira federal de 5 anos interage com programas estaduais), declaração de impostos estaduais e como os DMVs lidam com solicitações de registro eleitoral (LPRs não têm elegibilidade para votar em eleições federais nem na maioria das estaduais).\n\nO MoveSafe não substitui orientação jurídica. Considere consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado para questões que afetem a situação migratória e um profissional tributário qualificado para declarações entre estados.",
        "Lease decisions made based on origin-state assumptions may not match destination-state rules.": "Decisões sobre contrato tomadas com base em suposições do estado de origem podem não corresponder às regras do estado de destino.",
        "Lease terms, security deposits, notice periods, and tenant protections.": "Termos do contrato, depósitos de garantia, prazos de aviso e proteções ao inquilino.",
        "Legal aid (general info)": "Assistência jurídica (informação geral)",
        "License transfer, deadlines, documents, and REAL ID awareness.": "Transferência de carteira, prazos, documentos e atenção ao REAL ID.",
        "Licensure requirements can affect clinical placement, NCLEX eligibility, endorsement, and employment timing.": "Exigências de licenciamento podem afetar o estágio clínico, a elegibilidade ao NCLEX, o endosso e o tempo até o emprego.",
        "Links to official state agency sources": "Direciona a fontes oficiais de órgãos estaduais",
        "Load example": "Carregar exemplo",
        "Local city/county rules may add protections. Review lease language directly.": "Regras de cidade/condado locais podem adicionar proteções. Revise diretamente o texto do contrato.",
        "Local ordinance": "Ordenança local",
        "Local pet licensing requirements": "Exigências de licenciamento local de animais",
        "Main USCIS page for H-1B specialty occupations classification.": "Página principal do USCIS para a classificação H-1B specialty occupations.",
        "Many nonimmigrant visa holders are not within the standard Medicare or Medicaid eligibility groups, and federal rules in this area have been changing. Destination-state Medicaid rules add another layer that may differ from origin-state rules.": "Muitos portadores de visto de não imigrante não estão dentro dos grupos padrão de elegibilidade ao Medicare ou ao Medicaid, e as regras federais nessa área têm mudado. As regras do Medicaid do estado de destino acrescentam outra camada que pode diferir das regras do estado de origem.",
        "Many states require new residents to obtain a state driver's license within a specific period after becoming a resident.": "Muitos estados exigem que novos residentes obtenham uma carteira de motorista estadual dentro de um período específico após se tornarem residentes.",
        "Mark as not verified": "Marcar como não conferido",
        "Mark as verified": "Marcar como conferido",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for nonresidents using Form 1-NR/PY. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Guia do Massachusetts Department of Revenue sobre imposto de renda pessoa física para nonresidents usando o Formulário 1-NR/PY. O mass.gov retorna 403 a requisições que não vêm de navegador (Cloudflare); este é um falso negativo conhecido.",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for part-year residents. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Guia do Massachusetts Department of Revenue sobre imposto de renda pessoa física para part-year residents. O mass.gov retorna 403 a requisições que não vêm de navegador (Cloudflare); este é um falso negativo conhecido.",
        "Massachusetts RMV identification requirements page covering REAL ID, standard licenses, and lawful presence documentation. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov-hosted state portal.": "Página de exigências de identificação do Massachusetts RMV cobrindo REAL ID, carteiras padrão e documentação de lawful presence. O mass.gov retorna 403 a requisições que não vêm de navegador (Cloudflare); este é um falso negativo conhecido no portal estadual hospedado em .gov de longa data.",
        "May involve penalties or licensing consequences.": "Pode envolver sanções ou consequências para o licenciamento.",
        "Minimum coverage, state-specific rules, and policy address updates.": "Cobertura mínima, regras específicas do estado e atualizações de endereço na apólice.",
        "Missing a school or hospital onboarding requirement can delay clinical hours and graduation timing.": "Deixar de cumprir uma exigência de integração na escola ou no hospital pode atrasar as horas clínicas e a formatura.",
        "Missing a state motor vehicle deadline can create administrative or driving-related problems after relocation.": "Perder um prazo do órgão estadual de veículos motorizados pode criar problemas administrativos ou relacionados à direção após a mudança.",
        "Missing source": "Fonte ausente",
        "Missing the transfer reporting steps at the new school, or letting the transfer release date and program start fall out of sync, can affect status maintenance and access to on-campus work.": "Perder as etapas de comparecimento de transferência na nova escola, ou deixar a data de transfer release e o início do programa fora de sintonia, pode afetar a manutenção da situação migratória e o acesso a trabalho on-campus.",
        "Mixed jurisdiction": "Jurisdição mista",
        "MoveSafe checklist": "Checklist do MoveSafe",
        "MoveSafe is a source-first checklist tool. It links you to official resources and highlights topics to verify. It does not provide legal advice.": "O MoveSafe é uma ferramenta de checklist focada em fontes oficiais. Ele direciona você a recursos oficiais e destaca tópicos a conferir. Não oferece aconselhamento jurídico.",
        "MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves. You can still build a checklist, but some items may not apply.": "O MoveSafe foi feito para mudanças entre estados. Você ainda pode montar um checklist, mas alguns itens podem não se aplicar.",
        "MoveSafe prefers official agency sources. Placeholder entries should be replaced with verified URLs before production use.": "O MoveSafe prioriza fontes oficiais de órgãos. Entradas provisórias devem ser substituídas por URLs verificadas antes do uso em produção.",
        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "O MoveSafe fornece informações jurídicas e administrativas gerais com base em fontes publicamente disponíveis. Ele não oferece aconselhamento jurídico, não cria relação advogado-cliente e não deve ser usado em substituição à orientação de um advogado licenciado na sua jurisdição. As leis e as regras dos órgãos mudam com frequência. Sempre confira as informações em fontes oficiais antes de tomar decisões.",
        "Moving across state lines? Know what to verify before you go.": "Vai se mudar para outro estado? Saiba o que conferir antes de ir.",
        "Moving for school": "Mudar para estudar",
        "Moving for work": "Mudar para trabalhar",
        "Moving from %1$@ to %2$@": "Mudança de %1$@ para %2$@",
        "Moving from one state's aid program to another's may change which aid applications to consider and which documents to gather, and this can affect how to plan tuition and living costs at the destination.": "Mudar de um programa estadual de auxílio para outro pode alterar quais pedidos de auxílio considerar e quais documentos reunir, e isso pode afetar como planejar mensalidade e custo de vida no destino.",
        "Moving may change which state tax withholding forms apply, and remote work can create cross-state payroll questions.": "A mudança pode alterar quais formulários de retenção de imposto estadual se aplicam, e o trabalho remoto pode gerar questões de folha de pagamento entre estados.",
        "Moving to another state for clinical rotations, externships, or supervised practice.": "Mudança para outro estado para rotações clínicas, externships ou prática supervisionada.",
        "NCLEX and license-by-endorsement steps can stall when documentation does not match a destination board's current rules, which can delay clinical placement, hire dates, and compact-state recognition.": "As etapas do NCLEX e do licenciamento por endosso podem travar quando a documentação não corresponde às regras atuais do conselho do estado de destino, o que pode atrasar o estágio clínico, as datas de contratação e o reconhecimento via compact.",
        "NCLEX eligibility requirements": "Exigências de elegibilidade ao NCLEX",
        "NCSBN Licensure Compacts overview, including Nurse Licensure Compact context for non-citizen primary state of residency declarations.": "Visão geral do NCSBN sobre licensure compacts, incluindo o contexto do Nurse Licensure Compact para declarações de primary state of residency por não cidadão.",
        "National Council of State Boards of Nursing licensure guidance page for background context across boards.": "Página de orientação sobre licenciamento do National Council of State Boards of Nursing, com contexto de fundo entre os conselhos.",
        "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education page summarizing the Tuition Equality Act and the 2020 statute affecting dependent students of H-1B holders.": "Página do New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education resumindo o Tuition Equality Act e a lei de 2020 que afeta estudantes dependentes de portadores de H-1B.",
        "New York DMV REAL ID page noting that an Enhanced ID is for U.S. citizens only and that REAL ID issued to applicants with temporary lawful status may expire with the federal document.": "Página de REAL ID do New York DMV registrando que o Enhanced ID é apenas para cidadãos dos EUA e que o REAL ID emitido para candidatos com situação temporária em conformidade com a lei pode vencer com o documento federal.",
        "New York DMV documentation guidance for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including REAL ID and standard credentials.": "Orientação de documentação do New York DMV para candidatos não cidadãos dos EUA, incluindo REAL ID e credenciais padrão.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance FAQ on residency, nonresident filing, and telecommuting.": "Página de perguntas frequentes do New York Department of Taxation and Finance sobre residência, declaração nonresident e teletrabalho.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance page on nonresident and part-year filing using Form IT-203.": "Página do New York Department of Taxation and Finance sobre declaração nonresident e part-year usando o Formulário IT-203.",
        "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN licensure requirements page, which administers nursing licensure for New York.": "Página de exigências de licenciamento RN do Office of the Professions do New York State Education Department, que administra o licenciamento em enfermagem em New York.",
        "No items match your filters": "Nenhum item corresponde aos seus filtros",
        "No source has been added yet for this item. Add an official source before relying on it.": "Nenhuma fonte foi adicionada ainda para este item. Adicione uma fonte oficial antes de confiar nele.",
        "No sources are attached to the items in this view.": "Não há fontes anexadas aos itens nesta visualização.",
        "Nonimmigrant visa holders (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, and others) face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID (often tied to I-94 / visa dates), in-state tuition (most public universities classify F-1 students as out-of-state), professional licensure documentation, tax residency rules, and health-insurance options. USCIS also requires reporting any address change within 10 days via Form AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney, your school's DSO if on F-1, employer HR or immigration counsel if on a work visa, and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Portadores de visto de não imigrante (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1 e outros) enfrentam variações estado a estado em documentos para carteira de motorista e REAL ID (frequentemente vinculados ao I-94 / às datas do visto), em mensalidade in-state (a maior parte das universidades públicas classifica estudantes F-1 como out-of-state), em documentação para licenciamento profissional, em regras de residência fiscal e em opções de plano de saúde. O USCIS também exige reportar qualquer mudança de endereço em até 10 dias via Formulário AR-11.\n\nO MoveSafe não substitui orientação jurídica. Considere consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado, o DSO da sua escola se estiver com F-1, o RH do empregador ou o setor de imigração se estiver com visto de trabalho, e um profissional tributário qualificado para declarações entre estados.",
        "Not sure yet": "Ainda não tenho certeza",
        "Note for editors: %@": "Nota para editores: %@",
        "Notes:": "Notas:",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact general information": "Informações gerais do Nurse Licensure Compact",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact participation": "Participação no Nurse Licensure Compact",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact public FAQ page including the rule that a non-citizen applicant may declare either country of origin or the compact state as primary state of residency.": "Página pública de perguntas frequentes do Nurse Licensure Compact, incluindo a regra de que um candidato não cidadão pode declarar tanto o país de origem quanto o estado do compact como primary state of residency.",
        "Nursing / healthcare licensure": "Licenciamento em enfermagem / saúde",
        "Nursing education, licensure, endorsement, temporary permits, and compact license rules are handled by state boards of nursing and may differ by state.": "Educação, licenciamento, endosso, autorizações temporárias e regras de licenças por compacto em enfermagem são tratados pelos conselhos estaduais de enfermagem e podem diferir por estado.",
        "Nursing school / healthcare training": "Escola de enfermagem / formação em saúde",
        "OFFICIAL SOURCES": "FONTES OFICIAIS",
        "Official destination state attorney general - tenant resources": "Procuradoria-geral oficial do estado de destino - recursos para inquilinos",
        "Official destination state board of nursing": "Board of nursing oficial do estado de destino",
        "Official destination state department of agriculture - pet entry": "Departamento oficial de agricultura do estado de destino - entrada de animais",
        "Official destination state department of health": "Departamento oficial de saúde do estado de destino",
        "Official destination state department of labor": "Departamento oficial do trabalho do estado de destino",
        "Official destination state motor vehicle agency": "Órgão oficial de veículos motorizados do estado de destino",
        "Official destination state professional licensing portal": "Portal oficial de licenciamento profissional do estado de destino",
        "Official destination state tax agency": "Órgão fiscal oficial do estado de destino",
        "Official federal agency": "Órgão oficial federal",
        "Official local agency": "Órgão oficial local",
        "Official origin state motor vehicle agency": "Órgão oficial de veículos motorizados do estado de origem",
        "Official source needed before relying on this item.": "É necessária uma fonte oficial antes de confiar neste item.",
        "Official state agency": "Órgão oficial estadual",
        "Open official source": "Abrir fonte oficial",
        "Optional profile": "Perfil opcional",
        "Origin and destination are the same. MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves - some items may not apply.": "Origem e destino são iguais. O MoveSafe foi feito para mudanças entre estados - alguns itens podem não se aplicar.",
        "Origin state": "Estado de origem",
        "Origin state DMV / MVA": "DMV / MVA do estado de origem",
        "Origin:": "Origem:",
        "Parking permit and campus housing rules": "Regras de licença de estacionamento e moradia no campus",
        "Part-year residency, remote work, and school attendance may all affect state tax filing.": "Residência por parte do ano, trabalho remoto e frequência escolar podem todos afetar a declaração de imposto estadual.",
        "Permanent relocation": "Mudança permanente",
        "Pet rules may be set by state, local, or housing-provider policies. Each layer can have different requirements.": "As regras para animais podem ser definidas por políticas estaduais, locais ou do fornecedor de moradia. Cada camada pode ter exigências diferentes.",
        "Pets": "Animais de estimação",
        "Pick a purpose and the categories that apply.": "Selecione um objetivo e as categorias aplicáveis.",
        "Placeholder - replace with official source": "Provisório - substituir por fonte oficial",
        "Placeholder source": "Fonte provisória",
        "Placeholder source. Replace with an official source before relying on this item.": "Fonte provisória. Substitua por uma fonte oficial antes de confiar neste item.",
        "Plate requirements (front and/or rear)": "Exigências de placa (dianteira e/ou traseira)",
        "Please confirm the disclaimer to continue.": "Confirme o aviso legal para continuar.",
        "Please fix the following:": "Corrija o seguinte:",
        "Possibly outdated": "Possivelmente desatualizado",
        "Practical requirement": "Exigência prática",
        "Prescription medications, especially controlled substances, may be subject to state, federal, and pharmacy-level rules during interstate moves.": "Medicamentos com prescrição, especialmente substâncias controladas, podem estar sujeitos a regras estaduais, federais e em nível de farmácia durante mudanças entre estados.",
        "Primary USCIS landing page for Form AR-11.": "Página principal do USCIS sobre o Formulário AR-11.",
        "Primary care access after moving": "Acesso à atenção primária após a mudança",
        "Primary state of residence requirements": "Exigências de estado principal de residência",
        "Professional and occupational licensing boards (including nursing, medicine, law, engineering, and many others) set their own documentation rules. Whether a state board accepts an EAD, asks for an SSN, accepts an ITIN or affidavit, accepts an I-797 for an H-1B or O-1 worker, or requires fingerprint background checks tied to a specific status can differ across states and across professions within a state. Some boards specifically address F-1 OPT and J-1 academic-training applicants.": "Os conselhos de licenciamento profissional e ocupacional (incluindo enfermagem, medicina, advocacia, engenharia e muitos outros) estabelecem suas próprias regras de documentação. Se um conselho estadual aceita um EAD, pede um SSN, aceita um ITIN ou declaração juramentada, aceita um I-797 para um trabalhador H-1B ou O-1 ou exige verificações de antecedentes por digitais atreladas a uma situação migratória específica pode variar entre estados e entre profissões dentro de um mesmo estado. Alguns conselhos tratam especificamente de candidatos em F-1 OPT e em academic training de J-1.",
        "Professional and occupational licensing boards set their own documentation rules. Whether a state board accepts an Employment Authorization Document, asks for an SSN, accepts an ITIN, or requires an attestation about lawful presence can differ across states and across professions within a state.": "Os conselhos de licenciamento profissional e ocupacional estabelecem suas próprias regras de documentação. Se um conselho estadual aceita um Employment Authorization Document, pede um SSN, aceita um ITIN ou exige uma declaração sobre presença em conformidade com a lei pode variar entre estados e entre profissões dentro de um mesmo estado.",
        "Professional license transfer": "Transferência de licença profissional",
        "Professional licensing board": "Conselho de licenciamento profissional",
        "Provide legal advice or attorney-client services": "Fornecer aconselhamento jurídico ou serviços advogado-cliente",
        "Public college and university residency rules for tuition often treat nonimmigrant visa holders (such as F-1 and J-1 students) differently from U.S. citizens and lawful permanent residents. Some visa categories are considered able to establish a domicile in a state, while others generally are not, and some states have separate statutes or board regulations that apply to high school graduates from the state regardless of status. Rules vary across the state higher-education agency, a system office, and individual institutions.": "As regras de residência de faculdades e universidades públicas para mensalidade muitas vezes tratam portadores de visto de não imigrante (como estudantes F-1 e J-1) de modo diferente dos cidadãos dos EUA e dos LPRs. Algumas categorias de visto são consideradas aptas a estabelecer domicílio em um estado, enquanto outras em geral não são, e alguns estados têm leis ou regulamentos de conselho à parte que se aplicam a quem concluiu o ensino médio no estado, independentemente da situação migratória. As regras variam entre o órgão estadual de ensino superior, o escritório do sistema e cada instituição.",
        "Purpose": "Objetivo",
        "Purpose:": "Objetivo:",
        "Purpose: %@": "Objetivo: %@",
        "REAL ID and standard credentials use different document checklists and have different uses for federal purposes such as boarding domestic flights or entering certain federal buildings.": "O REAL ID e as credenciais padrão usam listas de documentos diferentes e têm usos diferentes para finalidades federais, como embarcar em voos domésticos ou entrar em determinados prédios federais.",
        "RISK": "RISCO",
        "Rabies and other vaccination documentation requirements": "Exigências de documentação para raiva e outras vacinações",
        "Receiving school registrar / residency office": "Registrar da escola receptora / escritório de residência",
        "Recently verified": "Conferido recentemente",
        "Registering or being recorded as registered, even by mistake, may create issues for naturalization, status renewal, or future immigration filings. The risk of an inadvertent record can depend on how a state's DMV workflow is designed.": "Se registrar ou aparecer como registrado, mesmo por engano, pode gerar problemas para naturalização, renovação de situação migratória ou pedidos futuros junto à imigração. O risco de um registro inadvertido pode depender de como o fluxo de trabalho do DMV de um estado está estruturado.",
        "Registration deadline after establishing residency": "Prazo de registro após estabelecer residência",
        "Registration deadlines, inspection, emissions, title, and plate rules.": "Prazos de registro, inspeção, emissões, título e regras de placa.",
        "Registration, inspection, emissions, title, and plate requirements can differ by state.": "Exigências de registro, inspeção, emissões, título e placa podem diferir conforme o estado.",
        "Relocating for a job or new employer.": "Mudança em razão de um emprego ou novo empregador.",
        "Relocating for a nursing or healthcare program (ABSN, MEPN, MSN, allied health, etc.).": "Mudança em razão de um programa de enfermagem ou saúde (ABSN, MEPN, MSN, saúde aliada etc.).",
        "Relocating to attend an undergraduate or graduate program.": "Mudança para cursar um programa de graduação ou pós-graduação.",
        "Relocating with family members or dependents.": "Mudança com familiares ou dependentes.",
        "Replace official agency or licensed-professional guidance": "Substituir as orientações oficiais de órgãos ou de profissionais habilitados",
        "Replace with an official URL from the destination state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "Substitua por uma URL oficial do órgão de veículos motorizados do estado de destino antes de confiar neste item.",
        "Replace with an official URL from the origin state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "Substitua por uma URL oficial do órgão de veículos motorizados do estado de origem antes de confiar neste item.",
        "Replace with official federal tax-authority guidance. Use only as general orientation; consult a qualified tax professional.": "Substitua por orientação oficial da autoridade fiscal federal. Use apenas como orientação geral; consulte um profissional tributário qualificado.",
        "Replace with the destination state agriculture / animal-health agency. Some species, breeds, or vaccinations have specific entry rules.": "Substitua pelo órgão de agricultura / saúde animal do estado de destino. Algumas espécies, raças ou vacinações têm regras específicas de entrada.",
        "Replace with the destination state department of health URL.": "Substitua pela URL do departamento de saúde do estado de destino.",
        "Replace with the destination state labor agency for paid leave, withholding, and labor law basics.": "Substitua pelo órgão estadual do trabalho do destino para licenças remuneradas, retenção e noções de legislação trabalhista.",
        "Replace with the destination state's attorney general or housing agency. Local ordinances may add protections.": "Substitua pela procuradoria-geral ou pelo órgão de moradia do estado de destino. Ordenanças locais podem acrescentar proteções.",
        "Replace with the destination state's official tax agency website. Tax rules and forms change frequently.": "Substitua pelo site oficial do órgão fiscal do estado de destino. As regras e os formulários fiscais mudam com frequência.",
        "Replace with the destination state's professional licensing portal or relevant board for the specific profession.": "Substitua pelo portal de licenciamento profissional do estado de destino ou pelo conselho pertinente à profissão específica.",
        "Replace with the official NLC information page. Participation status and rules can change.": "Substitua pela página oficial de informações do NLC. A situação de participação e as regras podem mudar.",
        "Replace with the official destination state board of nursing URL. Board rules govern eligibility and endorsement.": "Substitua pela URL oficial do board of nursing do estado de destino. As regras do conselho regem a elegibilidade e o endosso.",
        "Replace with the receiving school's residency or tuition classification page. School rules differ from state-agency rules.": "Substitua pela página de residência ou de classificação de mensalidade da escola receptora. As regras da escola diferem das regras do órgão estadual.",
        "Required documents for the application": "Documentos exigidos para o pedido",
        "Required notice periods for ending a lease": "Prazos de aviso exigidos para encerrar um contrato",
        "Reset all selections": "Redefinir todas as seleções",
        "Reset progress": "Redefinir progresso",
        "Residency can affect tuition, taxes, licensing, and benefits, and is determined by the relevant state agency, school, or tax authority - not by MoveSafe.": "A residência pode afetar mensalidade, impostos, licenciamento e benefícios, e é determinada pelo órgão estadual, escola ou autoridade tributária pertinente - não pelo MoveSafe.",
        "Review destination-state lease and tenant basics": "Revise as noções de contrato e de inquilino no estado de destino",
        "Review recommended": "Revisão recomendada",
        "Risk level: %@": "Nível de risco: %@",
        "Road trip": "Viagem de carro",
        "Rules around possession, documentation, and refills can differ across states and pharmacies.": "Regras sobre posse, documentação e novos suprimentos podem diferir entre estados e farmácias.",
        "Rules may differ substantially by jurisdiction, and MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in a specific situation.": "As regras podem diferir bastante por jurisdição, e o MoveSafe não determina se a posse, o transporte ou o uso está em conformidade com a lei em uma situação específica.",
        "Rules vary widely. Verify with official sources.": "As regras variam bastante. Confira em fontes oficiais.",
        "SSA POMS section on the lawful presence framework that informs Medicare and other federal benefits.": "Seção do SSA POMS sobre o arcabouço de lawful presence que orienta o Medicare e outros benefícios federais.",
        "SSN or identity documentation requirements if applicable": "Exigências de SSN ou documentação de identidade quando aplicáveis",
        "School / institution policy": "Política da escola / instituição",
        "School or institution": "Escola ou instituição",
        "School residency / tuition classification policy": "Política da escola sobre residência / classificação de mensalidade",
        "School residency classification": "Classificação de residência da escola",
        "School residency classification, immunization, student insurance, housing.": "Classificação de residência na escola, imunização, seguro estudantil e moradia.",
        "School-level requirements can affect tuition classification, enrollment, and clinical participation.": "Exigências no nível da escola podem afetar a classificação de mensalidade, a matrícula e a participação clínica.",
        "School-specific clinical onboarding requirements": "Exigências de integração clínica específicas da escola",
        "Schools set their own residency, health-insurance, and immunization requirements separate from state-agency rules.": "As escolas definem suas próprias exigências de residência, seguro de saúde e imunização, separadas das regras do órgão estadual.",
        "Secondary reference": "Referência secundária",
        "Security deposit limits and return deadlines": "Limites de depósito de garantia e prazos de devolução",
        "Security deposit limits, notice periods, eviction rules, and late-fee rules can differ between states and between cities.": "Limites de depósito de garantia, prazos de aviso, regras de despejo e regras de multa por atraso podem diferir entre estados e entre cidades.",
        "Select a destination state.": "Selecione um estado de destino.",
        "Select a purpose.": "Selecione um objetivo.",
        "Select a purpose…": "Selecione um objetivo…",
        "Select a state…": "Selecione um estado…",
        "Select an origin state.": "Selecione um estado de origem.",
        "Select at least one category.": "Selecione ao menos uma categoria.",
        "Select one or more. You can change these later.": "Selecione uma ou mais. Você pode alterá-las depois.",
        "Selective Service System FAQ page.": "Página de perguntas frequentes do Selective Service System.",
        "Selective Service System PDF chart that lists categories and exceptions.": "Tabela em PDF do Selective Service System listando categorias e exceções.",
        "Selective Service System main Who Needs to Register page, with nonimmigrant exception language.": "Página principal Who Needs to Register do Selective Service System, com texto sobre a exceção para não imigrante.",
        "Selective Service System materials generally describe a Selective Service registration requirement for almost all men ages 18 through 25 living in the United States, with an exception for men who are in the United States on a current valid nonimmigrant visa while that status remains valid up to age 26.": "Os materiais do Selective Service System em geral descrevem uma exigência de registro no Selective Service para quase todos os homens de 18 a 25 anos que vivem nos Estados Unidos, com uma exceção para homens que estão nos Estados Unidos com um visto de não imigrante vigente válido enquanto essa situação permanecer válida até os 26 anos.",
        "Selective Service registration is a federal requirement for almost all males ages 18 through 25 in the United States, regardless of citizenship, and many states link license or ID applications to that registration.": "O registro no Selective Service é uma exigência federal para quase todos os homens de 18 a 25 anos nos Estados Unidos, independentemente de cidadania, e muitos estados vinculam pedidos de carteira ou ID a esse registro.",
        "Setting up mail forwarding or updating a state license can give a false sense that the federal address record is current, while a pending USCIS case may still be sending notices to an old address.": "Configurar o encaminhamento de correspondência ou atualizar uma carteira estadual pode dar a falsa sensação de que o cadastro federal de endereço está atualizado, enquanto um caso pendente no USCIS pode estar enviando avisos a um endereço antigo.",
        "Settings": "Configurações",
        "Share checklist": "Compartilhar checklist",
        "Short-to-medium term internship or co-op in another state.": "Internship ou co-op de curto a médio prazo em outro estado.",
        "Show high-risk categories separately": "Mostrar categorias de alto risco separadamente",
        "Some checklist items use placeholder sources. Replace with official sources before relying on them.": "Alguns itens do checklist usam fontes provisórias. Substitua por fontes oficiais antes de confiar nelas.",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules.": "Alguns itens podem ser regulamentados de forma diferente entre estados e podem envolver lei estadual, ordenanças locais, lei federal ou regras de órgãos.",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in any specific situation. Verify directly with official sources and consult a licensed attorney or relevant agency if needed.": "Alguns itens podem ser regulamentados de forma diferente entre estados e podem envolver lei estadual, ordenanças locais, lei federal ou regras de órgãos. O MoveSafe não determina se a posse, o transporte ou o uso está em conformidade com a lei em qualquer situação específica. Confira diretamente em fontes oficiais e consulte um advogado licenciado ou o órgão pertinente se necessário.",
        "Some sources have not been verified recently. Check the official website before relying on them.": "Algumas fontes não foram conferidas recentemente. Confira o site oficial antes de confiar nelas.",
        "Some states issue driver licenses or state IDs to nonimmigrant visa applicants on a shortened renewal cycle that tracks the I-94 or an underlying federal document, instead of the multi-year cycle used for citizens. Fees, renewal timing, and steps after a status extension can differ between origin and destination states.": "Alguns estados emitem carteiras de motorista ou state IDs para candidatos com visto de não imigrante em um ciclo de renovação encurtado que acompanha o I-94 ou um documento federal subjacente, em vez do ciclo plurianual usado para cidadãos. Taxas, cronograma de renovação e etapas após uma extensão de situação migratória podem diferir entre os estados de origem e de destino.",
        "Source not yet documented": "Fonte ainda não documentada",
        "Source status: %@": "Situação da fonte: %@",
        "Sources referenced in this checklist": "Fontes citadas neste checklist",
        "Sources to verify only": "Apenas fontes a conferir",
        "Sources:": "Fontes:",
        "Sources: placeholder - verify with the relevant official agency.": "Fontes: provisórias - confira no órgão oficial pertinente.",
        "Stale or placeholder sources only": "Apenas fontes desatualizadas ou provisórias",
        "Stale source": "Fonte desatualizada",
        "Stale source warning": "Aviso de fonte desatualizada",
        "Start fresh": "Começar do zero",
        "Starting work at a new worksite outside the LCA's MSA without an amended petition can affect status maintenance, and the timing of the amended petition filing matters for when the worker can begin at the new location.": "Começar a trabalhar em um novo worksite fora da MSA da LCA sem uma petição emendada pode afetar a manutenção da situação migratória, e o momento do envio da petição emendada importa para quando o trabalhador pode começar no novo local.",
        "State DMV document checklists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 and similar) can differ from those used for U.S. citizens or lawful permanent residents. Accepted combinations of passport, visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, and I-797 or employer letter may vary, and some states ask for an SSN card or an SSA ineligibility letter.": "As listas de documentos dos DMVs estaduais para candidatos com visto de não imigrante (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 e similares) podem ser diferentes das usadas para cidadãos dos EUA ou LPRs. As combinações aceitas de passaporte, visto, I-94, I-20 ou DS-2019 e I-797 ou carta do empregador podem variar, e alguns estados pedem cartão de SSN ou carta de inelegibilidade da SSA.",
        "State University of New York Board of Trustees policy on residency for tuition purposes, including which visa categories can establish New York domicile. suny.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing state university system domain.": "Política do Board of Trustees da State University of New York sobre residência para fins de mensalidade, incluindo quais categorias de visto podem estabelecer domicílio em New York. O suny.edu retorna 403 a requisições que não vêm de navegador (Cloudflare); este é um falso negativo conhecido no domínio do sistema estadual universitário de longa data.",
        "State filing requirements, part-year residency, remote work implications.": "Exigências de declaração estadual, residência por parte do ano e implicações do trabalho remoto.",
        "State grant and scholarship programs each have their own rules about whether non-citizen students may be considered, what application form (FAFSA, a state alternative, or an institutional form) is used, and what documentation is needed.": "Os programas estaduais de bolsa e auxílio têm cada um regras próprias sobre se estudantes não cidadãos podem ser considerados, qual formulário de pedido (FAFSA, uma alternativa estadual ou um formulário institucional) é usado e qual documentação é necessária.",
        "State labor law basics (paid sick leave, breaks, final pay rules)": "Noções de legislação trabalhista estadual (licença médica remunerada, intervalos, regras de pagamento final)",
        "State law": "Lei estadual",
        "State residency basics": "Noções sobre residência estadual",
        "State tax filing can apply even when income is earned remotely. Rules differ by state.": "A declaração de imposto estadual pode se aplicar mesmo quando a renda é ganha de forma remota. As regras diferem por estado.",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. A person treated as a nonresident alien on the federal return may still be a resident, part-year resident, or nonresident for state purposes depending on domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors. States may or may not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "A residência fiscal estadual é determinada pelas regras de cada estado, que podem diferir da residência fiscal federal. Uma pessoa tratada como nonresident alien na declaração federal pode ainda ser resident, part-year resident ou nonresident para fins estaduais, dependendo de domicílio, dias de presença física, localização do empregador e outros fatores. Os estados podem ou não acompanhar as exclusões federais de tratado tributário sobre renda.",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. Domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors can each play a role.": "A residência fiscal estadual é determinada pelas regras de cada estado, que podem diferir da residência fiscal federal. Domicílio, dias de presença física, localização do empregador e outros fatores podem cada um ter um papel.",
        "State tax withholding, labor law basics, remote work considerations.": "Retenção de imposto estadual, noções de legislação trabalhista e pontos do trabalho remoto.",
        "States and individual public colleges and universities use different tuition-classification rules for non-citizens, including how prior in-state high school attendance, current immigration status, and a parent's residency are considered.": "Os estados e as faculdades e universidades públicas usam regras de classificação de mensalidade diferentes para não cidadãos, incluindo como são consideradas a frequência prévia ao ensino médio in-state, a situação migratória atual e a residência de um responsável.",
        "States may require proof of identity, residency, lawful presence, school documents, or other paperwork.": "Os estados podem exigir prova de identidade, residência, presença em conformidade com a lei, documentos escolares ou outros papéis.",
        "Staying in another state temporarily without intending to become a resident.": "Ficar em outro estado temporariamente sem a intenção de se tornar residente.",
        "Student health insurance requirements": "Exigências de seguro de saúde estudantil",
        "Student or temporary resident exceptions": "Exceções para estudante ou residente temporário",
        "Student relocation": "Mudança de estudante",
        "Subleasing rules": "Regras de sublocação",
        "TSA REAL ID FAQs page covering documentation for citizens and non-citizens.": "Página de perguntas frequentes da TSA sobre REAL ID, cobrindo documentação para cidadãos e não cidadãos.",
        "TSA REAL ID overview page. Note: www.dhs.gov/real-id now redirects to TSA's REAL ID page.": "Página de visão geral do REAL ID na TSA. Observação: www.dhs.gov/real-id agora redireciona para a página do REAL ID na TSA.",
        "Tap to collapse": "Toque para recolher",
        "Tap to expand": "Toque para expandir",
        "Taxes / state filing awareness": "Impostos / atenção à declaração estadual",
        "Temporary permit availability": "Disponibilidade de autorização temporária",
        "Temporary stay": "Estadia temporária",
        "Texas Board of Nursing endorsement information page, relevant when moving from another state with a license.": "Página de informações sobre endosso do Texas Board of Nursing, relevante para quem se muda de outro estado com uma licença.",
        "Texas Board of Nursing licensure eligibility page covering general requirements and documentation expectations.": "Página do Texas Board of Nursing sobre elegibilidade ao licenciamento, cobrindo exigências gerais e expectativas de documentação.",
        "Texas Department of Public Safety driver license identification documentation page covering U.S. citizen and non-U.S. citizen applicants.": "Página de documentação de identificação para carteira de motorista do Texas Department of Public Safety, cobrindo candidatos cidadãos dos EUA e não cidadãos dos EUA.",
        "Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board page on residency for tuition purposes, including categories of nonimmigrant applicants and special pathways under the Texas Education Code.": "Página do Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board sobre residência para fins de mensalidade, incluindo categorias de candidatos com situação de não imigrante e caminhos especiais sob o Texas Education Code.",
        "The deadline for applying for a destination-state license": "O prazo para solicitar a carteira no estado de destino",
        "This checklist is based on your selected categories and available source data. It may not include every requirement that applies to your situation.": "Este checklist se baseia nas categorias que você selecionou e nos dados de fontes disponíveis. Pode não incluir todas as exigências aplicáveis à sua situação.",
        "This checklist is not a legal conclusion. Verify with official sources and consult a licensed professional where appropriate.": "Este checklist não é uma conclusão jurídica. Confira em fontes oficiais e consulte um profissional licenciado quando for apropriado.",
        "This source has not been verified in more than a year. Treat as stale and verify directly with the official source.": "Esta fonte não é conferida há mais de um ano. Trate como desatualizada e confira diretamente na fonte oficial.",
        "This source has not been verified in more than six months. Check the official website before relying on it.": "Esta fonte não é conferida há mais de seis meses. Confira o site oficial antes de confiar nela.",
        "This source was checked more than 90 days ago. Review recommended.": "Esta fonte foi conferida há mais de 90 dias. Revisão recomendada.",
        "Title transfer process": "Processo de transferência de título",
        "Total topics to verify: %d": "Total de tópicos a conferir: %d",
        "Travel documentation if flying with a pet": "Documentação de viagem se for voar com um animal",
        "Treating an intra-MSA worksite change as a full new petition can create unnecessary cost and timing risk, while assuming portability rules apply without checking the MSA boundaries can lead to status questions later.": "Tratar uma troca de worksite dentro da MSA como uma petição nova completa pode gerar custo e risco de prazo desnecessários, e supor que as regras de portabilidade se aplicam sem checar os limites da MSA pode levar a dúvidas sobre situação migratória depois.",
        "Treats high-risk categories with a \"Do not assume\" label": "Trata categorias de alto risco com o aviso \"Não presuma\"",
        "Try clearing risk filters or the high-risk / stale-source toggles.": "Tente limpar os filtros de risco ou as opções de alto risco / fonte desatualizada.",
        "USCIS Employment Authorization page providing background on the EAD (Form I-766) used in some state DMV and licensing document lists.": "Página de Employment Authorization do USCIS com contexto sobre o EAD (Formulário I-766) usado em algumas listas de documentos de DMVs estaduais e de licenciamento.",
        "USCIS Form AR-11 PDF": "PDF do Formulário AR-11 do USCIS",
        "USCIS H-1B Specialty Occupations Landing Page": "Página inicial do USCIS sobre H-1B Specialty Occupations",
        "USCIS L-1A classification page.": "Página do USCIS sobre a classificação L-1A.",
        "USCIS L-1B classification page.": "Página do USCIS sobre a classificação L-1B.",
        "USCIS O-1 classification page.": "Página do USCIS sobre a classificação O-1.",
        "USCIS Policy Manual chapter that describes federal address-change reporting.": "Capítulo do USCIS Policy Manual que descreve a notificação federal de mudança de endereço.",
        "USCIS archive page summarizing the 2015 Simeio Solutions final guidance and the LCA-amendment trigger for worksite changes outside the MSA.": "Página de arquivo do USCIS resumindo a orientação final de Simeio Solutions de 2015 e o acionador de emenda de LCA para mudanças de worksite fora da MSA.",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that a U.S. Postal Service change-of-address request does not change a record with USCIS and that USPS does not forward USCIS mail. A destination-state DMV address update is also a separate step from the federal AR-11 filing.": "A orientação do USCIS em geral indica que um pedido de mudança de endereço no U.S. Postal Service não altera um cadastro no USCIS e que o USPS não encaminha a correspondência do USCIS. Uma atualização de endereço no DMV do estado de destino também é uma etapa separada do registro federal do AR-11.",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that an H-1B worker moving to a new worksite within the same MSA or area of intended employment as the existing LCA does not require a new LCA or an amended H-1B petition, although the existing LCA may still need to be posted at the new worksite. The federal AR-11 address change requirement still applies to the worker.": "A orientação do USCIS em geral indica que um trabalhador H-1B que se mude para um novo worksite dentro da mesma MSA ou área de emprego pretendida da LCA existente não precisa de nova LCA nem de petição emendada de H-1B, embora a LCA atual ainda possa precisar ser afixada no novo worksite. A exigência federal AR-11 de mudança de endereço continua valendo para o trabalhador.",
        "USCIS newsroom alert describing the online change-of-address tool and clarifying that USPS forwarding does not change a USCIS record.": "Aviso da sala de imprensa do USCIS descrevendo a ferramenta on-line de mudança de endereço e esclarecendo que o encaminhamento do USPS não altera um cadastro do USCIS.",
        "USCIS umbrella page on the federal change-of-address requirement, including the online change-of-address tool.": "Página geral do USCIS sobre a exigência federal de mudança de endereço, incluindo a ferramenta on-line de mudança de endereço.",
        "USPS mail-forwarding page; referenced to clarify that USPS change-of-address does not substitute for federal AR-11 filing per USCIS guidance.": "Página do USPS sobre encaminhamento de correspondência; referenciada para esclarecer que a mudança de endereço no USPS não substitui o registro federal do AR-11, conforme orientação do USCIS.",
        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "Sob o 22 CFR Part 62, os sponsors de programa J-1 mantêm o registro no SEVIS e acompanham o site of activity de cada exchange visitor. Uma mudança que altere residência, site of activity ou host organization em geral aciona uma obrigação de o exchange visitor reportar ao sponsor e uma atualização do sponsor no SEVIS.",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "Sob a orientação do USCIS após Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), a mudança de um trabalhador H-1B para um worksite fora da metropolitan statistical area (MSA) ou da área de emprego pretendida listada na Labor Condition Application (LCA) atual em geral é uma mudança material que pede uma nova LCA e uma petição emendada de H-1B.",
        "Understand how the destination state defines residency": "Entenda como o estado de destino define residência",
        "University of California admissions page on the AB 540 nonresident tuition exemption, noting that most nonimmigrant visa holders such as F-1 or J-1 generally cannot establish California residency for tuition purposes.": "Página de admissões da University of California sobre a isenção AB 540 de mensalidade nonresident, registrando que a maioria dos portadores de visto de não imigrante, como F-1 ou J-1, em geral não consegue estabelecer residência na California para fins de mensalidade.",
        "Update employment paperwork and state tax forms": "Atualize a documentação de emprego e os formulários de imposto estadual",
        "Use do not assume language. Do not state that USPS or DMV updates can substitute for AR-11 (USCIS guidance says they generally do not). Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "Use linguagem do tipo \"não presuma\". Não afirme que atualizações no USPS ou no DMV substituem o AR-11 (a orientação do USCIS diz que em geral não substituem). Evite a lista de evitar do SafeCopy do iOS (frases de conclusão jurídica e frases sobre escapar de sanções).",
        "Vaccination, licensing, breed restrictions, housing pet policies.": "Vacinação, licenciamento, restrições por raça e políticas de animais nas moradias.",
        "Vaccination, local licensing, breed restrictions, and landlord pet policies can vary across destination states and cities.": "Vacinação, licenciamento local, restrições por raça e políticas de animais do locador podem variar entre estados de destino e cidades.",
        "Vehicle registration": "Registro de veículo",
        "Vehicle registration rules can change after a state-to-state move, especially if the destination state treats you as a new resident.": "As regras de registro de veículo podem mudar após uma mudança entre estados, especialmente se o estado de destino tratar você como novo residente.",
        "Verification progress": "Progresso da conferência",
        "Verified: %1$d of %2$d": "Conferido: %1$d de %2$d",
        "Verify ACA marketplace categories described as lawfully present for nonimmigrants": "Confira as categorias do marketplace da ACA descritas como lawfully present para não imigrantes",
        "Verify F-1 SEVIS school-transfer steps if the move is to a different school": "Confira as etapas de transferência de escola no SEVIS para F-1 se a mudança for para uma escola diferente",
        "Verify FICA (Social Security and Medicare) handling for F-1 and J-1 nonresident aliens": "Confira o tratamento do FICA (Social Security e Medicare) para nonresident aliens F-1 e J-1",
        "Verify H-1B portability and address handling for a move within the same MSA": "Confira a portabilidade do H-1B e o tratamento do endereço em uma mudança dentro da mesma MSA",
        "Verify J-1 program sponsor reporting for site-of-activity or host-organization changes": "Confira o reporte ao sponsor do programa J-1 para mudanças de site of activity ou de host organization",
        "Verify L-1 or O-1 worksite change handling against the approved petition": "Confira o tratamento da mudança de worksite L-1 ou O-1 em relação à petição aprovada",
        "Verify Medicare and Medicaid eligibility rules that may apply to nonimmigrants after a move": "Confira as regras de elegibilidade ao Medicare e ao Medicaid que podem se aplicar a não imigrantes após uma mudança",
        "Verify SEVP Portal updates for address, employer, and unemployment-day tracking on OPT or STEM OPT": "Confira as atualizações no SEVP Portal de endereço, empregador e contagem de dias de desemprego em OPT ou STEM OPT",
        "Verify destination Board of Nursing documentation for non-citizen applicants": "Confira a documentação do Board of Nursing do estado de destino para candidatos não cidadãos",
        "Verify destination-state DMV documents for non-citizen applicants": "Confira os documentos do DMV do estado de destino para candidatos não cidadãos",
        "Verify destination-state DMV documents for nonimmigrant visa applicants": "Confira os documentos do DMV do estado de destino para candidatos com visto de não imigrante",
        "Verify destination-state financial aid eligibility rules for non-citizens": "Confira as regras de elegibilidade a auxílio financeiro do estado de destino para não cidadãos",
        "Verify destination-state professional licensing documentation rules for visa or OPT applicants": "Confira as regras de documentação para licenciamento profissional no estado de destino para candidatos com visto ou OPT",
        "Verify destination-state tuition classification rules for non-citizen students": "Confira as regras de classificação de mensalidade no estado de destino para estudantes não cidadãos",
        "Verify destination-state tuition classification rules for nonimmigrant visa students": "Confira as regras de classificação de mensalidade no estado de destino para estudantes com visto de não imigrante",
        "Verify documentation a destination-state licensing board requires for non-citizens": "Confira a documentação que um conselho de licenciamento do estado de destino exige de não cidadãos",
        "Verify dual-status year considerations for the federal return covering a move": "Confira os aspectos de dual-status year na declaração federal que abrange a mudança",
        "Verify federal tax residency under the Substantial Presence Test after a move": "Confira a residência fiscal federal pelo Substantial Presence Test após a mudança",
        "Verify health-insurance marketplace options in the destination state": "Confira as opções do marketplace de seguro de saúde no estado de destino",
        "Verify how Selective Service registration applies to a specific nonimmigrant status": "Confira como o registro no Selective Service se aplica a uma situação de não imigrante específica",
        "Verify how a destination-state REAL ID expiration may track an underlying federal document": "Confira como o vencimento do REAL ID do estado de destino pode acompanhar um documento federal subjacente",
        "Verify how the federal five-year waiting period applies in the destination state": "Confira como o período federal de espera de cinco anos se aplica no estado de destino",
        "Verify license fee and renewal-cycle rules that may follow an I-94 expiration": "Confira as regras de taxa e de ciclo de renovação da carteira que podem acompanhar o vencimento do I-94",
        "Verify rules for transporting prescription medication across state lines": "Confira as regras para transportar medicamentos com prescrição entre estados",
        "Verify soon": "Conferir em breve",
        "Verify state tax residency and filing rules after a move": "Confira a residência fiscal estadual e as regras de declaração após a mudança",
        "Verify state tax residency rules and how they interact with federal nonresident alien status": "Confira as regras de residência fiscal estadual e como interagem com a situação federal de nonresident alien",
        "Verify state-funded benefit programs that may apply during a federal waiting period": "Confira os programas de benefícios financiados pelo estado que podem se aplicar durante um período federal de espera",
        "Verify the 10-day DSO or sponsor SEVIS address update for F-1 and J-1 status": "Confira a atualização de endereço no SEVIS via DSO ou sponsor, em até 10 dias, para situação F-1 e J-1",
        "Verify the 10-day USCIS address change filing after an interstate move": "Confira o registro de mudança de endereço no USCIS, em até 10 dias, após uma mudança entre estados",
        "Verify the destination-state driver's license deadline": "Confira o prazo da carteira de motorista no estado de destino",
        "Verify vehicle registration requirements after moving": "Confira as exigências de registro de veículo após a mudança",
        "Verify whether an H-1B amended petition is needed for a worksite move to a new MSA": "Confira se é necessária uma petição emendada de H-1B para uma mudança de worksite para uma nova MSA",
        "Verify whether to apply for a REAL ID or a standard credential": "Confira se deve solicitar um REAL ID ou uma credencial padrão",
        "Version": "Versão",
        "View example checklist": "Ver checklist de exemplo",
        "WHAT TO VERIFY": "O QUE CONFERIR",
        "WHY THIS MATTERS": "POR QUE ISSO IMPORTA",
        "Washington Department of Licensing proof-of-identity page including non-citizen documents such as I-551 annotations and U.S. visa stamps.": "Página de comprovação de identidade do Washington Department of Licensing, incluindo documentos de não cidadão como anotações I-551 e carimbos de visto dos EUA.",
        "What MoveSafe does": "O que o MoveSafe faz",
        "What MoveSafe does not do": "O que o MoveSafe não faz",
        "What confirmation record (receipt, screenshot, mailed copy) to keep after filing": "Qual registro de confirmação (recibo, captura de tela, cópia enviada pelo correio) guardar após enviar",
        "What documentation, if any, the DMV keeps if a non-citizen declines": "Que documentação, se houver, o DMV mantém quando um não cidadão recusa",
        "What documents (for example, EAD, transcripts, affidavits, tax records) the registrar requires to support a tuition-classification request": "Quais documentos (por exemplo, EAD, históricos, declarações juramentadas, registros fiscais) o registrar exige para fundamentar um pedido de classificação de mensalidade",
        "What documents (for example, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, transcripts, affidavits, tax records) the registrar requires to support a classification request": "Quais documentos (por exemplo, I-94, I-20 ou DS-2019, I-797, históricos, declarações juramentadas, registros fiscais) o registrar exige para fundamentar um pedido de classificação",
        "What tax or residency documentation the state aid agency requires": "Qual documentação fiscal ou de residência o órgão estadual de auxílio exige",
        "What to verify:": "O que conferir:",
        "Whether AR-11 has been filed separately with USCIS within the federal 10-day window": "Se o AR-11 foi enviado em separado ao USCIS dentro da janela federal de 10 dias",
        "Whether DACA recipients are currently considered for marketplace coverage, since this category has changed at the federal level": "Se beneficiários do DACA são atualmente considerados para a cobertura do marketplace, já que essa categoria mudou em nível federal",
        "Whether Medicaid or state marketplace rules differ": "Se as regras do Medicaid ou do marketplace estadual diferem",
        "Whether REAL ID and standard (non-REAL-ID) credentials use different document checklists": "Se as credenciais REAL ID e a credencial padrão (não REAL ID) usam listas de documentos diferentes",
        "Whether REAL ID requirements apply for your situation": "Se as exigências do REAL ID se aplicam à sua situação",
        "Whether USPS mail forwarding is in place for the new address": "Se o encaminhamento de correspondência do USPS está ativo para o novo endereço",
        "Whether a Social Security card or an SSA ineligibility letter is required to apply": "Se um cartão de Social Security ou uma carta de inelegibilidade da SSA é exigida para se candidatar",
        "Whether a USPS change-of-address forwards mail from USCIS (USCIS guidance generally indicates it does not)": "Se uma mudança de endereço no USPS encaminha a correspondência do USCIS (a orientação do USCIS em geral indica que não)",
        "Whether a change in site of activity or host organization needs prior sponsor authorization before it occurs": "Se uma mudança de site of activity ou de host organization precisa de autorização prévia do sponsor antes de ocorrer",
        "Whether a closer connection exception or a tax-treaty tie-breaker rule may apply": "Se uma exceção de closer connection ou uma regra de desempate de tratado tributário pode se aplicar",
        "Whether a first-year choice or a tax-treaty election can change the analysis": "Se uma first-year choice ou uma eleição de tratado tributário pode mudar a análise",
        "Whether a fresh I-94 printout or an updated I-797 is needed at the time of renewal, and whether the DMV verifies status through a federal system in real time": "Se é necessário um I-94 atualizado impresso ou um I-797 atualizado no momento da renovação, e se o DMV confere a situação migratória por um sistema federal em tempo real",
        "Whether a license issued to a non-citizen may have a renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Se uma licença emitida para não cidadão pode ter um ciclo de renovação vinculado a um documento federal",
        "Whether a license issued to a non-citizen may have a shorter renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Se uma licença emitida para não cidadão pode ter um ciclo de renovação mais curto, vinculado a um documento federal",
        "Whether a license issued to a visa holder may have a shorter renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Se uma licença emitida a um portador de visto pode ter um ciclo de renovação mais curto, atrelado a um documento federal",
        "Whether a move that includes a change of school or program site requires additional SEVIS steps beyond an address update": "Se uma mudança que inclua troca de escola ou de local do programa exige etapas adicionais no SEVIS além de uma atualização de endereço",
        "Whether a move triggers a special enrollment period and what documents the marketplace requires to verify status": "Se uma mudança aciona um special enrollment period e quais documentos o marketplace exige para conferir a situação migratória",
        "Whether a new Form I-20 from the destination school has been issued and signed": "Se um novo Formulário I-20 da escola de destino foi emitido e assinado",
        "Whether a new application is required": "Se é necessária uma nova inscrição",
        "Whether a separate identifier or marking appears on credentials issued to applicants with temporary lawful status in that state": "Se um identificador ou marcação separada aparece em credenciais emitidas para candidatos com situação temporária em conformidade com a lei naquele estado",
        "Whether a short-term placement exception (subject to federal time limits) applies before an amendment is needed": "Se uma exceção de short-term placement (sujeita a limites federais de tempo) se aplica antes de ser necessária uma emenda",
        "Whether a standard (non-REAL-ID) credential is offered as an alternative": "Se uma credencial padrão (não REAL ID) é oferecida como alternativa",
        "Whether a standard (non-REAL-ID) credential is offered as an alternative and whether its expiration is also tied to a federal document": "Se uma credencial padrão (não REAL ID) é oferecida como alternativa e se o seu vencimento também está vinculado a um documento federal",
        "Whether a state return for the destination or origin state must be filed alongside the federal dual-status return": "Se é necessário enviar declaração estadual do estado de destino ou de origem junto com a declaração federal em dual status",
        "Whether a student is classified as in-state, out-of-state, or under a tuition-equity policy can change the cost of attendance significantly, and rules can differ between the state higher-education agency, a state university system, and individual institutions.": "Se um estudante é classificado como in-state, out-of-state ou sob uma política de equidade de mensalidade, isso pode mudar muito o custo dos estudos, e as regras podem diferir entre o órgão estadual de ensino superior, um sistema universitário estadual e cada instituição.",
        "Whether a student is classified as resident, nonresident, or under a state tuition-equity provision can change the cost of attendance significantly, and rules vary across origin and destination states and across institutions within a state.": "Se um estudante é classificado como resident, nonresident ou sob uma disposição estadual de equidade de mensalidade, isso pode mudar muito o custo dos estudos, e as regras variam entre estados de origem e de destino e entre instituições dentro de um estado.",
        "Whether a year of transition to resident-alien status under the Substantial Presence Test changes FICA treatment": "Se um ano de transição para a situação de resident alien pelo Substantial Presence Test altera o tratamento do FICA",
        "Whether an SSN is required to apply, and whether an ITIN, an SSA ineligibility letter, or an affidavit is accepted as an alternative": "Se um SSN é exigido para se candidatar e se um ITIN, uma carta de inelegibilidade da SSA ou uma declaração juramentada é aceita como alternativa",
        "Whether an exempt-individual rule (for certain F, J, M, Q categories) may apply and for how many years": "Se uma regra de exempt individual (para certas categorias F, J, M, Q) pode se aplicar e por quantos anos",
        "Whether any active USCIS receipt number has its own e-Notification or online-account address that needs to be checked": "Se algum número de recibo ativo do USCIS tem seu próprio endereço de e-Notification ou de conta on-line que precisa ser conferido",
        "Whether any category-specific rules (research scholar, professor, intern, trainee, physician, au pair, and others) add steps that the sponsor must approve": "Se regras específicas da categoria (research scholar, professor, intern, trainee, physician, au pair e outras) acrescentam etapas que o sponsor precisa aprovar",
        "Whether any change in job duties, hours, or wage triggers a separate amendment analysis even when the worksite stays in the same MSA": "Se qualquer mudança em atribuições, jornada ou salário aciona uma análise de emenda à parte mesmo quando o worksite permanece na mesma MSA",
        "Whether any pending USCIS case (I-129, I-485, I-765, I-130, and similar) requires a separate address update beyond AR-11": "Se algum caso pendente no USCIS (I-129, I-485, I-765, I-130 e similares) exige uma atualização de endereço à parte, além do AR-11",
        "Whether any state credit programs (for example, an earned-income or family credit) consider non-citizen filers": "Se programas estaduais de crédito (por exemplo, earned-income ou family credit) consideram declarantes não cidadãos",
        "Whether benefits use by certain immigrant categories can interact with future immigration filings, and whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before applying": "Se o uso de benefícios por certas categorias de imigrantes pode interagir com pedidos futuros junto à imigração e se você deve consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de se candidatar",
        "Whether both physical and mailing addresses are recorded in SEVIS if they differ": "Se tanto o endereço físico quanto o postal estão registrados no SEVIS quando forem diferentes",
        "Whether clinicals can begin before full licensure": "Se as atividades clínicas podem começar antes do licenciamento completo",
        "Whether destination-state Medicaid offers emergency-only coverage to nonimmigrants and what documentation it requires": "Se o Medicaid do estado de destino oferece cobertura apenas para emergências a não imigrantes e qual documentação ele exige",
        "Whether documentation (original container, prescription) is recommended": "Se documentação (recipiente original, receita) é recomendada",
        "Whether employer name, address, supervisor, and start or end dates are current in the SEVP Portal or reported to the DSO": "Se nome do empregador, endereço, supervisor e datas de início ou término estão atualizados no SEVP Portal ou reportados ao DSO",
        "Whether federal rules apply to interstate transportation": "Se as regras federais se aplicam ao transporte entre estados",
        "Whether high school attendance or graduation in the destination state is one of the qualifying paths": "Se a frequência ou a conclusão do ensino médio no estado de destino é um dos caminhos que qualificam",
        "Whether identity, residency, and SSN documents are required in addition to status documents": "Se são exigidos documentos de identidade, residência e SSN além dos documentos de situação migratória",
        "Whether immigration status or school documents affect the process": "Se a situação migratória ou os documentos escolares afetam o processo",
        "Whether institutional aid at your destination school is governed by separate rules from state aid": "Se o auxílio institucional da sua escola de destino é regido por regras separadas das do auxílio estadual",
        "Whether internationally educated nurses must complete a credentials-evaluation step (for example, CGFNS)": "Se enfermeiros com formação no exterior precisam concluir uma etapa de avaliação de credenciais (por exemplo, CGFNS)",
        "Whether local ordinances are stricter than state rules": "Se as ordenanças locais são mais rígidas que as regras estaduais",
        "Whether local taxes apply": "Se aplicam-se impostos locais",
        "Whether local tenant protections apply": "Se aplicam-se proteções locais ao inquilino",
        "Whether moving mid-coverage requires reapplication in the destination state": "Se mudar durante a cobertura exige novo pedido no estado de destino",
        "Whether moving mid-program changes the classification timeline": "Se mudar durante o programa altera o cronograma de classificação",
        "Whether out-of-state students need special documentation": "Se estudantes de fora do estado precisam de documentação especial",
        "Whether part-year residency rules apply": "Se aplicam-se regras de residência por parte do ano",
        "Whether pending discipline or incomplete education affects transfer": "Se processos disciplinares pendentes ou formação incompleta afetam a transferência",
        "Whether permits, age restrictions, documentation, or location-specific rules apply": "Se aplicam-se autorizações, restrições por idade, documentação ou regras específicas de local",
        "Whether posting requirements for the existing LCA at the new location, when in the same MSA, have been satisfied": "Se as exigências de afixação da LCA atual no novo local, quando dentro da mesma MSA, foram cumpridas",
        "Whether premium tax credit or cost-sharing reduction eligibility rules have changed for the relevant year": "Se as regras de elegibilidade a premium tax credit ou a cost-sharing reduction mudaram para o ano em questão",
        "Whether prescriptions can be transferred": "Se as prescrições podem ser transferidas",
        "Whether professional legal advice is needed": "Se é necessário aconselhamento jurídico profissional",
        "Whether proof of in-state residency is needed in addition to identity and status documents": "Se é necessária comprovação de residência in-state além dos documentos de identidade e de situação migratória",
        "Whether proof of in-state residency is required in addition to identity and status documents, and what residency proofs the DMV accepts for new arrivals": "Se é exigida comprovação de residência in-state além dos documentos de identidade e de situação migratória, e quais comprovantes de residência o DMV aceita para recém-chegados",
        "Whether remote work creates state tax or payroll issues": "Se o trabalho remoto cria problemas de imposto estadual ou de folha de pagamento",
        "Whether remote work may create tax issues": "Se o trabalho remoto pode criar questões tributárias",
        "Whether renewal fees and step counts differ from the standard renewal process used for citizens": "Se as taxas de renovação e a quantidade de etapas diferem do processo padrão de renovação usado para cidadãos",
        "Whether residency affects tuition, taxes, licenses, or benefits": "Se a residência afeta mensalidade, impostos, licenças ou benefícios",
        "Whether school attendance affects residency": "Se a frequência escolar afeta a residência",
        "Whether school attendance affects tax residency": "Se a frequência escolar afeta a residência fiscal",
        "Whether specific state grants or scholarships consider DACA recipients or lawful permanent residents in their eligibility criteria": "Se bolsas ou auxílios estaduais específicos consideram beneficiários do DACA ou LPRs em seus critérios de elegibilidade",
        "Whether state-specific uninsured/underinsured motorist rules apply": "Se aplicam-se regras específicas do estado para motorista sem seguro ou com seguro insuficiente",
        "Whether student health insurance is required": "Se o seguro de saúde estudantil é obrigatório",
        "Whether students or temporary residents are treated differently": "Se estudantes ou residentes temporários recebem tratamento diferente",
        "Whether temporary practice permits exist": "Se existem autorizações de prática temporária",
        "Whether the 10-day clock starts on the move date or the date the new address becomes permanent": "Se o prazo de 10 dias começa na data da mudança ou na data em que o novo endereço passa a ser permanente",
        "Whether the DSO has confirmed the SEVIS record was updated and any documentation that confirms the update": "Se o DSO confirmou que o registro SEVIS foi atualizado e qualquer documentação que confirme a atualização",
        "Whether the J-1 sponsor has been notified within 10 days of any change in U.S. address, telephone, or email": "Se o sponsor J-1 foi notificado em até 10 dias de qualquer mudança de endereço, telefone ou e-mail nos EUA",
        "Whether the REAL ID expiration date may be tied to the I-94, the visa, or an I-797 or I-20 or DS-2019, and how renewal works after a status extension": "Se a data de vencimento do REAL ID pode estar vinculada ao I-94, ao visto ou a um I-797 ou I-20 ou DS-2019, e como funciona a renovação após uma extensão de situação migratória",
        "Whether the REAL ID expiration date may be tied to the underlying federal document": "Se a data de vencimento do REAL ID pode estar vinculada ao documento federal subjacente",
        "Whether the application asks for a lawful presence attestation": "Se o pedido requer uma declaração de presença em conformidade com a lei",
        "Whether the application asks for a lawful presence attestation and what document supports it": "Se o pedido requer uma declaração de presença em conformidade com a lei e qual documento a fundamenta",
        "Whether the board accepts background-check results processed under your current status": "Se o conselho aceita resultados de verificação de antecedentes processados sob a sua situação migratória atual",
        "Whether the calendar-year count of days under the Substantial Presence Test meets the federal threshold for the current year": "Se a contagem de dias no ano civil pelo Substantial Presence Test atinge o limite federal do ano corrente",
        "Whether the current nonimmigrant status appears on the current HealthCare.gov lawfully present list": "Se a situação atual de não imigrante consta da lista atual de lawfully present do HealthCare.gov",
        "Whether the current school DSO and the new school DSO have coordinated a SEVIS transfer release date": "Se o DSO da escola atual e o DSO da nova escola coordenaram uma data de transfer release no SEVIS",
        "Whether the current status is within a recognized federal eligibility group for Medicare or Medicaid": "Se a situação migratória atual está dentro de um grupo de elegibilidade federal reconhecido para Medicare ou Medicaid",
        "Whether the destination Board of Nursing requires an SSN at application, and whether an ITIN, attestation, or affidavit is accepted as an alternative": "Se o Board of Nursing do estado de destino exige um SSN no pedido e se um ITIN, declaração ou affidavit é aceito como alternativa",
        "Whether the destination DMV requires original documents and current address proofs, and whether copies or translations are accepted": "Se o DMV do destino exige documentos originais e comprovantes de endereço atuais e se cópias ou traduções são aceitas",
        "Whether the destination address is being reported to the DSO or J-1 sponsor within 10 days of the move": "Se o endereço de destino está sendo reportado ao DSO ou ao sponsor J-1 em até 10 dias da mudança",
        "Whether the destination state accepts an ITIN where an SSN is requested on its return": "Se o estado de destino aceita um ITIN onde a declaração estadual pede um SSN",
        "Whether the destination state accepts an ITIN where an SSN is requested on its return, and whether a separate state tax ID is offered": "Se o estado de destino aceita um ITIN onde a declaração estadual pede um SSN, e se um state tax ID separado é oferecido",
        "Whether the destination state conforms to federal income tax treaty exclusions for nonresident aliens, or taxes that income at the state level": "Se o estado de destino acompanha as exclusões federais de tratado tributário sobre renda para nonresident aliens ou tributa essa renda no nível estadual",
        "Whether the destination state considers you a resident": "Se o estado de destino considera você residente",
        "Whether the destination state defines residency by domicile, by days of physical presence, or by a combination": "Se o estado de destino define residência por domicílio, por dias de presença física ou por uma combinação",
        "Whether the destination state has a tuition-equity or high-school-attendance provision that could apply, and what documentation it requires": "Se o estado de destino tem uma disposição de equidade de mensalidade ou de frequência ao ensino médio que possa se aplicar, e qual documentação ela exige",
        "Whether the destination state has a tuition-equity policy that may apply, and what documentation it requires": "Se o estado de destino tem uma política de equidade de mensalidade que pode se aplicar e qual documentação ela exige",
        "Whether the destination state has additional reporting or filling rules": "Se o estado de destino tem regras adicionais de notificação ou de aviamento",
        "Whether the destination state has different tax withholding forms": "Se o estado de destino tem formulários diferentes de retenção de imposto",
        "Whether the destination state has elected the CHIPRA option to cover lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals without a federal waiting period": "Se o estado de destino optou pela opção CHIPRA para cobrir lawfully residing children e gestantes sem período federal de espera",
        "Whether the destination state imposes a minimum remaining stay on the I-94 before issuing a credential": "Se o estado de destino impõe um tempo mínimo de permanência restante no I-94 antes de emitir uma credencial",
        "Whether the destination state offers a separate marked credential for some non-citizen applicants": "Se o estado de destino oferece uma credencial marcada à parte para alguns candidatos não cidadãos",
        "Whether the destination state offers any state-funded coverage for non-citizens who do not qualify for federal Medicaid": "Se o estado de destino oferece alguma cobertura financiada pelo estado para não cidadãos que não se qualificam ao Medicaid federal",
        "Whether the destination state offers any state-funded coverage for people not eligible for the federal marketplace": "Se o estado de destino oferece alguma cobertura financiada pelo estado para pessoas que não são elegíveis ao marketplace federal",
        "Whether the destination state offers any voting that is open to non-citizens (for example, certain local elections), and how that may interact with federal voter rolls": "Se o estado de destino oferece alguma votação aberta a não cidadãos (por exemplo, certas eleições locais) e como isso pode interagir com listas eleitorais federais",
        "Whether the destination state operates a non-FAFSA aid application for students who cannot file a FAFSA": "Se o estado de destino opera um pedido de auxílio que não usa o FAFSA, para estudantes que não podem enviar um FAFSA",
        "Whether the destination state operates state-funded SNAP, TANF, or cash-assistance programs that may apply during the federal waiting period": "Se o estado de destino opera programas estaduais de SNAP, TANF ou assistência em dinheiro que possam se aplicar durante o período federal de espera",
        "Whether the destination state participates in the Nurse Licensure Compact and how that interacts with non-citizen documentation": "Se o estado de destino participa do Nurse Licensure Compact e como isso interage com a documentação de não cidadão",
        "Whether the destination state recognizes your specific visa category as one that may establish a domicile for tuition purposes": "Se o estado de destino reconhece a sua categoria de visto específica como uma que pode estabelecer domicílio para fins de mensalidade",
        "Whether the destination state requires a Social Security card or an SSA ineligibility letter, and how the visa category interacts with SSN issuance timing": "Se o estado de destino exige cartão de Social Security ou carta de inelegibilidade da SSA, e como a categoria do visto interage com o cronograma de emissão do SSN",
        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace": "Se o estado de destino usa o HealthCare.gov ou opera o próprio marketplace estadual",
        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace with separate documentation rules": "Se o estado de destino usa o HealthCare.gov ou opera o próprio marketplace estadual com regras de documentação separadas",
        "Whether the destination state uses the CHIPRA/ICHIA option to remove the waiting period for children, pregnant people, or both": "Se o estado de destino usa a opção CHIPRA/ICHIA para retirar o período de espera para crianças, gestantes ou ambos",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV asks all applicants about voter registration, including non-citizens": "Se o DMV do estado de destino pergunta a todos os candidatos sobre registro eleitoral, inclusive não cidadãos",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV record reflects the new address on its own timeline": "Se o cadastro no DMV do estado de destino reflete o novo endereço no seu próprio cronograma",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV typically issues a credential to your visa category for the standard multi-year cycle or for a shortened cycle keyed to the I-94 or another federal document": "Se o DMV do estado de destino normalmente emite uma credencial para a sua categoria de visto pelo ciclo plurianual padrão ou por um ciclo encurtado, atrelado ao I-94 ou a outro documento federal",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV will issue a REAL ID to your specific visa category and which federal documents it requires": "Se o DMV do estado de destino emitirá um REAL ID para a sua categoria de visto específica e quais documentos federais ele exige",
        "Whether the destination-state board for your profession lists DACA recipients or lawful permanent residents in its documentation guidance": "Se o conselho do estado de destino para a sua profissão lista beneficiários do DACA ou LPRs em sua orientação documental",
        "Whether the destination-state board for your profession lists nonimmigrant visa categories or OPT or academic training in its documentation guidance": "Se o conselho do estado de destino para a sua profissão lista categorias de visto de não imigrante, OPT ou academic training na sua orientação documental",
        "Whether the destination-state license or ID application automatically initiates Selective Service registration": "Se o pedido de carteira ou ID do estado de destino inicia automaticamente o registro no Selective Service",
        "Whether the employer is filing a new LCA and an amended Form I-129 before or shortly after the worker reports to the new worksite": "Se o empregador está enviando uma nova LCA e um Formulário I-129 emendado antes ou pouco depois do trabalhador se apresentar no novo worksite",
        "Whether the employer or petitioner is filing an amended Form I-129 before the worker reports to the new location": "Se o empregador ou peticionário está enviando um Formulário I-129 emendado antes de o trabalhador se apresentar no novo local",
        "Whether the exception covers a specific person depends on age, current status, and continuity of valid nonimmigrant status, and a later transition to LPR or naturalization can revive a registration question relevant to federal benefits and naturalization.": "Se a exceção cobre uma pessoa específica depende da idade, da situação migratória atual e da continuidade da situação válida de não imigrante, e uma transição posterior para LPR ou para a naturalização pode reabrir uma questão de registro relevante para benefícios federais e para a naturalização.",
        "Whether the existing LCA needs to be posted at the new worksite for the required period": "Se a LCA atual precisa ser afixada no novo worksite pelo período exigido",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 address change has been filed within 10 days of the residential move": "Se a mudança de endereço federal AR-11 foi enviada em até 10 dias da mudança residencial",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 filing is also needed as a separate step": "Se o registro federal AR-11 também é necessário como etapa separada",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 filing is also needed in addition to sponsor notification": "Se o registro federal AR-11 também é necessário além da notificação ao sponsor",
        "Whether the institution you plan to attend sets its own classification rules in addition to any state policy": "Se a instituição em que você pretende estudar define regras próprias de classificação além de qualquer política estadual",
        "Whether the item is regulated by state law": "Se o item é regulamentado pela lei estadual",
        "Whether the license expiration is tied to the federal document expiration date": "Se o vencimento da carteira está vinculado à data de vencimento do documento federal",
        "Whether the medication is a controlled substance under federal or state law": "Se o medicamento é uma substância controlada pela lei federal ou estadual",
        "Whether the move triggers a special enrollment period and the documentation needed to verify status": "Se a mudança aciona um special enrollment period e qual a documentação necessária para conferir a situação migratória",
        "Whether the new employer's payroll setup reflects the exemption": "Se a configuração de folha de pagamento do novo empregador reflete a isenção",
        "Whether the new physical and mailing address has been entered in the SEVP Portal or reported to the DSO within 10 days": "Se o novo endereço físico e postal foi inserido no SEVP Portal ou reportado ao DSO em até 10 dias",
        "Whether the new worksite falls inside the MSA or area of intended employment listed on the current LCA": "Se o novo worksite cai dentro da MSA ou área de emprego pretendida listada na LCA atual",
        "Whether the new worksite is inside the same MSA or area of intended employment as the current LCA, or in a new MSA": "Se o novo worksite está dentro da mesma MSA ou área de emprego pretendida da LCA atual ou em uma nova MSA",
        "Whether the online change-of-address tool in a USCIS online account is the right path, or whether a paper Form AR-11 is needed": "Se a ferramenta on-line de mudança de endereço em uma conta on-line do USCIS é o caminho correto ou se é necessário um Formulário AR-11 em papel",
        "Whether the original L-1 or O-1 petition listed a specific worksite, employer location, or itinerary that the move changes": "Se a petição original L-1 ou O-1 listou um worksite, local do empregador ou itinerário específicos que a mudança altera",
        "Whether the person is within the age range to which the federal requirement may apply": "Se a pessoa está na faixa etária à qual a exigência federal pode se aplicar",
        "Whether the program start date and on-campus reporting deadline at the new school have been confirmed": "Se a data de início do programa e o prazo de comparecimento on-campus na nova escola foram confirmados",
        "Whether the tax year of the move includes both nonresident and resident periods for federal tax purposes": "Se o ano fiscal da mudança inclui períodos como nonresident e como resident para fins fiscais federais",
        "Whether the waiting period applies, whether a state option removes it for children or pregnancy, and which documents are accepted can change between origin and destination states and affect coverage continuity.": "Se o período de espera se aplica, se uma opção estadual o retira para crianças ou gestação e quais documentos são aceitos pode mudar entre estados de origem e de destino e afetar a continuidade da cobertura.",
        "Whether the worker still meets the IRS conditions for the F-1, J-1, M-1, or Q FICA exemption (status type, primary purpose, and federal tax residency)": "Se o trabalhador ainda atende às condições do IRS para a isenção de FICA em F-1, J-1, M-1 ou Q (tipo de situação migratória, propósito principal e residência fiscal federal)",
        "Whether their current nonimmigrant status is on the list described by the Selective Service System as covered by the exception": "Se a sua situação atual de não imigrante está na lista descrita pelo Selective Service System como coberta pela exceção",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney about how AR-11 interacts with a specific status": "Se deve consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado sobre como o AR-11 interage com uma situação migratória específica",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney about how registration history may interact with later filings": "Se deve consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado sobre como o histórico de registro pode interagir com pedidos posteriores",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney before submitting status documentation to the marketplace": "Se deve consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de enviar documentação de situação migratória ao marketplace",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer familiar with non-citizen federal tax issues before relying on a particular residency conclusion": "Se deve consultar um preparador de impostos familiarizado com questões fiscais federais de não cidadãos antes de confiar em uma conclusão específica sobre residência",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer or the employer's payroll team to verify FICA setup after the move": "Se deve consultar um preparador de impostos ou a equipe de folha de pagamento do empregador para conferir a configuração do FICA após a mudança",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer who handles dual-status filings": "Se deve consultar um preparador de impostos que lide com declarações em dual status",
        "Whether to consult employer counsel and a licensed immigration attorney before the worker starts at the new location": "Se deve consultar a equipe jurídica do empregador e um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de o trabalhador começar no novo local",
        "Whether to consult employer counsel before relying on intra-MSA treatment": "Se deve consultar a equipe jurídica do empregador antes de confiar no tratamento dentro da mesma MSA",
        "Whether to consult petitioner counsel and a licensed immigration attorney before the worker starts at the new location": "Se deve consultar a equipe jurídica do peticionário e um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de o trabalhador começar no novo local",
        "Whether to consult the DSO and a licensed immigration attorney before changing employers around an interstate move": "Se deve consultar o DSO e um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de trocar de empregador no entorno de uma mudança entre estados",
        "Whether to consult the DSO and a licensed immigration attorney before making decisions that affect the transfer timeline": "Se deve consultar o DSO e um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de tomar decisões que afetem o cronograma de transferência",
        "Whether to consult the destination-state Medicaid agency for current eligibility categories": "Se deve consultar o órgão estadual de Medicaid do destino para as categorias atuais de elegibilidade",
        "Whether to consult the responsible officer or alternate responsible officer at the sponsor and a licensed immigration attorney for category-specific guidance": "Se deve consultar o responsible officer ou o alternate responsible officer no sponsor e um advogado de imigração licenciado para orientação específica da categoria",
        "Whether to keep dated confirmations of each address update in case a later filing relies on it": "Se deve guardar confirmações datadas de cada atualização de endereço caso um pedido posterior dependa disso",
        "Whether translations or originals are required, and whether copies are accepted": "Se traduções ou originais são exigidos e se cópias são aceitas",
        "Whether you fall within a federal exception (for example, qualifying work history, certain humanitarian categories, or specific military-connected categories)": "Se você se enquadra em uma exceção federal (por exemplo, histórico de trabalho que qualifica, certas categorias humanitárias ou categorias específicas ligadas às forças armadas)",
        "Whether you fall within a federal exception to the five-year waiting period (for example, certain humanitarian categories, military-connected status, or qualifying work history)": "Se você se enquadra em uma exceção federal ao período de espera de cinco anos (por exemplo, certas categorias humanitárias, situação ligada às forças armadas ou histórico de trabalho que qualifica)",
        "Whether you fall within the federal age range and category that must register": "Se você se enquadra na faixa etária e categoria federal que deve se registrar",
        "Whether you may owe a part-year return in the origin state and another in the destination state for the year of the move": "Se você pode dever uma declaração de part-year no estado de origem e outra no estado de destino para o ano da mudança",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney about how Selective Service registration interacts with your specific status": "Se você deve consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado sobre como o registro no Selective Service interage com a sua situação migratória específica",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before signing any voter-related paperwork": "Se você deve consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de assinar qualquer papelada relacionada a voto",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before signing licensing attestations": "Se você deve consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de assinar declarações de licenciamento",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before submitting any marketplace documents related to status": "Se você deve consultar um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de enviar qualquer documento de situação migratória ao marketplace",
        "Whether you should consult a tax preparer familiar with nonresident alien filers in the destination state": "Se você deve consultar um preparador de impostos familiarizado com declarantes nonresident alien no estado de destino",
        "Whether you should consult a tax preparer who is familiar with non-citizen filers in the destination state": "Se você deve consultar um preparador de impostos familiarizado com declarantes não cidadãos no estado de destino",
        "Whether you should consult both the board and a licensed immigration attorney before signing licensing attestations": "Se você deve consultar tanto o conselho quanto um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de assinar declarações de licenciamento",
        "Whether you should consult both the financial-aid office and a licensed immigration attorney about how your status documentation will be used": "Se você deve consultar tanto o escritório de auxílio financeiro quanto um advogado de imigração licenciado sobre como a documentação da sua situação migratória será usada",
        "Whether you should consult both the registrar and a licensed immigration attorney about how your documentation may interact with classification": "Se você deve consultar tanto o registrar quanto um advogado de imigração licenciado sobre como a sua documentação pode interagir com a classificação",
        "Whether you should consult the registrar, your designated school official, and a licensed immigration attorney about how your documentation interacts with classification": "Se você deve consultar o registrar, o seu designated school official e um advogado de imigração licenciado sobre como a sua documentação interage com a classificação",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing a DMV renewal around a pending federal filing": "Se você deve consultar o seu designated school official, o contato de imigração do empregador ou um advogado de imigração licenciado sobre como programar uma renovação no DMV em torno de um pedido federal pendente",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing renewals around an extension or change of status": "Se você deve consultar o seu designated school official, o contato de imigração do empregador ou um advogado de imigração licenciado sobre como programar renovações em torno de uma extensão ou mudança de situação migratória",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney before applying": "Se você deve consultar o seu designated school official, o contato de imigração do empregador ou um advogado de imigração licenciado antes de se candidatar",
        "Whether you should speak with your prescriber or pharmacist": "Se você deve falar com seu prescritor ou farmacêutico",
        "Whether your EAD or permanent resident card is on the accepted-documents list": "Se o seu EAD ou permanent resident card está na lista de documentos aceitos",
        "Whether your EAD or permanent resident card is on the board's current accepted-documents list": "Se o seu EAD ou permanent resident card está na lista atual de documentos aceitos pelo conselho",
        "Whether your current immigration status is on the marketplace's current 'lawfully present' list": "Se a sua situação migratória atual está na lista atual de \"lawfully present\" do marketplace",
        "Whether your current license remains usable during a transition period": "Se sua carteira atual continua utilizável durante um período de transição",
        "Whether your current policy covers driving in the destination state": "Se sua apólice atual cobre dirigir no estado de destino",
        "Whether your employer needs an updated address": "Se seu empregador precisa de um endereço atualizado",
        "Whether your employer needs updated state tax forms": "Se seu empregador precisa de formulários atualizados de imposto estadual",
        "Whether your employer's state tax withholding should be updated after the move": "Se a retenção de imposto estadual do seu empregador deve ser atualizada após a mudança",
        "Whether your employer's state tax withholding should be updated after the move and which form is used": "Se a retenção de imposto estadual do seu empregador deve ser atualizada após a mudança e qual formulário é usado",
        "Whether your federal status document is on the destination-state DMV's accepted list for REAL ID": "Se o seu documento federal de situação migratória está na lista de aceitos do DMV do estado de destino para REAL ID",
        "Whether your health insurance network covers the destination state": "Se a rede do seu seguro de saúde cobre o estado de destino",
        "Whether your insurer requires you to update your policy address": "Se sua seguradora exige que você atualize o endereço da apólice",
        "Whether your license transfers via endorsement or reciprocity": "Se sua licença é transferida por endosso ou reciprocidade",
        "Whether your pharmacy can transfer the prescription": "Se sua farmácia pode transferir a prescrição",
        "Whether your specific school sets its own tuition-classification rules in addition to any state policy": "Se a sua escola define regras próprias de classificação de mensalidade além de qualquer política estadual",
        "Whether your visa documents (passport with visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, EAD) are on the accepted-documents list": "Se os seus documentos de visto (passaporte com visto, I-94, I-20 ou DS-2019, I-797, EAD) estão na lista de documentos aceitos",
        "Which documents the destination state Medicaid agency uses to verify status": "Quais documentos o órgão estadual de Medicaid do destino usa para conferir a situação migratória",
        "Which documents the destination-state agency uses to verify status": "Quais documentos o órgão do estado de destino usa para conferir a situação migratória",
        "Which factors apply (lease, employment, vehicle registration, voting, tax filing)": "Quais fatores se aplicam (contrato de aluguel, emprego, registro de veículo, voto, declaração de impostos)",
        "Which federal immigration documents (for example, EAD, permanent resident card, USCIS notices) the destination-state DMV currently lists as acceptable": "Quais documentos federais de imigração (por exemplo, EAD, permanent resident card, notificações do USCIS) o DMV do estado de destino atualmente lista como aceitáveis",
        "Which federal immigration documents the destination-state DMV currently lists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (for example, passport with visa stamp, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, employer support letter)": "Quais documentos federais de imigração o DMV do estado de destino atualmente lista para candidatos com visto de não imigrante (por exemplo, passaporte com carimbo de visto, I-94, I-20 ou DS-2019, I-797, carta de apoio do empregador)",
        "Which forms (1040, 1040-NR, and supporting statements) apply for a dual-status year": "Quais formulários (1040, 1040-NR e demonstrativos de apoio) se aplicam a um ano em dual status",
        "Withholding the wrong state's taxes can lead to filing complications and unexpected balances.": "Reter impostos do estado errado pode levar a complicações na declaração e a saldos inesperados.",
        "Working in a licensed profession before completing the destination state's licensing process may have regulatory consequences.": "Trabalhar em uma profissão licenciada antes de concluir o processo de licenciamento no estado de destino pode ter consequências regulatórias.",
        "Worth knowing about. Usually administrative or low-stakes to verify.": "Vale conhecer. Em geral administrativo ou de baixa importância para conferir.",
        "YOUR CHECKLIST": "SEU CHECKLIST",
        "Your selections aren't saved or shared. The checklist is generated locally.": "Suas seleções não são salvas nem compartilhadas. O checklist é gerado localmente.",
        "eCFR Part 62 covers J-1 Exchange Visitor Program regulations. Curl returned 200 but with an unblock.federalregister.gov redirect, consistent with an anti-bot challenge on a long-standing .gov resource; the canonical eCFR URL still resolves in a browser.": "O eCFR Part 62 cobre os regulamentos do programa J-1 Exchange Visitor. O curl retornou 200, mas com um redirecionamento a unblock.federalregister.gov, condizente com um desafio antibot em um recurso .gov de longa data; a URL canônica do eCFR ainda resolve em um navegador.",
        "eCFR section that describes J-1 sponsor and exchange-visitor notification obligations. Same eCFR anti-bot redirect observed.": "Seção do eCFR que descreve as obrigações de notificação do sponsor J-1 e do exchange visitor. O mesmo redirecionamento antibot do eCFR foi observado.",
    ]

    /// German (Deutsch) - formal Sie register.
    /// Generated 2026-05-19 / 2026-05-21.
    static let german: [String: String] = [
        "%1$@: %2$d topics": "%1$@: %2$d Themen",
        "%1$d of %2$d items verified": "%1$d von %2$d Einträgen geprüft",
        "%d item": "%d Eintrag",
        "%d items": "%d Einträge",
        "%d topic to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "%d Thema vor dem Umzug zu prüfen. Diese Checkliste ist keine rechtliche Schlussfolgerung.",
        "%d topics to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "%d Themen vor dem Umzug zu prüfen. Diese Checkliste ist keine rechtliche Schlussfolgerung.",
        "A first or last year in the United States, or a year that includes adjustment to LPR status, can involve different forms, allowable deductions, and treatment of foreign income than a standard resident or nonresident return.": "Ein erstes oder letztes Jahr in den Vereinigten Staaten oder ein Jahr, das die Anpassung an den LPR-Status beinhaltet, kann andere Formulare, zulässige Abzüge und Behandlung ausländischer Einkünfte als eine Standard-Resident- oder Nonresident-Steuererklärung beinhalten.",
        "A health plan that works at home may have limited in-network access in the destination state.": "Ein Gesundheitsplan, der zu Hause funktioniert, kann im Zielstaat einen begrenzten Netzwerkzugang haben.",
        "A household that was covered by a state-funded program in the origin state may not find an equivalent program at the destination, which can affect a move plan.": "Ein Haushalt, der im Herkunftsstaat durch ein landesfinanziertes Programm abgedeckt war, findet am Ziel möglicherweise kein gleichwertiges Programm, was sich auf den Umzugsplan auswirken kann.",
        "A missed AR-11 filing can disrupt USCIS notice delivery for any pending or future case, and may create a question of status maintenance that compounds with employer and school records that also need updating.": "Eine versäumte AR-11-Meldung kann die Zustellung von USCIS-Mitteilungen für jeden anhängigen oder zukünftigen Fall stören und kann eine Frage der Statuserhaltung aufwerfen, die sich mit Arbeitgeber- und Schulunterlagen, die ebenfalls aktualisiert werden müssen, summiert.",
        "A move part-way through a tax year can lead to part-year filings, multiple state filings, or unexpected withholding, and rules for non-citizens generally follow the same state framework as for citizens but documentation can differ.": "Ein Umzug mitten im Steuerjahr kann zu Teilzeit-Steuererklärungen, mehreren bundesstaatlichen Steuererklärungen oder unerwartetem Steuereinbehalt führen, und die Regeln für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft folgen im Allgemeinen demselben bundesstaatlichen Rahmen wie für Bürger, aber die Dokumentation kann sich unterscheiden.",
        "A move part-way through a tax year may produce part-year filings, multiple state filings, or unexpected withholding, and the interaction between federal nonresident alien treatment and state residency rules can change between origin and destination.": "Ein Umzug mitten im Steuerjahr kann zu Teilzeit-Steuererklärungen, mehreren bundesstaatlichen Steuererklärungen oder unerwartetem Steuereinbehalt führen, und das Zusammenwirken zwischen der bundesrechtlichen Nonresident-Alien-Behandlung und den bundesstaatlichen Ansässigkeitsregeln kann sich zwischen Herkunft und Ziel ändern.",
        "A move that triggers a fresh application in the destination state may produce a credential with a different renewal cycle than the prior state used, and timing renewal around an I-94 or visa extension can affect work, study, and travel logistics.": "Ein Umzug, der einen erneuten Antrag im Zielstaat auslöst, kann zu einem Ausweis mit einem anderen Verlängerungszyklus führen als dem, den der vorherige Bundesstaat verwendet hat, und das Timing der Verlängerung um eine I-94- oder Visumverlängerung kann sich auf Arbeit, Studium und Reiselogistik auswirken.",
        "A move that triggers loss of prior coverage may open a marketplace special enrollment period, and the eligibility framework for nonimmigrants can differ from Medicaid waiting-period rules. Federal rules in this area have been changing.": "Ein Umzug, der den Verlust der vorherigen Deckung auslöst, kann eine Marketplace-Sonder-Einschreibefrist eröffnen, und der Anspruchsberechtigungsrahmen für Nichteinwanderer kann sich von den Medicaid-Wartezeit-Regeln unterscheiden. Bundesrechtliche Regeln in diesem Bereich haben sich geändert.",
        "About": "Über die App",
        "About Dreamer status": "Über den Dreamer-Status",
        "About green card holder status": "Über den Green-Card-Inhaberstatus",
        "About visa-holder status": "Über den Status als Visuminhaber",
        "Administrative guidance only. Not medical advice.": "Nur administrative Hinweise. Keine medizinische Beratung.",
        "Administrative requirement": "Verwaltungsanforderung",
        "After a move that involves a new employer, payroll systems may default to withholding FICA, and a misclassification can take time to correct through the employer or via an IRS refund claim.": "Nach einem Umzug, der einen neuen Arbeitgeber beinhaltet, können Lohnabrechnungssysteme standardmäßig FICA einbehalten, und eine Fehlklassifizierung kann Zeit benötigen, um über den Arbeitgeber oder über einen IRS-Rückerstattungsantrag korrigiert zu werden.",
        "Agency rule": "Behördenvorschrift",
        "All": "Alle",
        "An F-1 student moving to another SEVP-certified school generally goes through a SEVIS record transfer between the current school's DSO and the new school's DSO, with a transfer release date, an initial reporting requirement at the new school, and a new Form I-20.": "Ein F-1-Student, der zu einer anderen SEVP-zertifizierten Schule wechselt, durchläuft im Allgemeinen eine SEVIS-Datenübertragung zwischen dem DSO der aktuellen Schule und dem DSO der neuen Schule, mit einem Transfer-Release-Datum, einer erstmaligen Meldepflicht an der neuen Schule und einem neuen Formular I-20.",
        "An interstate move during OPT or STEM OPT often coincides with an employer change, and missed reporting can affect both SEVIS standing and the running count of unemployment days, which is tracked at the federal level rather than by the destination state.": "Ein Umzug zwischen Bundesstaaten während des OPT oder STEM OPT fällt oft mit einem Arbeitgeberwechsel zusammen, und versäumte Meldungen können sowohl die SEVIS-Position als auch die laufende Zählung der Arbeitslosigkeitstage beeinträchtigen, die auf Bundesebene und nicht vom Zielstaat verfolgt werden.",
        "An outdated SEVIS address can interfere with notice delivery from SEVP or the program sponsor, and uncorrected records can place a SEVIS record at risk of termination, which can have downstream effects on status, work authorization, and travel.": "Eine veraltete SEVIS-Adresse kann die Zustellung von Mitteilungen von SEVP oder dem Programm-Sponsor stören, und unkorrigierte Einträge können einen SEVIS-Eintrag dem Risiko der Beendigung aussetzen, was nachgelagerte Auswirkungen auf den Status, die Arbeitserlaubnis und Reisen haben kann.",
        "Apartment or landlord pet policies": "Haustierregeln von Wohnung oder Vermieter",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements.": "Antragsverzögerungen, Ablehnungen oder erneute Fingerabdrücke können folgen, wenn die eingereichten Dokumente nicht den aktuellen Regeln der Behörde des Zielstaates entsprechen, insbesondere bei einem Umzug aus einem Bundesstaat mit anderen Anforderungen.",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements. Boards of Nursing also vary in how they treat the Nurse Licensure Compact for non-citizen primary state of residency.": "Antragsverzögerungen, Ablehnungen oder erneute Fingerabdrücke können folgen, wenn die eingereichten Dokumente nicht den aktuellen Regeln der Behörde des Zielstaates entsprechen, insbesondere bei einem Umzug aus einem Bundesstaat mit anderen Anforderungen. Boards of Nursing variieren auch darin, wie sie den Nurse Licensure Compact für den Hauptwohnsitz von Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft behandeln.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance and other tasks that rely on a state ID after a move.": "Eine Ankunft ohne die Dokumentenkombination, die das DMV des Zielstaates erwartet, kann die Ausstellung des Führerscheins und andere Aufgaben verzögern, die nach einem Umzug auf eine staatliche ID angewiesen sind.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance, which then delays other tasks that rely on a state credential after a move, including rental, employer onboarding, and school registration.": "Eine Ankunft ohne die Dokumentenkombination, die das DMV des Zielstaates erwartet, kann die Ausstellung des Führerscheins verzögern, was dann andere Aufgaben verzögert, die nach einem Umzug auf einen bundesstaatlichen Ausweis angewiesen sind, einschließlich Vermietung, Arbeitgeber-Onboarding und Schulanmeldung.",
        "Arriving without the right documents can delay your license and other tasks that depend on it.": "Eine Ankunft ohne die richtigen Dokumente kann Ihren Führerschein und andere davon abhängige Aufgaben verzögern.",
        "Assuming H-1B-style MSA logic for L-1 or O-1 can lead to a missed amendment when the original petition described a specific worksite or itinerary that no longer matches.": "Die Anwendung der H-1B-MSA-Logik auf L-1 oder O-1 anzunehmen, kann zu einer versäumten Änderung führen, wenn der ursprüngliche Antrag einen bestimmten Arbeitsort oder eine Reiseroute beschrieben hat, die nicht mehr übereinstimmt.",
        "Auto insurance": "Kfz-Versicherung",
        "Auto insurance minimums and rules differ by state. Insurers may need to update your policy after a move.": "Mindestdeckungen und Regeln für die Kfz-Versicherung unterscheiden sich je nach Bundesstaat. Versicherer müssen Ihre Police nach einem Umzug möglicherweise aktualisieren.",
        "Auto-detected: %@": "Automatisch erkannt: %@",
        "Awareness item": "Aufmerksamkeits-Eintrag",
        "Back to builder": "Zurück zum Ersteller",
        "Back to home": "Zurück zur Startseite",
        "Background check and fingerprinting requirements": "Anforderungen an Hintergrund-Checks und Fingerabdrücke",
        "Background check or fingerprinting requirements": "Anforderungen an Hintergrund-Checks oder Fingerabdrücke",
        "Based on your selected states and purpose, here are topics to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "Basierend auf Ihren ausgewählten Bundesstaaten und Ihrem Zweck finden Sie hier Themen, die vor dem Umzug zu prüfen sind. Diese Checkliste ist keine rechtliche Schlussfolgerung.",
        "Because the J-1 sponsor (not USCIS) controls the SEVIS record and may need Department of State approval for certain changes, a move can affect program compliance differently from H-1B or F-1 scenarios.": "Da der J-1-Sponsor (nicht USCIS) den SEVIS-Eintrag kontrolliert und für bestimmte Änderungen möglicherweise die Genehmigung des Department of State benötigt, kann ein Umzug die Programm-Compliance anders beeinflussen als H-1B- oder F-1-Szenarien.",
        "Beneficiary-facing CMS site on Medicare basics.": "An Leistungsempfänger gerichtete CMS-Website zu den Grundlagen von Medicare.",
        "Board of nursing requirements, compact licenses, clinical placement.": "Anforderungen der Pflegeaufsichtsbehörde, Compact-Lizenzen, klinische Praxisstellen.",
        "Boards of Nursing may have specific guidance about documentation for non-citizen applicants, including whether an SSN is required, whether an ITIN or attestation is accepted, how foreign education is evaluated, and how license endorsement works when moving from another state.": "Boards of Nursing können spezifische Anleitungen zur Dokumentation für Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft haben, einschließlich der Frage, ob eine SSN erforderlich ist, ob eine ITIN oder eidesstattliche Erklärung akzeptiert wird, wie ausländische Ausbildung bewertet wird und wie eine Lizenzempfehlung beim Umzug aus einem anderen Bundesstaat funktioniert.",
        "Breed or species restrictions (state, local, or housing-level)": "Rassen- oder Artbeschränkungen (auf bundesstaatlicher, lokaler oder Wohnungsebene)",
        "Build a state-to-state checklist for licenses, vehicles, housing, pets, work, school, healthcare licensure, and other rules that may change when you move.": "Erstellen Sie eine Checkliste von Bundesstaat zu Bundesstaat für Führerscheine, Fahrzeuge, Wohnen, Haustiere, Arbeit, Schule, Berufszulassungen im Gesundheitswesen und andere Regeln, die sich beim Umzug ändern können.",
        "Build checklist": "Checkliste erstellen",
        "Build my checklist": "Meine Checkliste erstellen",
        "Build your relocation checklist": "Erstellen Sie Ihre Umzugscheckliste",
        "Builder options": "Optionen des Erstellers",
        "CBP I-94 site for retrieving the most recent admission record.": "CBP I-94-Site zum Abruf des aktuellsten Einreiseeintrags.",
        "CHECKLIST BUILDER": "CHECKLISTEN-ERSTELLER",
        "CMS landing page on the federal and state marketplaces. Redirected from a cciio URL.": "CMS-Landingpage zu den bundesrechtlichen und bundesstaatlichen Marketplaces. Weitergeleitet von einer cciio-URL.",
        "CMS page summarizing Original Medicare eligibility, including the five-year continuous residency provision for lawfully admitted permanent residents.": "CMS-Seite, die die Anspruchsberechtigung für Original Medicare zusammenfasst, einschließlich der fünfjährigen Aufenthaltsbestimmung für rechtmäßig zum Daueraufenthalt zugelassene Personen.",
        "CMS press release on April 2026 guidance to implement statutory limits on federal Medicaid and CHIP funding for certain noncitizens, taking effect October 1, 2026, and noting the carve-out for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "CMS-Pressemitteilung zur Anleitung vom April 2026 zur Umsetzung gesetzlicher Grenzen für die bundesrechtliche Medicaid- und CHIP-Finanzierung bestimmter Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, mit Wirkung zum 1. Oktober 2026, und mit Hinweis auf die Ausnahme für rechtmäßig ansässige Kinder und Schwangere.",
        "CPR / BLS certification": "CPR-/BLS-Zertifizierung",
        "CROSS-STATE RELOCATION CHECKLIST": "CHECKLISTE FÜR DEN UMZUG ZWISCHEN BUNDESSTAATEN",
        "CUNY tuition and fee manual chapter on residency, covering nonimmigrant visa categories that may establish New York domicile and high-school-attendance provisions.": "CUNY-Studiengebühren- und -Gebührenhandbuch-Kapitel zum Wohnsitz, das Nichteinwanderungs-Visumkategorien, die einen New Yorker Domicile begründen können, und Highschool-Besuchsvorschriften abdeckt.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing applicant FAQ page covering documentation, SSN, and immigration-status questions.": "FAQ-Seite des California Board of Registered Nursing für Antragsteller, die Dokumentation, SSN und einwanderungsstatusbezogene Fragen abdeckt.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing page on international endorsement requirements, including credentials evaluation.": "Seite des California Board of Registered Nursing zu internationalen Endorsement-Anforderungen, einschließlich Qualifikationsbewertung.",
        "California DMV REAL ID page covering documentation for non-U.S. citizens, including how the credential expiration may track the underlying federal document.": "California DMV REAL ID-Seite, die die Dokumentation für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft behandelt, einschließlich der Art, wie das Ausweis-Ablaufdatum dem zugrunde liegenden bundesrechtlichen Dokument folgen kann.",
        "California FTB page on part-year and nonresident filers, including a note that California does not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "California FTB-Seite zu Part-Year- und Nonresident-Filern, einschließlich des Hinweises, dass California den bundesrechtlichen Einkommensteuerabkommens-Ausschlüssen nicht entspricht.",
        "California Franchise Tax Board page on residency, nonresidency, and part-year status for state income tax purposes.": "Seite des California Franchise Tax Board zu Resident-, Nonresident- und Part-Year-Status für die staatliche Einkommensteuer.",
        "Can cause inconvenience, fees, or compliance problems if ignored.": "Kann zu Unannehmlichkeiten, Gebühren oder Compliance-Problemen führen, wenn nicht beachtet.",
        "Categories": "Kategorien",
        "Categories where rules vary substantially. Verify directly with official sources.": "Kategorien, in denen sich die Regeln erheblich unterscheiden. Prüfen Sie direkt bei offiziellen Quellen.",
        "Check insurance networks, student health, and prescription transfer": "Versicherungsnetzwerke, Studentengesundheit und Rezeptübertragung prüfen",
        "Check pet vaccination, licensing, and housing rules": "Impf-, Lizenz- und Wohnregeln für Haustiere prüfen",
        "Check the destination state board of nursing requirements": "Anforderungen der Pflegeaufsichtsbehörde des Zielstaates prüfen",
        "Check whether a destination-state license application triggers Selective Service registration": "Prüfen, ob ein Führerscheinantrag im Zielstaat eine Selective-Service-Registrierung auslöst",
        "Check whether moving creates a state tax filing requirement": "Prüfen, ob ein Umzug eine bundesstaatliche Steuererklärungspflicht auslöst",
        "Check whether your professional license transfers": "Prüfen, ob Ihre Berufszulassung übertragen wird",
        "Checklist": "Checkliste",
        "Checklist builder": "Checklisten-Ersteller",
        "Choose your origin and destination state.": "Wählen Sie Ihren Herkunfts- und Zielstaat.",
        "Choose your origin and destination, your purpose, and the categories that apply. MoveSafe will generate a list of topics to verify before moving.": "Wählen Sie Ihren Herkunfts- und Zielstaat, Ihren Zweck und die zutreffenden Kategorien. MoveSafe erstellt eine Liste mit Themen, die vor dem Umzug zu prüfen sind.",
        "Choose your states, purpose, and categories. MoveSafe will assemble a source-linked checklist with risk badges.": "Wählen Sie Ihre Bundesstaaten, Ihren Zweck und Ihre Kategorien. MoveSafe stellt eine quellenverknüpfte Checkliste mit Risikohinweisen zusammen.",
        "Choosing the wrong credential type at the destination-state DMV can mean reapplying later, and document expiration may shorten the validity of a REAL ID issued to non-citizens.": "Die Wahl des falschen Ausweistyps beim DMV des Zielstaates kann bedeuten, dass Sie später einen erneuten Antrag stellen müssen, und das Ablaufdatum des Dokuments kann die Gültigkeit eines an Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft ausgestellten REAL ID verkürzen.",
        "Clears the verified state on items currently shown.": "Setzt den geprüften Status der derzeit angezeigten Einträge zurück.",
        "Clinical placement": "Klinische Praxisstelle",
        "Clinical sites and schools may require immunizations, drug screens, CPR/BLS, background checks, and other clearances separate from board licensure.": "Klinische Einrichtungen und Schulen können Impfungen, Drogentests, CPR/BLS, Hintergrund-Checks und andere Freigaben separat von der Behördenzulassung verlangen.",
        "Confirm clinical placement and school onboarding requirements": "Klinische Praxisstelle und Schul-Onboarding-Anforderungen bestätigen",
        "Confirm required documents for a destination-state license": "Erforderliche Dokumente für einen Führerschein im Zielstaat bestätigen",
        "Confirm school residency, insurance, and immunization rules": "Wohnsitz-, Versicherungs- und Impfregeln der Schule bestätigen",
        "Confirm your auto insurance covers the destination state": "Bestätigen, dass Ihre Kfz-Versicherung den Zielstaat abdeckt",
        "Continue my checklist": "Meine Checkliste fortsetzen",
        "Continuing education requirements": "Anforderungen an die Weiterbildung",
        "Continuity of coverage after a move depends on whether the destination state operates its own marketplace, which categories of non-citizens it considers, and whether state-funded coverage is offered to people who are not eligible for the federal marketplace.": "Die Kontinuität der Deckung nach einem Umzug hängt davon ab, ob der Zielstaat einen eigenen Marketplace betreibt, welche Kategorien von Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft er berücksichtigt und ob landesfinanzierte Deckung für Personen angeboten wird, die nicht für den bundesweiten Marketplace berechtigt sind.",
        "Could not generate checklist": "Checkliste konnte nicht erstellt werden",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page covering personal information updates.": "DHS Study in the States SEVIS Help Hub-Seite, die persönliche Informationsaktualisierungen behandelt.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on F-1 SEVIS transfer mechanics.": "DHS Study in the States SEVIS Help Hub-Seite zur Mechanik der F-1-SEVIS-Übertragung.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on STEM OPT.": "DHS Study in the States SEVIS Help Hub-Seite zu STEM OPT.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVP Portal help page describing OPT reporting.": "DHS Study in the States SEVP-Portal-Hilfeseite, die die OPT-Meldung beschreibt.",
        "DHS Study in the States blog post on the 10-day DSO reporting expectation.": "DHS Study in the States Blogbeitrag zur 10-tägigen DSO-Meldeerwartung.",
        "DHS Study in the States guidance for F-1 and M-1 students on reporting address changes to the designated school official within 10 days.": "DHS Study in the States-Anleitung für F-1- und M-1-Studenten zur Meldung von Adressänderungen an den Designated School Official innerhalb von 10 Tagen.",
        "DHS Study in the States post on SEVIS address-of-record.": "DHS Study in the States-Beitrag zur SEVIS-Adressdatei.",
        "DOL FLAG portal that handles LCA and other foreign-labor filings. The dol.gov subpages returned 403 to curl with Mozilla user-agent, consistent with anti-bot behavior on a long-standing .gov domain, so this canonical FLAG portal URL is used.": "DOL FLAG-Portal, das LCA und andere ausländische Arbeitsanträge bearbeitet. Die dol.gov-Unterseiten gaben mit dem Mozilla-User-Agent ein 403 an curl zurück, was mit Anti-Bot-Verhalten auf einer etablierten .gov-Domain übereinstimmt, sodass diese kanonische FLAG-Portal-URL verwendet wird.",
        "Decide your residency, eligibility, or tax status": "Über Ihren Wohnsitz, Ihre Anspruchsberechtigung oder Ihren Steuerstatus entscheiden",
        "Department of Homeland Security guidance for F-1 and M-1 students, and Department of State regulations for J-1 exchange visitors, generally require reporting an address change to a designated school official (DSO) or program sponsor within 10 days so the SEVIS record can be updated.": "Die Anleitung des Department of Homeland Security für F-1- und M-1-Studenten und die Vorschriften des Department of State für J-1-Austauschbesucher verlangen im Allgemeinen, dass eine Adressänderung innerhalb von 10 Tagen an einen designated school official (DSO) oder Programm-Sponsor gemeldet wird, damit der SEVIS-Eintrag aktualisiert werden kann.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA categories overview.": "Department of State BridgeUSA-Kategorienübersicht.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA landing page for the J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.": "Landingpage des Department of State BridgeUSA für das J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.",
        "Destination state": "Zielstaat",
        "Destination state DMV / MVA": "DMV / MVA des Zielstaates",
        "Destination state attorney general": "Generalstaatsanwalt des Zielstaates",
        "Destination state board of nursing": "Pflegeaufsichtsbehörde des Zielstaates",
        "Destination state department of agriculture": "Landwirtschaftsministerium des Zielstaates",
        "Destination state department of health": "Gesundheitsministerium des Zielstaates",
        "Destination state department of labor": "Arbeitsministerium des Zielstaates",
        "Destination state professional licensing": "Berufszulassung des Zielstaates",
        "Destination state tax agency": "Steuerbehörde des Zielstaates",
        "Destination-state minimum coverage requirements": "Mindestdeckungsanforderungen des Zielstaates",
        "Destination:": "Ziel:",
        "Determine whether a specific act is lawful": "Feststellen, ob eine bestimmte Handlung rechtmäßig ist",
        "Different agencies may apply different residency tests. The same person can be a resident for one purpose and not another.": "Verschiedene Behörden können unterschiedliche Wohnsitztests anwenden. Dieselbe Person kann für einen Zweck als Bewohner gelten und für einen anderen nicht.",
        "Direct users to confirm coverage with their insurer. Do not state whether coverage applies.": "Verweisen Sie die Nutzer darauf, die Deckung mit ihrem Versicherer zu bestätigen. Geben Sie nicht an, ob die Deckung greift.",
        "Disclaimer. %@": "Haftungsausschluss. %@",
        "Do not assert that any group is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID rules involve both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only.": "Behaupten Sie nicht, dass eine Gruppe in einem bestimmten Bundesstaat für REAL ID berechtigt ist oder nicht. REAL-ID-Regeln umfassen sowohl bundesstaatliche Mindestanforderungen als auch die bundesstaatliche Umsetzung, die sich ändern kann. Verwenden Sie nur die Formulierungen \"prüfen\" und \"kann variieren\".",
        "Do not assert that any specific state always uses a shortened renewal cycle for a given visa category. Frame as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Behaupten Sie nicht, dass ein bestimmter Bundesstaat für eine bestimmte Visumkategorie immer einen verkürzten Verlängerungszyklus verwendet. Formulieren Sie es als beim DMV des Zielstaates zu prüfende Punkte. Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not assert that any visa category is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID involves both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Behaupten Sie nicht, dass eine Visumkategorie in einem bestimmten Bundesstaat für REAL ID berechtigt ist oder nicht. REAL ID umfasst sowohl bundesrechtliche Mindestanforderungen als auch die bundesstaatliche Umsetzung, die sich ändern kann. Verwenden Sie nur die Formulierungen \"prüfen\" und \"kann variieren\" und befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not assume": "Gehen Sie nicht davon aus",
        "Do not assume a USPS or DMV address update satisfies the federal AR-11 step": "Gehen Sie nicht davon aus, dass eine USPS- oder DMV-Adressaktualisierung den bundesrechtlichen AR-11-Schritt erfüllt",
        "Do not assume regulated items follow the same rules across state lines": "Gehen Sie nicht davon aus, dass regulierte Gegenstände in allen Bundesstaaten denselben Regeln unterliegen",
        "Do not assume rules from your origin state apply. Rules vary across state, local, and federal jurisdictions. Verify directly with official sources.": "Gehen Sie nicht davon aus, dass die Regeln Ihres Herkunftsstaates gelten. Die Regeln unterscheiden sich je nach bundesstaatlicher, kommunaler und bundesrechtlicher Zuständigkeit. Prüfen Sie direkt bei offiziellen Quellen.",
        "Do not characterize voter registration by non-citizens using legal-conclusion or accusatory language. Use neutral framing such as 'generally not eligible' and 'may create immigration complications'. Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney. Do not give procedural advice for any specific state.": "Charakterisieren Sie die Wählerregistrierung von Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft nicht mit Worten, die einer rechtlichen Schlussfolgerung gleichkommen oder beschuldigend wirken. Verwenden Sie neutrale Formulierungen wie \"im Allgemeinen nicht berechtigt\" und \"kann Einwanderungskomplikationen verursachen\". Verweisen Sie die Leser darauf, einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren. Geben Sie keine Verfahrensanweisungen für einen bestimmten Bundesstaat.",
        "Do not characterize whether any visa category can establish residency in a specific state as a determination. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Charakterisieren Sie nicht, ob eine Visumkategorie in einem bestimmten Bundesstaat einen Wohnsitz als Feststellung begründen kann. Formulieren Sie es als Klassifizierungsregeln, die beim Schul-Registrar und der bundesstaatlichen Hochschulbehörde zu prüfen sind. Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not determine residency. List factors to verify. Direct to the relevant agency or school.": "Bestimmen Sie nicht den Wohnsitz. Nennen Sie zu prüfende Faktoren. Verweisen Sie auf die zuständige Behörde oder Schule.",
        "Do not determine that a household 'is' or 'is not' eligible for Medicaid. Frame as items to verify with the state Medicaid agency. Use 'may apply' and 'rules differ by jurisdiction'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Bestimmen Sie nicht, dass ein Haushalt für Medicaid \"berechtigt\" oder \"nicht berechtigt\" ist. Formulieren Sie es als bei der staatlichen Medicaid-Agentur zu prüfende Punkte. Verwenden Sie \"kann zutreffen\" und \"die Regeln unterscheiden sich je nach Zuständigkeit\". Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not list which states grant in-state tuition for DACA recipients. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency.": "Listen Sie nicht auf, welche Bundesstaaten DACA-Empfängern In-State-Studiengebühren gewähren. Formulieren Sie es als Klassifizierungsregeln, die beim Schul-Registrar und der bundesstaatlichen Hochschulbehörde zu prüfen sind.",
        "Do not provide a public-charge determination or say that using benefits 'will' or 'will not' affect immigration. Frame as 'may interact' and recommend consulting a licensed immigration attorney. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Geben Sie keine Public-Charge-Bestimmung ab und sagen Sie nicht, dass die Inanspruchnahme von Leistungen die Einwanderung \"beeinflussen wird\" oder \"nicht beeinflussen wird\". Formulieren Sie es als \"kann zusammenwirken\" und empfehlen Sie, einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren. Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not provide medical or transport instructions for controlled substances.": "Geben Sie keine medizinischen oder Transport-Anweisungen für kontrollierte Substanzen.",
        "Do not provide tactical instructions for transporting, possessing, hiding, storing, modifying, or avoiding enforcement for regulated items.": "Geben Sie keine taktischen Anweisungen zum Transport, Besitz, Verstecken, Lagern, Verändern oder zur Umgehung der Durchsetzung für regulierte Gegenstände.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to official tax agency and qualified professionals.": "Bieten Sie keine Steuerberatung. Verweisen Sie auf die offizielle Steuerbehörde und qualifizierte Fachleute.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to state tax agency or qualified tax professional.": "Bieten Sie keine Steuerberatung. Verweisen Sie auf die staatliche Steuerbehörde oder eine qualifizierte Steuerfachkraft.",
        "Do not say a Board of Nursing in a particular state grants or refuses an applicant's NCLEX path. Use 'verify with the destination Board of Nursing'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Sagen Sie nicht, ein Board of Nursing in einem bestimmten Bundesstaat gewährt oder verweigert den NCLEX-Weg eines Antragstellers. Verwenden Sie \"beim Board of Nursing am Zielort prüfen\". Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not say a particular aid program 'is open to' or 'is closed to' DACA recipients or LPRs. Use 'verify with the state aid agency and the school financial-aid office'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Sagen Sie nicht, dass ein bestimmtes Förderprogramm DACA-Empfängern oder LPRs \"offensteht\" oder \"verschlossen ist\". Verwenden Sie \"bei der staatlichen Förderagentur und dem Studienförderbüro der Schule prüfen\". Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not say a person 'can' or 'cannot' enroll. Use 'verify current eligibility categories with the marketplace operator' since federal rules have changed. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Sagen Sie nicht, dass eine Person sich einschreiben \"kann\" oder \"nicht kann\". Verwenden Sie \"aktuelle Anspruchsberechtigungskategorien beim Marketplace-Betreiber prüfen\", da sich die bundesrechtlichen Regeln geändert haben. Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency for a given visa category or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Geben Sie nicht an, wie ein bestimmter Bundesstaat den Wohnsitz für eine bestimmte Visumkategorie definiert oder dass jemand ein \"Bewohner\" ist. Formulieren Sie es als \"die Regeln unterscheiden sich je nach Zuständigkeit\" und \"bei der Steuerbehörde des Zielstaates prüfen\". Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Geben Sie nicht an, wie ein bestimmter Bundesstaat den Wohnsitz definiert oder dass jemand ein \"Bewohner\" ist. Formulieren Sie es als \"die Regeln unterscheiden sich je nach Zuständigkeit\" und \"bei der Steuerbehörde des Zielstaates prüfen\". Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license a given visa category. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine bestimmte Behörde eine bestimmte Visumkategorie zulässt oder nicht. Formulieren Sie alles als bei der Behörde des Zielstaates zu prüfende Punkte. Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license non-citizens. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine bestimmte Behörde Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft Lizenzen erteilt oder nicht. Formulieren Sie alles als bei der Behörde des Zielstaates zu prüfende Punkte. Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Frame as a federal requirement that 'may apply' depending on age and sex, with state implementation details to verify. Use neutral language and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine bestimmte Person sich registrieren muss oder nicht. Formulieren Sie es als bundesrechtliche Anforderung, die \"je nach Alter und Geschlecht zutreffen kann\", mit zu prüfenden bundesstaatlichen Umsetzungsdetails. Verwenden Sie eine neutrale Sprache und befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Do not state whether the user is eligible for licensure. Only identify requirements to verify.": "Geben Sie nicht an, ob der Nutzer für eine Zulassung berechtigt ist. Nennen Sie nur die zu prüfenden Anforderungen.",
        "Do not state which states do or do not issue licenses to a given group, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV.": "Geben Sie nicht an, welche Bundesstaaten Führerscheine an eine bestimmte Gruppe ausstellen oder nicht, und listen Sie keine spezifischen akzeptierten Dokumente auf. Formulieren Sie alles als beim DMV des Zielstaates zu prüfende Punkte.",
        "Do not state which states issue or do not issue licenses to a given visa category, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Geben Sie nicht an, welche Bundesstaaten an eine bestimmte Visumkategorie Führerscheine ausstellen oder nicht, und listen Sie keine spezifischen akzeptierten Dokumente auf. Formulieren Sie alles als beim DMV des Zielstaates zu prüfende Punkte. Befolgen Sie die SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Document lists accepted by state DMVs for non-citizen license or state-ID applicants can differ from those accepted for U.S. citizens, and accepted combinations may vary by jurisdiction.": "Die Listen der von bundesstaatlichen DMVs akzeptierten Dokumente für Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft für Führerscheine oder bundesstaatliche IDs können sich von denen für US-Bürger unterscheiden, und akzeptierte Kombinationen können je nach Zuständigkeit variieren.",
        "Done": "Fertig",
        "Driver's license": "Führerschein",
        "Driving across one or more state lines for travel.": "Fahrt über eine oder mehrere Staatsgrenzen zu Reisezwecken.",
        "Driving with coverage that does not meet destination-state minimums can create compliance and financial problems.": "Mit einer Deckung zu fahren, die die Mindestanforderungen des Zielstaates nicht erfüllt, kann Compliance- und finanzielle Probleme verursachen.",
        "Drug screen requirements": "Anforderungen an Drogentests",
        "Edit selections": "Auswahl bearbeiten",
        "Emissions testing requirement": "Pflicht zur Emissionsprüfung",
        "Employer policy": "Arbeitgeberrichtlinie",
        "Employment paperwork": "Arbeitsunterlagen",
        "Endorsement requirements if already licensed": "Empfehlungsanforderungen, wenn bereits zugelassen",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary permits, and continuing education requirements vary by state and profession.": "Empfehlung, Gegenseitigkeit, vorübergehende Genehmigungen und Anforderungen an die Weiterbildung variieren je nach Bundesstaat und Beruf.",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary practice, and continuing education.": "Empfehlung, Gegenseitigkeit, vorübergehende Berufsausübung und Weiterbildung.",
        "Establishing a new permanent residence in the destination state.": "Begründung eines neuen dauerhaften Wohnsitzes im Zielstaat.",
        "Eviction and late-fee rules": "Regeln zu Räumung und Säumniszuschlägen",
        "Example checklist categories": "Beispiel-Kategorien der Checkliste",
        "Exploring options. Receive a broad overview checklist.": "Optionen sondieren. Eine allgemeine Übersichts-Checkliste erhalten.",
        "F-1 OPT and STEM OPT specific. Use verify with the DSO and SEVP Portal guidance. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Do not advise on a specific status outcome.": "Speziell F-1 OPT und STEM OPT. Verwenden Sie \"beim DSO und der SEVP-Portal-Anleitung prüfen\". Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste (Formulierungen, die einer rechtlichen Schlussfolgerung gleichkommen, und Formulierungen zur Vermeidung von Sanktionen). Beraten Sie nicht zu einem spezifischen Statusausgang.",
        "F-1 specific. Frame as verify with both DSOs and reference Study in the States or ICE materials. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Speziell F-1. Formulieren Sie es als beim DSO beider Schulen zu prüfen und verweisen Sie auf Study-in-the-States- oder ICE-Materialien. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "F-1 students on post-completion OPT or a STEM OPT extension generally use the SEVP Portal or work with their DSO to update physical and mailing address, employer information, and other personal data, typically within 10 days of a change. Unemployment-day limits during OPT continue to apply during and after a move.": "F-1-Studenten in Post-Completion-OPT oder einer STEM-OPT-Verlängerung verwenden im Allgemeinen das SEVP-Portal oder arbeiten mit ihrem DSO zusammen, um physische und Postadressen, Arbeitgeberinformationen und andere persönliche Daten zu aktualisieren, in der Regel innerhalb von 10 Tagen nach einer Änderung. Die Grenzen der Arbeitslosigkeitstage während des OPT gelten weiter, auch während und nach einem Umzug.",
        "F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q specific. Frame as items to verify with IRS guidance and the employer. Do not state that a particular worker is exempt from FICA. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Speziell F-1, J-1, M-1 und Q. Formulieren Sie es als bei der IRS-Anleitung und dem Arbeitgeber zu prüfende Punkte. Geben Sie nicht an, dass ein bestimmter Arbeitnehmer von FICA befreit ist. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Factors that may affect residency for tuition, taxes, licensing, benefits.": "Faktoren, die den Wohnsitz für Studiengebühren, Steuern, Lizenzen und Leistungen beeinflussen können.",
        "Failing to register on time may affect eligibility for federal benefits, federal jobs, and naturalization later, even though the requirement is federal. State DMV workflows can also trigger automatic registration, which applicants should understand before applying.": "Eine nicht rechtzeitige Registrierung kann sich auf die Anspruchsberechtigung für Bundesleistungen, Bundesstellen und die spätere Einbürgerung auswirken, auch wenn die Anforderung eine bundesrechtliche ist. Die DMV-Arbeitsabläufe der Bundesstaaten können auch eine automatische Registrierung auslösen, was Antragsteller vor der Antragstellung verstehen sollten.",
        "Family move": "Familienumzug",
        "Federal HealthCare.gov guidance describes a list of immigration statuses considered lawfully present for purposes of the Affordable Care Act marketplace, which includes many common nonimmigrant categories. These categories can purchase coverage without a five-year waiting period that applies in many Medicaid contexts.": "Die bundesrechtliche HealthCare.gov-Anleitung beschreibt eine Liste von Einwanderungsstatus, die für die Zwecke des Affordable Care Act Marketplace als lawfully present gelten, einschließlich vieler gängiger Nichteinwanderungs-Kategorien. Diese Kategorien können Deckung ohne die fünfjährige Wartezeit kaufen, die in vielen Medicaid-Kontexten gilt.",
        "Federal Medicaid and CHIP rules generally include a five-year waiting period for many qualified non-citizens after obtaining qualified status, with several federal exceptions. States may use an option that removes the waiting period for children and pregnant people, and some states cover certain groups with state funds.": "Bundesrechtliche Medicaid- und CHIP-Regeln enthalten im Allgemeinen eine fünfjährige Wartezeit für viele qualifizierte Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft nach Erhalt des qualifizierenden Status, mit mehreren bundesrechtlichen Ausnahmen. Bundesstaaten können eine Option nutzen, die die Wartezeit für Kinder und Schwangere aufhebt, und einige Bundesstaaten decken bestimmte Gruppen mit Landesmitteln ab.",
        "Federal Medicare guidance generally describes eligibility for non-citizens who are lawfully admitted for permanent residence and have lived in the United States for five continuous years. Federal Medicaid rules for most nonimmigrants are narrower than for LPRs, with state-specific options for emergency Medicaid and for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "Die bundesrechtliche Medicare-Anleitung beschreibt im Allgemeinen die Anspruchsberechtigung für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, die rechtmäßig zum Daueraufenthalt zugelassen sind und seit fünf zusammenhängenden Jahren in den Vereinigten Staaten leben. Die bundesrechtlichen Medicaid-Regeln für die meisten Nichteinwanderer sind enger als für LPRs, mit bundesstaatsspezifischen Optionen für Notfall-Medicaid und für rechtmäßig ansässige Kinder und Schwangere.",
        "Federal REAL ID rules require evidence of lawful status, and many states issue a REAL ID to nonimmigrant visa holders only with an expiration date that does not extend past the I-94, the visa, or another underlying federal document. Implementation differs between states, and standard (non-REAL-ID) options may or may not be offered.": "Die bundesrechtlichen REAL-ID-Regeln verlangen Nachweise des rechtmäßigen Status, und viele Bundesstaaten stellen Inhabern nichteinwanderungsbezogener Visa nur dann ein REAL ID aus, wenn das Ablaufdatum nicht über die I-94, das Visum oder ein anderes zugrunde liegendes bundesrechtliches Dokument hinausgeht. Die Umsetzung unterscheidet sich zwischen den Bundesstaaten, und Standard-Optionen (kein REAL ID) werden möglicherweise angeboten oder nicht.",
        "Federal SNAP, TANF, and similar programs apply a waiting period to many qualified non-citizens. Some states use state funds to operate replacement or supplemental programs that cover groups not eligible for the federal program, with differing rules.": "Bundesweite SNAP-, TANF- und ähnliche Programme wenden bei vielen qualifizierten Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft eine Wartezeit an. Einige Bundesstaaten verwenden Landesmittel, um Ersatz- oder Ergänzungsprogramme zu betreiben, die Gruppen abdecken, die nicht für das Bundesprogramm berechtigt sind, mit unterschiedlichen Regeln.",
        "Federal law": "Bundesrecht",
        "Federal law (INA section 265) generally directs non-citizens to report a change of address to USCIS within 10 days of moving, typically through Form AR-11 or the USCIS online change-of-address tool. The federal filing is separate from updating a state DMV record, an employer, a school, or the U.S. Postal Service.": "Bundesrecht (INA Abschnitt 265) verlangt im Allgemeinen, dass Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft eine Adressänderung innerhalb von 10 Tagen nach dem Umzug an USCIS melden, typischerweise über das Formular AR-11 oder das Online-Tool von USCIS für Adressänderungen. Die bundesrechtliche Meldung ist getrennt von der Aktualisierung eines bundesstaatlichen DMV-Eintrags, eines Arbeitgebers, einer Schule oder des U.S. Postal Service.",
        "Federal law generally requires motor vehicle offices to offer voter registration to applicants, and forms are screened for citizenship attestations. Non-citizens generally are not eligible to register for federal elections, and a registration record can later create immigration complications.": "Bundesrecht verlangt im Allgemeinen, dass Kraftfahrzeugbehörden Antragstellern die Wählerregistrierung anbieten, und die Formulare werden auf Staatsbürgerschaftserklärungen geprüft. Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft sind im Allgemeinen nicht berechtigt, sich für Bundeswahlen zu registrieren, und ein Registrierungseintrag kann später zu Einwanderungskomplikationen führen.",
        "Federal residency for tax purposes determines whether worldwide income is reported, which IRS forms apply, and how an interstate move's first and last year are filed at the federal level, separately from state residency rules.": "Die bundesrechtliche Ansässigkeit für Steuerzwecke bestimmt, ob das weltweite Einkommen gemeldet wird, welche IRS-Formulare gelten und wie das erste und letzte Jahr eines Umzugs zwischen Bundesstaaten auf Bundesebene eingereicht wird, getrennt von den bundesstaatlichen Ansässigkeitsregeln.",
        "Federal rules govern which immigration statuses can purchase coverage and receive financial help through the Affordable Care Act marketplace, and those rules have changed. State-based marketplaces and state-funded programs add another layer that can differ between origin and destination.": "Bundesrechtliche Regeln bestimmen, welche Einwanderungsstatus Deckung kaufen und finanzielle Unterstützung über den Affordable Care Act Marketplace erhalten können, und diese Regeln haben sich geändert. Staatlich betriebene Marketplaces und landesfinanzierte Programme fügen eine weitere Ebene hinzu, die sich zwischen Herkunft und Ziel unterscheiden kann.",
        "Federal tax authority": "Bundesrechtliche Steuerbehörde",
        "Federal tax authority general guidance": "Allgemeine Anleitung der bundesrechtlichen Steuerbehörde",
        "Flags risk levels so you know where to focus": "Kennzeichnet Risikostufen, damit Sie wissen, worauf Sie sich konzentrieren sollten",
        "Florida Board of Governors page on residency for tuition purposes for the State University System. flbog.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Seite des Florida Board of Governors zum Wohnsitz für Studiengebührenzwecke für das State University System. flbog.edu gibt für Nicht-Browser-Anfragen 403 zurück (Cloudflare); dies ist ein bekanntes Falsch-Negativ.",
        "Florida FLHSMV documentation page for nonimmigrant applicants for driver licenses and identification cards.": "Florida FLHSMV-Dokumentationsseite für Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft für Führerscheine und Personalausweise.",
        "Follow device language": "Gerätesprache übernehmen",
        "For L-1, whether the new worksite is the same qualifying U.S. office described in the petition or a different one": "Für L-1, ob der neue Arbeitsort dasselbe qualifizierende US-Büro ist, das im Antrag beschrieben wurde, oder ein anderes",
        "For L-1A, L-1B, and O-1 status, USCIS treats a move to a new worksite as a material change in some fact patterns and not others, depending on what the original petition described and whether the new location is consistent with the approved terms. The analysis follows the underlying petition, not LCA-based MSA rules.": "Für L-1A-, L-1B- und O-1-Status behandelt USCIS einen Wechsel zu einem neuen Arbeitsort in einigen Sachlagen als wesentliche Änderung und in anderen nicht, abhängig davon, was der ursprüngliche Antrag beschrieben hat und ob der neue Standort mit den genehmigten Bedingungen übereinstimmt. Die Analyse folgt dem zugrunde liegenden Antrag, nicht den LCA-basierten MSA-Regeln.",
        "For O-1, whether the new venue, event, engagement, or agent arrangement falls within the approved petition scope": "Für O-1, ob der neue Veranstaltungsort, das Event, das Engagement oder die Agent-Vereinbarung in den Geltungsbereich des genehmigten Antrags fällt",
        "For federal tax purposes, a non-citizen is generally treated as a resident alien if they meet the Substantial Presence Test or hold lawful permanent resident status, with separate rules in IRS Publication 519 for exempt individuals (such as certain F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q students and scholars) whose days of presence may not count.": "Für bundesrechtliche Steuerzwecke wird eine Person ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft im Allgemeinen als Resident Alien behandelt, wenn sie den Substantial Presence Test erfüllt oder rechtmäßigen Daueraufenthaltsstatus hat, mit separaten Regeln in IRS Publication 519 für Exempt Individuals (wie bestimmte F-1-, J-1-, M-1- und Q-Studenten und -Wissenschaftler), deren Anwesenheitstage möglicherweise nicht zählen.",
        "For nursing specifically, how the destination state treats primary state of residency under the Nurse Licensure Compact for a non-citizen who declares either the country of origin or the compact state, and any credentials-evaluation requirement (for example, CGFNS) for internationally educated applicants": "Speziell für die Pflege, wie der Zielstaat den Hauptwohnsitz unter dem Nurse Licensure Compact für eine Person ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft behandelt, die entweder das Herkunftsland oder den Compact-Staat angibt, und etwaige Anforderungen zur Qualifikationsbewertung (z. B. CGFNS) für international ausgebildete Antragsteller",
        "Form AR-11 paper version posted on uscis.gov.": "Papierversion des Formulars AR-11, veröffentlicht auf uscis.gov.",
        "Frame AR-11 as a federal reporting step to verify, not a guarantee of status. Do not state that any specific status category is or is not covered without source. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing such as the i-word, the p-words, and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney for status-specific guidance.": "Formulieren Sie AR-11 als bundesrechtlichen Meldeschritt, der zu prüfen ist, nicht als Statusgarantie. Geben Sie nicht ohne Quelle an, dass eine bestimmte Statuskategorie abgedeckt ist oder nicht. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste (Formulierungen, die einer rechtlichen Schlussfolgerung gleichkommen, wie das i-Wort, die p-Wörter und Formulierungen zur Vermeidung von Sanktionen). Verweisen Sie die Leser darauf, einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt für statusspezifische Anleitung zu konsultieren.",
        "Frame as a federal requirement that may apply, with a nonimmigrant exception that may apply based on continuous valid status. Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Formulieren Sie es als bundesrechtliche Anforderung, die zutreffen kann, mit einer Nichteinwanderungs-Ausnahme, die je nach kontinuierlichem gültigen Status zutreffen kann. Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine bestimmte Person sich registrieren muss oder nicht. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Frame as items to verify in IRS Publication 519 and with a qualified tax preparer. Do not state a person is a dual-status filer for a particular year. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Formulieren Sie es als in IRS Publication 519 und bei einem qualifizierten Steuerberater zu prüfende Punkte. Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine Person für ein bestimmtes Jahr ein Dual-Status-Filer ist. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Frame as items to verify with CMS and the destination-state Medicaid agency. Federal rules have changed and may continue to change. Do not state a person is or is not eligible. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Formulieren Sie es als bei CMS und der Medicaid-Agentur des Zielstaates zu prüfende Punkte. Bundesrechtliche Regeln haben sich geändert und können sich weiter ändern. Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine Person berechtigt ist oder nicht. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Frame as items to verify with IRS Publication 519 and a tax preparer. Do not state a person is or is not a resident alien for federal tax purposes. Use may apply and rules differ by jurisdiction. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Formulieren Sie es als bei IRS Publication 519 und einem Steuerberater zu prüfende Punkte. Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine Person für bundesrechtliche Steuerzwecke ein Resident Alien ist oder nicht. Verwenden Sie \"kann zutreffen\" und \"die Regeln unterscheiden sich je nach Zuständigkeit\". Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Frame as items to verify with the DSO or J-1 sponsor and Study in the States or ICE guidance. This item is specific to F-1, M-1, and J-1 status. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "Formulieren Sie es als Punkte, die beim DSO oder J-1-Sponsor und der Study-in-the-States- oder ICE-Anleitung zu prüfen sind. Dieser Punkt gilt speziell für F-1-, M-1- und J-1-Status. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste (Formulierungen, die einer rechtlichen Schlussfolgerung gleichkommen, und Formulierungen zur Vermeidung von Sanktionen).",
        "Frame as items to verify with the current HealthCare.gov or state-based marketplace lists. Do not state any specific category is or is not on the lawfully present list, since federal rules have changed. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Formulieren Sie es als bei den aktuellen HealthCare.gov- oder staatlichen Marketplace-Listen zu prüfende Punkte. Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine bestimmte Kategorie auf der Lawfully-Present-Liste steht oder nicht, da sich die bundesrechtlichen Regeln geändert haben. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Full disclaimer:": "Vollständiger Haftungsausschluss:",
        "General information only. Not legal advice. Verify with official sources.": "Nur allgemeine Informationen. Keine Rechtsberatung. Bei offiziellen Quellen prüfen.",
        "General information only. Verify with the relevant official source. Not legal advice.": "Nur allgemeine Informationen. Prüfen Sie sie bei der jeweiligen offiziellen Quelle. Keine Rechtsberatung.",
        "Generate checklist": "Checkliste erstellen",
        "Generated:": "Erstellt:",
        "Generates a checklist of topics to verify before moving": "Erstellt eine Checkliste mit Themen, die vor dem Umzug zu prüfen sind",
        "Georgia Department of Driver Services page for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including a 30-day rule for establishing Georgia residency.": "Georgia Department of Driver Services-Seite für Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, einschließlich einer 30-Tage-Regel zur Begründung des Wohnsitzes in Georgia.",
        "Get a grouped checklist with risk badges and links to official sources.": "Erhalten Sie eine gruppierte Checkliste mit Risikohinweisen und Links zu offiziellen Quellen.",
        "H-1B specific. Frame as verify with employer counsel and USCIS or DOL guidance. Do not state that an amendment is or is not required in a particular fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Speziell H-1B. Formulieren Sie es als bei der Rechtsberatung des Arbeitgebers und der USCIS- oder DOL-Anleitung zu prüfen. Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine Änderung in einer bestimmten Sachlage erforderlich ist oder nicht. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "H-1B specific. Use verify whether MSA boundaries cover the new worksite. Do not assert that no amendment is needed in any specific fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Speziell H-1B. Verwenden Sie \"prüfen, ob die MSA-Grenzen den neuen Arbeitsort abdecken\". Behaupten Sie nicht, dass in einer bestimmten Sachlage keine Änderung erforderlich ist. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "HOW IT WORKS": "SO FUNKTIONIERT ES",
        "Health clearance documentation": "Dokumentation zur Gesundheitsfreigabe",
        "HealthCare.gov general page on immigrant coverage options.": "Allgemeine HealthCare.gov-Seite zu Deckungsoptionen für Einwanderer.",
        "HealthCare.gov list and explanation of lawfully present categories for ACA marketplace coverage.": "HealthCare.gov-Liste und Erklärung der lawfully present-Kategorien für ACA-Marketplace-Deckung.",
        "HealthCare.gov page on which statuses qualify for marketplace coverage.": "HealthCare.gov-Seite zu den Status, die für eine Marketplace-Deckung qualifizieren.",
        "Healthcare access / insurance": "Zugang zur Gesundheitsversorgung / Versicherung",
        "Help avoid enforcement or recommend workarounds": "Bei der Vermeidung von Vollzugsmaßnahmen helfen oder Umgehungen empfehlen",
        "Helps tailor the checklist. None of these flags create legal conclusions.": "Hilft dabei, die Checkliste anzupassen. Keines dieser Merkmale erzeugt rechtliche Schlussfolgerungen.",
        "High risk only": "Nur hohes Risiko",
        "High-risk categories require separate verification.": "Hochrisiko-Kategorien erfordern eine gesonderte Prüfung.",
        "High-risk categories require separate verification. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use of regulated items is lawful.": "Hochrisiko-Kategorien erfordern eine gesonderte Prüfung. MoveSafe entscheidet nicht, ob der Besitz, Transport oder die Verwendung regulierter Gegenstände rechtmäßig ist.",
        "High-risk items to verify separately": "Hochrisiko-Punkte gesondert zu prüfen",
        "High-risk only": "Nur hohes Risiko",
        "High-risk warning. High-risk categories require separate verification.": "Hochrisiko-Warnung. Hochrisiko-Kategorien erfordern eine gesonderte Prüfung.",
        "Highlights stale or placeholder sources": "Hebt veraltete oder Platzhalter-Quellen hervor",
        "Housing / renter basics": "Grundlagen zu Wohnen / Miete",
        "How CHIP coverage rules in the destination state interact with the waiting period for your household": "Wie die CHIP-Deckungsregeln des Zielstaates mit der Wartezeit für Ihren Haushalt zusammenwirken",
        "How OPT or STEM OPT employment is treated for FICA while the worker remains a nonresident alien": "Wie OPT- oder STEM-OPT-Beschäftigung für FICA behandelt wird, während der Arbeitnehmer Nonresident Alien bleibt",
        "How a future change to LPR status before age 26 may affect the registration question": "Wie sich eine zukünftige Änderung zum LPR-Status vor dem 26. Lebensjahr auf die Registrierungsfrage auswirken kann",
        "How a mid-year move between states may affect aid-application deadlines": "Wie sich ein Umzug zwischen Bundesstaaten in der Mitte des Jahres auf Antragsfristen für Förderungen auswirken kann",
        "How a move mid-coverage may affect the reasonable opportunity period for documentation": "Wie sich ein Umzug während des Deckungszeitraums auf die angemessene Frist zur Vorlage von Dokumenten auswirken kann",
        "How a transfer interacts with current employment authorization, on-campus work, and any pending OPT": "Wie sich eine Übertragung auf die aktuelle Arbeitserlaubnis, die Arbeit auf dem Campus und ein anhängiges OPT auswirkt",
        "How a year of arrival to or departure from the United States interacts with the test": "Wie sich ein Jahr der Einreise in die oder der Ausreise aus den Vereinigten Staaten auf den Test auswirkt",
        "How an in-progress extension of status (for example, an H-1B amendment or an F-1 transfer) interacts with renewing or replacing the credential": "Wie eine laufende Statusverlängerung (z. B. eine H-1B-Änderung oder ein F-1-Transfer) mit der Verlängerung oder dem Ersatz des Ausweises zusammenwirkt",
        "How clinical-placement and background-check requirements interact with your immigration status": "Wie die Anforderungen an klinische Praxisstellen und Hintergrund-Checks mit Ihrem Einwanderungsstatus zusammenwirken",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification": "Wie lange Sie den Wohnsitz im Zielstaat behalten müssen, bevor Sie für eine In-State-Klassifizierung berücksichtigt werden",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification, and whether time on a nonimmigrant visa counts": "Wie lange Sie den Wohnsitz im Zielstaat behalten müssen, bevor Sie für eine In-State-Klassifizierung berücksichtigt werden, und ob die Zeit mit einem Nichteinwanderungsvisum zählt",
        "How temporary stay is treated differently from permanent relocation": "Wie ein vorübergehender Aufenthalt anders behandelt wird als ein dauerhafter Umzug",
        "How the destination state defines residency": "Wie der Zielstaat den Wohnsitz definiert",
        "How the destination state's DMV or other application workflows interact with Selective Service screening": "Wie die DMV- oder andere Antragsabläufe des Zielstaates mit dem Selective-Service-Screening zusammenwirken",
        "How the move affects any STEM OPT Form I-983 training plan and the destination employer's E-Verify status": "Wie sich der Umzug auf einen STEM-OPT-Trainingsplan nach Formular I-983 und auf den E-Verify-Status des Zielarbeitgebers auswirkt",
        "How the move and any change in employer-sponsored coverage interact with marketplace special enrollment timing": "Wie der Umzug und eine Änderung der arbeitgeberfinanzierten Deckung mit dem Timing der Marketplace-Sonder-Einschreibung zusammenwirken",
        "How the move interacts with H-4 dependent status and any pending I-485 or I-140": "Wie sich der Umzug auf den H-4-Familienangehörigenstatus und eine anhängige I-485 oder I-140 auswirkt",
        "How to confirm a registration after applying for a license": "Wie eine Registrierung nach der Beantragung eines Führerscheins zu bestätigen ist",
        "How to correct the record if a non-citizen registration was submitted in error": "Wie der Eintrag zu korrigieren ist, falls eine Registrierung einer Person ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft irrtümlich eingereicht wurde",
        "How to decline voter registration when offered at the DMV in that state": "Wie Sie die Wählerregistrierung ablehnen können, wenn sie beim DMV in diesem Bundesstaat angeboten wird",
        "How to obtain or replace a Selective Service registration record if needed for future immigration or federal-benefit filings": "Wie ein Selective-Service-Registrierungseintrag zu erhalten oder zu ersetzen ist, falls für zukünftige Einwanderungs- oder Bundesleistungsanträge benötigt",
        "How unemployment days are counted during a gap between employers around a move": "Wie Arbeitslosigkeitstage während einer Lücke zwischen Arbeitgebern rund um einen Umzug gezählt werden",
        "I am a nursing or healthcare student": "Ich bin Pflege- oder Gesundheitsstudent",
        "I am moving for school": "Ich ziehe wegen der Schule um",
        "I am moving for work": "Ich ziehe wegen der Arbeit um",
        "I have a car": "Ich habe ein Auto",
        "I hold or need a professional license": "Ich besitze oder benötige eine Berufszulassung",
        "I may stay temporarily": "Ich bleibe möglicherweise vorübergehend",
        "I may work in the destination state": "Ich werde möglicherweise im Zielstaat arbeiten",
        "I own a pet": "Ich habe ein Haustier",
        "I plan to relocate permanently": "Ich plane einen dauerhaften Umzug",
        "I rent housing": "Ich miete eine Wohnung",
        "I understand": "Ich verstehe",
        "I understand that MoveSafe provides general information and source links, not legal advice.": "Ich verstehe, dass MoveSafe allgemeine Informationen und Quellenlinks bereitstellt, jedoch keine Rechtsberatung.",
        "I'm a Dreamer (DACA / similar)": "Ich bin ein Dreamer (DACA / ähnlich)",
        "I'm a green card holder (LPR)": "Ich bin Green-Card-Inhaber (LPR)",
        "I'm on a nonimmigrant visa (F-1, H-1B, J-1, etc.)": "Ich habe ein nichteinwanderungsbezogenes Visum (F-1, H-1B, J-1 usw.)",
        "ICE SEVIS landing page.": "ICE SEVIS-Landingpage.",
        "ICE SEVIS overview page for background context on F, M, and J record management.": "ICE SEVIS-Übersichtsseite für Hintergrundkontext zur F-, M- und J-Datenverwaltung.",
        "ICE page describing F-1 SEVIS transfers.": "ICE-Seite, die F-1-SEVIS-Übertragungen beschreibt.",
        "IRS Publication 519 describes a dual-status tax year for non-citizens who are both a nonresident and a resident for federal tax purposes during the same year, which can apply to many arrival, departure, and adjustment-of-status fact patterns rather than interstate moves alone.": "IRS Publication 519 beschreibt ein Dual-Status-Steuerjahr für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, die im selben Jahr sowohl Nonresident als auch Resident für bundesrechtliche Steuerzwecke sind, was auf viele Sachlagen von Einreise, Ausreise und Anpassung des Status zutreffen kann, anstatt nur auf Umzüge zwischen Bundesstaaten.",
        "IRS Publication 519 main page.": "Hauptseite von IRS Publication 519.",
        "IRS dual-status filer page. Final redirected URL uses the dual-status-individuals slug.": "IRS-Seite für Dual-Status-Filer. Die finale weitergeleitete URL verwendet den Slug dual-status-individuals.",
        "IRS general page on taxation of nonresident aliens.": "Allgemeine IRS-Seite zur Besteuerung von Nonresident Aliens.",
        "IRS guidance generally describes an exemption from FICA tax for wages paid for services performed by F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q nonresident-alien students, scholars, teachers, researchers, and trainees, when the work is part of the activity for which they were admitted and they remain nonresident aliens for federal tax purposes.": "Die IRS-Anleitung beschreibt im Allgemeinen eine Befreiung von der FICA-Steuer für Löhne, die für Dienstleistungen von F-1-, J-1-, M-1- und Q-Nonresident-Alien-Studenten, -Wissenschaftlern, -Lehrern, -Forschern und -Praktikanten gezahlt werden, wenn die Arbeit Teil der Tätigkeit ist, für die sie zugelassen wurden, und sie für bundesrechtliche Steuerzwecke weiterhin Nonresident Aliens bleiben.",
        "IRS overview page for non-citizen tax residency status.": "IRS-Übersichtsseite für den Steueransässigkeitsstatus von Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft.",
        "IRS page describing the Substantial Presence Test for federal tax residency.": "IRS-Seite, die den Substantial Presence Test für die bundesrechtliche Steueransässigkeit beschreibt.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for F, J, M, Q nonresident-alien students and scholars.": "IRS-Seite zur FICA-Steuerbehandlung für F-, J-, M-, Q-Nonresident-Alien-Studenten und -Wissenschaftler.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for non-citizens employed in the U.S.": "IRS-Seite zur FICA-Steuerbehandlung für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, die in den USA beschäftigt sind.",
        "Identity and residency documents accepted by the destination state": "Vom Zielstaat akzeptierte Identitäts- und Wohnsitzdokumente",
        "If a credential is issued with an unexpected short term tied to a federal document, the timing of renewal can affect domestic flights, federal building access, and other tasks that may rely on a REAL ID after a move.": "Wenn ein Ausweis mit einer unerwartet kurzen Laufzeit ausgestellt wird, die an ein bundesrechtliches Dokument gekoppelt ist, kann das Timing der Verlängerung Inlandsflüge, den Zutritt zu Bundesgebäuden und andere Aufgaben beeinflussen, die nach einem Umzug auf ein REAL ID angewiesen sein können.",
        "Illinois Board of Higher Education directory page on campus liaisons supporting students under state tuition-equity provisions.": "Seite des Illinois Board of Higher Education zum Verzeichnis der Campus-Ansprechpartner, die Studierende unter bundesstaatlichen Tuition-Equity-Vorschriften unterstützen.",
        "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL) page. ilsos.gov returns a 302 redirect to its own page for curl HEAD requests, which is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov domain; the URL was confirmed via the Secretary of State's own search index.": "Seite des Illinois Secretary of State zum Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL). ilsos.gov gibt für curl-HEAD-Anfragen eine 302-Weiterleitung auf seine eigene Seite zurück, was ein bekanntes Falsch-Negativ auf der etablierten .gov-Domain ist; die URL wurde über den Suchindex des Secretary of State bestätigt.",
        "Illinois Student Assistance Commission resources page for non-U.S. citizen students including RISE Act and Alternative Application context. isac.org returns 403 to non-browser requests (anti-bot); this is a known false negative.": "Ressourcenseite der Illinois Student Assistance Commission für Studierende ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, einschließlich Kontext zum RISE Act und zur Alternativen Bewerbung. isac.org gibt für Nicht-Browser-Anfragen 403 zurück (Anti-Bot); dies ist ein bekanntes Falsch-Negativ.",
        "Immigration status - including Dreamer / DACA status - can significantly affect driver's licenses and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing and healthcare), in-state tuition, SSN-related requirements, and state tax filing. Rules vary by state and federal law and change frequently.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney before relying on any state-by-state summary.": "Der Einwanderungsstatus - einschließlich des Dreamer-/DACA-Status - kann sich erheblich auf Führerscheine und REAL ID, Berufszulassungen (insbesondere in der Pflege und im Gesundheitswesen), die Studiengebühren für staatliche Bewohner, SSN-bezogene Anforderungen und die staatliche Steuererklärung auswirken. Die Regeln unterscheiden sich je nach Bundesstaat und Bundesgesetz und ändern sich häufig.\n\nMoveSafe ist kein Ersatz für rechtlichen Beistand. Erwägen Sie, einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren, bevor Sie sich auf eine bundesstaatliche Übersicht verlassen.",
        "Immunization requirements": "Impfanforderungen",
        "Important to verify": "Wichtig zu prüfen",
        "Inspection requirement": "Inspektionspflicht",
        "Insurance networks, Medicaid and marketplace rules, and prescription transfer processes vary by state.": "Versicherungsnetzwerke, Medicaid- und Marketplace-Regeln sowie Verfahren zur Rezeptübertragung variieren je nach Bundesstaat.",
        "Insurance networks, student health, prescriptions, primary care access.": "Versicherungsnetzwerke, Studentengesundheit, Rezepte, Zugang zur Primärversorgung.",
        "Internship": "Praktikum",
        "J-1 specific. Frame as verify with the program sponsor and reference 22 CFR Part 62. Do not state that any specific category does or does not require sponsor pre-approval for a particular change. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Speziell J-1. Formulieren Sie es als beim Programm-Sponsor zu prüfen und verweisen Sie auf 22 CFR Part 62. Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine bestimmte Kategorie eine vorherige Sponsor-Genehmigung für eine bestimmte Änderung erfordert oder nicht. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Jurisdiction: %@": "Zuständigkeit: %@",
        "Know how to respond if asked to register to vote at the DMV": "Wissen, wie Sie reagieren, wenn Sie beim DMV gebeten werden, sich zur Wahl zu registrieren",
        "L-1 and O-1 specific. Frame as verify against the approved petition and consult petitioner counsel. Do not state that an amendment is or is not needed for any specific scenario. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Speziell L-1 und O-1. Formulieren Sie es als anhand des genehmigten Antrags zu prüfen und die Rechtsberatung des Antragstellers zu konsultieren. Geben Sie nicht an, dass eine Änderung für ein bestimmtes Szenario erforderlich ist oder nicht. Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste.",
        "Language": "Sprache",
        "Last verified:": "Zuletzt geprüft:",
        "Last verified: %@": "Zuletzt geprüft: %@",
        "Lawful permanent residents (LPRs / green card holders) can face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing - foreign credentials evaluation may apply), Medicaid and state-marketplace eligibility (the federal 5-year bar interacts with state programs), state tax filing, and how DMVs handle voter-registration prompts (LPRs are not eligible to vote in federal or most state elections).\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney for status-affecting questions and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Rechtmäßige Daueraufenthaltsberechtigte (LPRs / Green-Card-Inhaber) können bundesstaatliche Unterschiede bei Führerscheindokumenten und REAL ID erleben, bei Berufszulassungen (insbesondere in der Pflege - eine Bewertung ausländischer Qualifikationen kann zutreffen), bei der Anspruchsberechtigung für Medicaid und den staatlichen Marketplace (das bundesstaatliche 5-Jahres-Verbot wirkt mit staatlichen Programmen zusammen), bei der staatlichen Steuererklärung und bei der Art, wie DMVs Aufforderungen zur Wählerregistrierung handhaben (LPRs sind nicht berechtigt, an Bundes- oder den meisten bundesstaatlichen Wahlen teilzunehmen).\n\nMoveSafe ist kein Ersatz für rechtlichen Beistand. Erwägen Sie, einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt für statusrelevante Fragen und eine qualifizierte Steuerfachkraft für die staatenübergreifende Steuererklärung zu konsultieren.",
        "Lease decisions made based on origin-state assumptions may not match destination-state rules.": "Mietentscheidungen, die auf Annahmen des Herkunftsstaates beruhen, entsprechen möglicherweise nicht den Regeln des Zielstaates.",
        "Lease terms, security deposits, notice periods, and tenant protections.": "Mietbedingungen, Kautionen, Kündigungsfristen und Mieterschutzregeln.",
        "Legal aid (general info)": "Rechtshilfe (allgemeine Informationen)",
        "License transfer, deadlines, documents, and REAL ID awareness.": "Führerscheinübertragung, Fristen, Dokumente und Hinweise zu REAL ID.",
        "Licensure requirements can affect clinical placement, NCLEX eligibility, endorsement, and employment timing.": "Zulassungsanforderungen können sich auf klinische Praxisstellen, die NCLEX-Berechtigung, Empfehlungen und den Beschäftigungsbeginn auswirken.",
        "Links to official state agency sources": "Verweist auf offizielle Quellen staatlicher Behörden",
        "Load example": "Beispiel laden",
        "Local city/county rules may add protections. Review lease language directly.": "Lokale Stadt-/Bezirksregeln können zusätzliche Schutzregeln vorsehen. Überprüfen Sie den Mietvertragstext direkt.",
        "Local ordinance": "Kommunale Verordnung",
        "Local pet licensing requirements": "Lokale Anforderungen an die Haustierlizenzierung",
        "Main USCIS page for H-1B specialty occupations classification.": "Haupt-USCIS-Seite zur H-1B Specialty Occupations Klassifizierung.",
        "Many nonimmigrant visa holders are not within the standard Medicare or Medicaid eligibility groups, and federal rules in this area have been changing. Destination-state Medicaid rules add another layer that may differ from origin-state rules.": "Viele Inhaber nichteinwanderungsbezogener Visa fallen nicht in die Standard-Anspruchsgruppen für Medicare oder Medicaid, und die bundesrechtlichen Regeln in diesem Bereich haben sich geändert. Die Medicaid-Regeln des Zielstaates fügen eine weitere Ebene hinzu, die sich von den Regeln des Herkunftsstaates unterscheiden kann.",
        "Many states require new residents to obtain a state driver's license within a specific period after becoming a resident.": "Viele Bundesstaaten verlangen von neuen Bewohnern, innerhalb einer bestimmten Frist nach Begründung des Wohnsitzes einen staatlichen Führerschein zu erwerben.",
        "Mark as not verified": "Als nicht geprüft markieren",
        "Mark as verified": "Als geprüft markieren",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for nonresidents using Form 1-NR/PY. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Leitfaden des Massachusetts Department of Revenue zur persönlichen Einkommensteuer für Nonresidents mit Formular 1-NR/PY. mass.gov gibt für Nicht-Browser-Anfragen 403 zurück (Cloudflare); dies ist ein bekanntes Falsch-Negativ.",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for part-year residents. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Leitfaden des Massachusetts Department of Revenue zur persönlichen Einkommensteuer für Part-Year-Residents. mass.gov gibt für Nicht-Browser-Anfragen 403 zurück (Cloudflare); dies ist ein bekanntes Falsch-Negativ.",
        "Massachusetts RMV identification requirements page covering REAL ID, standard licenses, and lawful presence documentation. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov-hosted state portal.": "Massachusetts RMV-Seite zu Identifikationsanforderungen, die REAL ID, Standard-Führerscheine und Dokumentation des rechtmäßigen Aufenthalts abdeckt. mass.gov gibt für Nicht-Browser-Anfragen 403 zurück (Cloudflare); dies ist ein bekanntes Falsch-Negativ auf dem etablierten .gov-gehosteten Bundesstaats-Portal.",
        "May involve penalties or licensing consequences.": "Kann Sanktionen oder Folgen für die Berufszulassung beinhalten.",
        "Minimum coverage, state-specific rules, and policy address updates.": "Mindestdeckung, bundesstaatsspezifische Regeln und Aktualisierung der Adresse in der Police.",
        "Missing a school or hospital onboarding requirement can delay clinical hours and graduation timing.": "Das Verpassen einer Schul- oder Krankenhaus-Onboarding-Anforderung kann klinische Stunden und den Abschlusszeitpunkt verzögern.",
        "Missing a state motor vehicle deadline can create administrative or driving-related problems after relocation.": "Das Verpassen einer Kraftfahrzeugfrist im Bundesstaat kann nach dem Umzug zu administrativen oder fahrbezogenen Problemen führen.",
        "Missing source": "Fehlende Quelle",
        "Missing the transfer reporting steps at the new school, or letting the transfer release date and program start fall out of sync, can affect status maintenance and access to on-campus work.": "Das Verpassen der Meldeschritte zur Übertragung an der neuen Schule oder das Auseinanderlaufen des Transfer-Release-Datums und des Programmstarts kann die Statuserhaltung und den Zugang zur Arbeit auf dem Campus beeinträchtigen.",
        "Mixed jurisdiction": "Gemischte Zuständigkeit",
        "MoveSafe checklist": "MoveSafe Checkliste",
        "MoveSafe is a source-first checklist tool. It links you to official resources and highlights topics to verify. It does not provide legal advice.": "MoveSafe ist ein quellenbasiertes Checklisten-Tool. Es verweist Sie auf offizielle Ressourcen und hebt Themen hervor, die Sie prüfen sollten. Es bietet keine Rechtsberatung.",
        "MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves. You can still build a checklist, but some items may not apply.": "MoveSafe ist für Umzüge zwischen US-Bundesstaaten konzipiert. Sie können dennoch eine Checkliste erstellen, aber einige Punkte sind möglicherweise nicht zutreffend.",
        "MoveSafe prefers official agency sources. Placeholder entries should be replaced with verified URLs before production use.": "MoveSafe bevorzugt offizielle Behördenquellen. Platzhalter-Einträge sollten vor der produktiven Nutzung durch verifizierte URLs ersetzt werden.",
        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "MoveSafe stellt allgemeine rechtliche und administrative Informationen auf der Grundlage öffentlich zugänglicher Quellen bereit. Es bietet keine Rechtsberatung, begründet kein Mandatsverhältnis und sollte nicht als Ersatz für die Beratung durch einen in Ihrem Zuständigkeitsbereich zugelassenen Anwalt verwendet werden. Gesetze und Behördenregeln ändern sich häufig. Prüfen Sie Informationen stets bei offiziellen Quellen, bevor Sie Entscheidungen treffen.",
        "Moving across state lines? Know what to verify before you go.": "Ziehen Sie über die Grenze eines US-Bundesstaates? Wissen Sie, was Sie vor der Abreise prüfen sollten.",
        "Moving for school": "Umzug wegen der Schule",
        "Moving for work": "Umzug wegen der Arbeit",
        "Moving from %1$@ to %2$@": "Umzug von %1$@ nach %2$@",
        "Moving from one state's aid program to another's may change which aid applications to consider and which documents to gather, and this can affect how to plan tuition and living costs at the destination.": "Ein Wechsel von einem bundesstaatlichen Förderprogramm zu einem anderen kann ändern, welche Anträge auf Förderung zu berücksichtigen sind und welche Dokumente zu beschaffen sind, und dies kann sich darauf auswirken, wie Studiengebühren und Lebenshaltungskosten am Zielort geplant werden.",
        "Moving may change which state tax withholding forms apply, and remote work can create cross-state payroll questions.": "Ein Umzug kann ändern, welche bundesstaatlichen Steuereinbehaltsformulare gelten, und Fernarbeit kann staatenübergreifende Lohnabrechnungsfragen aufwerfen.",
        "Moving to another state for clinical rotations, externships, or supervised practice.": "Umzug in einen anderen Bundesstaat für klinische Rotationen, Praktika oder beaufsichtigte Berufsausübung.",
        "NCLEX and license-by-endorsement steps can stall when documentation does not match a destination board's current rules, which can delay clinical placement, hire dates, and compact-state recognition.": "Schritte zur NCLEX und zur Lizenz-by-Endorsement können stocken, wenn die Dokumentation nicht den aktuellen Regeln einer Behörde am Zielort entspricht, was klinische Praxisstellen, Einstellungstermine und die Anerkennung in Compact-Staaten verzögern kann.",
        "NCLEX eligibility requirements": "Anforderungen an die NCLEX-Berechtigung",
        "NCSBN Licensure Compacts overview, including Nurse Licensure Compact context for non-citizen primary state of residency declarations.": "NCSBN-Übersicht zu Licensure Compacts, einschließlich Kontext zum Nurse Licensure Compact für Erklärungen des Hauptwohnsitzes von Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft.",
        "National Council of State Boards of Nursing licensure guidance page for background context across boards.": "Lizenzanleitungsseite des National Council of State Boards of Nursing für Hintergrundkontext über Behörden hinweg.",
        "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education page summarizing the Tuition Equality Act and the 2020 statute affecting dependent students of H-1B holders.": "Seite des New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education, die den Tuition Equality Act und das Statut von 2020 für abhängige Studierende von H-1B-Inhabern zusammenfasst.",
        "New York DMV REAL ID page noting that an Enhanced ID is for U.S. citizens only and that REAL ID issued to applicants with temporary lawful status may expire with the federal document.": "New York DMV REAL ID-Seite mit dem Hinweis, dass eine Enhanced ID nur für US-Bürger ist und dass an Antragsteller mit vorübergehendem rechtmäßigen Status ausgestellte REAL IDs mit dem bundesrechtlichen Dokument ablaufen können.",
        "New York DMV documentation guidance for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including REAL ID and standard credentials.": "New York DMV-Dokumentationsanleitung für Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, einschließlich REAL ID und Standard-Ausweisen.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance FAQ on residency, nonresident filing, and telecommuting.": "FAQ des New York Department of Taxation and Finance zu Wohnsitz, Nonresident-Einreichung und Telearbeit.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance page on nonresident and part-year filing using Form IT-203.": "Seite des New York Department of Taxation and Finance zur Nonresident- und Part-Year-Einreichung mit Formular IT-203.",
        "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN licensure requirements page, which administers nursing licensure for New York.": "Seite des New York State Education Department Office of the Professions zu RN-Lizenzanforderungen, das die Pflegelizenzierung für New York verwaltet.",
        "No items match your filters": "Keine Einträge entsprechen Ihren Filtern",
        "No source has been added yet for this item. Add an official source before relying on it.": "Für diesen Eintrag wurde noch keine Quelle hinzugefügt. Fügen Sie eine offizielle Quelle hinzu, bevor Sie sich darauf verlassen.",
        "No sources are attached to the items in this view.": "An die Elemente in dieser Ansicht sind keine Quellen angehängt.",
        "Nonimmigrant visa holders (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, and others) face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID (often tied to I-94 / visa dates), in-state tuition (most public universities classify F-1 students as out-of-state), professional licensure documentation, tax residency rules, and health-insurance options. USCIS also requires reporting any address change within 10 days via Form AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney, your school's DSO if on F-1, employer HR or immigration counsel if on a work visa, and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Inhaber nichteinwanderungsbezogener Visa (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1 und andere) erleben bundesstaatliche Unterschiede bei Führerscheindokumenten und REAL ID (häufig an I-94- / Visum-Daten gekoppelt), bei den Studiengebühren für staatliche Bewohner (die meisten öffentlichen Universitäten stufen F-1-Studierende als außerstaatlich ein), bei der Dokumentation für Berufszulassungen, bei den Regeln zur Steueransässigkeit und bei den Krankenversicherungsoptionen. USCIS verlangt zudem, dass jede Adressänderung innerhalb von 10 Tagen über das Formular AR-11 gemeldet wird.\n\nMoveSafe ist kein Ersatz für rechtlichen Beistand. Erwägen Sie, einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren, den DSO Ihrer Schule, wenn Sie ein F-1-Visum haben, die Personal- oder Einwanderungsberatung Ihres Arbeitgebers, wenn Sie ein Arbeitsvisum haben, sowie eine qualifizierte Steuerfachkraft für die staatenübergreifende Steuererklärung.",
        "Not sure yet": "Noch nicht sicher",
        "Note for editors: %@": "Hinweis für Bearbeiter: %@",
        "Notes:": "Notizen:",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact general information": "Allgemeine Informationen zum Nurse Licensure Compact",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact participation": "Teilnahme am Nurse Licensure Compact",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact public FAQ page including the rule that a non-citizen applicant may declare either country of origin or the compact state as primary state of residency.": "Öffentliche FAQ-Seite des Nurse Licensure Compact, einschließlich der Regel, dass ein Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft entweder das Herkunftsland oder den Compact-Staat als Hauptwohnsitz angeben kann.",
        "Nursing / healthcare licensure": "Berufszulassung in der Pflege / im Gesundheitswesen",
        "Nursing education, licensure, endorsement, temporary permits, and compact license rules are handled by state boards of nursing and may differ by state.": "Pflegeausbildung, Zulassung, Empfehlung, vorübergehende Genehmigungen und Compact-Lizenzregeln werden von bundesstaatlichen Pflegeaufsichtsbehörden gehandhabt und können je nach Bundesstaat unterschiedlich sein.",
        "Nursing school / healthcare training": "Pflegeschule / Ausbildung im Gesundheitswesen",
        "OFFICIAL SOURCES": "OFFIZIELLE QUELLEN",
        "Official destination state attorney general - tenant resources": "Offizieller Generalstaatsanwalt des Zielstaates - Mieter-Ressourcen",
        "Official destination state board of nursing": "Offizielle Pflegeaufsichtsbehörde des Zielstaates",
        "Official destination state department of agriculture - pet entry": "Offizielles Landwirtschaftsministerium des Zielstaates - Einreise von Haustieren",
        "Official destination state department of health": "Offizielles Gesundheitsministerium des Zielstaates",
        "Official destination state department of labor": "Offizielles Arbeitsministerium des Zielstaates",
        "Official destination state motor vehicle agency": "Offizielle Kraftfahrzeugbehörde des Zielstaates",
        "Official destination state professional licensing portal": "Offizielles Portal für Berufszulassungen des Zielstaates",
        "Official destination state tax agency": "Offizielle Steuerbehörde des Zielstaates",
        "Official federal agency": "Offizielle Bundesbehörde",
        "Official local agency": "Offizielle kommunale Behörde",
        "Official origin state motor vehicle agency": "Offizielle Kraftfahrzeugbehörde des Herkunftsstaates",
        "Official source needed before relying on this item.": "Eine offizielle Quelle ist erforderlich, bevor Sie sich auf diesen Punkt verlassen.",
        "Official state agency": "Offizielle bundesstaatliche Behörde",
        "Open official source": "Offizielle Quelle öffnen",
        "Optional profile": "Optionales Profil",
        "Origin and destination are the same. MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves - some items may not apply.": "Herkunft und Ziel sind identisch. MoveSafe ist für Umzüge zwischen US-Bundesstaaten konzipiert - einige Punkte sind möglicherweise nicht zutreffend.",
        "Origin state": "Herkunftsstaat",
        "Origin state DMV / MVA": "DMV / MVA des Herkunftsstaates",
        "Origin:": "Herkunft:",
        "Parking permit and campus housing rules": "Parkausweis- und Campus-Wohnregeln",
        "Part-year residency, remote work, and school attendance may all affect state tax filing.": "Teilzeit-Wohnsitz, Fernarbeit und Schulbesuch können alle die bundesstaatliche Steuererklärung beeinflussen.",
        "Permanent relocation": "Dauerhafter Umzug",
        "Pet rules may be set by state, local, or housing-provider policies. Each layer can have different requirements.": "Regeln für Haustiere können auf bundesstaatlicher, lokaler oder Wohnanbieter-Ebene festgelegt sein. Jede Ebene kann unterschiedliche Anforderungen haben.",
        "Pets": "Haustiere",
        "Pick a purpose and the categories that apply.": "Wählen Sie einen Zweck und die zutreffenden Kategorien aus.",
        "Placeholder - replace with official source": "Platzhalter - durch offizielle Quelle ersetzen",
        "Placeholder source": "Platzhalter-Quelle",
        "Placeholder source. Replace with an official source before relying on this item.": "Platzhalter-Quelle. Ersetzen Sie sie durch eine offizielle Quelle, bevor Sie sich auf diesen Eintrag verlassen.",
        "Plate requirements (front and/or rear)": "Kennzeichenanforderungen (vorne und/oder hinten)",
        "Please confirm the disclaimer to continue.": "Bitte bestätigen Sie den Haftungsausschluss, um fortzufahren.",
        "Please fix the following:": "Bitte beheben Sie Folgendes:",
        "Possibly outdated": "Möglicherweise veraltet",
        "Practical requirement": "Praktische Anforderung",
        "Prescription medications, especially controlled substances, may be subject to state, federal, and pharmacy-level rules during interstate moves.": "Verschreibungspflichtige Medikamente, insbesondere kontrollierte Substanzen, können bei Umzügen zwischen Bundesstaaten bundesstaatlichen, bundesweiten und apothekenbezogenen Regeln unterliegen.",
        "Primary USCIS landing page for Form AR-11.": "Primäre USCIS-Landingpage für das Formular AR-11.",
        "Primary care access after moving": "Zugang zur Primärversorgung nach dem Umzug",
        "Primary state of residence requirements": "Anforderungen an den Hauptwohnsitz",
        "Professional and occupational licensing boards (including nursing, medicine, law, engineering, and many others) set their own documentation rules. Whether a state board accepts an EAD, asks for an SSN, accepts an ITIN or affidavit, accepts an I-797 for an H-1B or O-1 worker, or requires fingerprint background checks tied to a specific status can differ across states and across professions within a state. Some boards specifically address F-1 OPT and J-1 academic-training applicants.": "Berufliche und gewerbliche Zulassungsbehörden (einschließlich Pflege, Medizin, Recht, Ingenieurwesen und viele andere) legen eigene Dokumentationsregeln fest. Ob eine bundesstaatliche Behörde ein EAD akzeptiert, nach einer SSN fragt, eine ITIN oder eidesstattliche Erklärung akzeptiert, ein I-797 für einen H-1B- oder O-1-Arbeitnehmer akzeptiert oder Fingerabdruck-Hintergrund-Checks verlangt, die an einen bestimmten Status gekoppelt sind, kann sich zwischen Bundesstaaten und Berufen innerhalb eines Bundesstaates unterscheiden. Einige Behörden behandeln speziell F-1-OPT- und J-1-Academic-Training-Antragsteller.",
        "Professional and occupational licensing boards set their own documentation rules. Whether a state board accepts an Employment Authorization Document, asks for an SSN, accepts an ITIN, or requires an attestation about lawful presence can differ across states and across professions within a state.": "Berufliche und gewerbliche Zulassungsbehörden legen eigene Dokumentationsregeln fest. Ob eine bundesstaatliche Behörde ein Employment Authorization Document akzeptiert, nach einer SSN fragt, eine ITIN akzeptiert oder eine Erklärung über den rechtmäßigen Aufenthalt verlangt, kann sich zwischen Bundesstaaten und Berufen innerhalb eines Bundesstaates unterscheiden.",
        "Professional license transfer": "Übertragung der Berufszulassung",
        "Professional licensing board": "Berufszulassungsbehörde",
        "Provide legal advice or attorney-client services": "Rechtsberatung oder Mandatsverhältnis-Dienste anbieten",
        "Public college and university residency rules for tuition often treat nonimmigrant visa holders (such as F-1 and J-1 students) differently from U.S. citizens and lawful permanent residents. Some visa categories are considered able to establish a domicile in a state, while others generally are not, and some states have separate statutes or board regulations that apply to high school graduates from the state regardless of status. Rules vary across the state higher-education agency, a system office, and individual institutions.": "Die Wohnsitzregeln öffentlicher Colleges und Universitäten für Studiengebühren behandeln Inhaber nichteinwanderungsbezogener Visa (wie F-1- und J-1-Studierende) oft anders als US-Bürger und rechtmäßige Daueraufenthaltsberechtigte. Einige Visumkategorien können in einem Bundesstaat einen Domicile begründen, während andere dies im Allgemeinen nicht können, und einige Bundesstaaten haben separate Statuten oder Verordnungen, die für Highschool-Absolventen aus dem Bundesstaat unabhängig vom Status gelten. Die Regeln variieren zwischen der bundesstaatlichen Hochschulbehörde, einem System Office und einzelnen Institutionen.",
        "Purpose": "Zweck",
        "Purpose:": "Zweck:",
        "Purpose: %@": "Zweck: %@",
        "REAL ID and standard credentials use different document checklists and have different uses for federal purposes such as boarding domestic flights or entering certain federal buildings.": "REAL ID und Standard-Ausweise verwenden unterschiedliche Dokumentenchecklisten und haben unterschiedliche Verwendungen für bundesstaatliche Zwecke wie das Boarding von Inlandsflügen oder den Zutritt zu bestimmten Bundesgebäuden.",
        "RISK": "RISIKO",
        "Rabies and other vaccination documentation requirements": "Dokumentationsanforderungen für Tollwut- und andere Impfungen",
        "Receiving school registrar / residency office": "Registrar / Wohnsitzbüro der aufnehmenden Schule",
        "Recently verified": "Kürzlich geprüft",
        "Registering or being recorded as registered, even by mistake, may create issues for naturalization, status renewal, or future immigration filings. The risk of an inadvertent record can depend on how a state's DMV workflow is designed.": "Eine Registrierung oder die Aufzeichnung einer Registrierung, selbst irrtümlich, kann Probleme für die Einbürgerung, die Statusverlängerung oder zukünftige Einwanderungsanträge schaffen. Das Risiko eines unbeabsichtigten Eintrags kann davon abhängen, wie der DMV-Arbeitsablauf eines Bundesstaates gestaltet ist.",
        "Registration deadline after establishing residency": "Zulassungsfrist nach Begründung des Wohnsitzes",
        "Registration deadlines, inspection, emissions, title, and plate rules.": "Zulassungsfristen, Inspektion, Emissionen, Titel und Kennzeichenregeln.",
        "Registration, inspection, emissions, title, and plate requirements can differ by state.": "Zulassungs-, Inspektions-, Emissions-, Titel- und Kennzeichenanforderungen können sich je nach Bundesstaat unterscheiden.",
        "Relocating for a job or new employer.": "Umzug für eine Stelle oder einen neuen Arbeitgeber.",
        "Relocating for a nursing or healthcare program (ABSN, MEPN, MSN, allied health, etc.).": "Umzug für ein Pflege- oder Gesundheitsprogramm (ABSN, MEPN, MSN, verwandte Gesundheitsberufe usw.).",
        "Relocating to attend an undergraduate or graduate program.": "Umzug zur Teilnahme an einem Bachelor- oder Masterprogramm.",
        "Relocating with family members or dependents.": "Umzug mit Familienmitgliedern oder Angehörigen.",
        "Replace official agency or licensed-professional guidance": "Offizielle Behörden- oder zugelassene Fachberatung ersetzen",
        "Replace with an official URL from the destination state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch eine offizielle URL der Kraftfahrzeugbehörde des Zielstaates, bevor Sie sich auf diesen Eintrag verlassen.",
        "Replace with an official URL from the origin state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch eine offizielle URL der Kraftfahrzeugbehörde des Herkunftsstaates, bevor Sie sich auf diesen Eintrag verlassen.",
        "Replace with official federal tax-authority guidance. Use only as general orientation; consult a qualified tax professional.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch die offizielle Anleitung der bundesrechtlichen Steuerbehörde. Verwenden Sie sie nur zur allgemeinen Orientierung; konsultieren Sie eine qualifizierte Steuerfachkraft.",
        "Replace with the destination state agriculture / animal-health agency. Some species, breeds, or vaccinations have specific entry rules.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch die Landwirtschafts-/Tiergesundheitsbehörde des Zielstaates. Für bestimmte Arten, Rassen oder Impfungen gelten spezifische Einreiseregeln.",
        "Replace with the destination state department of health URL.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch die URL des Gesundheitsministeriums des Zielstaates.",
        "Replace with the destination state labor agency for paid leave, withholding, and labor law basics.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch die Arbeitsbehörde des Zielstaates für bezahlten Urlaub, Steuereinbehalt und Grundlagen des Arbeitsrechts.",
        "Replace with the destination state's attorney general or housing agency. Local ordinances may add protections.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch den Generalstaatsanwalt oder die Wohnungsbehörde des Zielstaates. Lokale Verordnungen können zusätzliche Schutzregeln vorsehen.",
        "Replace with the destination state's official tax agency website. Tax rules and forms change frequently.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch die offizielle Website der Steuerbehörde des Zielstaates. Steuerregeln und Formulare ändern sich häufig.",
        "Replace with the destination state's professional licensing portal or relevant board for the specific profession.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch das Portal für Berufszulassungen des Zielstaates oder die zuständige Behörde für den jeweiligen Beruf.",
        "Replace with the official NLC information page. Participation status and rules can change.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch die offizielle Informationsseite des NLC. Teilnahmestatus und Regeln können sich ändern.",
        "Replace with the official destination state board of nursing URL. Board rules govern eligibility and endorsement.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch die offizielle URL der Pflegeaufsichtsbehörde des Zielstaates. Behördenregeln regeln Anspruchsberechtigung und Empfehlung.",
        "Replace with the receiving school's residency or tuition classification page. School rules differ from state-agency rules.": "Ersetzen Sie sie durch die Wohnsitz- oder Studiengebühren-Klassifizierungsseite der aufnehmenden Schule. Schulregeln unterscheiden sich von Regeln staatlicher Behörden.",
        "Required documents for the application": "Erforderliche Dokumente für den Antrag",
        "Required notice periods for ending a lease": "Erforderliche Kündigungsfristen für die Beendigung eines Mietvertrags",
        "Reset all selections": "Alle Auswahlen zurücksetzen",
        "Reset progress": "Fortschritt zurücksetzen",
        "Residency can affect tuition, taxes, licensing, and benefits, and is determined by the relevant state agency, school, or tax authority - not by MoveSafe.": "Der Wohnsitz kann Studiengebühren, Steuern, Lizenzierung und Leistungen beeinflussen und wird von der zuständigen staatlichen Behörde, Schule oder Steuerbehörde bestimmt - nicht von MoveSafe.",
        "Review destination-state lease and tenant basics": "Mietvertrag und Mietrechtsgrundlagen des Zielstaates überprüfen",
        "Review recommended": "Überprüfung empfohlen",
        "Risk level: %@": "Risikostufe: %@",
        "Road trip": "Roadtrip",
        "Rules around possession, documentation, and refills can differ across states and pharmacies.": "Regeln zu Besitz, Dokumentation und Nachfüllungen können sich zwischen Bundesstaaten und Apotheken unterscheiden.",
        "Rules may differ substantially by jurisdiction, and MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in a specific situation.": "Die Regeln können sich je nach Zuständigkeit erheblich unterscheiden, und MoveSafe entscheidet nicht, ob Besitz, Transport oder Verwendung in einer bestimmten Situation rechtmäßig ist.",
        "Rules vary widely. Verify with official sources.": "Die Regeln variieren stark. Prüfen Sie sie bei offiziellen Quellen.",
        "SSA POMS section on the lawful presence framework that informs Medicare and other federal benefits.": "SSA-POMS-Abschnitt zum Lawful-Presence-Rahmen, der Medicare und andere Bundesleistungen informiert.",
        "SSN or identity documentation requirements if applicable": "Anforderungen an SSN- oder Identitätsdokumente, falls zutreffend",
        "School / institution policy": "Schul- / Hochschulrichtlinie",
        "School or institution": "Schule oder Hochschule",
        "School residency / tuition classification policy": "Wohnsitz- / Studiengebühren-Klassifizierungsrichtlinie der Schule",
        "School residency classification": "Wohnsitz-Klassifizierung der Schule",
        "School residency classification, immunization, student insurance, housing.": "Schulische Wohnsitzklassifizierung, Impfungen, Studentenversicherung, Wohnen.",
        "School-level requirements can affect tuition classification, enrollment, and clinical participation.": "Anforderungen auf Schulebene können die Studiengebühren-Klassifizierung, die Einschreibung und die Teilnahme an klinischen Praxisstellen beeinflussen.",
        "School-specific clinical onboarding requirements": "Schulspezifische Onboarding-Anforderungen für klinische Praxisstellen",
        "Schools set their own residency, health-insurance, and immunization requirements separate from state-agency rules.": "Schulen legen eigene Anforderungen an Wohnsitz, Krankenversicherung und Impfungen fest, getrennt von den Regeln staatlicher Behörden.",
        "Secondary reference": "Sekundäre Referenz",
        "Security deposit limits and return deadlines": "Kautionsgrenzen und Rückgabefristen",
        "Security deposit limits, notice periods, eviction rules, and late-fee rules can differ between states and between cities.": "Kautionsgrenzen, Kündigungsfristen, Räumungsregeln und Regeln für Säumniszuschläge können sich zwischen Bundesstaaten und zwischen Städten unterscheiden.",
        "Select a destination state.": "Wählen Sie einen Zielstaat aus.",
        "Select a purpose.": "Wählen Sie einen Zweck aus.",
        "Select a purpose…": "Zweck auswählen…",
        "Select a state…": "Bundesstaat auswählen…",
        "Select an origin state.": "Wählen Sie einen Herkunftsstaat aus.",
        "Select at least one category.": "Wählen Sie mindestens eine Kategorie aus.",
        "Select one or more. You can change these later.": "Wählen Sie eine oder mehrere aus. Sie können diese später ändern.",
        "Selective Service System FAQ page.": "FAQ-Seite des Selective Service System.",
        "Selective Service System PDF chart that lists categories and exceptions.": "PDF-Tabelle des Selective Service System, die Kategorien und Ausnahmen auflistet.",
        "Selective Service System main Who Needs to Register page, with nonimmigrant exception language.": "Selective Service System Hauptseite \"Who Needs to Register\" mit Formulierungen zur Ausnahme für Nichteinwanderer.",
        "Selective Service System materials generally describe a Selective Service registration requirement for almost all men ages 18 through 25 living in the United States, with an exception for men who are in the United States on a current valid nonimmigrant visa while that status remains valid up to age 26.": "Materialien des Selective Service System beschreiben im Allgemeinen eine Selective-Service-Registrierungspflicht für fast alle Männer im Alter von 18 bis 25 Jahren, die in den Vereinigten Staaten leben, mit einer Ausnahme für Männer, die sich mit einem aktuellen gültigen Nichteinwanderungsvisum in den Vereinigten Staaten aufhalten, solange dieser Status bis zum Alter von 26 Jahren gültig bleibt.",
        "Selective Service registration is a federal requirement for almost all males ages 18 through 25 in the United States, regardless of citizenship, and many states link license or ID applications to that registration.": "Die Selective-Service-Registrierung ist eine bundesrechtliche Anforderung für fast alle Männer im Alter von 18 bis 25 Jahren in den Vereinigten Staaten, unabhängig von der Staatsbürgerschaft, und viele Bundesstaaten koppeln Führerschein- oder ID-Anträge an diese Registrierung.",
        "Setting up mail forwarding or updating a state license can give a false sense that the federal address record is current, while a pending USCIS case may still be sending notices to an old address.": "Das Einrichten der Postweiterleitung oder das Aktualisieren eines bundesstaatlichen Führerscheins kann den falschen Eindruck erwecken, dass der bundesrechtliche Adresseintrag aktuell ist, während ein anhängiger USCIS-Fall möglicherweise noch Mitteilungen an eine alte Adresse sendet.",
        "Settings": "Einstellungen",
        "Share checklist": "Checkliste teilen",
        "Short-to-medium term internship or co-op in another state.": "Kurz- bis mittelfristiges Praktikum oder Co-op-Programm in einem anderen Bundesstaat.",
        "Show high-risk categories separately": "Hochrisiko-Kategorien gesondert anzeigen",
        "Some checklist items use placeholder sources. Replace with official sources before relying on them.": "Einige Checklistenpunkte verwenden Platzhalter-Quellen. Ersetzen Sie diese durch offizielle Quellen, bevor Sie sich darauf verlassen.",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules.": "Manche Punkte können über Staatsgrenzen hinweg unterschiedlich geregelt sein und können staatliches Recht, kommunale Vorschriften, Bundesrecht oder Behördenregeln betreffen.",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in any specific situation. Verify directly with official sources and consult a licensed attorney or relevant agency if needed.": "Manche Punkte können über Staatsgrenzen hinweg unterschiedlich geregelt sein und können staatliches Recht, kommunale Vorschriften, Bundesrecht oder Behördenregeln betreffen. MoveSafe entscheidet nicht, ob Besitz, Transport oder Verwendung in einer bestimmten Situation rechtmäßig ist. Prüfen Sie direkt bei offiziellen Quellen und konsultieren Sie bei Bedarf einen zugelassenen Anwalt oder die zuständige Behörde.",
        "Some sources have not been verified recently. Check the official website before relying on them.": "Einige Quellen wurden in letzter Zeit nicht überprüft. Überprüfen Sie die offizielle Website, bevor Sie sich darauf verlassen.",
        "Some states issue driver licenses or state IDs to nonimmigrant visa applicants on a shortened renewal cycle that tracks the I-94 or an underlying federal document, instead of the multi-year cycle used for citizens. Fees, renewal timing, and steps after a status extension can differ between origin and destination states.": "Einige Bundesstaaten stellen Antragstellern mit Nichteinwanderungsvisum Führerscheine oder Personalausweise in einem verkürzten Verlängerungszyklus aus, der der I-94 oder einem zugrunde liegenden bundesrechtlichen Dokument folgt, anstelle des mehrjährigen Zyklus, der für Bürger verwendet wird. Gebühren, das Timing der Verlängerung und Schritte nach einer Statusverlängerung können sich zwischen Herkunfts- und Zielstaaten unterscheiden.",
        "Source not yet documented": "Quelle noch nicht dokumentiert",
        "Source status: %@": "Quellenstatus: %@",
        "Sources referenced in this checklist": "In dieser Checkliste verwendete Quellen",
        "Sources to verify only": "Nur zu prüfende Quellen",
        "Sources:": "Quellen:",
        "Sources: placeholder - verify with the relevant official agency.": "Quellen: Platzhalter - bei der zuständigen offiziellen Behörde prüfen.",
        "Stale or placeholder sources only": "Nur veraltete oder Platzhalter-Quellen",
        "Stale source": "Veraltete Quelle",
        "Stale source warning": "Warnung zu veralteter Quelle",
        "Start fresh": "Neu beginnen",
        "Starting work at a new worksite outside the LCA's MSA without an amended petition can affect status maintenance, and the timing of the amended petition filing matters for when the worker can begin at the new location.": "Die Arbeit an einem neuen Arbeitsort außerhalb der MSA der LCA ohne geänderten Antrag aufzunehmen, kann die Statuserhaltung beeinträchtigen, und das Timing der Einreichung des geänderten Antrags ist relevant dafür, wann der Arbeitnehmer am neuen Standort beginnen kann.",
        "State DMV document checklists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 and similar) can differ from those used for U.S. citizens or lawful permanent residents. Accepted combinations of passport, visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, and I-797 or employer letter may vary, and some states ask for an SSN card or an SSA ineligibility letter.": "DMV-Dokumentchecklisten von Bundesstaaten für Antragsteller mit Nichteinwanderungsvisum (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 und ähnliche) können sich von denen für US-Bürger oder rechtmäßige Daueraufenthaltsberechtigte unterscheiden. Akzeptierte Kombinationen aus Reisepass, Visum, I-94, I-20 oder DS-2019 und I-797 oder Arbeitgeberschreiben können variieren, und einige Bundesstaaten verlangen eine SSN-Karte oder ein SSA-Schreiben über die Nichtberechtigung.",
        "State University of New York Board of Trustees policy on residency for tuition purposes, including which visa categories can establish New York domicile. suny.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing state university system domain.": "State University of New York Board of Trustees-Richtlinie zum Wohnsitz für Studiengebührenzwecke, einschließlich welcher Visumkategorien einen New Yorker Domicile begründen können. suny.edu gibt für Nicht-Browser-Anfragen 403 zurück (Cloudflare); dies ist ein bekanntes Falsch-Negativ auf der etablierten Domain des bundesstaatlichen Universitätssystems.",
        "State filing requirements, part-year residency, remote work implications.": "Anforderungen an die staatliche Steuererklärung, Teilzeit-Wohnsitz, Auswirkungen von Fernarbeit.",
        "State grant and scholarship programs each have their own rules about whether non-citizen students may be considered, what application form (FAFSA, a state alternative, or an institutional form) is used, and what documentation is needed.": "Bundesstaatliche Stipendien- und Förderprogramme haben jeweils eigene Regeln dazu, ob Studierende ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft berücksichtigt werden, welches Antragsformular (FAFSA, eine bundesstaatliche Alternative oder ein institutionelles Formular) verwendet wird und welche Dokumentation benötigt wird.",
        "State labor law basics (paid sick leave, breaks, final pay rules)": "Grundlagen des bundesstaatlichen Arbeitsrechts (bezahlter Krankenstand, Pausen, Regeln zur letzten Lohnzahlung)",
        "State law": "Bundesstaatliches Recht",
        "State residency basics": "Grundlagen zum Wohnsitz im Bundesstaat",
        "State tax filing can apply even when income is earned remotely. Rules differ by state.": "Eine bundesstaatliche Steuererklärung kann auch dann erforderlich sein, wenn das Einkommen aus der Ferne erzielt wird. Die Regeln unterscheiden sich je nach Bundesstaat.",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. A person treated as a nonresident alien on the federal return may still be a resident, part-year resident, or nonresident for state purposes depending on domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors. States may or may not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "Die bundesstaatliche Steueransässigkeit wird nach den eigenen Regeln jedes Bundesstaates bestimmt, die sich von der bundesrechtlichen Steueransässigkeit unterscheiden können. Eine Person, die auf der bundesrechtlichen Steuererklärung als Nonresident Alien behandelt wird, kann für bundesstaatliche Zwecke je nach Domicile, Tagen der physischen Anwesenheit, Arbeitgeberstandort und anderen Faktoren weiterhin Resident, Part-Year Resident oder Nonresident sein. Bundesstaaten können bundesrechtlichen Einkommensteuerabkommens-Ausschlüssen entsprechen oder auch nicht.",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. Domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors can each play a role.": "Die bundesstaatliche Steueransässigkeit wird nach den eigenen Regeln jedes Bundesstaates bestimmt, die sich von der bundesrechtlichen Steueransässigkeit unterscheiden können. Wohnsitz, Tage der physischen Anwesenheit, Arbeitgeberstandort und andere Faktoren können jeweils eine Rolle spielen.",
        "State tax withholding, labor law basics, remote work considerations.": "Bundesstaatlicher Steuereinbehalt, Grundlagen des Arbeitsrechts, Erwägungen zur Fernarbeit.",
        "States and individual public colleges and universities use different tuition-classification rules for non-citizens, including how prior in-state high school attendance, current immigration status, and a parent's residency are considered.": "Bundesstaaten und einzelne öffentliche Colleges und Universitäten verwenden unterschiedliche Studiengebühren-Klassifizierungsregeln für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, einschließlich der Frage, wie der vorherige Highschool-Besuch im Bundesstaat, der aktuelle Einwanderungsstatus und der Wohnsitz eines Elternteils berücksichtigt werden.",
        "States may require proof of identity, residency, lawful presence, school documents, or other paperwork.": "Bundesstaaten können Nachweise zur Identität, zum Wohnsitz, zum rechtmäßigen Aufenthalt, Schulunterlagen oder andere Dokumente verlangen.",
        "Staying in another state temporarily without intending to become a resident.": "Vorübergehender Aufenthalt in einem anderen Bundesstaat ohne die Absicht, dort Wohnsitz zu nehmen.",
        "Student health insurance requirements": "Anforderungen an die studentische Krankenversicherung",
        "Student or temporary resident exceptions": "Ausnahmen für Studierende oder vorübergehende Bewohner",
        "Student relocation": "Umzug von Studierenden",
        "Subleasing rules": "Regeln zur Untervermietung",
        "TSA REAL ID FAQs page covering documentation for citizens and non-citizens.": "TSA REAL ID-FAQ-Seite, die Dokumentation für Bürger und Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft abdeckt.",
        "TSA REAL ID overview page. Note: www.dhs.gov/real-id now redirects to TSA's REAL ID page.": "TSA REAL ID-Übersichtsseite. Hinweis: www.dhs.gov/real-id leitet jetzt auf die TSA REAL ID-Seite um.",
        "Tap to collapse": "Tippen Sie zum Zusammenklappen",
        "Tap to expand": "Tippen Sie zum Erweitern",
        "Taxes / state filing awareness": "Steuern / Hinweise zur staatlichen Steuererklärung",
        "Temporary permit availability": "Verfügbarkeit vorübergehender Genehmigungen",
        "Temporary stay": "Vorübergehender Aufenthalt",
        "Texas Board of Nursing endorsement information page, relevant when moving from another state with a license.": "Endorsement-Informationsseite des Texas Board of Nursing, relevant bei einem Umzug aus einem anderen Bundesstaat mit einer Lizenz.",
        "Texas Board of Nursing licensure eligibility page covering general requirements and documentation expectations.": "Seite des Texas Board of Nursing zur Lizenzberechtigung, die allgemeine Anforderungen und Dokumentationserwartungen abdeckt.",
        "Texas Department of Public Safety driver license identification documentation page covering U.S. citizen and non-U.S. citizen applicants.": "Dokumentationsseite des Texas Department of Public Safety zur Identifikation für Führerscheine, die sowohl Antragsteller mit als auch ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft abdeckt.",
        "Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board page on residency for tuition purposes, including categories of nonimmigrant applicants and special pathways under the Texas Education Code.": "Seite des Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board zum Wohnsitz für Studiengebührenzwecke, einschließlich Kategorien von Antragstellern mit Nichteinwanderungsvisum und besonderer Wege unter dem Texas Education Code.",
        "The deadline for applying for a destination-state license": "Die Frist für die Beantragung eines Führerscheins im Zielstaat",
        "This checklist is based on your selected categories and available source data. It may not include every requirement that applies to your situation.": "Diese Checkliste basiert auf Ihren ausgewählten Kategorien und den verfügbaren Quellendaten. Sie enthält möglicherweise nicht jede Anforderung, die auf Ihre Situation zutrifft.",
        "This checklist is not a legal conclusion. Verify with official sources and consult a licensed professional where appropriate.": "Diese Checkliste ist keine rechtliche Schlussfolgerung. Prüfen Sie bei offiziellen Quellen und konsultieren Sie gegebenenfalls eine zugelassene Fachperson.",
        "This source has not been verified in more than a year. Treat as stale and verify directly with the official source.": "Diese Quelle wurde seit mehr als einem Jahr nicht überprüft. Behandeln Sie sie als veraltet und überprüfen Sie sie direkt bei der offiziellen Quelle.",
        "This source has not been verified in more than six months. Check the official website before relying on it.": "Diese Quelle wurde seit mehr als sechs Monaten nicht überprüft. Überprüfen Sie die offizielle Website, bevor Sie sich darauf verlassen.",
        "This source was checked more than 90 days ago. Review recommended.": "Diese Quelle wurde vor mehr als 90 Tagen überprüft. Überprüfung empfohlen.",
        "Title transfer process": "Verfahren der Titelübertragung",
        "Total topics to verify: %d": "Themen zur Prüfung insgesamt: %d",
        "Travel documentation if flying with a pet": "Reisedokumente bei Flugreisen mit einem Haustier",
        "Treating an intra-MSA worksite change as a full new petition can create unnecessary cost and timing risk, while assuming portability rules apply without checking the MSA boundaries can lead to status questions later.": "Eine Intra-MSA-Arbeitsortänderung als vollständigen neuen Antrag zu behandeln, kann unnötige Kosten und Timing-Risiken verursachen, während die Annahme, dass Portabilitätsregeln gelten, ohne die MSA-Grenzen zu prüfen, später zu Statusfragen führen kann.",
        "Treats high-risk categories with a \"Do not assume\" label": "Versieht Hochrisiko-Kategorien mit dem Hinweis \"Gehen Sie nicht davon aus\"",
        "Try clearing risk filters or the high-risk / stale-source toggles.": "Versuchen Sie, die Risikofilter oder die Schalter für hohes Risiko / veraltete Quellen zurückzusetzen.",
        "USCIS Employment Authorization page providing background on the EAD (Form I-766) used in some state DMV and licensing document lists.": "USCIS Employment Authorization-Seite mit Hintergrundinformationen zur EAD (Formular I-766), die in einigen bundesstaatlichen DMV- und Lizenzdokumentenlisten verwendet wird.",
        "USCIS L-1A classification page.": "USCIS L-1A-Klassifizierungsseite.",
        "USCIS L-1B classification page.": "USCIS L-1B-Klassifizierungsseite.",
        "USCIS O-1 classification page.": "USCIS O-1-Klassifizierungsseite.",
        "USCIS Policy Manual chapter that describes federal address-change reporting.": "Kapitel des USCIS Policy Manual, das die bundesrechtliche Adressänderungsmeldung beschreibt.",
        "USCIS archive page summarizing the 2015 Simeio Solutions final guidance and the LCA-amendment trigger for worksite changes outside the MSA.": "USCIS-Archivseite, die die endgültige Anleitung zu Simeio Solutions von 2015 und den LCA-Änderungsauslöser für Arbeitsortänderungen außerhalb der MSA zusammenfasst.",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that a U.S. Postal Service change-of-address request does not change a record with USCIS and that USPS does not forward USCIS mail. A destination-state DMV address update is also a separate step from the federal AR-11 filing.": "Die USCIS-Anleitung weist im Allgemeinen darauf hin, dass eine Adressänderungsanfrage beim U.S. Postal Service den Eintrag bei USCIS nicht ändert und dass USPS USCIS-Post nicht weiterleitet. Eine DMV-Adressaktualisierung im Zielstaat ist ebenfalls ein separater Schritt von der bundesrechtlichen AR-11-Meldung.",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that an H-1B worker moving to a new worksite within the same MSA or area of intended employment as the existing LCA does not require a new LCA or an amended H-1B petition, although the existing LCA may still need to be posted at the new worksite. The federal AR-11 address change requirement still applies to the worker.": "Die USCIS-Anleitung weist im Allgemeinen darauf hin, dass ein H-1B-Arbeitnehmer, der zu einem neuen Arbeitsort innerhalb derselben MSA oder desselben Bereichs der beabsichtigten Beschäftigung wie die bestehende LCA wechselt, keine neue LCA oder einen geänderten H-1B-Antrag benötigt, obwohl die bestehende LCA möglicherweise immer noch am neuen Arbeitsort ausgehängt werden muss. Die bundesrechtliche AR-11-Adressänderungsanforderung gilt weiterhin für den Arbeitnehmer.",
        "USCIS newsroom alert describing the online change-of-address tool and clarifying that USPS forwarding does not change a USCIS record.": "USCIS-Newsroom-Meldung, die das Online-Tool für Adressänderungen beschreibt und klarstellt, dass die USPS-Weiterleitung keinen USCIS-Eintrag ändert.",
        "USCIS umbrella page on the federal change-of-address requirement, including the online change-of-address tool.": "USCIS-Übersichtsseite zur bundesrechtlichen Adressänderungsanforderung, einschließlich des Online-Tools für Adressänderungen.",
        "USPS mail-forwarding page; referenced to clarify that USPS change-of-address does not substitute for federal AR-11 filing per USCIS guidance.": "USPS Postweiterleitungsseite; referenziert, um klarzustellen, dass eine USPS-Adressänderung gemäß USCIS-Anleitung nicht den bundesrechtlichen AR-11-Einreichungsvorgang ersetzt.",
        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "Nach 22 CFR Part 62 verwalten J-1-Programm-Sponsoren den SEVIS-Eintrag und überwachen den Site of Activity für jeden Austauschbesucher. Ein Umzug, der den Wohnsitz, den Site of Activity oder die Host Organization ändert, löst im Allgemeinen eine Meldepflicht des Austauschbesuchers an den Sponsor und eine Sponsor-Aktualisierung in SEVIS aus.",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "Nach der USCIS-Anleitung nach Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015) ist der Wechsel eines H-1B-Arbeitnehmers zu einem Arbeitsort außerhalb der Metropolitan Statistical Area (MSA) oder des in der aktuellen Labor Condition Application (LCA) genannten Bereichs der beabsichtigten Beschäftigung im Allgemeinen eine wesentliche Änderung, die eine neue LCA und einen geänderten H-1B-Antrag erfordert.",
        "Understand how the destination state defines residency": "Verstehen, wie der Zielstaat den Wohnsitz definiert",
        "University of California admissions page on the AB 540 nonresident tuition exemption, noting that most nonimmigrant visa holders such as F-1 or J-1 generally cannot establish California residency for tuition purposes.": "University of California-Zulassungsseite zur AB-540-Nichtresident-Studiengebühren-Ausnahme, mit dem Hinweis, dass die meisten Inhaber nichteinwanderungsbezogener Visa wie F-1 oder J-1 im Allgemeinen keinen kalifornischen Wohnsitz für Studiengebührenzwecke begründen können.",
        "Update employment paperwork and state tax forms": "Arbeitsunterlagen und bundesstaatliche Steuerformulare aktualisieren",
        "Use do not assume language. Do not state that USPS or DMV updates can substitute for AR-11 (USCIS guidance says they generally do not). Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "Verwenden Sie die Formulierung \"gehen Sie nicht davon aus\". Geben Sie nicht an, dass USPS- oder DMV-Aktualisierungen AR-11 ersetzen können (die USCIS-Anleitung sagt, dass sie es im Allgemeinen nicht tun). Vermeiden Sie die iOS SafeCopy-Vermeidungsliste (Formulierungen, die einer rechtlichen Schlussfolgerung gleichkommen, und Formulierungen zur Vermeidung von Sanktionen).",
        "Vaccination, licensing, breed restrictions, housing pet policies.": "Impfungen, Lizenzierung, Rassebeschränkungen, Haustierregeln in Wohnungen.",
        "Vaccination, local licensing, breed restrictions, and landlord pet policies can vary across destination states and cities.": "Impfungen, lokale Lizenzierung, Rassebeschränkungen und Vermieterregeln zu Haustieren können je nach Zielstaat und Stadt variieren.",
        "Vehicle registration": "Fahrzeugzulassung",
        "Vehicle registration rules can change after a state-to-state move, especially if the destination state treats you as a new resident.": "Die Regeln zur Fahrzeugzulassung können sich nach einem Umzug zwischen Bundesstaaten ändern, insbesondere wenn der Zielstaat Sie als neuen Bewohner behandelt.",
        "Verification progress": "Prüfungsfortschritt",
        "Verified: %1$d of %2$d": "Geprüft: %1$d von %2$d",
        "Verify ACA marketplace categories described as lawfully present for nonimmigrants": "ACA-Marketplace-Kategorien prüfen, die für Nichteinwanderer als lawfully present beschrieben werden",
        "Verify F-1 SEVIS school-transfer steps if the move is to a different school": "F-1-SEVIS-Schulwechselschritte prüfen, wenn der Umzug zu einer anderen Schule führt",
        "Verify FICA (Social Security and Medicare) handling for F-1 and J-1 nonresident aliens": "FICA-Behandlung (Social Security und Medicare) für F-1- und J-1-Nonresident Aliens prüfen",
        "Verify H-1B portability and address handling for a move within the same MSA": "H-1B-Portabilität und Adressbehandlung für einen Umzug innerhalb derselben MSA prüfen",
        "Verify J-1 program sponsor reporting for site-of-activity or host-organization changes": "J-1-Programm-Sponsor-Meldung für Site-of-Activity- oder Host-Organization-Änderungen prüfen",
        "Verify L-1 or O-1 worksite change handling against the approved petition": "Handhabung von L-1- oder O-1-Arbeitsortänderungen gegen den genehmigten Antrag prüfen",
        "Verify Medicare and Medicaid eligibility rules that may apply to nonimmigrants after a move": "Medicare- und Medicaid-Anspruchsberechtigungsregeln prüfen, die für Nichteinwanderer nach einem Umzug zutreffen können",
        "Verify SEVP Portal updates for address, employer, and unemployment-day tracking on OPT or STEM OPT": "SEVP-Portal-Aktualisierungen für Adresse, Arbeitgeber und Tracking der Arbeitslosigkeitstage bei OPT oder STEM OPT prüfen",
        "Verify destination Board of Nursing documentation for non-citizen applicants": "Dokumentation des Board of Nursing am Zielort für Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft prüfen",
        "Verify destination-state DMV documents for non-citizen applicants": "DMV-Dokumente des Zielstaates für Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft prüfen",
        "Verify destination-state DMV documents for nonimmigrant visa applicants": "DMV-Dokumente des Zielstaates für Antragsteller mit Nichteinwanderungsvisum prüfen",
        "Verify destination-state financial aid eligibility rules for non-citizens": "Anspruchsberechtigungsregeln für finanzielle Studienhilfe des Zielstaates für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft prüfen",
        "Verify destination-state professional licensing documentation rules for visa or OPT applicants": "Berufszulassungs-Dokumentationsregeln des Zielstaates für Visum- oder OPT-Antragsteller prüfen",
        "Verify destination-state tuition classification rules for non-citizen students": "Studiengebühren-Klassifizierungsregeln des Zielstaates für Studierende ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft prüfen",
        "Verify destination-state tuition classification rules for nonimmigrant visa students": "Studiengebühren-Klassifizierungsregeln des Zielstaates für Studierende mit Nichteinwanderungsvisum prüfen",
        "Verify documentation a destination-state licensing board requires for non-citizens": "Dokumentation prüfen, die eine Zulassungsbehörde des Zielstaates von Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft verlangt",
        "Verify dual-status year considerations for the federal return covering a move": "Erwägungen zum Dual-Status-Jahr für die bundesrechtliche Steuererklärung, die einen Umzug abdeckt, prüfen",
        "Verify federal tax residency under the Substantial Presence Test after a move": "Bundesrechtliche Steueransässigkeit nach dem Substantial Presence Test nach einem Umzug prüfen",
        "Verify health-insurance marketplace options in the destination state": "Optionen des Krankenversicherungs-Marketplace im Zielstaat prüfen",
        "Verify how Selective Service registration applies to a specific nonimmigrant status": "Prüfen, wie die Selective-Service-Registrierung auf einen bestimmten Nichteinwanderungsstatus angewendet wird",
        "Verify how a destination-state REAL ID expiration may track an underlying federal document": "Prüfen, wie das Ablaufdatum eines REAL ID im Zielstaat einem zugrunde liegenden bundesrechtlichen Dokument folgen kann",
        "Verify how the federal five-year waiting period applies in the destination state": "Prüfen, wie die bundesrechtliche fünfjährige Wartezeit im Zielstaat angewendet wird",
        "Verify license fee and renewal-cycle rules that may follow an I-94 expiration": "Lizenzgebühren und Verlängerungszyklusregeln prüfen, die einer I-94-Ablaufzeit folgen können",
        "Verify rules for transporting prescription medication across state lines": "Regeln für den Transport verschreibungspflichtiger Medikamente über Staatsgrenzen hinweg prüfen",
        "Verify soon": "Bald prüfen",
        "Verify state tax residency and filing rules after a move": "Steueransässigkeit und Steuererklärungsregeln des Bundesstaates nach einem Umzug prüfen",
        "Verify state tax residency rules and how they interact with federal nonresident alien status": "Bundesstaatliche Steueransässigkeitsregeln prüfen und wie sie mit dem bundesrechtlichen Nonresident-Alien-Status zusammenwirken",
        "Verify state-funded benefit programs that may apply during a federal waiting period": "Landesfinanzierte Leistungsprogramme prüfen, die während einer bundesrechtlichen Wartezeit zutreffen können",
        "Verify the 10-day DSO or sponsor SEVIS address update for F-1 and J-1 status": "Die 10-tägige DSO- oder Sponsor-SEVIS-Adressaktualisierung für F-1- und J-1-Status prüfen",
        "Verify the 10-day USCIS address change filing after an interstate move": "Die 10-tägige USCIS-Adressänderungsmeldung nach einem Umzug zwischen Bundesstaaten prüfen",
        "Verify the destination-state driver's license deadline": "Führerscheinfrist des Zielstaates prüfen",
        "Verify vehicle registration requirements after moving": "Fahrzeugzulassungsanforderungen nach dem Umzug prüfen",
        "Verify whether an H-1B amended petition is needed for a worksite move to a new MSA": "Prüfen, ob ein H-1B-Änderungsantrag für einen Wechsel des Arbeitsorts in eine neue MSA erforderlich ist",
        "Verify whether to apply for a REAL ID or a standard credential": "Prüfen, ob ein REAL ID oder ein Standard-Ausweis zu beantragen ist",
        "View example checklist": "Beispiel-Checkliste ansehen",
        "WHAT TO VERIFY": "WAS ZU PRÜFEN IST",
        "WHY THIS MATTERS": "WARUM DIES WICHTIG IST",
        "Washington Department of Licensing proof-of-identity page including non-citizen documents such as I-551 annotations and U.S. visa stamps.": "Washington Department of Licensing-Seite zum Identitätsnachweis, einschließlich Dokumenten für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft wie I-551-Annotationen und U.S.-Visumstempel.",
        "What MoveSafe does": "Was MoveSafe tut",
        "What MoveSafe does not do": "Was MoveSafe nicht tut",
        "What confirmation record (receipt, screenshot, mailed copy) to keep after filing": "Welche Bestätigung (Quittung, Screenshot, mit der Post versandte Kopie) nach der Einreichung aufzubewahren ist",
        "What documentation, if any, the DMV keeps if a non-citizen declines": "Welche Dokumentation, falls vorhanden, das DMV aufbewahrt, wenn eine Person ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft ablehnt",
        "What documents (for example, EAD, transcripts, affidavits, tax records) the registrar requires to support a tuition-classification request": "Welche Dokumente (z. B. EAD, Zeugnisse, eidesstattliche Erklärungen, Steuerunterlagen) der Registrar zur Unterstützung eines Antrags auf Studiengebühren-Klassifizierung verlangt",
        "What documents (for example, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, transcripts, affidavits, tax records) the registrar requires to support a classification request": "Welche Dokumente (z. B. I-94, I-20 oder DS-2019, I-797, Zeugnisse, eidesstattliche Erklärungen, Steuerunterlagen) der Registrar zur Unterstützung eines Klassifizierungsantrags verlangt",
        "What tax or residency documentation the state aid agency requires": "Welche Steuer- oder Wohnsitzdokumentation die staatliche Förderagentur verlangt",
        "What to verify:": "Was zu prüfen ist:",
        "Whether AR-11 has been filed separately with USCIS within the federal 10-day window": "Ob AR-11 separat bei USCIS innerhalb des bundesrechtlichen 10-Tage-Fensters eingereicht wurde",
        "Whether DACA recipients are currently considered for marketplace coverage, since this category has changed at the federal level": "Ob DACA-Empfänger derzeit für eine Marketplace-Deckung berücksichtigt werden, da sich diese Kategorie auf Bundesebene geändert hat",
        "Whether Medicaid or state marketplace rules differ": "Ob die Medicaid- oder staatlichen Marketplace-Regeln abweichen",
        "Whether REAL ID and standard (non-REAL-ID) credentials use different document checklists": "Ob REAL ID und Standard-Ausweise (kein REAL ID) unterschiedliche Dokumentenchecklisten verwenden",
        "Whether REAL ID requirements apply for your situation": "Ob für Ihre Situation REAL-ID-Anforderungen gelten",
        "Whether USPS mail forwarding is in place for the new address": "Ob die USPS-Postweiterleitung für die neue Adresse eingerichtet ist",
        "Whether a Social Security card or an SSA ineligibility letter is required to apply": "Ob eine Sozialversicherungskarte oder ein SSA-Schreiben über die Nichtberechtigung für den Antrag erforderlich ist",
        "Whether a USPS change-of-address forwards mail from USCIS (USCIS guidance generally indicates it does not)": "Ob eine USPS-Adressänderung Post von USCIS weiterleitet (die USCIS-Anleitung weist im Allgemeinen darauf hin, dass dies nicht der Fall ist)",
        "Whether a change in site of activity or host organization needs prior sponsor authorization before it occurs": "Ob eine Änderung des Site of Activity oder der Host Organization eine vorherige Sponsor-Genehmigung benötigt, bevor sie erfolgt",
        "Whether a closer connection exception or a tax-treaty tie-breaker rule may apply": "Ob eine Closer-Connection-Ausnahme oder eine Steuerabkommens-Tie-Breaker-Regel zutreffen kann",
        "Whether a first-year choice or a tax-treaty election can change the analysis": "Ob eine First-Year-Choice oder eine Steuerabkommens-Wahl die Analyse ändern kann",
        "Whether a fresh I-94 printout or an updated I-797 is needed at the time of renewal, and whether the DMV verifies status through a federal system in real time": "Ob zum Zeitpunkt der Verlängerung ein frischer I-94-Ausdruck oder ein aktualisiertes I-797 benötigt wird und ob das DMV den Status in Echtzeit über ein bundesweites System überprüft",
        "Whether a license issued to a non-citizen may have a renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Ob eine an eine Person ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft ausgestellte Lizenz einen Verlängerungszyklus haben kann, der an ein bundesstaatliches Dokument gekoppelt ist",
        "Whether a license issued to a non-citizen may have a shorter renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Ob eine an eine Person ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft ausgestellte Lizenz einen kürzeren Verlängerungszyklus haben kann, der an ein bundesstaatliches Dokument gekoppelt ist",
        "Whether a license issued to a visa holder may have a shorter renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Ob eine an einen Visuminhaber ausgestellte Lizenz einen kürzeren Verlängerungszyklus haben kann, der an ein bundesrechtliches Dokument gekoppelt ist",
        "Whether a move that includes a change of school or program site requires additional SEVIS steps beyond an address update": "Ob ein Umzug, der einen Wechsel der Schule oder des Programmstandorts beinhaltet, zusätzliche SEVIS-Schritte über eine Adressaktualisierung hinaus erfordert",
        "Whether a move triggers a special enrollment period and what documents the marketplace requires to verify status": "Ob ein Umzug eine Sonder-Einschreibefrist auslöst und welche Dokumente der Marketplace zur Statusüberprüfung verlangt",
        "Whether a new Form I-20 from the destination school has been issued and signed": "Ob ein neues Formular I-20 von der Zielschule ausgestellt und unterzeichnet wurde",
        "Whether a new application is required": "Ob ein neuer Antrag erforderlich ist",
        "Whether a separate identifier or marking appears on credentials issued to applicants with temporary lawful status in that state": "Ob auf Ausweisen, die in diesem Bundesstaat an Antragsteller mit vorübergehendem rechtmäßigen Status ausgestellt werden, eine separate Kennung oder Markierung erscheint",
        "Whether a short-term placement exception (subject to federal time limits) applies before an amendment is needed": "Ob eine Ausnahme für eine kurzfristige Entsendung (vorbehaltlich bundesrechtlicher Fristen) gilt, bevor eine Änderung erforderlich ist",
        "Whether a standard (non-REAL-ID) credential is offered as an alternative": "Ob ein Standard-Ausweis (kein REAL ID) als Alternative angeboten wird",
        "Whether a standard (non-REAL-ID) credential is offered as an alternative and whether its expiration is also tied to a federal document": "Ob ein Standard-Ausweis (kein REAL ID) als Alternative angeboten wird und ob sein Ablaufdatum ebenfalls an ein bundesrechtliches Dokument gekoppelt ist",
        "Whether a state return for the destination or origin state must be filed alongside the federal dual-status return": "Ob eine bundesstaatliche Steuererklärung für den Ziel- oder Herkunftsstaat zusammen mit der bundesrechtlichen Dual-Status-Steuererklärung einzureichen ist",
        "Whether a student is classified as in-state, out-of-state, or under a tuition-equity policy can change the cost of attendance significantly, and rules can differ between the state higher-education agency, a state university system, and individual institutions.": "Ob ein Student als in-state, out-of-state oder unter einer Tuition-Equity-Richtlinie klassifiziert wird, kann die Studienkosten erheblich verändern, und die Regeln können sich zwischen der bundesstaatlichen Hochschulbehörde, einem System der staatlichen Universität und einzelnen Institutionen unterscheiden.",
        "Whether a student is classified as resident, nonresident, or under a state tuition-equity provision can change the cost of attendance significantly, and rules vary across origin and destination states and across institutions within a state.": "Ob ein Student als Resident, Nonresident oder unter einer bundesstaatlichen Tuition-Equity-Vorschrift klassifiziert wird, kann die Studienkosten erheblich verändern, und die Regeln variieren zwischen Herkunfts- und Zielstaaten und zwischen Institutionen innerhalb eines Bundesstaates.",
        "Whether a year of transition to resident-alien status under the Substantial Presence Test changes FICA treatment": "Ob ein Jahr des Übergangs zum Resident-Alien-Status nach dem Substantial Presence Test die FICA-Behandlung ändert",
        "Whether an SSN is required to apply, and whether an ITIN, an SSA ineligibility letter, or an affidavit is accepted as an alternative": "Ob eine SSN für den Antrag erforderlich ist und ob eine ITIN, ein SSA-Schreiben über die Nichtberechtigung oder eine eidesstattliche Erklärung als Alternative akzeptiert wird",
        "Whether an exempt-individual rule (for certain F, J, M, Q categories) may apply and for how many years": "Ob eine Exempt-Individual-Regel (für bestimmte F-, J-, M-, Q-Kategorien) zutreffen kann und für wie viele Jahre",
        "Whether any active USCIS receipt number has its own e-Notification or online-account address that needs to be checked": "Ob eine aktive USCIS-Quittungsnummer eine eigene E-Notification- oder Online-Konto-Adresse hat, die zu prüfen ist",
        "Whether any category-specific rules (research scholar, professor, intern, trainee, physician, au pair, and others) add steps that the sponsor must approve": "Ob kategorienspezifische Regeln (Research Scholar, Professor, Intern, Trainee, Physician, Au Pair und andere) Schritte hinzufügen, die der Sponsor genehmigen muss",
        "Whether any change in job duties, hours, or wage triggers a separate amendment analysis even when the worksite stays in the same MSA": "Ob eine Änderung der Tätigkeiten, Stunden oder Vergütung eine separate Änderungsanalyse auslöst, auch wenn der Arbeitsort in derselben MSA bleibt",
        "Whether any pending USCIS case (I-129, I-485, I-765, I-130, and similar) requires a separate address update beyond AR-11": "Ob anhängige USCIS-Fälle (I-129, I-485, I-765, I-130 und ähnliche) eine separate Adressaktualisierung über AR-11 hinaus erfordern",
        "Whether any state credit programs (for example, an earned-income or family credit) consider non-citizen filers": "Ob bestimmte bundesstaatliche Steuergutschriftsprogramme (z. B. eine Earned-Income- oder Family-Gutschrift) Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft berücksichtigen",
        "Whether benefits use by certain immigrant categories can interact with future immigration filings, and whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before applying": "Ob die Inanspruchnahme von Leistungen durch bestimmte Einwanderungskategorien sich auf zukünftige Einwanderungsanträge auswirken kann und ob Sie vor der Beantragung einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten",
        "Whether both physical and mailing addresses are recorded in SEVIS if they differ": "Ob sowohl die physische als auch die Postadresse in SEVIS erfasst sind, falls sie sich unterscheiden",
        "Whether clinicals can begin before full licensure": "Ob klinische Praxisstellen vor vollständiger Zulassung beginnen können",
        "Whether destination-state Medicaid offers emergency-only coverage to nonimmigrants and what documentation it requires": "Ob das Medicaid des Zielstaates Nichteinwanderern eine reine Notfalldeckung anbietet und welche Dokumentation es verlangt",
        "Whether documentation (original container, prescription) is recommended": "Ob Dokumentation (Originalbehälter, Rezept) empfohlen wird",
        "Whether employer name, address, supervisor, and start or end dates are current in the SEVP Portal or reported to the DSO": "Ob Arbeitgebername, Adresse, Vorgesetzter und Start- oder Enddaten im SEVP-Portal aktuell sind oder an den DSO gemeldet wurden",
        "Whether federal rules apply to interstate transportation": "Ob Bundesregeln für den zwischenstaatlichen Transport gelten",
        "Whether high school attendance or graduation in the destination state is one of the qualifying paths": "Ob der Besuch oder der Abschluss der Highschool im Zielstaat einer der qualifizierenden Wege ist",
        "Whether identity, residency, and SSN documents are required in addition to status documents": "Ob zusätzlich zu Statusdokumenten Identitäts-, Wohnsitz- und SSN-Dokumente erforderlich sind",
        "Whether immigration status or school documents affect the process": "Ob der Einwanderungsstatus oder Schulunterlagen den Vorgang beeinflussen",
        "Whether institutional aid at your destination school is governed by separate rules from state aid": "Ob institutionelle Förderung an Ihrer Zielschule durch von der staatlichen Förderung getrennte Regeln geregelt ist",
        "Whether internationally educated nurses must complete a credentials-evaluation step (for example, CGFNS)": "Ob international ausgebildete Pflegekräfte einen Schritt zur Qualifikationsbewertung absolvieren müssen (z. B. CGFNS)",
        "Whether local ordinances are stricter than state rules": "Ob lokale Verordnungen strenger sind als bundesstaatliche Regeln",
        "Whether local taxes apply": "Ob lokale Steuern anfallen",
        "Whether local tenant protections apply": "Ob lokale Mieterschutzregeln gelten",
        "Whether moving mid-coverage requires reapplication in the destination state": "Ob ein Umzug während des Deckungszeitraums eine erneute Antragstellung im Zielstaat erfordert",
        "Whether moving mid-program changes the classification timeline": "Ob ein Umzug während des Programms den Klassifizierungszeitplan ändert",
        "Whether out-of-state students need special documentation": "Ob außerstaatliche Studierende besondere Dokumentation benötigen",
        "Whether part-year residency rules apply": "Ob Teilzeit-Wohnsitzregeln gelten",
        "Whether pending discipline or incomplete education affects transfer": "Ob anhängige Disziplinarmaßnahmen oder eine unvollständige Ausbildung die Übertragung beeinflussen",
        "Whether permits, age restrictions, documentation, or location-specific rules apply": "Ob Genehmigungen, Altersbeschränkungen, Dokumentation oder ortsspezifische Regeln gelten",
        "Whether posting requirements for the existing LCA at the new location, when in the same MSA, have been satisfied": "Ob die Aushangerfordernisse für die bestehende LCA am neuen Standort, wenn in derselben MSA, erfüllt wurden",
        "Whether premium tax credit or cost-sharing reduction eligibility rules have changed for the relevant year": "Ob sich die Anspruchsberechtigungsregeln für Premium Tax Credit oder Cost-Sharing Reduction für das relevante Jahr geändert haben",
        "Whether prescriptions can be transferred": "Ob Rezepte übertragen werden können",
        "Whether professional legal advice is needed": "Ob professionelle Rechtsberatung erforderlich ist",
        "Whether proof of in-state residency is needed in addition to identity and status documents": "Ob zusätzlich zu Identitäts- und Statusdokumenten ein Nachweis des bundesstaatlichen Wohnsitzes benötigt wird",
        "Whether proof of in-state residency is required in addition to identity and status documents, and what residency proofs the DMV accepts for new arrivals": "Ob zusätzlich zu Identitäts- und Statusdokumenten ein Nachweis des bundesstaatlichen Wohnsitzes erforderlich ist und welche Wohnsitznachweise das DMV für Neuankömmlinge akzeptiert",
        "Whether remote work creates state tax or payroll issues": "Ob Fernarbeit bundesstaatliche Steuer- oder Lohnabrechnungsfragen aufwirft",
        "Whether remote work may create tax issues": "Ob Fernarbeit Steuerfragen aufwerfen kann",
        "Whether renewal fees and step counts differ from the standard renewal process used for citizens": "Ob sich Verlängerungsgebühren und Schritte vom Standard-Verlängerungsprozess für Bürger unterscheiden",
        "Whether residency affects tuition, taxes, licenses, or benefits": "Ob der Wohnsitz Studiengebühren, Steuern, Lizenzen oder Leistungen beeinflusst",
        "Whether school attendance affects residency": "Ob der Schulbesuch den Wohnsitz beeinflusst",
        "Whether school attendance affects tax residency": "Ob der Schulbesuch die Steueransässigkeit beeinflusst",
        "Whether specific state grants or scholarships consider DACA recipients or lawful permanent residents in their eligibility criteria": "Ob bestimmte bundesstaatliche Stipendien oder Förderprogramme DACA-Empfänger oder rechtmäßige Daueraufenthaltsberechtigte in ihren Anspruchsberechtigungskriterien berücksichtigen",
        "Whether state-specific uninsured/underinsured motorist rules apply": "Ob bundesstaatsspezifische Regeln für unversicherte/unterversicherte Fahrer gelten",
        "Whether student health insurance is required": "Ob eine studentische Krankenversicherung erforderlich ist",
        "Whether students or temporary residents are treated differently": "Ob Studierende oder vorübergehende Bewohner anders behandelt werden",
        "Whether temporary practice permits exist": "Ob vorübergehende Berufsausübungsgenehmigungen bestehen",
        "Whether the 10-day clock starts on the move date or the date the new address becomes permanent": "Ob die 10-Tage-Frist am Umzugsdatum oder am Datum beginnt, an dem die neue Adresse dauerhaft wird",
        "Whether the DSO has confirmed the SEVIS record was updated and any documentation that confirms the update": "Ob der DSO bestätigt hat, dass der SEVIS-Eintrag aktualisiert wurde, und welche Dokumentation die Aktualisierung bestätigt",
        "Whether the J-1 sponsor has been notified within 10 days of any change in U.S. address, telephone, or email": "Ob der J-1-Sponsor innerhalb von 10 Tagen über jede Änderung der US-Adresse, der Telefonnummer oder der E-Mail-Adresse informiert wurde",
        "Whether the REAL ID expiration date may be tied to the I-94, the visa, or an I-797 or I-20 or DS-2019, and how renewal works after a status extension": "Ob das Ablaufdatum des REAL ID an die I-94, das Visum oder ein I-797 oder I-20 oder DS-2019 gekoppelt sein kann und wie die Verlängerung nach einer Statusverlängerung funktioniert",
        "Whether the REAL ID expiration date may be tied to the underlying federal document": "Ob das Ablaufdatum des REAL ID an das zugrunde liegende bundesstaatliche Dokument gekoppelt sein kann",
        "Whether the application asks for a lawful presence attestation": "Ob im Antrag eine Erklärung über den rechtmäßigen Aufenthalt verlangt wird",
        "Whether the application asks for a lawful presence attestation and what document supports it": "Ob im Antrag eine Erklärung über den rechtmäßigen Aufenthalt verlangt wird und welches Dokument sie stützt",
        "Whether the board accepts background-check results processed under your current status": "Ob die Behörde Ergebnisse von Hintergrund-Checks akzeptiert, die unter Ihrem aktuellen Status verarbeitet wurden",
        "Whether the calendar-year count of days under the Substantial Presence Test meets the federal threshold for the current year": "Ob die Zählung der Kalenderjahrestage nach dem Substantial Presence Test die bundesrechtliche Schwelle für das laufende Jahr erfüllt",
        "Whether the current nonimmigrant status appears on the current HealthCare.gov lawfully present list": "Ob der aktuelle Nichteinwanderungsstatus auf der aktuellen HealthCare.gov-Liste der lawfully present erscheint",
        "Whether the current school DSO and the new school DSO have coordinated a SEVIS transfer release date": "Ob der DSO der aktuellen Schule und der DSO der neuen Schule ein SEVIS-Transfer-Release-Datum koordiniert haben",
        "Whether the current status is within a recognized federal eligibility group for Medicare or Medicaid": "Ob der aktuelle Status innerhalb einer anerkannten bundesrechtlichen Anspruchsgruppe für Medicare oder Medicaid liegt",
        "Whether the destination Board of Nursing requires an SSN at application, and whether an ITIN, attestation, or affidavit is accepted as an alternative": "Ob das Board of Nursing am Zielort bei der Antragstellung eine SSN verlangt und ob eine ITIN, eidesstattliche Erklärung oder Versicherung als Alternative akzeptiert wird",
        "Whether the destination DMV requires original documents and current address proofs, and whether copies or translations are accepted": "Ob das DMV des Ziels Originaldokumente und aktuelle Adressnachweise verlangt und ob Kopien oder Übersetzungen akzeptiert werden",
        "Whether the destination address is being reported to the DSO or J-1 sponsor within 10 days of the move": "Ob die Zieladresse innerhalb von 10 Tagen nach dem Umzug an den DSO oder J-1-Sponsor gemeldet wird",
        "Whether the destination state accepts an ITIN where an SSN is requested on its return": "Ob der Zielstaat eine ITIN akzeptiert, wo auf seiner Erklärung eine SSN angefordert wird",
        "Whether the destination state accepts an ITIN where an SSN is requested on its return, and whether a separate state tax ID is offered": "Ob der Zielstaat eine ITIN akzeptiert, wo auf seiner Erklärung eine SSN angefordert wird, und ob eine separate bundesstaatliche Steuer-ID angeboten wird",
        "Whether the destination state conforms to federal income tax treaty exclusions for nonresident aliens, or taxes that income at the state level": "Ob der Zielstaat den bundesrechtlichen Einkommensteuerabkommens-Ausschlüssen für Nonresident Aliens entspricht oder dieses Einkommen auf bundesstaatlicher Ebene besteuert",
        "Whether the destination state considers you a resident": "Ob Sie vom Zielstaat als Bewohner betrachtet werden",
        "Whether the destination state defines residency by domicile, by days of physical presence, or by a combination": "Ob der Zielstaat den Wohnsitz nach Domicile, Tagen der physischen Anwesenheit oder einer Kombination definiert",
        "Whether the destination state has a tuition-equity or high-school-attendance provision that could apply, and what documentation it requires": "Ob der Zielstaat eine Tuition-Equity- oder Highschool-Besuchs-Vorschrift hat, die zutreffen könnte, und welche Dokumentation sie verlangt",
        "Whether the destination state has a tuition-equity policy that may apply, and what documentation it requires": "Ob der Zielstaat eine Tuition-Equity-Richtlinie hat, die zutreffen kann, und welche Dokumentation sie verlangt",
        "Whether the destination state has additional reporting or filling rules": "Ob der Zielstaat zusätzliche Melde- oder Befüllungsregeln hat",
        "Whether the destination state has different tax withholding forms": "Ob der Zielstaat andere Steuereinbehaltsformulare verwendet",
        "Whether the destination state has elected the CHIPRA option to cover lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals without a federal waiting period": "Ob der Zielstaat die CHIPRA-Option gewählt hat, um rechtmäßig ansässige Kinder und Schwangere ohne bundesrechtliche Wartezeit abzudecken",
        "Whether the destination state imposes a minimum remaining stay on the I-94 before issuing a credential": "Ob der Zielstaat vor der Ausstellung eines Ausweises eine Mindestrestaufenthaltsdauer auf der I-94 verlangt",
        "Whether the destination state offers a separate marked credential for some non-citizen applicants": "Ob der Zielstaat einen separaten gekennzeichneten Ausweis für bestimmte Antragsteller ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft anbietet",
        "Whether the destination state offers any state-funded coverage for non-citizens who do not qualify for federal Medicaid": "Ob der Zielstaat eine landesfinanzierte Deckung für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft anbietet, die nicht für bundesrechtliches Medicaid qualifizieren",
        "Whether the destination state offers any state-funded coverage for people not eligible for the federal marketplace": "Ob der Zielstaat eine landesfinanzierte Deckung für Personen anbietet, die nicht für den bundesweiten Marketplace berechtigt sind",
        "Whether the destination state offers any voting that is open to non-citizens (for example, certain local elections), and how that may interact with federal voter rolls": "Ob der Zielstaat Wahlen anbietet, die Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft offenstehen (z. B. bestimmte lokale Wahlen), und wie sich dies mit den bundesstaatlichen Wählerlisten auswirken kann",
        "Whether the destination state operates a non-FAFSA aid application for students who cannot file a FAFSA": "Ob der Zielstaat einen Nicht-FAFSA-Förderantrag für Studierende betreibt, die keine FAFSA einreichen können",
        "Whether the destination state operates state-funded SNAP, TANF, or cash-assistance programs that may apply during the federal waiting period": "Ob der Zielstaat landesfinanzierte SNAP-, TANF- oder Sozialhilfeprogramme betreibt, die während der bundesrechtlichen Wartezeit zutreffen können",
        "Whether the destination state participates in the Nurse Licensure Compact and how that interacts with non-citizen documentation": "Ob der Zielstaat am Nurse Licensure Compact teilnimmt und wie das mit der Dokumentation für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft zusammenwirkt",
        "Whether the destination state recognizes your specific visa category as one that may establish a domicile for tuition purposes": "Ob der Zielstaat Ihre spezifische Visumkategorie als eine anerkennt, die für Studiengebührenzwecke einen Domicile begründen kann",
        "Whether the destination state requires a Social Security card or an SSA ineligibility letter, and how the visa category interacts with SSN issuance timing": "Ob der Zielstaat eine Sozialversicherungskarte oder ein SSA-Schreiben über die Nichtberechtigung verlangt und wie die Visumkategorie mit dem Zeitpunkt der SSN-Ausstellung zusammenwirkt",
        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace": "Ob der Zielstaat HealthCare.gov nutzt oder einen eigenen staatlich betriebenen Marketplace betreibt",
        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace with separate documentation rules": "Ob der Zielstaat HealthCare.gov nutzt oder einen eigenen staatlich betriebenen Marketplace mit separaten Dokumentationsregeln betreibt",
        "Whether the destination state uses the CHIPRA/ICHIA option to remove the waiting period for children, pregnant people, or both": "Ob der Zielstaat die CHIPRA-/ICHIA-Option nutzt, um die Wartezeit für Kinder, Schwangere oder beide aufzuheben",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV asks all applicants about voter registration, including non-citizens": "Ob das DMV des Zielstaates alle Antragsteller, einschließlich Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft, nach der Wählerregistrierung fragt",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV record reflects the new address on its own timeline": "Ob der DMV-Eintrag des Zielstaates die neue Adresse in seinem eigenen Zeitrahmen widerspiegelt",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV typically issues a credential to your visa category for the standard multi-year cycle or for a shortened cycle keyed to the I-94 or another federal document": "Ob das DMV des Zielstaates Ihrer Visumkategorie typischerweise einen Ausweis für den Standard-Mehrjahreszyklus oder für einen verkürzten Zyklus ausstellt, der an die I-94 oder ein anderes bundesrechtliches Dokument gekoppelt ist",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV will issue a REAL ID to your specific visa category and which federal documents it requires": "Ob das DMV des Zielstaates ein REAL ID an Ihre spezifische Visumkategorie ausstellt und welche bundesrechtlichen Dokumente es verlangt",
        "Whether the destination-state board for your profession lists DACA recipients or lawful permanent residents in its documentation guidance": "Ob die Behörde des Zielstaates für Ihren Beruf DACA-Empfänger oder rechtmäßige Daueraufenthaltsberechtigte in ihrer Dokumentations-Anleitung aufführt",
        "Whether the destination-state board for your profession lists nonimmigrant visa categories or OPT or academic training in its documentation guidance": "Ob die Behörde des Zielstaates für Ihren Beruf Nichteinwanderungs-Visumkategorien oder OPT oder Academic Training in ihrer Dokumentations-Anleitung aufführt",
        "Whether the destination-state license or ID application automatically initiates Selective Service registration": "Ob der Führerschein- oder ID-Antrag des Zielstaates automatisch eine Selective-Service-Registrierung einleitet",
        "Whether the employer is filing a new LCA and an amended Form I-129 before or shortly after the worker reports to the new worksite": "Ob der Arbeitgeber eine neue LCA und ein geändertes Formular I-129 vor oder kurz nach der Meldung des Arbeitnehmers am neuen Arbeitsort einreicht",
        "Whether the employer or petitioner is filing an amended Form I-129 before the worker reports to the new location": "Ob der Arbeitgeber oder Antragsteller ein geändertes Formular I-129 einreicht, bevor der Arbeitnehmer am neuen Standort beginnt",
        "Whether the exception covers a specific person depends on age, current status, and continuity of valid nonimmigrant status, and a later transition to LPR or naturalization can revive a registration question relevant to federal benefits and naturalization.": "Ob die Ausnahme eine bestimmte Person abdeckt, hängt vom Alter, dem aktuellen Status und der Kontinuität eines gültigen Nichteinwanderungsstatus ab, und ein späterer Übergang zu LPR oder Einbürgerung kann eine Registrierungsfrage neu aufwerfen, die für Bundesleistungen und die Einbürgerung relevant ist.",
        "Whether the existing LCA needs to be posted at the new worksite for the required period": "Ob die bestehende LCA am neuen Arbeitsort für den erforderlichen Zeitraum ausgehängt werden muss",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 address change has been filed within 10 days of the residential move": "Ob die bundesrechtliche AR-11-Adressänderung innerhalb von 10 Tagen nach dem Wohnsitzumzug eingereicht wurde",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 filing is also needed as a separate step": "Ob die bundesrechtliche AR-11-Meldung ebenfalls als separater Schritt erforderlich ist",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 filing is also needed in addition to sponsor notification": "Ob die bundesrechtliche AR-11-Meldung zusätzlich zur Sponsor-Benachrichtigung erforderlich ist",
        "Whether the institution you plan to attend sets its own classification rules in addition to any state policy": "Ob die Institution, die Sie besuchen möchten, zusätzlich zu einer bundesstaatlichen Richtlinie eigene Klassifizierungsregeln festlegt",
        "Whether the item is regulated by state law": "Ob der Gegenstand durch bundesstaatliches Recht reguliert wird",
        "Whether the license expiration is tied to the federal document expiration date": "Ob das Ablaufdatum des Führerscheins an das Ablaufdatum des bundesstaatlichen Dokuments gekoppelt ist",
        "Whether the medication is a controlled substance under federal or state law": "Ob das Medikament nach Bundes- oder bundesstaatlichem Recht eine kontrollierte Substanz ist",
        "Whether the move triggers a special enrollment period and the documentation needed to verify status": "Ob der Umzug eine Sonder-Einschreibefrist auslöst und welche Dokumentation zur Statusüberprüfung benötigt wird",
        "Whether the new employer's payroll setup reflects the exemption": "Ob das Lohnabrechnungssystem des neuen Arbeitgebers die Befreiung widerspiegelt",
        "Whether the new physical and mailing address has been entered in the SEVP Portal or reported to the DSO within 10 days": "Ob die neue physische und Postadresse innerhalb von 10 Tagen im SEVP-Portal eingegeben oder an den DSO gemeldet wurde",
        "Whether the new worksite falls inside the MSA or area of intended employment listed on the current LCA": "Ob der neue Arbeitsort innerhalb der MSA oder des Bereichs der beabsichtigten Beschäftigung liegt, der in der aktuellen LCA aufgeführt ist",
        "Whether the new worksite is inside the same MSA or area of intended employment as the current LCA, or in a new MSA": "Ob der neue Arbeitsort in derselben MSA oder demselben Bereich der beabsichtigten Beschäftigung wie die aktuelle LCA liegt oder in einer neuen MSA",
        "Whether the online change-of-address tool in a USCIS online account is the right path, or whether a paper Form AR-11 is needed": "Ob das Online-Tool für Adressänderungen in einem USCIS-Online-Konto der richtige Weg ist oder ob ein papiernes Formular AR-11 erforderlich ist",
        "Whether the original L-1 or O-1 petition listed a specific worksite, employer location, or itinerary that the move changes": "Ob der ursprüngliche L-1- oder O-1-Antrag einen bestimmten Arbeitsort, Arbeitgeberstandort oder eine Reiseroute aufgeführt hat, die der Umzug ändert",
        "Whether the person is within the age range to which the federal requirement may apply": "Ob die Person im Altersbereich liegt, in dem die bundesrechtliche Anforderung zutreffen kann",
        "Whether the program start date and on-campus reporting deadline at the new school have been confirmed": "Ob das Programmstartdatum und die Onboarding-Frist auf dem Campus an der neuen Schule bestätigt wurden",
        "Whether the tax year of the move includes both nonresident and resident periods for federal tax purposes": "Ob das Steuerjahr des Umzugs für bundesrechtliche Steuerzwecke sowohl Nonresident- als auch Resident-Zeiträume umfasst",
        "Whether the waiting period applies, whether a state option removes it for children or pregnancy, and which documents are accepted can change between origin and destination states and affect coverage continuity.": "Ob die Wartezeit gilt, ob eine bundesstaatliche Option sie für Kinder oder Schwangerschaft aufhebt und welche Dokumente akzeptiert werden, kann sich zwischen Herkunfts- und Zielstaaten ändern und die Versicherungskontinuität beeinflussen.",
        "Whether the worker still meets the IRS conditions for the F-1, J-1, M-1, or Q FICA exemption (status type, primary purpose, and federal tax residency)": "Ob der Arbeitnehmer noch die IRS-Bedingungen für die FICA-Befreiung für F-1, J-1, M-1 oder Q erfüllt (Statustyp, Hauptzweck und bundesrechtliche Steueransässigkeit)",
        "Whether their current nonimmigrant status is on the list described by the Selective Service System as covered by the exception": "Ob ihr aktueller Nichteinwanderungsstatus auf der vom Selective Service System beschriebenen Liste der durch die Ausnahme abgedeckten Status steht",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney about how AR-11 interacts with a specific status": "Ob ein zugelassener Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren ist, wie AR-11 mit einem bestimmten Status zusammenwirkt",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney about how registration history may interact with later filings": "Ob ein zugelassener Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren ist, wie die Registrierungshistorie mit späteren Anträgen zusammenwirken kann",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney before submitting status documentation to the marketplace": "Ob ein zugelassener Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren ist, bevor Statusdokumentation an den Marketplace übermittelt wird",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer familiar with non-citizen federal tax issues before relying on a particular residency conclusion": "Ob ein Steuerberater zu konsultieren ist, der mit bundesrechtlichen Steuerfragen für Personen ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft vertraut ist, bevor man sich auf eine bestimmte Ansässigkeitsschlussfolgerung verlässt",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer or the employer's payroll team to verify FICA setup after the move": "Ob ein Steuerberater oder das Lohnabrechnungsteam des Arbeitgebers zu konsultieren ist, um die FICA-Einrichtung nach dem Umzug zu prüfen",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer who handles dual-status filings": "Ob ein Steuerberater zu konsultieren ist, der Dual-Status-Einreichungen bearbeitet",
        "Whether to consult employer counsel and a licensed immigration attorney before the worker starts at the new location": "Ob die Rechtsberatung des Arbeitgebers und ein zugelassener Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren sind, bevor der Arbeitnehmer am neuen Standort beginnt",
        "Whether to consult employer counsel before relying on intra-MSA treatment": "Ob die Rechtsberatung des Arbeitgebers zu konsultieren ist, bevor man sich auf die Intra-MSA-Behandlung verlässt",
        "Whether to consult petitioner counsel and a licensed immigration attorney before the worker starts at the new location": "Ob die Rechtsberatung des Antragstellers und ein zugelassener Einwanderungsanwalt vor dem Beginn des Arbeitnehmers am neuen Standort zu konsultieren sind",
        "Whether to consult the DSO and a licensed immigration attorney before changing employers around an interstate move": "Ob der DSO und ein zugelassener Einwanderungsanwalt vor einem Arbeitgeberwechsel rund um einen Umzug zwischen Bundesstaaten zu konsultieren sind",
        "Whether to consult the DSO and a licensed immigration attorney before making decisions that affect the transfer timeline": "Ob der DSO und ein zugelassener Einwanderungsanwalt zu konsultieren sind, bevor Entscheidungen getroffen werden, die den Übertragungszeitplan beeinflussen",
        "Whether to consult the destination-state Medicaid agency for current eligibility categories": "Ob die Medicaid-Agentur des Zielstaates zu den aktuellen Anspruchskategorien zu konsultieren ist",
        "Whether to consult the responsible officer or alternate responsible officer at the sponsor and a licensed immigration attorney for category-specific guidance": "Ob der Responsible Officer oder Alternate Responsible Officer beim Sponsor und ein zugelassener Einwanderungsanwalt für kategorienspezifische Anleitung zu konsultieren sind",
        "Whether to keep dated confirmations of each address update in case a later filing relies on it": "Ob datierte Bestätigungen jeder Adressaktualisierung aufzubewahren sind, falls eine spätere Einreichung darauf angewiesen ist",
        "Whether translations or originals are required, and whether copies are accepted": "Ob Übersetzungen oder Originale erforderlich sind und ob Kopien akzeptiert werden",
        "Whether you fall within a federal exception (for example, qualifying work history, certain humanitarian categories, or specific military-connected categories)": "Ob Sie unter eine bundesrechtliche Ausnahme fallen (z. B. qualifizierende Beschäftigungshistorie, bestimmte humanitäre Kategorien oder bestimmte Kategorien mit militärischer Verbindung)",
        "Whether you fall within a federal exception to the five-year waiting period (for example, certain humanitarian categories, military-connected status, or qualifying work history)": "Ob Sie unter eine bundesrechtliche Ausnahme von der fünfjährigen Wartezeit fallen (z. B. bestimmte humanitäre Kategorien, Status mit militärischer Verbindung oder qualifizierende Beschäftigungshistorie)",
        "Whether you fall within the federal age range and category that must register": "Ob Sie in den bundesrechtlichen Alters- und Kategoriebereich fallen, der sich registrieren muss",
        "Whether you may owe a part-year return in the origin state and another in the destination state for the year of the move": "Ob Sie für das Jahr des Umzugs möglicherweise eine Teilzeit-Steuererklärung im Herkunftsstaat und eine weitere im Zielstaat einreichen müssen",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney about how Selective Service registration interacts with your specific status": "Ob Sie einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, wie die Selective-Service-Registrierung mit Ihrem spezifischen Status zusammenwirkt",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before signing any voter-related paperwork": "Ob Sie einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, bevor Sie wahlbezogene Unterlagen unterzeichnen",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before signing licensing attestations": "Ob Sie einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, bevor Sie Zulassungserklärungen unterzeichnen",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before submitting any marketplace documents related to status": "Ob Sie einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, bevor Sie statusbezogene Marketplace-Dokumente einreichen",
        "Whether you should consult a tax preparer familiar with nonresident alien filers in the destination state": "Ob Sie einen Steuerberater konsultieren sollten, der mit Nonresident-Alien-Antragstellern im Zielstaat vertraut ist",
        "Whether you should consult a tax preparer who is familiar with non-citizen filers in the destination state": "Ob Sie einen Steuerberater konsultieren sollten, der mit Antragstellern ohne US-Staatsbürgerschaft im Zielstaat vertraut ist",
        "Whether you should consult both the board and a licensed immigration attorney before signing licensing attestations": "Ob Sie sowohl die Behörde als auch einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, bevor Sie Zulassungserklärungen unterzeichnen",
        "Whether you should consult both the financial-aid office and a licensed immigration attorney about how your status documentation will be used": "Ob Sie sowohl das Studienförderbüro als auch einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, wie Ihre Statusdokumentation verwendet wird",
        "Whether you should consult both the registrar and a licensed immigration attorney about how your documentation may interact with classification": "Ob Sie sowohl den Registrar als auch einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, wie Ihre Dokumentation mit der Klassifizierung zusammenwirken kann",
        "Whether you should consult the registrar, your designated school official, and a licensed immigration attorney about how your documentation interacts with classification": "Ob Sie den Registrar, Ihren Designated School Official und einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, wie Ihre Dokumentation mit der Klassifizierung zusammenwirkt",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing a DMV renewal around a pending federal filing": "Ob Sie Ihren Designated School Official, den Einwanderungsansprechpartner Ihres Arbeitgebers oder einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, wie das Timing einer DMV-Verlängerung um eine anhängige bundesrechtliche Einreichung zu planen ist",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing renewals around an extension or change of status": "Ob Sie Ihren Designated School Official, den Einwanderungsansprechpartner Ihres Arbeitgebers oder einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt konsultieren sollten, wie das Timing von Verlängerungen um eine Verlängerung oder Statusänderung zu planen ist",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney before applying": "Ob Sie Ihren Designated School Official, den Einwanderungsansprechpartner Ihres Arbeitgebers oder einen zugelassenen Einwanderungsanwalt vor der Antragstellung konsultieren sollten",
        "Whether you should speak with your prescriber or pharmacist": "Ob Sie mit Ihrem verschreibenden Arzt oder Apotheker sprechen sollten",
        "Whether your EAD or permanent resident card is on the accepted-documents list": "Ob Ihr EAD oder Permanent Resident Card auf der Liste der akzeptierten Dokumente steht",
        "Whether your EAD or permanent resident card is on the board's current accepted-documents list": "Ob Ihr EAD oder Ihre Permanent Resident Card auf der aktuellen Liste der von der Behörde akzeptierten Dokumente steht",
        "Whether your current immigration status is on the marketplace's current 'lawfully present' list": "Ob Ihr aktueller Einwanderungsstatus auf der aktuellen Liste der Marketplace-Kategorie \"lawfully present\" steht",
        "Whether your current license remains usable during a transition period": "Ob Ihr aktueller Führerschein während einer Übergangszeit nutzbar bleibt",
        "Whether your current policy covers driving in the destination state": "Ob Ihre aktuelle Police das Fahren im Zielstaat abdeckt",
        "Whether your employer needs an updated address": "Ob Ihr Arbeitgeber eine aktualisierte Adresse benötigt",
        "Whether your employer needs updated state tax forms": "Ob Ihr Arbeitgeber aktualisierte bundesstaatliche Steuerformulare benötigt",
        "Whether your employer's state tax withholding should be updated after the move": "Ob der bundesstaatliche Steuereinbehalt Ihres Arbeitgebers nach dem Umzug aktualisiert werden sollte",
        "Whether your employer's state tax withholding should be updated after the move and which form is used": "Ob der bundesstaatliche Steuereinbehalt Ihres Arbeitgebers nach dem Umzug aktualisiert werden sollte und welches Formular verwendet wird",
        "Whether your federal status document is on the destination-state DMV's accepted list for REAL ID": "Ob Ihr bundesstaatliches Statusdokument auf der vom DMV des Zielstaates akzeptierten Liste für REAL ID steht",
        "Whether your health insurance network covers the destination state": "Ob Ihr Krankenversicherungsnetzwerk den Zielstaat abdeckt",
        "Whether your insurer requires you to update your policy address": "Ob Ihr Versicherer verlangt, dass Sie die Anschrift in Ihrer Police aktualisieren",
        "Whether your license transfers via endorsement or reciprocity": "Ob Ihre Lizenz per Empfehlung oder Gegenseitigkeit übertragen wird",
        "Whether your pharmacy can transfer the prescription": "Ob Ihre Apotheke das Rezept übertragen kann",
        "Whether your specific school sets its own tuition-classification rules in addition to any state policy": "Ob Ihre spezifische Schule zusätzlich zu einer bundesstaatlichen Richtlinie eigene Klassifizierungsregeln festlegt",
        "Whether your visa documents (passport with visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, EAD) are on the accepted-documents list": "Ob Ihre Visumdokumente (Reisepass mit Visum, I-94, I-20 oder DS-2019, I-797, EAD) auf der Liste der akzeptierten Dokumente stehen",
        "Which documents the destination state Medicaid agency uses to verify status": "Welche Dokumente die Medicaid-Agentur des Zielstaates zur Statusüberprüfung verwendet",
        "Which documents the destination-state agency uses to verify status": "Welche Dokumente die Behörde des Zielstaates zur Statusüberprüfung verwendet",
        "Which factors apply (lease, employment, vehicle registration, voting, tax filing)": "Welche Faktoren gelten (Mietvertrag, Beschäftigung, Fahrzeugzulassung, Wahlen, Steuererklärung)",
        "Which federal immigration documents (for example, EAD, permanent resident card, USCIS notices) the destination-state DMV currently lists as acceptable": "Welche bundesstaatlichen Einwanderungsdokumente (z. B. EAD, Permanent Resident Card, USCIS-Mitteilungen) das DMV des Zielstaates derzeit als akzeptabel auflistet",
        "Which federal immigration documents the destination-state DMV currently lists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (for example, passport with visa stamp, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, employer support letter)": "Welche bundesrechtlichen Einwanderungsdokumente das DMV des Zielstaates derzeit für Antragsteller mit Nichteinwanderungsvisum auflistet (z. B. Reisepass mit Visumstempel, I-94, I-20 oder DS-2019, I-797, Arbeitgeber-Unterstützungsschreiben)",
        "Which forms (1040, 1040-NR, and supporting statements) apply for a dual-status year": "Welche Formulare (1040, 1040-NR und ergänzende Erklärungen) für ein Dual-Status-Jahr gelten",
        "Withholding the wrong state's taxes can lead to filing complications and unexpected balances.": "Der Einbehalt der falschen bundesstaatlichen Steuern kann zu Komplikationen bei der Steuererklärung und unerwarteten Nachzahlungen führen.",
        "Working in a licensed profession before completing the destination state's licensing process may have regulatory consequences.": "Die Ausübung eines lizenzierten Berufs vor Abschluss des Zulassungsverfahrens des Zielstaates kann regulatorische Folgen haben.",
        "Worth knowing about. Usually administrative or low-stakes to verify.": "Wissenswert. In der Regel administrativ oder mit geringen Folgen zu prüfen.",
        "YOUR CHECKLIST": "IHRE CHECKLISTE",
        "Your selections aren't saved or shared. The checklist is generated locally.": "Ihre Auswahl wird nicht gespeichert oder geteilt. Die Checkliste wird lokal erstellt.",
        "eCFR Part 62 covers J-1 Exchange Visitor Program regulations. Curl returned 200 but with an unblock.federalregister.gov redirect, consistent with an anti-bot challenge on a long-standing .gov resource; the canonical eCFR URL still resolves in a browser.": "eCFR Part 62 deckt die Vorschriften des J-1 Exchange Visitor Program ab. Curl gab 200 zurück, aber mit einer unblock.federalregister.gov-Weiterleitung, was mit einer Anti-Bot-Herausforderung auf einer etablierten .gov-Ressource übereinstimmt; die kanonische eCFR-URL lässt sich in einem Browser weiterhin auflösen.",
        "eCFR section that describes J-1 sponsor and exchange-visitor notification obligations. Same eCFR anti-bot redirect observed.": "eCFR-Abschnitt, der die Meldepflichten von J-1-Sponsoren und Austauschbesuchern beschreibt. Dieselbe eCFR-Anti-Bot-Weiterleitung wurde beobachtet.",
    ]

    /// Afrikaans - formal register.
    /// Generated 2026-05-19 / 2026-05-21.
    static let afrikaans: [String: String] = [
        "%1$@: %2$d topics": "%1$@: %2$d onderwerpe",
        "%1$d of %2$d items verified": "%1$d uit %2$d items geverifieer",
        "%d topic to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "%d onderwerp om te verifieer voor u trek. Hierdie kontrolelys is nie 'n regsgevolgtrekking nie.",
        "%d topics to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "%d onderwerpe om te verifieer voor u trek. Hierdie kontrolelys is nie 'n regsgevolgtrekking nie.",
        "A first or last year in the United States, or a year that includes adjustment to LPR status, can involve different forms, allowable deductions, and treatment of foreign income than a standard resident or nonresident return.": "'n Eerste of laaste jaar in die Verenigde State, of 'n jaar wat aanpassing tot LPR-status insluit, kan verskillende vorms, toelaatbare aftrekkings en hantering van buitelandse inkomste behels as 'n standaard-inwoner- of nie-inwoner-staat.",
        "A health plan that works at home may have limited in-network access in the destination state.": "'n Gesondheidsplan wat tuis werk, kan beperkte in-netwerk-toegang in die bestemmingstaat hê.",
        "A household that was covered by a state-funded program in the origin state may not find an equivalent program at the destination, which can affect a move plan.": "'n Huishouding wat deur 'n staat-gefinansierde program in die oorsprongstaat gedek is, mag nie 'n ekwivalente program by die bestemming vind nie, wat 'n trekplan kan beïnvloed.",
        "A missed AR-11 filing can disrupt USCIS notice delivery for any pending or future case, and may create a question of status maintenance that compounds with employer and school records that also need updating.": "'n Gemiste AR-11-indiening kan USCIS-kennisgewing-aflewering vir enige hangende of toekomstige saak ontwrig, en kan 'n vraag van status-instandhouding skep wat saam met werkgewer- en skool-rekords wat ook opgedateer moet word, opbou.",
        "A move part-way through a tax year can lead to part-year filings, multiple state filings, or unexpected withholding, and rules for non-citizens generally follow the same state framework as for citizens but documentation can differ.": "'n Trek deels deur 'n belastingjaar kan tot deeljaar-indienings, veelvuldige staatsindienings of onverwagte afhouding lei, en reëls vir nie-burgers volg oor die algemeen dieselfde staatsraamwerk as vir burgers maar dokumentasie kan verskil.",
        "A move part-way through a tax year may produce part-year filings, multiple state filings, or unexpected withholding, and the interaction between federal nonresident alien treatment and state residency rules can change between origin and destination.": "'n Trek deels deur 'n belastingjaar kan deeljaar-indienings, veelvuldige staatsindienings of onverwagte afhouding oplewer, en die interaksie tussen federale nie-inwonende-vreemdeling-hantering en staatsinwonerskap-reëls kan tussen oorsprong en bestemming verander.",
        "A move that triggers a fresh application in the destination state may produce a credential with a different renewal cycle than the prior state used, and timing renewal around an I-94 or visa extension can affect work, study, and travel logistics.": "'n Trek wat 'n nuwe aansoek in die bestemmingstaat aktiveer, kan 'n geloofsbrief met 'n ander hernuwingsiklus oplewer as wat die vorige staat gebruik het, en tydsberekening van hernuwing rondom 'n I-94- of visum-verlenging kan werk-, studie- en reis-logistiek beïnvloed.",
        "A move that triggers loss of prior coverage may open a marketplace special enrollment period, and the eligibility framework for nonimmigrants can differ from Medicaid waiting-period rules. Federal rules in this area have been changing.": "'n Trek wat verlies van vorige dekking aktiveer, kan 'n mark-spesiale-inskrywingstydperk open, en die kwalifikasie-raamwerk vir nie-immigrante kan verskil van Medicaid-wagtydperk-reëls. Federale reëls in hierdie gebied het verander.",
        "About": "Oor",
        "About Dreamer status": "Oor Dreamer-status",
        "About green card holder status": "Oor groenkaarthouer-status",
        "About visa-holder status": "Oor visumhouer-status",
        "Administrative guidance only. Not medical advice.": "Slegs administratiewe leiding. Nie mediese advies nie.",
        "Administrative requirement": "Administratiewe vereiste",
        "After a move that involves a new employer, payroll systems may default to withholding FICA, and a misclassification can take time to correct through the employer or via an IRS refund claim.": "Na 'n trek wat 'n nuwe werkgewer behels, kan betaalstaat-stelsels by verstek FICA afhou, en 'n verkeerde klassifikasie kan tyd neem om reg te stel deur die werkgewer of via 'n IRS-terugbetalingseis.",
        "Agency rule": "Agentskapreël",
        "All": "Alles",
        "An F-1 student moving to another SEVP-certified school generally goes through a SEVIS record transfer between the current school's DSO and the new school's DSO, with a transfer release date, an initial reporting requirement at the new school, and a new Form I-20.": "'n F-1-student wat na 'n ander SEVP-gesertifiseerde skool trek, gaan oor die algemeen deur 'n SEVIS-rekord-oordrag tussen die huidige skool se DSO en die nuwe skool se DSO, met 'n oordrag-vrystellingsdatum, 'n aanvanklike rapporteringsvereiste by die nuwe skool, en 'n nuwe Vorm I-20.",
        "An interstate move during OPT or STEM OPT often coincides with an employer change, and missed reporting can affect both SEVIS standing and the running count of unemployment days, which is tracked at the federal level rather than by the destination state.": "'n Trek tussen state tydens OPT of STEM OPT val dikwels saam met 'n werkgewer-verandering, en gemiste rapportering kan beide SEVIS-status en die lopende telling van werkloosheidsdae beïnvloed, wat op die federale vlak eerder as deur die bestemmingstaat opgevolg word.",
        "An outdated SEVIS address can interfere with notice delivery from SEVP or the program sponsor, and uncorrected records can place a SEVIS record at risk of termination, which can have downstream effects on status, work authorization, and travel.": "'n Verouderde SEVIS-adres kan kennisgewing-aflewering van SEVP of die programborg belemmer, en ongekorrigeerde rekords kan 'n SEVIS-rekord aan beëindigingsrisiko blootstel, wat afwaartse uitwerkings op status, werkmagtiging en reis kan hê.",
        "Apartment or landlord pet policies": "Woonstel- of verhuurder-troeteldierbeleide",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements.": "Aansoekvertragings, weierings of hervingerafdruk-prosedures kan volg as die dokumente wat u indien nie by die bestemmingstaat se raad se huidige reëls pas nie, veral wanneer u uit 'n staat met verskillende vereistes trek.",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements. Boards of Nursing also vary in how they treat the Nurse Licensure Compact for non-citizen primary state of residency.": "Aansoekvertragings, weierings of hervingerafdruk-prosedures kan volg as die dokumente wat u indien nie by die bestemmingstaat se raad se huidige reëls pas nie, veral wanneer u uit 'n staat met verskillende vereistes trek. Boards of Nursing verskil ook in hoe hulle die Nurse Licensure Compact vir nie-burger primêre staat van inwonerskap behandel.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance and other tasks that rely on a state ID after a move.": "Om sonder die dokumentkombinasie aan te kom wat die bestemmingstaat se DMV verwag, kan lisensie-uitreiking en ander take wat na 'n trek op 'n staats-ID staatmaak vertraag.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance, which then delays other tasks that rely on a state credential after a move, including rental, employer onboarding, and school registration.": "Om sonder die dokumentkombinasie aan te kom wat die bestemmingstaat se DMV verwag, kan lisensie-uitreiking vertraag, wat dan ander take vertraag wat na 'n trek op 'n staats-geloofsbrief staatmaak, insluitend huurontvangs, werkgewer-aansluiting en skoolregistrasie.",
        "Arriving without the right documents can delay your license and other tasks that depend on it.": "Om sonder die regte dokumente aan te kom kan u lisensie en ander take wat daarop staatmaak vertraag.",
        "Assuming H-1B-style MSA logic for L-1 or O-1 can lead to a missed amendment when the original petition described a specific worksite or itinerary that no longer matches.": "Om H-1B-styl MSA-logika vir L-1 of O-1 aan te neem, kan tot 'n gemiste wysiging lei wanneer die oorspronklike petisie 'n spesifieke werksplek of reisplan beskryf het wat nie meer pas nie.",
        "Auto insurance": "Motorversekering",
        "Auto insurance minimums and rules differ by state. Insurers may need to update your policy after a move.": "Motorversekering-minimums en -reëls verskil per staat. Versekeraars mag dalk u polis na 'n trek moet opdateer.",
        "Auto-detected: %@": "Outomaties bespeur: %@",
        "Awareness item": "Bewustheidsitem",
