        "Based on your selected states and purpose, here are topics to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "Gebaseer op u gekose state en doel, hier is onderwerpe om te verifieer voor u trek. Hierdie kontrolelys is nie 'n regsgevolgtrekking nie.",
        "Because the J-1 sponsor (not USCIS) controls the SEVIS record and may need Department of State approval for certain changes, a move can affect program compliance differently from H-1B or F-1 scenarios.": "Omdat die J-1-borg (nie USCIS nie) die SEVIS-rekord beheer en Department of State-goedkeuring vir sekere veranderings kan benodig, kan 'n trek programnakoming anders beïnvloed as H-1B- of F-1-scenario's.",
        "Beneficiary-facing CMS site on Medicare basics.": "Begunstigde-gerigte CMS-werf oor Medicare-basiese inligting.",
        "Board of nursing requirements, compact licenses, clinical placement.": "Verpleegraad-vereistes, kompak-lisensies, kliniese plasing.",
        "Boards of Nursing may have specific guidance about documentation for non-citizen applicants, including whether an SSN is required, whether an ITIN or attestation is accepted, how foreign education is evaluated, and how license endorsement works when moving from another state.": "Boards of Nursing kan spesifieke leiding hê oor dokumentasie vir nie-burger-aansoekers, insluitend of 'n SSN vereis word, of 'n ITIN of bekragtiging aanvaar word, hoe buitelandse opleiding geëvalueer word, en hoe lisensie-onderskrywing werk wanneer u uit 'n ander staat trek.",
        "Breed or species restrictions (state, local, or housing-level)": "Ras- of spesies-beperkings (staats-, plaaslik of behuisingsvlak)",
        "Build a state-to-state checklist for licenses, vehicles, housing, pets, work, school, healthcare licensure, and other rules that may change when you move.": "Stel 'n staat-tot-staat-kontrolelys saam vir lisensies, voertuie, behuising, troeteldiere, werk, skool, gesondheidsorglisensiëring en ander reëls wat kan verander wanneer u trek.",
        "Build checklist": "Stel kontrolelys saam",
