        "CHECKLIST BUILDER": "KONTROLELYSBOUER",
        "CMS landing page on the federal and state marketplaces. Redirected from a cciio URL.": "CMS-landingsbladsy oor die federale en staatsmarkte. Herlei vanaf 'n cciio-URL.",
        "CMS page summarizing Original Medicare eligibility, including the five-year continuous residency provision for lawfully admitted permanent residents.": "CMS-bladsy wat Original Medicare-kwalifikasie opsom, insluitend die vyfjarige deurlopende inwonerskap-bepaling vir wettig opgeneem permanente inwoners.",
        "CMS press release on April 2026 guidance to implement statutory limits on federal Medicaid and CHIP funding for certain noncitizens, taking effect October 1, 2026, and noting the carve-out for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "CMS-persvrystelling oor April 2026-leiding om wetlike perke op federale Medicaid- en CHIP-befondsing vir sekere nie-burgers te implementeer, wat op 1 Oktober 2026 in werking tree, en let op die uitsondering vir wettig wonende kinders en swanger individue.",
        "CPR / BLS certification": "CPR / BLS-sertifisering",
