        "CUNY tuition and fee manual chapter on residency, covering nonimmigrant visa categories that may establish New York domicile and high-school-attendance provisions.": "CUNY-klasgeld- en fooi-handleiding-hoofstuk oor inwonerskap, wat nie-immigrant-visumkategorieë dek wat New York-domisilie kan vestig en hoërskoolbywoning-bepalings.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing applicant FAQ page covering documentation, SSN, and immigration-status questions.": "California Board of Registered Nursing-aansoeker-FAQ-bladsy wat dokumentasie-, SSN- en immigrasiestatus-vrae dek.",
