        "California DMV REAL ID page covering documentation for non-U.S. citizens, including how the credential expiration may track the underlying federal document.": "California DMV REAL ID-bladsy wat dokumentasie vir nie-Amerikaanse burgers dek, insluitend hoe die geloofsbrief-vervaldatum die onderliggende federale dokument kan volg.",
        "California FTB page on part-year and nonresident filers, including a note that California does not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "California FTB-bladsy oor deeljaar- en nie-inwoner-indieners, insluitend 'n nota dat California nie aan federale inkomstebelasting-verdrag-uitsluitings voldoen nie.",
        "California Franchise Tax Board page on residency, nonresidency, and part-year status for state income tax purposes.": "California Franchise Tax Board-bladsy oor inwonerskap, nie-inwonerskap en deeljaar-status vir staats-inkomstebelasting-doeleindes.",
        "Can cause inconvenience, fees, or compliance problems if ignored.": "Kan ongerief, fooie of nakomingsprobleme veroorsaak indien geïgnoreer.",
        "Categories": "Kategorieë",
        "Categories where rules vary substantially. Verify directly with official sources.": "Kategorieë waar reëls aansienlik verskil. Verifieer direk met amptelike bronne.",
        "Check insurance networks, student health, and prescription transfer": "Gaan versekeringsnetwerke, studente-gesondheid en voorskrif-oordrag na",
        "Check pet vaccination, licensing, and housing rules": "Gaan troeteldier-inenting, lisensiëring en behuisingreëls na",
        "Check the destination state board of nursing requirements": "Gaan die bestemmingstaat se verpleegraad-vereistes na",
        "Check whether a destination-state license application triggers Selective Service registration": "Gaan na of 'n bestemmingstaat-lisensie-aansoek Selective Service-registrasie aktiveer",
        "Check whether moving creates a state tax filing requirement": "Gaan na of trek 'n staatsbelastingindiening-vereiste skep",
        "Check whether your professional license transfers": "Gaan na of u professionele lisensie oorgedra word",
        "Checklist": "Kontrolelys",
        "Checklist builder": "Kontrolelysbouer",
        "Choose your origin and destination state.": "Kies u oorsprong- en bestemmingstaat.",
        "Choose your origin and destination, your purpose, and the categories that apply. MoveSafe will generate a list of topics to verify before moving.": "Kies u oorsprong en bestemming, u doel en die kategorieë wat van toepassing is. MoveSafe sal 'n lys van onderwerpe genereer om te verifieer voor u trek.",
        "Choose your states, purpose, and categories. MoveSafe will assemble a source-linked checklist with risk badges.": "Kies u state, doel en kategorieë. MoveSafe sal 'n bron-geskakelde kontrolelys met risiko-aanduiders saamstel.",
        "Choosing the wrong credential type at the destination-state DMV can mean reapplying later, and document expiration may shorten the validity of a REAL ID issued to non-citizens.": "Om die verkeerde geloofsbrief-tipe by die bestemmingstaat se DMV te kies, kan beteken dat u later weer moet aansoek doen, en dokumentvervaldatum kan die geldigheid van 'n REAL ID wat aan nie-burgers uitgereik is, verkort.",
        "Clears the verified state on items currently shown.": "Maak die geverifieerde status skoon vir items wat tans gewys word.",
        "Clinical placement": "Kliniese plasing",
        "Clinical sites and schools may require immunizations, drug screens, CPR/BLS, background checks, and other clearances separate from board licensure.": "Kliniese terreine en skole kan inentings, dwelmtoetse, CPR/BLS, agtergrondkontroles en ander klarings vereis afsonderlik van raadlisensiëring.",
        "Confirm clinical placement and school onboarding requirements": "Bevestig kliniese plasing- en skoolaansluitings-vereistes",
        "Confirm required documents for a destination-state license": "Bevestig vereiste dokumente vir 'n bestemmingstaat-lisensie",
        "Confirm school residency, insurance, and immunization rules": "Bevestig skool-inwonerskap-, versekering- en inentingsreëls",
        "Confirm your auto insurance covers the destination state": "Bevestig dat u motorversekering die bestemmingstaat dek",
        "Continue my checklist": "Gaan voort met my kontrolelys",
        "Continuing education requirements": "Voortgesette opleiding-vereistes",
        "Continuity of coverage after a move depends on whether the destination state operates its own marketplace, which categories of non-citizens it considers, and whether state-funded coverage is offered to people who are not eligible for the federal marketplace.": "Kontinuïteit van dekking na 'n trek hang af van of die bestemmingstaat sy eie mark bedryf, watter kategorieë van nie-burgers dit oorweeg, en of staat-gefinansierde dekking aan mense aangebied word wat nie vir die federale mark kwalifiseer nie.",
        "Could not generate checklist": "Kon nie kontrolelys genereer nie",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page covering personal information updates.": "DHS Study in the States SEVIS-hulpsentrum-bladsy wat persoonlike-inligting-opdaterings dek.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on F-1 SEVIS transfer mechanics.": "DHS Study in the States SEVIS-hulpsentrum-bladsy oor F-1 SEVIS-oordragmeganika.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on STEM OPT.": "DHS Study in the States SEVIS-hulpsentrum-bladsy oor STEM OPT.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVP Portal help page describing OPT reporting.": "DHS Study in the States SEVP Portal-hulpblad wat OPT-rapportering beskryf.",
        "DHS Study in the States blog post on the 10-day DSO reporting expectation.": "DHS Study in the States-blogpos oor die 10-dag DSO-rapporteringverwagting.",
        "DHS Study in the States guidance for F-1 and M-1 students on reporting address changes to the designated school official within 10 days.": "DHS Study in the States-leiding vir F-1- en M-1-studente oor die rapportering van adresveranderings aan die aangewese skoolbeampte binne 10 dae.",
        "DHS Study in the States post on SEVIS address-of-record.": "DHS Study in the States-pos oor SEVIS-rekord-adres.",
        "DOL FLAG portal that handles LCA and other foreign-labor filings. The dol.gov subpages returned 403 to curl with Mozilla user-agent, consistent with anti-bot behavior on a long-standing .gov domain, so this canonical FLAG portal URL is used.": "DOL FLAG-portaal wat LCA en ander buitelandse-arbeid-indienings hanteer. Die dol.gov-subblaaie het 403 op curl met Mozilla user-agent geretourneer, in lyn met anti-bot-gedrag op 'n langdurige .gov-domein, dus word hierdie kanonieke FLAG-portaal-URL gebruik.",
        "Decide your residency, eligibility, or tax status": "Besluit oor u inwonerskap, kwalifikasie of belastingstatus",
        "Department of Homeland Security guidance for F-1 and M-1 students, and Department of State regulations for J-1 exchange visitors, generally require reporting an address change to a designated school official (DSO) or program sponsor within 10 days so the SEVIS record can be updated.": "Department of Homeland Security-leiding vir F-1- en M-1-studente, en Department of State-regulasies vir J-1-uitruilbesoekers, vereis oor die algemeen dat 'n adresverandering binne 10 dae by 'n aangewese skoolbeampte (DSO) of programborg aangemeld word sodat die SEVIS-rekord opgedateer kan word.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA categories overview.": "Department of State BridgeUSA-kategorieë-oorsig.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA landing page for the J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.": "Department of State BridgeUSA-landingsbladsy vir die J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.",
        "Destination state": "Bestemmingstaat",
        "Destination state DMV / MVA": "Bestemmingstaat DMV / MVA",
        "Destination state attorney general": "Bestemmingstaat se prokureur-generaal",
        "Destination state board of nursing": "Bestemmingstaat se Board of Nursing",
        "Destination state department of agriculture": "Bestemmingstaat se departement van landbou",
        "Destination state department of health": "Bestemmingstaat se departement van gesondheid",
        "Destination state department of labor": "Bestemmingstaat se departement van arbeid",
        "Destination state professional licensing": "Bestemmingstaat se professionele lisensiëring",
        "Destination state tax agency": "Bestemmingstaat-belastingagentskap",
        "Destination-state minimum coverage requirements": "Bestemmingstaat se minimum dekkingsvereistes",
        "Destination:": "Bestemming:",
        "Determine whether a specific act is lawful": "Bepaal of 'n bepaalde handeling regmatig is",
        "Different agencies may apply different residency tests. The same person can be a resident for one purpose and not another.": "Verskillende agentskappe mag verskillende inwonerskaptoetse toepas. Dieselfde persoon kan vir een doel 'n inwoner wees en nie vir 'n ander nie.",
        "Direct users to confirm coverage with their insurer. Do not state whether coverage applies.": "Verwys gebruikers om dekking met hul versekeraar te bevestig. Moenie verklaar of dekking van toepassing is nie.",
        "Disclaimer. %@": "Vrywaring. %@",
        "Do not assert that any group is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID rules involve both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only.": "Moenie beweer dat enige groep wel of nie kwalifiseer vir REAL ID in 'n gegewe staat nie. REAL ID-reëls behels beide federale minimums en staatsimplementering wat kan verander. Gebruik slegs 'verifieer'- en 'kan verskil'-taal.",
        "Do not assert that any specific state always uses a shortened renewal cycle for a given visa category. Frame as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie beweer dat enige spesifieke staat altyd 'n verkorte hernuwingsiklus vir 'n gegewe visumkategorie gebruik nie. Stel dit voor as items om met die bestemmingstaat se DMV te verifieer. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not assert that any visa category is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID involves both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie beweer dat enige visumkategorie wel of nie vir REAL ID in 'n gegewe staat kwalifiseer nie. REAL ID behels beide federale minimums en staatsimplementering wat kan verander. Gebruik slegs 'verifieer'- en 'kan verskil'-taal en volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not assume": "Moenie aanneem nie",
        "Do not assume a USPS or DMV address update satisfies the federal AR-11 step": "Moenie aanneem dat 'n USPS- of DMV-adres-opdatering die federale AR-11-stap bevredig nie",
        "Do not assume regulated items follow the same rules across state lines": "Moenie aanneem dat gereguleerde items dieselfde reëls oor staatsgrense heen volg nie",
        "Do not assume rules from your origin state apply. Rules vary across state, local, and federal jurisdictions. Verify directly with official sources.": "Moenie aanneem dat reëls van u oorsprongstaat van toepassing is nie. Reëls verskil oor staats-, plaaslike en federale jurisdiksies heen. Verifieer direk met amptelike bronne.",
        "Do not characterize voter registration by non-citizens using legal-conclusion or accusatory language. Use neutral framing such as 'generally not eligible' and 'may create immigration complications'. Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney. Do not give procedural advice for any specific state.": "Moenie kieserregistrasie deur nie-burgers met regsgevolgtrekking- of beskuldigende taal kenmerk nie. Gebruik neutrale formulering soos 'oor die algemeen nie geregtig nie' en 'kan immigrasie-komplikasies skep'. Verwys lesers om 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur te raadpleeg. Moenie prosedurele advies vir enige spesifieke staat verskaf nie.",
        "Do not characterize whether any visa category can establish residency in a specific state as a determination. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie kenmerk of enige visumkategorie inwonerskap in 'n spesifieke staat as 'n bepaling kan vestig nie. Stel dit voor as klassifikasiereëls om met die skoolregistrateur en die staats-hoëronderwysagentskap te verifieer. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not determine residency. List factors to verify. Direct to the relevant agency or school.": "Moenie inwonerskap bepaal nie. Lys faktore om te verifieer. Verwys na die relevante agentskap of skool.",
        "Do not determine that a household 'is' or 'is not' eligible for Medicaid. Frame as items to verify with the state Medicaid agency. Use 'may apply' and 'rules differ by jurisdiction'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie bepaal dat 'n huishouding wel of nie vir Medicaid kwalifiseer nie. Stel dit voor as items om met die staat se Medicaid-agentskap te verifieer. Gebruik 'kan van toepassing wees' en 'die reëls verskil afhangende van die jurisdiksie'. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not list which states grant in-state tuition for DACA recipients. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency.": "Moenie lys watter state binnestaat-klasgeld vir DACA-ontvangers toestaan nie. Stel dit voor as klassifikasiereëls om met die skoolregistrateur en die staats-hoëronderwysagentskap te verifieer.",
        "Do not provide a public-charge determination or say that using benefits 'will' or 'will not' affect immigration. Frame as 'may interact' and recommend consulting a licensed immigration attorney. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie 'n publieke-las-bepaling verskaf of sê dat die gebruik van voordele immigrasie 'sal' of 'nie sal' beïnvloed nie. Stel dit voor as 'kan saamwerk' en beveel aan om 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur te raadpleeg. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not provide medical or transport instructions for controlled substances.": "Moenie mediese of vervoer-instruksies vir beheerde stowwe verskaf nie.",
        "Do not provide tactical instructions for transporting, possessing, hiding, storing, modifying, or avoiding enforcement for regulated items.": "Moenie taktiese instruksies verskaf vir die vervoer, besit, verbergening, berging, wysiging of die systap van handhawing vir gereguleerde items nie.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to official tax agency and qualified professionals.": "Moenie belastingadvies verskaf nie. Verwys na amptelike belastingagentskap en gekwalifiseerde professionele persone.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to state tax agency or qualified tax professional.": "Moenie belastingadvies verskaf nie. Verwys na staatsbelastingagentskap of gekwalifiseerde belastingkenner.",
        "Do not say a Board of Nursing in a particular state grants or refuses an applicant's NCLEX path. Use 'verify with the destination Board of Nursing'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie sê dat 'n Board of Nursing in 'n bepaalde staat 'n aansoeker se NCLEX-pad toestaan of weier nie. Gebruik 'verifieer met die bestemming Board of Nursing'. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not say a particular aid program 'is open to' or 'is closed to' DACA recipients or LPRs. Use 'verify with the state aid agency and the school financial-aid office'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie sê dat 'n bepaalde hulpprogram 'oop is vir' of 'gesluit is vir' DACA-ontvangers of LPR's nie. Gebruik 'verifieer met die staatshulp-agentskap en die skool se finansiële-hulp-kantoor'. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not say a person 'can' or 'cannot' enroll. Use 'verify current eligibility categories with the marketplace operator' since federal rules have changed. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie sê dat 'n persoon kan of nie kan inskryf nie. Gebruik 'verifieer huidige kwalifikasie-kategorieë met die markoperateur' aangesien federale reëls verander het. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency for a given visa category or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie verklaar hoe 'n spesifieke staat inwonerskap vir 'n gegewe visumkategorie definieer of dat iemand 'n inwoner is nie. Stel dit voor as 'die reëls verskil afhangende van die jurisdiksie' en 'verifieer met die bestemmingstaat se belastingagentskap'. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie verklaar hoe 'n spesifieke staat inwonerskap definieer of dat iemand 'n inwoner is nie. Stel dit voor as 'die reëls verskil afhangende van die jurisdiksie' en 'verifieer met die bestemmingstaat se belastingagentskap'. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license a given visa category. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie verklaar dat enige spesifieke raad 'n gegewe visumkategorie wel of nie lisensieer nie. Stel alles voor as items om met die bestemmingstaat se raad te verifieer. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license non-citizens. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie verklaar dat enige spesifieke raad nie-burgers wel of nie lisensieer nie. Stel alles voor as items om met die bestemmingstaat se raad te verifieer. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Frame as a federal requirement that 'may apply' depending on age and sex, with state implementation details to verify. Use neutral language and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie verklaar dat enige spesifieke persoon wel of nie moet registreer nie. Stel dit voor as 'n federale vereiste wat 'kan van toepassing wees' afhangend van ouderdom en geslag, met staatsimplementering-besonderhede om te verifieer. Gebruik neutrale taal en volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Do not state whether the user is eligible for licensure. Only identify requirements to verify.": "Moenie verklaar of die gebruiker vir lisensiëring kwalifiseer nie. Identifiseer slegs vereistes om te verifieer.",
        "Do not state which states do or do not issue licenses to a given group, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV.": "Moenie verklaar watter state lisensies aan 'n gegewe groep uitreik of nie nie, en moenie spesifieke aanvaarde dokumente lys nie. Stel alles voor as items om met die bestemmingstaat se DMV te verifieer.",
        "Do not state which states issue or do not issue licenses to a given visa category, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Moenie verklaar watter state lisensies aan 'n gegewe visumkategorie uitreik of nie nie, en moenie spesifieke aanvaarde dokumente lys nie. Stel alles voor as items om met die bestemmingstaat se DMV te verifieer. Volg die SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Document lists accepted by state DMVs for non-citizen license or state-ID applicants can differ from those accepted for U.S. citizens, and accepted combinations may vary by jurisdiction.": "Dokumentlyste wat deur staats-DMV's aanvaar word vir nie-burger-lisensie- of staats-ID-aansoekers kan verskil van dié wat vir Amerikaanse burgers aanvaar word, en aanvaarde kombinasies kan per jurisdiksie verskil.",
        "Done": "Klaar",
        "Driver's license": "Bestuurslisensie",
        "Driving across one or more state lines for travel.": "Bestuur oor een of meer staatsgrense vir reis.",
        "Driving with coverage that does not meet destination-state minimums can create compliance and financial problems.": "Om te bestuur met dekking wat nie aan bestemmingstaat-minimums voldoen nie kan nakoming- en finansiële probleme veroorsaak.",
        "Drug screen requirements": "Dwelmtoets-vereistes",
        "Edit selections": "Wysig keuses",
        "Emissions testing requirement": "Emissietoetsing-vereiste",
        "Employer policy": "Werkgewerbeleid",
        "Employment paperwork": "Werknemerspapierwerk",
        "Endorsement requirements if already licensed": "Onderskrywing-vereistes indien reeds gelisensieer",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary permits, and continuing education requirements vary by state and profession.": "Onderskrywing, wedersydsheid, tydelike permitte en voortgesette opleiding-vereistes verskil per staat en beroep.",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary practice, and continuing education.": "Onderskrywing, wedersydsheid, tydelike praktyk en voortgesette opleiding.",
        "English": "Engels",
        "Establishing a new permanent residence in the destination state.": "Vestiging van 'n nuwe permanente woning in die bestemmingstaat.",
        "Eviction and late-fee rules": "Uitsetting- en laatfooireëls",
        "Example checklist categories": "Voorbeeld kontrolelys-kategorieë",
        "Exploring options. Receive a broad overview checklist.": "Ondersoek opsies. Ontvang 'n breë oorsig-kontrolelys.",
        "F-1 OPT and STEM OPT specific. Use verify with the DSO and SEVP Portal guidance. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Do not advise on a specific status outcome.": "F-1 OPT- en STEM OPT-spesifiek. Gebruik 'verifieer met die DSO en SEVP Portal-leiding'. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys (regsgevolgtrekking-formulering en boete-vermyding-formulering). Moenie advies oor 'n spesifieke statusuitkoms gee nie.",
        "F-1 specific. Frame as verify with both DSOs and reference Study in the States or ICE materials. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1-spesifiek. Stel dit voor as 'verifieer met beide DSO's' en verwys na Study in the States- of ICE-materiaal. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "F-1 students on post-completion OPT or a STEM OPT extension generally use the SEVP Portal or work with their DSO to update physical and mailing address, employer information, and other personal data, typically within 10 days of a change. Unemployment-day limits during OPT continue to apply during and after a move.": "F-1-studente op na-voltooiing-OPT of 'n STEM OPT-verlenging gebruik oor die algemeen die SEVP Portal of werk saam met hul DSO om fisiese en posadres, werkgewer-inligting en ander persoonlike data op te dateer, tipies binne 10 dae van 'n verandering. Werkloosheidsdag-perke gedurende OPT bly tydens en na 'n trek van toepassing.",
        "F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q specific. Frame as items to verify with IRS guidance and the employer. Do not state that a particular worker is exempt from FICA. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1-, J-1-, M-1- en Q-spesifiek. Stel dit voor as items om met IRS-leiding en die werkgewer te verifieer. Moenie verklaar dat 'n bepaalde werker van FICA vrygestel is nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Factors that may affect residency for tuition, taxes, licensing, benefits.": "Faktore wat inwonerskap kan beïnvloed vir klasgeld, belasting, lisensiëring en voordele.",
        "Failing to register on time may affect eligibility for federal benefits, federal jobs, and naturalization later, even though the requirement is federal. State DMV workflows can also trigger automatic registration, which applicants should understand before applying.": "Versuim om betyds te registreer kan kwalifikasie vir federale voordele, federale werk en naturalisering later beïnvloed, alhoewel die vereiste federaal is. Staats-DMV-werkvloei kan ook outomatiese registrasie aktiveer, wat aansoekers behoort te verstaan voor hulle aansoek doen.",
        "Family move": "Gesinstrek",
        "Federal HealthCare.gov guidance describes a list of immigration statuses considered lawfully present for purposes of the Affordable Care Act marketplace, which includes many common nonimmigrant categories. These categories can purchase coverage without a five-year waiting period that applies in many Medicaid contexts.": "Federale HealthCare.gov-leiding beskryf 'n lys van immigrasiestatusse wat as wettig teenwoordig vir doeleindes van die Affordable Care Act-mark beskou word, wat baie algemene nie-immigrant-kategorieë insluit. Hierdie kategorieë kan dekking koop sonder 'n vyfjaar-wagtydperk wat in baie Medicaid-kontekste van toepassing is.",
        "Federal Medicaid and CHIP rules generally include a five-year waiting period for many qualified non-citizens after obtaining qualified status, with several federal exceptions. States may use an option that removes the waiting period for children and pregnant people, and some states cover certain groups with state funds.": "Federale Medicaid- en CHIP-reëls sluit oor die algemeen 'n vyfjaar-wagtydperk in vir baie gekwalifiseerde nie-burgers nadat gekwalifiseerde status verkry is, met verskeie federale uitsonderings. State kan 'n opsie gebruik wat die wagtydperk vir kinders en swanger persone verwyder, en sommige state dek sekere groepe met staatsfondse.",
        "Federal Medicare guidance generally describes eligibility for non-citizens who are lawfully admitted for permanent residence and have lived in the United States for five continuous years. Federal Medicaid rules for most nonimmigrants are narrower than for LPRs, with state-specific options for emergency Medicaid and for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "Federale Medicare-leiding beskryf oor die algemeen kwalifikasie vir nie-burgers wat wettig vir permanente verblyf toegang ontvang het en vir vyf deurlopende jare in die Verenigde State gewoon het. Federale Medicaid-reëls vir die meeste nie-immigrante is nouer as vir LPR's, met staatspesifieke opsies vir noodgevallemedicaid en vir wettig wonende kinders en swanger individue.",
        "Federal REAL ID rules require evidence of lawful status, and many states issue a REAL ID to nonimmigrant visa holders only with an expiration date that does not extend past the I-94, the visa, or another underlying federal document. Implementation differs between states, and standard (non-REAL-ID) options may or may not be offered.": "Federale REAL ID-reëls vereis bewys van wettige status, en baie state reik 'n REAL ID aan nie-immigrant-visumhouers uit slegs met 'n vervaldatum wat nie verby die I-94, die visum of 'n ander onderliggende federale dokument strek nie. Implementering verskil tussen state, en standaard (nie-REAL-ID) opsies kan al dan nie aangebied word nie.",
        "Federal SNAP, TANF, and similar programs apply a waiting period to many qualified non-citizens. Some states use state funds to operate replacement or supplemental programs that cover groups not eligible for the federal program, with differing rules.": "Federale SNAP, TANF en soortgelyke programme pas 'n wagtydperk toe op baie gekwalifiseerde nie-burgers. Sommige state gebruik staatsfondse om vervangende of aanvullende programme te bedryf wat groepe dek wat nie vir die federale program kwalifiseer nie, met verskillende reëls.",
        "Federal law": "Federale wet",
        "Federal law (INA section 265) generally directs non-citizens to report a change of address to USCIS within 10 days of moving, typically through Form AR-11 or the USCIS online change-of-address tool. The federal filing is separate from updating a state DMV record, an employer, a school, or the U.S. Postal Service.": "Federale wet (INA-afdeling 265) rig nie-burgers oor die algemeen aan om 'n adresverandering binne 10 dae na 'n trek by USCIS aan te meld, tipies deur Vorm AR-11 of die USCIS aanlyn-adresverandering-instrument. Die federale indiening is afsonderlik van die opdatering van 'n staats-DMV-rekord, 'n werkgewer, 'n skool of die U.S. Postal Service.",
        "Federal law generally requires motor vehicle offices to offer voter registration to applicants, and forms are screened for citizenship attestations. Non-citizens generally are not eligible to register for federal elections, and a registration record can later create immigration complications.": "Federale wet vereis oor die algemeen dat motorvoertuig-kantore kieserregistrasie aan aansoekers aanbied, en vorms word vir burgerskap-bekragtigings nagegaan. Nie-burgers kwalifiseer oor die algemeen nie om vir federale verkiesings te registreer nie, en 'n registrasierekord kan later immigrasie-komplikasies skep.",
        "Federal residency for tax purposes determines whether worldwide income is reported, which IRS forms apply, and how an interstate move's first and last year are filed at the federal level, separately from state residency rules.": "Federale inwonerskap vir belastingdoeleindes bepaal of wêreldwye inkomste gerapporteer word, watter IRS-vorms van toepassing is, en hoe 'n trek tussen state se eerste en laaste jaar op die federale vlak ingedien word, afsonderlik van staatsinwonerskap-reëls.",
        "Federal rules govern which immigration statuses can purchase coverage and receive financial help through the Affordable Care Act marketplace, and those rules have changed. State-based marketplaces and state-funded programs add another layer that can differ between origin and destination.": "Federale reëls regeer watter immigrasiestatusse dekking kan koop en finansiële hulp deur die Affordable Care Act-mark kan ontvang, en daardie reëls het verander. Staatsgebaseerde markte en staat-gefinansierde programme voeg 'n ander laag by wat kan verskil tussen oorsprong en bestemming.",
        "Federal tax authority": "Federale belastingowerheid",
        "Federal tax authority general guidance": "Federale belastingowerheid algemene leiding",
        "Flags risk levels so you know where to focus": "Dui risikovlakke aan sodat u weet waarop om te fokus",
        "Florida Board of Governors page on residency for tuition purposes for the State University System. flbog.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Florida Board of Governors-bladsy oor inwonerskap vir klasgelddoeleindes vir die State University System. flbog.edu gee 403 vir nie-blaaier-versoeke (Cloudflare); dit is 'n bekende vals negatief.",
        "Florida FLHSMV documentation page for nonimmigrant applicants for driver licenses and identification cards.": "Florida FLHSMV-dokumentasie-bladsy vir nie-immigrant-aansoekers vir bestuurslisensies en identifikasiekaarte.",
        "Follow device language": "Volg toesteltaal",
        "For L-1, whether the new worksite is the same qualifying U.S. office described in the petition or a different one": "Vir L-1, of die nuwe werksplek dieselfde kwalifiserende V.S.-kantoor is wat in die petisie beskryf word of 'n ander een",
        "For L-1A, L-1B, and O-1 status, USCIS treats a move to a new worksite as a material change in some fact patterns and not others, depending on what the original petition described and whether the new location is consistent with the approved terms. The analysis follows the underlying petition, not LCA-based MSA rules.": "Vir L-1A-, L-1B- en O-1-status hanteer USCIS 'n trek na 'n nuwe werksplek as 'n wesenlike verandering in sommige feitepatrone en nie in ander nie, afhangend van wat die oorspronklike petisie beskryf het en of die nuwe ligging in lyn is met die goedgekeurde terme. Die ontleding volg die onderliggende petisie, nie LCA-gebaseerde MSA-reëls nie.",
        "For O-1, whether the new venue, event, engagement, or agent arrangement falls within the approved petition scope": "Vir O-1, of die nuwe lokaal, gebeurtenis, verbintenis of agent-reëling binne die goedgekeurde petisie-omvang val",
        "For federal tax purposes, a non-citizen is generally treated as a resident alien if they meet the Substantial Presence Test or hold lawful permanent resident status, with separate rules in IRS Publication 519 for exempt individuals (such as certain F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q students and scholars) whose days of presence may not count.": "Vir federale belastingdoeleindes word 'n nie-burger oor die algemeen as 'n inwonende vreemdeling behandel as hulle aan die Substantial Presence Test voldoen of wettige permanente-inwoner-status hou, met afsonderlike reëls in IRS Publication 519 vir vrygestelde individue (soos sekere F-1-, J-1-, M-1- en Q-studente en geleerdes) wie se dae van teenwoordigheid moontlik nie tel nie.",
        "For nursing specifically, how the destination state treats primary state of residency under the Nurse Licensure Compact for a non-citizen who declares either the country of origin or the compact state, and any credentials-evaluation requirement (for example, CGFNS) for internationally educated applicants": "Spesifiek vir verpleging, hoe die bestemmingstaat primêre staat van inwonerskap onder die Nurse Licensure Compact behandel vir 'n nie-burger wat óf die land van oorsprong óf die kompak-staat verklaar, en enige kwalifikasie-evaluering-vereiste (byvoorbeeld CGFNS) vir internasionaal opgeleide aansoekers",
        "Form AR-11 paper version posted on uscis.gov.": "Vorm AR-11 papierweergawe geplaas op uscis.gov.",
        "Frame AR-11 as a federal reporting step to verify, not a guarantee of status. Do not state that any specific status category is or is not covered without source. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing such as the i-word, the p-words, and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney for status-specific guidance.": "Stel AR-11 voor as 'n federale rapporteringstap om te verifieer, nie 'n waarborg van status nie. Moenie verklaar dat enige spesifieke statuskategorie wel of nie gedek word sonder bron nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys (regsgevolgtrekking-formulering soos die 'o'-woord, die 'v'-woorde, en boete-vermyding-formulering). Verwys lesers om 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur te raadpleeg vir status-spesifieke leiding.",
        "Frame as a federal requirement that may apply, with a nonimmigrant exception that may apply based on continuous valid status. Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Stel dit voor as 'n federale vereiste wat van toepassing kan wees, met 'n nie-immigrant-uitsondering wat van toepassing kan wees gebaseer op deurlopende geldige status. Moenie verklaar dat enige spesifieke persoon wel of nie moet registreer nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Frame as items to verify in IRS Publication 519 and with a qualified tax preparer. Do not state a person is a dual-status filer for a particular year. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Stel dit voor as items om in IRS Publication 519 en met 'n gekwalifiseerde belastingvoorbereider te verifieer. Moenie verklaar dat 'n persoon 'n dubbel-status-indiener vir 'n bepaalde jaar is nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Frame as items to verify with CMS and the destination-state Medicaid agency. Federal rules have changed and may continue to change. Do not state a person is or is not eligible. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Stel dit voor as items om met CMS en die bestemmingstaat se Medicaid-agentskap te verifieer. Federale reëls het verander en kan voortdurend verander. Moenie verklaar dat 'n persoon wel of nie kwalifiseer nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Frame as items to verify with IRS Publication 519 and a tax preparer. Do not state a person is or is not a resident alien for federal tax purposes. Use may apply and rules differ by jurisdiction. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Stel dit voor as items om met IRS Publication 519 en 'n belastingvoorbereider te verifieer. Moenie verklaar dat 'n persoon wel of nie 'n inwonende vreemdeling vir federale belastingdoeleindes is nie. Gebruik 'kan van toepassing wees' en 'die reëls verskil afhangende van die jurisdiksie'. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Frame as items to verify with the DSO or J-1 sponsor and Study in the States or ICE guidance. This item is specific to F-1, M-1, and J-1 status. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "Stel dit voor as items om met die DSO of J-1-borg en Study in the States- of ICE-leiding te verifieer. Hierdie item is spesifiek vir F-1-, M-1- en J-1-status. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys (regsgevolgtrekking-formulering en boete-vermyding-formulering).",
        "Frame as items to verify with the current HealthCare.gov or state-based marketplace lists. Do not state any specific category is or is not on the lawfully present list, since federal rules have changed. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "Stel dit voor as items om met die huidige HealthCare.gov- of staatsgebaseerde mark-lyste te verifieer. Moenie verklaar dat enige spesifieke kategorie wel of nie op die 'wettig teenwoordig'-lys is nie, aangesien federale reëls verander het. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Full disclaimer:": "Volledige vrywaring:",
        "General information only. Not legal advice. Verify with official sources.": "Slegs algemene inligting. Nie regsadvies nie. Verifieer met amptelike bronne.",
        "General information only. Verify with the relevant official source. Not legal advice.": "Slegs algemene inligting. Verifieer met die relevante amptelike bron. Nie regsadvies nie.",
        "Generate checklist": "Genereer kontrolelys",
        "Generated:": "Gegenereer:",
        "Generates a checklist of topics to verify before moving": "Genereer 'n kontrolelys van onderwerpe om te verifieer voor u trek",
        "Georgia Department of Driver Services page for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including a 30-day rule for establishing Georgia residency.": "Georgia Department of Driver Services-bladsy vir nie-Amerikaanse burger-aansoekers, insluitend 'n 30-dag-reël vir die vestiging van Georgia-inwonerskap.",
        "Get a grouped checklist with risk badges and links to official sources.": "Ontvang 'n gegroepeerde kontrolelys met risiko-aanduiders en skakels na amptelike bronne.",
        "H-1B specific. Frame as verify with employer counsel and USCIS or DOL guidance. Do not state that an amendment is or is not required in a particular fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "H-1B-spesifiek. Stel dit voor as 'verifieer met werkgewer-raadgewer en USCIS- of DOL-leiding'. Moenie verklaar dat 'n wysiging wel of nie in 'n bepaalde feitepatroon vereis word nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "H-1B specific. Use verify whether MSA boundaries cover the new worksite. Do not assert that no amendment is needed in any specific fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "H-1B-spesifiek. Gebruik 'verifieer of MSA-grense die nuwe werksplek dek'. Moenie beweer dat geen wysiging in enige spesifieke feitepatroon nodig is nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "HOW IT WORKS": "HOE DIT WERK",
        "Health clearance documentation": "Gesondheidsklaring-dokumentasie",
        "HealthCare.gov general page on immigrant coverage options.": "HealthCare.gov algemene bladsy oor immigrant-dekkingsopsies.",
        "HealthCare.gov list and explanation of lawfully present categories for ACA marketplace coverage.": "HealthCare.gov-lys en verduideliking van wettig teenwoordige kategorieë vir ACA-mark-dekking.",
        "HealthCare.gov page on which statuses qualify for marketplace coverage.": "HealthCare.gov-bladsy oor watter statusse kwalifiseer vir mark-dekking.",
        "Healthcare access / insurance": "Gesondheidsorgtoegang / versekering",
        "Help avoid enforcement or recommend workarounds": "Help om handhawing te systap of beveel omseilings aan",
        "Helps tailor the checklist. None of these flags create legal conclusions.": "Help om die kontrolelys te pasmaak. Geen van hierdie aanduiders skep regsgevolgtrekkings nie.",
        "High risk only": "Slegs hoë risiko",
        "High-risk categories require separate verification.": "Hoë-risiko-kategorieë vereis afsonderlike verifikasie.",
        "High-risk categories require separate verification. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use of regulated items is lawful.": "Hoë-risiko-kategorieë vereis afsonderlike verifikasie. MoveSafe bepaal nie of besit, vervoer of gebruik van gereguleerde items regmatig is nie.",
        "High-risk items to verify separately": "Hoë-risiko-items om afsonderlik te verifieer",
        "High-risk only": "Slegs hoë risiko",
        "High-risk warning. High-risk categories require separate verification.": "Hoë-risiko-waarskuwing. Hoë-risiko-kategorieë vereis afsonderlike verifikasie.",
        "Highlights stale or placeholder sources": "Lig verouderde of plekhouer-bronne uit",
        "Housing / renter basics": "Behuising / huurder-basiese inligting",
        "How CHIP coverage rules in the destination state interact with the waiting period for your household": "Hoe CHIP-dekkingsreëls in die bestemmingstaat met die wagtydperk vir u huishouding saamwerk",
        "How OPT or STEM OPT employment is treated for FICA while the worker remains a nonresident alien": "Hoe OPT- of STEM OPT-indiensneming vir FICA hanteer word terwyl die werker 'n nie-inwonende vreemdeling bly",
        "How a future change to LPR status before age 26 may affect the registration question": "Hoe 'n toekomstige verandering na LPR-status voor ouderdom 26 die registrasievraag kan beïnvloed",
        "How a mid-year move between states may affect aid-application deadlines": "Hoe 'n trek tussen state midde-in 'n jaar hulpaansoek-sperdatums kan beïnvloed",
        "How a move mid-coverage may affect the reasonable opportunity period for documentation": "Hoe 'n trek midde-in-dekking die redelike geleentheidstydperk vir dokumentasie kan beïnvloed",
        "How a transfer interacts with current employment authorization, on-campus work, and any pending OPT": "Hoe 'n oordrag met huidige werkmagtiging, op-kampus-werk en enige hangende OPT saamwerk",
        "How a year of arrival to or departure from the United States interacts with the test": "Hoe 'n jaar van aankoms in of vertrek uit die Verenigde State met die toets saamwerk",
        "How an in-progress extension of status (for example, an H-1B amendment or an F-1 transfer) interacts with renewing or replacing the credential": "Hoe 'n in-vordering-verlenging van status (byvoorbeeld 'n H-1B-wysiging of 'n F-1-oordrag) met die hernuwing of vervanging van die geloofsbrief saamwerk",
        "How clinical-placement and background-check requirements interact with your immigration status": "Hoe kliniese plasing- en agtergrondkontrole-vereistes met u immigrasiestatus saamwerk",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification": "Hoe lank u inwonerskap in die bestemmingstaat moet hou voordat u vir binnestaat-klassifikasie oorweeg word",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification, and whether time on a nonimmigrant visa counts": "Hoe lank u inwonerskap in die bestemmingstaat moet hou voor u vir binnestaat-klassifikasie oorweeg word, en of tyd op 'n nie-immigrant-visum tel",
        "How temporary stay is treated differently from permanent relocation": "Hoe tydelike verblyf anders hanteer word as permanente hervestiging",
        "How the destination state defines residency": "Hoe die bestemmingstaat inwonerskap definieer",
        "How the destination state's DMV or other application workflows interact with Selective Service screening": "Hoe die bestemmingstaat se DMV of ander aansoekwerkvloei met Selective Service-sifting saamwerk",
        "How the move affects any STEM OPT Form I-983 training plan and the destination employer's E-Verify status": "Hoe die trek enige STEM OPT-Vorm I-983-opleidingsplan en die bestemming-werkgewer se E-Verify-status beïnvloed",
        "How the move and any change in employer-sponsored coverage interact with marketplace special enrollment timing": "Hoe die trek en enige verandering in werkgewer-geborgde dekking met mark-spesiale-inskrywing-tydsberekening saamwerk",
        "How the move interacts with H-4 dependent status and any pending I-485 or I-140": "Hoe die trek met H-4-afhanklike status en enige hangende I-485 of I-140 saamwerk",
        "How to confirm a registration after applying for a license": "Hoe om 'n registrasie te bevestig na die aansoek om 'n lisensie",
        "How to correct the record if a non-citizen registration was submitted in error": "Hoe om die rekord reg te stel indien 'n nie-burger-registrasie per fout ingedien is",
        "How to decline voter registration when offered at the DMV in that state": "Hoe om kieserregistrasie van die hand te wys wanneer dit by die DMV in daardie staat aangebied word",
        "How to obtain or replace a Selective Service registration record if needed for future immigration or federal-benefit filings": "Hoe om 'n Selective Service-registrasierekord te verkry of te vervang indien dit benodig word vir toekomstige immigrasie- of federale-voordeel-indienings",
        "How unemployment days are counted during a gap between employers around a move": "Hoe werkloosheidsdae getel word tydens 'n gaping tussen werkgewers rondom 'n trek",
        "I am a nursing or healthcare student": "Ek is 'n verpleeg- of gesondheidsorgstudent",
        "I am moving for school": "Ek trek vir skool",
        "I am moving for work": "Ek trek vir werk",
        "I have a car": "Ek het 'n motor",
        "I hold or need a professional license": "Ek besit of benodig 'n professionele lisensie",
        "I may stay temporarily": "Ek mag tydelik bly",
        "I may work in the destination state": "Ek mag in die bestemmingstaat werk",
        "I own a pet": "Ek besit 'n troeteldier",
        "I plan to relocate permanently": "Ek beplan om permanent te hervestig",
        "I rent housing": "Ek huur behuising",
        "I understand": "Ek verstaan",
        "I understand that MoveSafe provides general information and source links, not legal advice.": "Ek verstaan dat MoveSafe algemene inligting en bronskakels verskaf, nie regsadvies nie.",
        "I'm a Dreamer (DACA / similar)": "Ek is 'n Dreamer (DACA / soortgelyk)",
        "I'm a green card holder (LPR)": "Ek is 'n groenkaarthouer (LPR)",
        "I'm on a nonimmigrant visa (F-1, H-1B, J-1, etc.)": "Ek is op 'n nie-immigrant-visum (F-1, H-1B, J-1, ens.)",
        "ICE SEVIS landing page.": "ICE SEVIS-landingsbladsy.",
        "ICE SEVIS overview page for background context on F, M, and J record management.": "ICE SEVIS-oorsigbladsy vir agtergrondkonteks oor F-, M- en J-rekord-bestuur.",
        "ICE page describing F-1 SEVIS transfers.": "ICE-bladsy wat F-1 SEVIS-oordragte beskryf.",
        "IRS Publication 519 describes a dual-status tax year for non-citizens who are both a nonresident and a resident for federal tax purposes during the same year, which can apply to many arrival, departure, and adjustment-of-status fact patterns rather than interstate moves alone.": "IRS Publication 519 beskryf 'n dubbel-status-belastingjaar vir nie-burgers wat beide 'n nie-inwoner en 'n inwoner vir federale belastingdoeleindes tydens dieselfde jaar is, wat van toepassing kan wees op baie aankoms-, vertrek- en status-aanpassing-feitepatrone eerder as net op trekke tussen state.",
        "IRS Publication 519 main page.": "IRS Publication 519 hoofbladsy.",
        "IRS dual-status filer page. Final redirected URL uses the dual-status-individuals slug.": "IRS-dubbel-status-indiener-bladsy. Finale herleide URL gebruik die dual-status-individuals-slug.",
        "IRS general page on taxation of nonresident aliens.": "IRS algemene bladsy oor belasting van nie-inwonende vreemdelinge.",
        "IRS guidance generally describes an exemption from FICA tax for wages paid for services performed by F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q nonresident-alien students, scholars, teachers, researchers, and trainees, when the work is part of the activity for which they were admitted and they remain nonresident aliens for federal tax purposes.": "IRS-leiding beskryf oor die algemeen 'n vrystelling van FICA-belasting vir lone betaal vir dienste uitgevoer deur F-1-, J-1-, M-1- en Q-nie-inwonende-vreemdeling-studente, geleerdes, onderwysers, navorsers en leerlinge, wanneer die werk deel is van die aktiwiteit waarvoor hulle toegang ontvang het en hulle vir federale belastingdoeleindes nie-inwonende vreemdelinge bly.",
        "IRS overview page for non-citizen tax residency status.": "IRS-oorsigbladsy vir nie-burger belasting-inwonerskap-status.",
        "IRS page describing the Substantial Presence Test for federal tax residency.": "IRS-bladsy wat die Substantial Presence Test vir federale belasting-inwonerskap beskryf.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for F, J, M, Q nonresident-alien students and scholars.": "IRS-bladsy oor FICA-belasting-hantering vir F-, J-, M-, Q-nie-inwonende-vreemdeling-studente en -geleerdes.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for non-citizens employed in the U.S.": "IRS-bladsy oor FICA-belasting-hantering vir nie-burgers in diens in die V.S.",
        "Identity and residency documents accepted by the destination state": "Identiteits- en inwonerskapdokumente wat deur die bestemmingstaat aanvaar word",
        "If a credential is issued with an unexpected short term tied to a federal document, the timing of renewal can affect domestic flights, federal building access, and other tasks that may rely on a REAL ID after a move.": "As 'n geloofsbrief met 'n onverwagte kort tydperk uitgereik word wat aan 'n federale dokument gekoppel is, kan die tydsberekening van hernuwing binnelandse vlugte, federale-gebou-toegang en ander take wat na 'n trek op 'n REAL ID staatmaak, beïnvloed.",
        "Illinois Board of Higher Education directory page on campus liaisons supporting students under state tuition-equity provisions.": "Illinois Board of Higher Education-gidsbladsy oor kampus-skakelpersone wat studente onder staats-klasgeld-gelykheid-bepalings ondersteun.",
        "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL) page. ilsos.gov returns a 302 redirect to its own page for curl HEAD requests, which is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov domain; the URL was confirmed via the Secretary of State's own search index.": "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL)-bladsy. ilsos.gov gee 'n 302-herleiding na sy eie bladsy vir curl HEAD-versoeke, wat 'n bekende vals negatief op die langdurige .gov-domein is; die URL is bevestig deur die Secretary of State se eie soekindeks.",
        "Illinois Student Assistance Commission resources page for non-U.S. citizen students including RISE Act and Alternative Application context. isac.org returns 403 to non-browser requests (anti-bot); this is a known false negative.": "Illinois Student Assistance Commission-hulpbronbladsy vir nie-Amerikaanse burger-studente insluitend RISE Act en Alternative Application-konteks. isac.org gee 403 vir nie-blaaier-versoeke (anti-bot); dit is 'n bekende vals negatief.",
        "Immigration status - including Dreamer / DACA status - can significantly affect driver's licenses and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing and healthcare), in-state tuition, SSN-related requirements, and state tax filing. Rules vary by state and federal law and change frequently.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney before relying on any state-by-state summary.": "Immigrasiestatus - insluitend Dreamer / DACA-status - kan bestuurslisensies en REAL ID, professionele lisensiëring (veral verpleging en gesondheidsorg), binnestaatklasgeld, SSN-verwante vereistes en staatsbelastingindiening aansienlik raak. Reëls verskil per staat en federale wet en verander gereeld.\n\nMoveSafe is nie 'n plaasvervanger vir regsraad nie. Oorweeg dit om 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur te raadpleeg voordat u op enige staat-tot-staat-opsomming staatmaak.",
        "Immunization requirements": "Inentingsvereistes",
        "Important to verify": "Belangrik om te verifieer",
        "Inspection requirement": "Inspeksievereiste",
        "Insurance networks, Medicaid and marketplace rules, and prescription transfer processes vary by state.": "Versekeringsnetwerke, Medicaid- en mark-reëls en voorskrif-oordragprosesse verskil per staat.",
        "Insurance networks, student health, prescriptions, primary care access.": "Versekeringsnetwerke, studentegesondheid, voorskrifte, toegang tot primêre sorg.",
        "Internship": "Internskap",
        "J-1 specific. Frame as verify with the program sponsor and reference 22 CFR Part 62. Do not state that any specific category does or does not require sponsor pre-approval for a particular change. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "J-1-spesifiek. Stel dit voor as 'verifieer met die programborg' en verwys na 22 CFR Deel 62. Moenie verklaar dat enige spesifieke kategorie borg-vooraf-goedkeuring vir 'n bepaalde verandering wel of nie vereis nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Jurisdiction: %@": "Jurisdiksie: %@",
        "Know how to respond if asked to register to vote at the DMV": "Weet hoe om te reageer indien daar gevra word om by die DMV vir stem te registreer",
        "L-1 and O-1 specific. Frame as verify against the approved petition and consult petitioner counsel. Do not state that an amendment is or is not needed for any specific scenario. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "L-1- en O-1-spesifiek. Stel dit voor as 'verifieer teen die goedgekeurde petisie en raadpleeg petisionaris-raadgewer'. Moenie verklaar dat 'n wysiging vir enige spesifieke scenario wel of nie nodig is nie. Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys.",
        "Language": "Taal",
        "Last verified:": "Laas geverifieer:",
        "Last verified: %@": "Laas geverifieer: %@",
        "Lawful permanent residents (LPRs / green card holders) can face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing - foreign credentials evaluation may apply), Medicaid and state-marketplace eligibility (the federal 5-year bar interacts with state programs), state tax filing, and how DMVs handle voter-registration prompts (LPRs are not eligible to vote in federal or most state elections).\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney for status-affecting questions and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Wettige permanente inwoners (LPR's / groenkaarthouers) kan staat-tot-staat-variasie ervaar in bestuurslisensiedokumente en REAL ID, professionele lisensiëring (veral verpleging - evaluering van buitelandse kwalifikasies kan van toepassing wees), Medicaid- en staatsmark-kwalifikasie (die federale 5-jaar-perk werk saam met staatsprogramme), staatsbelastingindiening en hoe DMV's kieserregistrasie-aansoeke hanteer (LPR's kwalifiseer nie om in federale of die meeste staatsverkiesings te stem nie).\n\nMoveSafe is nie 'n plaasvervanger vir regsraad nie. Oorweeg dit om 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur te raadpleeg vir status-rakende vrae en 'n gekwalifiseerde belastingkenner vir tussen-staat-indiening.",
        "Lease decisions made based on origin-state assumptions may not match destination-state rules.": "Huurbesluite wat op aannames van die oorsprongstaat gebaseer is, mag dalk nie by die bestemmingstaat se reëls pas nie.",
        "Lease terms, security deposits, notice periods, and tenant protections.": "Huurterme, sekuriteitsdeposito's, kennisgewingstydperke en huurderbeskerming.",
        "Legal aid (general info)": "Regshulp (algemene inligting)",
        "License transfer, deadlines, documents, and REAL ID awareness.": "Lisensie-oordrag, sperdatums, dokumente en REAL ID-bewustheid.",
        "Licensure requirements can affect clinical placement, NCLEX eligibility, endorsement, and employment timing.": "Lisensiëring-vereistes kan kliniese plasing, NCLEX-kwalifikasie, onderskrywing en indiensname-tydsberekening beïnvloed.",
        "Links to official state agency sources": "Skakels na amptelike staatsagentskap-bronne",
        "Load example": "Laai voorbeeld",
        "Local city/county rules may add protections. Review lease language directly.": "Plaaslike stad-/landdrosdistrik-reëls mag bykomende beskerming byvoeg. Hersien huurkontrak-taal direk.",
        "Local ordinance": "Plaaslike ordonnansie",
        "Local pet licensing requirements": "Plaaslike troeteldier-lisensiëring-vereistes",
        "Main USCIS page for H-1B specialty occupations classification.": "Hoof-USCIS-bladsy vir H-1B-spesialiteits-beroepsklassifikasie.",
        "Many nonimmigrant visa holders are not within the standard Medicare or Medicaid eligibility groups, and federal rules in this area have been changing. Destination-state Medicaid rules add another layer that may differ from origin-state rules.": "Baie nie-immigrant-visumhouers is nie binne die standaard Medicare- of Medicaid-kwalifikasie-groepe nie, en federale reëls in hierdie gebied het verander. Bestemmingstaat-Medicaid-reëls voeg 'n ander laag by wat van oorsprongstaat-reëls kan verskil.",
        "Many states require new residents to obtain a state driver's license within a specific period after becoming a resident.": "Baie state vereis dat nuwe inwoners 'n staatsbestuurslisensie binne 'n spesifieke tydperk na inwonerskap verkry.",
        "Mark as not verified": "Merk as nie geverifieer nie",
        "Mark as verified": "Merk as geverifieer",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for nonresidents using Form 1-NR/PY. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Massachusetts Department of Revenue-gids oor persoonlike inkomstebelasting vir nie-inwoners met Vorm 1-NR/PY. mass.gov gee 403 vir nie-blaaier-versoeke (Cloudflare); dit is 'n bekende vals negatief.",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for part-year residents. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Massachusetts Department of Revenue-gids oor persoonlike inkomstebelasting vir deeljaar-inwoners. mass.gov gee 403 vir nie-blaaier-versoeke (Cloudflare); dit is 'n bekende vals negatief.",
        "Massachusetts RMV identification requirements page covering REAL ID, standard licenses, and lawful presence documentation. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov-hosted state portal.": "Massachusetts RMV identifikasie-vereistes-bladsy wat REAL ID, standaard-lisensies en wettige-teenwoordigheid-dokumentasie dek. mass.gov gee 403 vir nie-blaaier-versoeke (Cloudflare); dit is 'n bekende vals negatief op die langdurige .gov-gehoste staatsportaal.",
        "May involve penalties or licensing consequences.": "Kan boetes of lisensiëring-gevolge behels.",
        "Minimum coverage, state-specific rules, and policy address updates.": "Minimum dekking, staatspesifieke reëls en polisadres-opdaterings.",
        "Missing a school or hospital onboarding requirement can delay clinical hours and graduation timing.": "Om 'n skool- of hospitaal-aansluitingsvereiste te mis kan kliniese ure en graduering-tydsberekening vertraag.",
        "Missing a state motor vehicle deadline can create administrative or driving-related problems after relocation.": "Om 'n staatsmotorvoertuig-sperdatum te mis kan administratiewe of bestuursverwante probleme veroorsaak na hervestiging.",
        "Missing source": "Ontbrekende bron",
        "Missing the transfer reporting steps at the new school, or letting the transfer release date and program start fall out of sync, can affect status maintenance and access to on-campus work.": "Om die oordrag-rapporteringstappe by die nuwe skool te mis, of toe te laat dat die oordrag-vrystellingsdatum en programbegin uit sinkronisasie raak, kan status-instandhouding en toegang tot op-kampus-werk beïnvloed.",
        "Mixed jurisdiction": "Gemengde jurisdiksie",
        "MoveSafe checklist": "MoveSafe-kontrolelys",
        "MoveSafe is a source-first checklist tool. It links you to official resources and highlights topics to verify. It does not provide legal advice.": "MoveSafe is 'n bron-eerste kontrolelys-instrument. Dit skakel u na amptelike hulpbronne en lig onderwerpe uit om te verifieer. Dit verskaf nie regsadvies nie.",
        "MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves. You can still build a checklist, but some items may not apply.": "MoveSafe is ontwerp vir trekke van staat tot staat. U kan steeds 'n kontrolelys saamstel, maar sommige items mag dalk nie van toepassing wees nie.",
        "MoveSafe prefers official agency sources. Placeholder entries should be replaced with verified URLs before production use.": "MoveSafe verkies amptelike agentskapsbronne. Plekhouer-inskrywings behoort met geverifieerde URL's vervang te word voor produksiegebruik.",
        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "MoveSafe verskaf algemene regs- en administratiewe inligting wat op openbaar beskikbare bronne gebaseer is. Dit verskaf nie regsadvies nie, skep nie 'n prokureur-kliënt-verhouding nie, en behoort nie gebruik te word as 'n plaasvervanger vir advies van 'n gelisensieerde prokureur in u jurisdiksie nie. Wette en agentskapsreëls verander gereeld. Verifieer altyd inligting met amptelike bronne voor u besluite neem.",
        "Moving across state lines? Know what to verify before you go.": "Trek u oor staatsgrense? Weet wat om te verifieer voordat u gaan.",
        "Moving for school": "Trek vir skool",
        "Moving for work": "Trek vir werk",
        "Moving from %1$@ to %2$@": "Trek van %1$@ na %2$@",
        "Moving from one state's aid program to another's may change which aid applications to consider and which documents to gather, and this can affect how to plan tuition and living costs at the destination.": "Om van een staat se hulpprogram na 'n ander s'n te trek, kan verander watter hulpaansoeke om te oorweeg en watter dokumente om in te samel, en dit kan beïnvloed hoe u klasgeld en lewenskoste by die bestemming beplan.",
        "Moving may change which state tax withholding forms apply, and remote work can create cross-state payroll questions.": "Trek kan verander watter staatsbelastingafhouding-vorms van toepassing is, en afgeleë werk kan tussen-staat-betaalstaatvrae skep.",
        "Moving to another state for clinical rotations, externships, or supervised practice.": "Trek na 'n ander staat vir kliniese rotasies, eksternskappe of toesighoudende praktyk.",
        "NCLEX and license-by-endorsement steps can stall when documentation does not match a destination board's current rules, which can delay clinical placement, hire dates, and compact-state recognition.": "NCLEX en lisensie-deur-onderskrywing-stappe kan vasval wanneer dokumentasie nie by 'n bestemmingsraad se huidige reëls pas nie, wat kliniese plasing, indiensname-datums en kompak-staat-erkenning kan vertraag.",
        "NCLEX eligibility requirements": "NCLEX-kwalifikasievereistes",
        "NCSBN Licensure Compacts overview, including Nurse Licensure Compact context for non-citizen primary state of residency declarations.": "NCSBN Licensure Compacts-oorsig, insluitend Nurse Licensure Compact-konteks vir nie-burger primêre staat van inwonerskap-verklarings.",
        "National Council of State Boards of Nursing licensure guidance page for background context across boards.": "National Council of State Boards of Nursing lisensiëring-leiding-bladsy vir agtergrondkonteks oor rade heen.",
        "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education page summarizing the Tuition Equality Act and the 2020 statute affecting dependent students of H-1B holders.": "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education-bladsy wat die Tuition Equality Act en die 2020-statuut wat afhanklike studente van H-1B-houers raak, opsom.",
        "New York DMV REAL ID page noting that an Enhanced ID is for U.S. citizens only and that REAL ID issued to applicants with temporary lawful status may expire with the federal document.": "New York DMV REAL ID-bladsy wat noem dat 'n Enhanced ID slegs vir Amerikaanse burgers is en dat REAL ID wat aan aansoekers met tydelike wettige status uitgereik word, met die federale dokument kan verval.",
        "New York DMV documentation guidance for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including REAL ID and standard credentials.": "New York DMV dokumentasie-leiding vir nie-Amerikaanse burger-aansoekers, insluitend REAL ID en standaard-geloofsbriewe.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance FAQ on residency, nonresident filing, and telecommuting.": "New York Department of Taxation and Finance-FAQ oor inwonerskap, nie-inwoner-indiening en telewerk.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance page on nonresident and part-year filing using Form IT-203.": "New York Department of Taxation and Finance-bladsy oor nie-inwoner- en deeljaar-indiening met Vorm IT-203.",
        "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN licensure requirements page, which administers nursing licensure for New York.": "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN-lisensiëring-vereistes-bladsy, wat verpleeg-lisensiëring vir New York administreer.",
        "No items match your filters": "Geen items pas by u filters nie",
        "No source has been added yet for this item. Add an official source before relying on it.": "Geen bron is nog vir hierdie item bygevoeg nie. Voeg 'n amptelike bron by voordat u daarop staatmaak.",
        "No sources are attached to the items in this view.": "Geen bronne is aan die items in hierdie aansig geheg nie.",
        "Nonimmigrant visa holders (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, and others) face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID (often tied to I-94 / visa dates), in-state tuition (most public universities classify F-1 students as out-of-state), professional licensure documentation, tax residency rules, and health-insurance options. USCIS also requires reporting any address change within 10 days via Form AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney, your school's DSO if on F-1, employer HR or immigration counsel if on a work visa, and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Nie-immigrant-visumhouers (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1 en ander) ondervind staat-tot-staat-variasie in bestuurslisensiedokumente en REAL ID (dikwels gekoppel aan I-94 / visumdatums), binnestaatklasgeld (die meeste openbare universiteite klassifiseer F-1-studente as buitestaatlik), professionele lisensiëringdokumentasie, belasting-inwonerskapreëls en gesondheidsversekering-opsies. USCIS vereis ook dat enige adresverandering binne 10 dae via Vorm AR-11 aangemeld word.\n\nMoveSafe is nie 'n plaasvervanger vir regsraad nie. Oorweeg dit om 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur te raadpleeg, u skool se DSO indien op F-1, werkgewer se MH of immigrasieraadgewer indien op 'n werkvisum, en 'n gekwalifiseerde belastingkenner vir tussen-staat-indiening.",
        "Not sure yet": "Nog nie seker nie",
        "Note for editors: %@": "Nota vir redakteurs: %@",
        "Notes:": "Notas:",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact general information": "Nurse Licensure Compact algemene inligting",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact participation": "Deelname aan Nurse Licensure Compact",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact public FAQ page including the rule that a non-citizen applicant may declare either country of origin or the compact state as primary state of residency.": "Nurse Licensure Compact openbare FAQ-bladsy insluitend die reël dat 'n nie-burger-aansoeker óf land van oorsprong óf die kompak-staat as primêre staat van inwonerskap kan verklaar.",
        "Nursing / healthcare licensure": "Verpleging / gesondheidsorglisensiëring",
        "Nursing education, licensure, endorsement, temporary permits, and compact license rules are handled by state boards of nursing and may differ by state.": "Verpleegopleiding, lisensiëring, onderskrywing, tydelike permitte en kompak-lisensie-reëls word deur staatsverpleegrade hanteer en kan per staat verskil.",
        "Nursing school / healthcare training": "Verpleegskool / gesondheidsorgopleiding",
        "OFFICIAL SOURCES": "AMPTELIKE BRONNE",
        "Official destination state attorney general - tenant resources": "Amptelike bestemmingstaat se prokureur-generaal - huurder-hulpbronne",
        "Official destination state board of nursing": "Amptelike bestemmingstaat se Board of Nursing",
        "Official destination state department of agriculture - pet entry": "Amptelike bestemmingstaat se departement van landbou - troeteldier-toegang",
        "Official destination state department of health": "Amptelike bestemmingstaat se departement van gesondheid",
        "Official destination state department of labor": "Amptelike bestemmingstaat se departement van arbeid",
        "Official destination state motor vehicle agency": "Amptelike bestemmingstaat-motorvoertuigagentskap",
        "Official destination state professional licensing portal": "Amptelike bestemmingstaat se professionele lisensiëring-portaal",
        "Official destination state tax agency": "Amptelike bestemmingstaat-belastingagentskap",
        "Official federal agency": "Amptelike federale agentskap",
        "Official local agency": "Amptelike plaaslike agentskap",
        "Official origin state motor vehicle agency": "Amptelike oorsprongstaat-motorvoertuigagentskap",
        "Official source needed before relying on this item.": "Amptelike bron word benodig voordat u op hierdie item staatmaak.",
        "Official state agency": "Amptelike staatsagentskap",
        "Open official source": "Open amptelike bron",
        "Optional profile": "Opsionele profiel",
        "Origin and destination are the same. MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves - some items may not apply.": "Oorsprong en bestemming is dieselfde. MoveSafe is ontwerp vir trekke tussen state - sommige items mag dalk nie van toepassing wees nie.",
        "Origin state": "Oorsprongstaat",
        "Origin state DMV / MVA": "Oorsprongstaat DMV / MVA",
        "Origin:": "Oorsprong:",
        "Parking permit and campus housing rules": "Parkeerpermit- en kampus-behuising-reëls",
        "Part-year residency, remote work, and school attendance may all affect state tax filing.": "Deeljaar-inwonerskap, afgeleë werk en skoolbywoning kan almal staatsbelastingindiening beïnvloed.",
        "Permanent relocation": "Permanente hervestiging",
        "Pet rules may be set by state, local, or housing-provider policies. Each layer can have different requirements.": "Troeteldierreëls kan deur staats-, plaaslike of behuisingsverskafferbeleide ingestel word. Elke laag kan verskillende vereistes hê.",
        "Pets": "Troeteldiere",
        "Pick a purpose and the categories that apply.": "Kies 'n doel en die kategorieë wat van toepassing is.",
        "Placeholder - replace with official source": "Plekhouer - vervang met amptelike bron",
        "Placeholder source": "Plekhouer-bron",
        "Placeholder source. Replace with an official source before relying on this item.": "Plekhouer-bron. Vervang met 'n amptelike bron voordat u op hierdie item staatmaak.",
        "Plate requirements (front and/or rear)": "Nommerplaatvereistes (voor en/of agter)",
        "Please confirm the disclaimer to continue.": "Bevestig asseblief die vrywaring om voort te gaan.",
        "Please fix the following:": "Stel asseblief die volgende reg:",
        "Possibly outdated": "Moontlik verouderd",
        "Practical requirement": "Praktiese vereiste",
        "Prescription medications, especially controlled substances, may be subject to state, federal, and pharmacy-level rules during interstate moves.": "Voorskrifmedikasie, veral beheerde stowwe, kan tydens tussen-staat-trekke aan staats-, federale en apteekvlak-reëls onderworpe wees.",
        "Primary USCIS landing page for Form AR-11.": "Primêre USCIS-landingsbladsy vir Vorm AR-11.",
        "Primary care access after moving": "Toegang tot primêre sorg na u trek",
        "Primary state of residence requirements": "Vereistes vir primêre staat van inwonerskap",
        "Professional and occupational licensing boards (including nursing, medicine, law, engineering, and many others) set their own documentation rules. Whether a state board accepts an EAD, asks for an SSN, accepts an ITIN or affidavit, accepts an I-797 for an H-1B or O-1 worker, or requires fingerprint background checks tied to a specific status can differ across states and across professions within a state. Some boards specifically address F-1 OPT and J-1 academic-training applicants.": "Professionele en beroeps-lisensiëringsrade (insluitend verpleging, geneeskunde, regte, ingenieurswese en baie ander) stel hul eie dokumentasiereëls in. Of 'n staatsraad 'n EAD aanvaar, om 'n SSN vra, 'n ITIN of verklaring aanvaar, 'n I-797 vir 'n H-1B- of O-1-werker aanvaar, of vingerafdruk-agtergrondkontroles gekoppel aan 'n spesifieke status vereis, kan verskil tussen state en tussen beroepe binne 'n staat. Sommige rade spreek spesifiek F-1 OPT- en J-1 akademiese-opleiding-aansoekers aan.",
        "Professional and occupational licensing boards set their own documentation rules. Whether a state board accepts an Employment Authorization Document, asks for an SSN, accepts an ITIN, or requires an attestation about lawful presence can differ across states and across professions within a state.": "Professionele en beroeps-lisensiëringsrade stel hul eie dokumentasiereëls in. Of 'n staatsraad 'n Employment Authorization Document aanvaar, om 'n SSN vra, 'n ITIN aanvaar of 'n bekragtiging oor wettige teenwoordigheid vereis, kan verskil tussen state en tussen beroepe binne 'n staat.",
        "Professional license transfer": "Professionele lisensie-oordrag",
        "Professional licensing board": "Professionele lisensiëringsraad",
        "Provide legal advice or attorney-client services": "Verskaf regsadvies of prokureur-kliënt-dienste",
        "Public college and university residency rules for tuition often treat nonimmigrant visa holders (such as F-1 and J-1 students) differently from U.S. citizens and lawful permanent residents. Some visa categories are considered able to establish a domicile in a state, while others generally are not, and some states have separate statutes or board regulations that apply to high school graduates from the state regardless of status. Rules vary across the state higher-education agency, a system office, and individual institutions.": "Openbare kollege- en universiteit-inwonerskap-reëls vir klasgeld behandel dikwels nie-immigrant-visumhouers (soos F-1- en J-1-studente) anders as Amerikaanse burgers en wettige permanente inwoners. Sommige visumkategorieë word beskou as in staat om 'n domisilie in 'n staat te vestig, terwyl ander oor die algemeen nie kan nie, en sommige state het afsonderlike statute of raadsregulasies wat van toepassing is op hoërskool-gegradueerdes van die staat ongeag status. Reëls verskil tussen die staats-hoëronderwysagentskap, 'n stelselkantoor en individuele instellings.",
        "Purpose": "Doel",
        "Purpose:": "Doel:",
        "Purpose: %@": "Doel: %@",
        "REAL ID and standard credentials use different document checklists and have different uses for federal purposes such as boarding domestic flights or entering certain federal buildings.": "REAL ID en standaard-geloofsbriewe gebruik verskillende dokument-kontrolelys en het verskillende gebruike vir federale doeleindes soos die bestyging van binnelandse vlugte of die betreding van sekere federale geboue.",
        "RISK": "RISIKO",
        "Rabies and other vaccination documentation requirements": "Hondsdolheid- en ander inentingdokumentasie-vereistes",
        "Receiving school registrar / residency office": "Ontvangende skoolregistrateur / inwonerskap-kantoor",
        "Recently verified": "Onlangs geverifieer",
        "Registering or being recorded as registered, even by mistake, may create issues for naturalization, status renewal, or future immigration filings. The risk of an inadvertent record can depend on how a state's DMV workflow is designed.": "Om te registreer of as geregistreer aangeteken te word, selfs per ongeluk, kan kwessies skep vir naturalisering, statushernuwing of toekomstige immigrasie-indienings. Die risiko van 'n onbedoelde rekord kan afhang van hoe 'n staat se DMV-werkvloei ontwerp is.",
        "Registration deadline after establishing residency": "Registrasie-sperdatum na vestiging van inwonerskap",
        "Registration deadlines, inspection, emissions, title, and plate rules.": "Registrasie-sperdatums, inspeksie, emissies, titel- en nommerplaatreëls.",
        "Registration, inspection, emissions, title, and plate requirements can differ by state.": "Registrasie-, inspeksie-, emissie-, titel- en nommerplaatvereistes kan per staat verskil.",
        "Relocating for a job or new employer.": "Hervestig vir 'n werk of nuwe werkgewer.",
        "Relocating for a nursing or healthcare program (ABSN, MEPN, MSN, allied health, etc.).": "Hervestig vir 'n verpleeg- of gesondheidsorgprogram (ABSN, MEPN, MSN, verwante gesondheid, ens.).",
        "Relocating to attend an undergraduate or graduate program.": "Hervestig om 'n voorgraadse of nagraadse program by te woon.",
        "Relocating with family members or dependents.": "Hervestig saam met gesinslede of afhanklikes.",
        "Replace official agency or licensed-professional guidance": "Vervang amptelike agentskap- of gelisensieerde professionele leiding",
        "Replace with an official URL from the destination state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "Vervang met 'n amptelike URL van die bestemmingstaat se motorvoertuigagentskap voordat u op hierdie item staatmaak.",
        "Replace with an official URL from the origin state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "Vervang met 'n amptelike URL van die oorsprongstaat se motorvoertuigagentskap voordat u op hierdie item staatmaak.",
        "Replace with official federal tax-authority guidance. Use only as general orientation; consult a qualified tax professional.": "Vervang met amptelike federale belastingowerheid-leiding. Gebruik slegs as algemene oriëntasie; raadpleeg 'n gekwalifiseerde belastingkenner.",
        "Replace with the destination state agriculture / animal-health agency. Some species, breeds, or vaccinations have specific entry rules.": "Vervang met die bestemmingstaat se landbou- / diergesondheidsagentskap. Sommige spesies, rasse of inentings het spesifieke toegangsreëls.",
        "Replace with the destination state department of health URL.": "Vervang met die bestemmingstaat se departement van gesondheid-URL.",
        "Replace with the destination state labor agency for paid leave, withholding, and labor law basics.": "Vervang met die bestemmingstaat se arbeidsagentskap vir betaalde verlof, afhouding en basiese arbeidsreg.",
        "Replace with the destination state's attorney general or housing agency. Local ordinances may add protections.": "Vervang met die bestemmingstaat se prokureur-generaal of behuisingsagentskap. Plaaslike ordonnansies kan bykomende beskerming byvoeg.",
        "Replace with the destination state's official tax agency website. Tax rules and forms change frequently.": "Vervang met die bestemmingstaat se amptelike belastingagentskap-webwerf. Belastingreëls en -vorms verander gereeld.",
        "Replace with the destination state's professional licensing portal or relevant board for the specific profession.": "Vervang met die bestemmingstaat se professionele lisensiëring-portaal of relevante raad vir die spesifieke beroep.",
        "Replace with the official NLC information page. Participation status and rules can change.": "Vervang met die amptelike NLC-inligtingsbladsy. Deelnamestatus en reëls kan verander.",
        "Replace with the official destination state board of nursing URL. Board rules govern eligibility and endorsement.": "Vervang met die amptelike bestemmingstaat se Board of Nursing-URL. Raadsreëls regeer kwalifikasie en onderskrywing.",
        "Replace with the receiving school's residency or tuition classification page. School rules differ from state-agency rules.": "Vervang met die ontvangende skool se inwonerskap- of klasgeld-klassifikasie-bladsy. Skoolreëls verskil van staatsagentskap-reëls.",
        "Required documents for the application": "Vereiste dokumente vir die aansoek",
        "Required notice periods for ending a lease": "Vereiste kennisgewingstydperke om 'n huurkontrak te beëindig",
        "Reset all selections": "Stel alle keuses terug",
        "Reset progress": "Stel vordering terug",
        "Residency can affect tuition, taxes, licensing, and benefits, and is determined by the relevant state agency, school, or tax authority - not by MoveSafe.": "Inwonerskap kan klasgeld, belasting, lisensiëring en voordele beïnvloed, en word bepaal deur die relevante staatsagentskap, skool of belastingowerheid - nie deur MoveSafe nie.",
        "Review destination-state lease and tenant basics": "Hersien bestemmingstaat se huur- en huurder-basiese inligting",
        "Review recommended": "Hersiening aanbeveel",
        "Risk level: %@": "Risikovlak: %@",
        "Road trip": "Padreis",
        "Rules around possession, documentation, and refills can differ across states and pharmacies.": "Reëls rondom besit, dokumentasie en hervullings kan verskil tussen state en apteke.",
        "Rules may differ substantially by jurisdiction, and MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in a specific situation.": "Reëls kan aansienlik per jurisdiksie verskil, en MoveSafe bepaal nie of besit, vervoer of gebruik regmatig is in 'n bepaalde situasie nie.",
        "Rules vary widely. Verify with official sources.": "Reëls verskil aansienlik. Verifieer met amptelike bronne.",
        "SSA POMS section on the lawful presence framework that informs Medicare and other federal benefits.": "SSA POMS-afdeling oor die wettige-teenwoordigheid-raamwerk wat Medicare en ander federale voordele inlig.",
        "SSN or identity documentation requirements if applicable": "SSN- of identiteitsdokumentasie-vereistes indien van toepassing",
        "School / institution policy": "Skool- / instellingsbeleid",
        "School or institution": "Skool of instelling",
        "School residency / tuition classification policy": "Skool-inwonerskap- / klasgeld-klassifikasie-beleid",
        "School residency classification": "Skool-inwonerskapklassifikasie",
        "School residency classification, immunization, student insurance, housing.": "Skool-inwonerskapklassifikasie, inenting, studenteversekering, behuising.",
        "School-level requirements can affect tuition classification, enrollment, and clinical participation.": "Skoolvlak-vereistes kan klasgeldklassifikasie, inskrywing en kliniese deelname beïnvloed.",
        "School-specific clinical onboarding requirements": "Skoolspesifieke kliniese aansluitings-vereistes",
        "Schools set their own residency, health-insurance, and immunization requirements separate from state-agency rules.": "Skole stel hul eie inwonerskap-, gesondheidsversekering- en inentingsvereistes vas afsonderlik van staatsagentskapsreëls.",
        "Secondary reference": "Sekondêre verwysing",
        "Security deposit limits and return deadlines": "Sekuriteitsdeposito-limiete en terugbetalingsperdatums",
        "Security deposit limits, notice periods, eviction rules, and late-fee rules can differ between states and between cities.": "Sekuriteitsdeposito-limiete, kennisgewingstydperke, uitsettingreëls en laatfooireëls kan tussen state en tussen stede verskil.",
        "Select a destination state.": "Kies 'n bestemmingstaat.",
        "Select a purpose.": "Kies 'n doel.",
        "Select a purpose…": "Kies 'n doel…",
        "Select a state…": "Kies 'n staat…",
        "Select an origin state.": "Kies 'n oorsprongstaat.",
        "Select at least one category.": "Kies ten minste een kategorie.",
        "Select one or more. You can change these later.": "Kies een of meer. U kan dit later verander.",
        "Selective Service System FAQ page.": "Selective Service System FAQ-bladsy.",
        "Selective Service System PDF chart that lists categories and exceptions.": "Selective Service System PDF-grafiek wat kategorieë en uitsonderings lys.",
        "Selective Service System main Who Needs to Register page, with nonimmigrant exception language.": "Selective Service System se hoof 'Who Needs to Register'-bladsy, met nie-immigrant-uitsondering-taal.",
        "Selective Service System materials generally describe a Selective Service registration requirement for almost all men ages 18 through 25 living in the United States, with an exception for men who are in the United States on a current valid nonimmigrant visa while that status remains valid up to age 26.": "Selective Service System-materiaal beskryf oor die algemeen 'n Selective Service-registrasievereiste vir byna alle mans tussen 18 en 25 jaar wat in die Verenigde State woon, met 'n uitsondering vir mans wat in die Verenigde State op 'n huidige geldige nie-immigrant-visum is terwyl daardie status geldig bly tot ouderdom 26.",
        "Selective Service registration is a federal requirement for almost all males ages 18 through 25 in the United States, regardless of citizenship, and many states link license or ID applications to that registration.": "Selective Service-registrasie is 'n federale vereiste vir byna alle mans tussen 18 en 25 jaar in die Verenigde State, ongeag burgerskap, en baie state koppel lisensie- of ID-aansoeke aan daardie registrasie.",
        "Setting up mail forwarding or updating a state license can give a false sense that the federal address record is current, while a pending USCIS case may still be sending notices to an old address.": "Om pos-aanstuur in te stel of 'n staatslisensie op te dateer kan 'n vals gevoel skep dat die federale adresrekord aktueel is, terwyl 'n hangende USCIS-saak nog kennisgewings na 'n ou adres mag stuur.",
        "Settings": "Instellings",
        "Share checklist": "Deel kontrolelys",
        "Short-to-medium term internship or co-op in another state.": "Kort- tot mediumtermyn-internskap of koöp in 'n ander staat.",
        "Show high-risk categories separately": "Wys hoë-risiko-kategorieë afsonderlik",
        "Some checklist items use placeholder sources. Replace with official sources before relying on them.": "Sommige kontrolelys-items gebruik plekhouer-bronne. Vervang met amptelike bronne voor u daarop staatmaak.",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules.": "Sommige items mag verskillend gereguleer word oor staatsgrense heen en kan staatswet, plaaslike ordonnansies, federale wet of agentskapsreëls behels.",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in any specific situation. Verify directly with official sources and consult a licensed attorney or relevant agency if needed.": "Sommige items mag verskillend gereguleer word oor staatsgrense heen en kan staatswet, plaaslike ordonnansies, federale wet of agentskapsreëls behels. MoveSafe bepaal nie of besit, vervoer of gebruik regmatig is in enige bepaalde situasie nie. Verifieer direk met amptelike bronne en raadpleeg 'n gelisensieerde prokureur of relevante agentskap indien nodig.",
        "Some sources have not been verified recently. Check the official website before relying on them.": "Sommige bronne is nie onlangs geverifieer nie. Gaan die amptelike webwerf na voor u daarop staatmaak.",
        "Some states issue driver licenses or state IDs to nonimmigrant visa applicants on a shortened renewal cycle that tracks the I-94 or an underlying federal document, instead of the multi-year cycle used for citizens. Fees, renewal timing, and steps after a status extension can differ between origin and destination states.": "Sommige state reik bestuurslisensies of staats-ID's aan nie-immigrant-visum-aansoekers uit op 'n verkorte hernuwingsiklus wat die I-94 of 'n onderliggende federale dokument volg, in plaas van die meerjarige siklus wat vir burgers gebruik word. Fooie, hernuwing-tydsberekening en stappe na 'n status-verlenging kan tussen oorsprong- en bestemmingstate verskil.",
        "Source not yet documented": "Bron nog nie gedokumenteer nie",
        "Source status: %@": "Bronstatus: %@",
        "Sources referenced in this checklist": "Bronne waarna in hierdie kontrolelys verwys word",
        "Sources to verify only": "Slegs bronne om te verifieer",
        "Sources:": "Bronne:",
        "Sources: placeholder - verify with the relevant official agency.": "Bronne: plekhouer - verifieer met die relevante amptelike agentskap.",
        "Stale or placeholder sources only": "Slegs verouderde of plekhouer-bronne",
        "Stale source": "Verouderde bron",
        "Stale source warning": "Waarskuwing oor verouderde bron",
        "Start fresh": "Begin van voor af",
        "Starting work at a new worksite outside the LCA's MSA without an amended petition can affect status maintenance, and the timing of the amended petition filing matters for when the worker can begin at the new location.": "Om werk by 'n nuwe werksplek buite die LCA se MSA sonder 'n gewysigde petisie te begin, kan status-instandhouding beïnvloed, en die tydsberekening van die gewysigde petisie-indiening is belangrik vir wanneer die werker by die nuwe ligging kan begin.",
        "State DMV document checklists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 and similar) can differ from those used for U.S. citizens or lawful permanent residents. Accepted combinations of passport, visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, and I-797 or employer letter may vary, and some states ask for an SSN card or an SSA ineligibility letter.": "Staats-DMV-dokument-kontrolelys vir nie-immigrant-visum-aansoekers (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 en soortgelyke) kan verskil van dié wat vir Amerikaanse burgers of wettige permanente inwoners gebruik word. Aanvaarde kombinasies van paspoort, visum, I-94, I-20 of DS-2019, en I-797 of werkgewer-brief kan verskil, en sommige state vra om 'n SSN-kaart of 'n SSA-onkwalifiseerbaarheidsbrief.",
        "State University of New York Board of Trustees policy on residency for tuition purposes, including which visa categories can establish New York domicile. suny.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing state university system domain.": "State University of New York Board of Trustees-beleid oor inwonerskap vir klasgelddoeleindes, insluitend watter visumkategorieë New York-domisilie kan vestig. suny.edu gee 403 vir nie-blaaier-versoeke (Cloudflare); dit is 'n bekende vals negatief op die langdurige staatsuniversiteit-stelseldomein.",
        "State filing requirements, part-year residency, remote work implications.": "Staatsindieningsvereistes, deeljaar-inwonerskap, implikasies van afgeleë werk.",
        "State grant and scholarship programs each have their own rules about whether non-citizen students may be considered, what application form (FAFSA, a state alternative, or an institutional form) is used, and what documentation is needed.": "Staatsbeurs- en studiebeursprogramme het elk hul eie reëls oor of nie-burger-studente oorweeg kan word, watter aansoekvorm (FAFSA, 'n staatsalternatief of 'n institusionele vorm) gebruik word, en watter dokumentasie benodig word.",
        "State labor law basics (paid sick leave, breaks, final pay rules)": "Basiese staatsarbeidsreg (betaalde siekverlof, pouses, finale-betalingreëls)",
        "State law": "Staatswet",
        "State residency basics": "Basiese staatsinwonerskap",
        "State tax filing can apply even when income is earned remotely. Rules differ by state.": "Staatsbelastingindiening kan van toepassing wees selfs wanneer inkomste afgeleë verdien word. Reëls verskil per staat.",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. A person treated as a nonresident alien on the federal return may still be a resident, part-year resident, or nonresident for state purposes depending on domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors. States may or may not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "Staatsbelasting-inwonerskap word onder elke staat se eie reëls bepaal, wat van federale belasting-inwonerskap kan verskil. 'n Persoon wat as 'n nie-inwonende vreemdeling op die federale staat behandel word, kan steeds 'n inwoner, deeljaar-inwoner of nie-inwoner vir staatsdoeleindes wees afhangend van domisilie, dae van fisiese teenwoordigheid, werkgewer-ligging en ander faktore. State kan al dan nie aan federale inkomstebelasting-verdrag-uitsluitings voldoen nie.",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. Domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors can each play a role.": "Staatsbelasting-inwonerskap word onder elke staat se eie reëls bepaal, wat van federale belasting-inwonerskap kan verskil. Domisilie, dae van fisiese teenwoordigheid, werkgewer-ligging en ander faktore kan elk 'n rol speel.",
        "State tax withholding, labor law basics, remote work considerations.": "Staatsbelastingafhouding, basiese arbeidsreg, oorwegings vir afgeleë werk.",
        "States and individual public colleges and universities use different tuition-classification rules for non-citizens, including how prior in-state high school attendance, current immigration status, and a parent's residency are considered.": "State en individuele openbare kolleges en universiteite gebruik verskillende klasgeld-klassifikasiereëls vir nie-burgers, insluitend hoe vorige binnestaat-hoërskoolbywoning, huidige immigrasiestatus en 'n ouer se inwonerskap oorweeg word.",
        "States may require proof of identity, residency, lawful presence, school documents, or other paperwork.": "State mag bewys van identiteit, inwonerskap, wettige teenwoordigheid, skooldokumente of ander papierwerk vereis.",
        "Staying in another state temporarily without intending to become a resident.": "Bly tydelik in 'n ander staat sonder die voorneme om 'n inwoner te word.",
        "Student health insurance requirements": "Studente-gesondheidsversekering-vereistes",
        "Student or temporary resident exceptions": "Uitsonderings vir studente of tydelike inwoners",
        "Student relocation": "Studentehervestiging",
        "Subleasing rules": "Onderverhuringsreëls",
        "TSA REAL ID FAQs page covering documentation for citizens and non-citizens.": "TSA REAL ID FAQ-bladsy wat dokumentasie vir burgers en nie-burgers dek.",
        "TSA REAL ID overview page. Note: www.dhs.gov/real-id now redirects to TSA's REAL ID page.": "TSA REAL ID-oorsigbladsy. Let wel: www.dhs.gov/real-id herlei nou na TSA se REAL ID-bladsy.",
        "Tap to collapse": "Tik om in te vou",
        "Tap to expand": "Tik om uit te brei",
        "Taxes / state filing awareness": "Belasting / staatsindieningbewustheid",
        "Temporary permit availability": "Beskikbaarheid van tydelike permit",
        "Temporary stay": "Tydelike verblyf",
        "Texas Board of Nursing endorsement information page, relevant when moving from another state with a license.": "Texas Board of Nursing-onderskrywingsinligting-bladsy, relevant wanneer u uit 'n ander staat met 'n lisensie trek.",
        "Texas Board of Nursing licensure eligibility page covering general requirements and documentation expectations.": "Texas Board of Nursing lisensiëring-kwalifikasie-bladsy wat algemene vereistes en dokumentasie-verwagtinge dek.",
        "Texas Department of Public Safety driver license identification documentation page covering U.S. citizen and non-U.S. citizen applicants.": "Texas Department of Public Safety se bestuurslisensie-identifikasie-dokumentasie-bladsy wat Amerikaanse burger- en nie-Amerikaanse burger-aansoekers dek.",
        "Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board page on residency for tuition purposes, including categories of nonimmigrant applicants and special pathways under the Texas Education Code.": "Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board-bladsy oor inwonerskap vir klasgelddoeleindes, insluitend kategorieë van nie-immigrant-aansoekers en spesiale paaie onder die Texas Education Code.",
        "The deadline for applying for a destination-state license": "Die sperdatum om aansoek te doen vir 'n bestemmingstaat-lisensie",
        "This checklist is based on your selected categories and available source data. It may not include every requirement that applies to your situation.": "Hierdie kontrolelys is gebaseer op u gekose kategorieë en beskikbare brondata. Dit mag nie elke vereiste insluit wat op u situasie van toepassing is nie.",
        "This checklist is not a legal conclusion. Verify with official sources and consult a licensed professional where appropriate.": "Hierdie kontrolelys is nie 'n regsgevolgtrekking nie. Verifieer met amptelike bronne en raadpleeg 'n gelisensieerde professionele persoon waar gepas.",
        "This source has not been verified in more than a year. Treat as stale and verify directly with the official source.": "Hierdie bron is in meer as 'n jaar nie geverifieer nie. Hanteer dit as verouderd en verifieer direk met die amptelike bron.",
        "This source has not been verified in more than six months. Check the official website before relying on it.": "Hierdie bron is in meer as ses maande nie geverifieer nie. Gaan die amptelike webwerf na voor u daarop staatmaak.",
        "This source was checked more than 90 days ago. Review recommended.": "Hierdie bron is meer as 90 dae gelede nagegaan. Hersiening word aanbeveel.",
        "Title transfer process": "Titel-oordragproses",
        "Total topics to verify: %d": "Totale onderwerpe om te verifieer: %d",
        "Travel documentation if flying with a pet": "Reisdokumentasie indien u met 'n troeteldier vlieg",
        "Treating an intra-MSA worksite change as a full new petition can create unnecessary cost and timing risk, while assuming portability rules apply without checking the MSA boundaries can lead to status questions later.": "Om 'n intra-MSA-werksplek-verandering as 'n volledige nuwe petisie te hanteer, kan onnodige koste- en tydsberekening-risiko skep, terwyl om aan te neem dat oordraagbaarheidsreëls van toepassing is sonder om die MSA-grense na te gaan, later tot statusvrae kan lei.",
        "Treats high-risk categories with a \"Do not assume\" label": "Hanteer hoë-risiko-kategorieë met 'n \"Moenie aanneem nie\"-etiket",
        "Try clearing risk filters or the high-risk / stale-source toggles.": "Probeer om risiko-filters of die hoë-risiko / verouderde-bron-skakelaars uit te skakel.",
        "USCIS Employment Authorization page providing background on the EAD (Form I-766) used in some state DMV and licensing document lists.": "USCIS Employment Authorization-bladsy wat agtergrond bied oor die EAD (Vorm I-766) wat in sommige staats-DMV- en lisensiëring-dokumentlys gebruik word.",
        "USCIS Form AR-11 PDF": "USCIS Vorm AR-11 PDF",
        "USCIS L-1A classification page.": "USCIS L-1A-klassifikasie-bladsy.",
        "USCIS L-1B classification page.": "USCIS L-1B-klassifikasie-bladsy.",
        "USCIS O-1 classification page.": "USCIS O-1-klassifikasie-bladsy.",
        "USCIS Policy Manual chapter that describes federal address-change reporting.": "USCIS Policy Manual-hoofstuk wat federale adresverandering-rapportering beskryf.",
        "USCIS archive page summarizing the 2015 Simeio Solutions final guidance and the LCA-amendment trigger for worksite changes outside the MSA.": "USCIS-argiefbladsy wat die 2015 Simeio Solutions-finale-leiding en die LCA-wysiging-snellermeganisme vir werksplek-veranderings buite die MSA opsom.",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that a U.S. Postal Service change-of-address request does not change a record with USCIS and that USPS does not forward USCIS mail. A destination-state DMV address update is also a separate step from the federal AR-11 filing.": "USCIS-leiding dui oor die algemeen aan dat 'n U.S. Postal Service-adresveranderingversoek nie 'n rekord by USCIS verander nie en dat USPS nie USCIS-pos aanstuur nie. 'n Bestemmingstaat-DMV-adres-opdatering is ook 'n afsonderlike stap van die federale AR-11-indiening.",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that an H-1B worker moving to a new worksite within the same MSA or area of intended employment as the existing LCA does not require a new LCA or an amended H-1B petition, although the existing LCA may still need to be posted at the new worksite. The federal AR-11 address change requirement still applies to the worker.": "USCIS-leiding dui oor die algemeen aan dat 'n H-1B-werker wat na 'n nuwe werksplek binne dieselfde MSA of gebied van voorgenome indiensneming as die bestaande LCA trek, nie 'n nuwe LCA of 'n gewysigde H-1B-petisie benodig nie, alhoewel die bestaande LCA dalk nog by die nuwe werksplek geplaas moet word. Die federale AR-11-adresverandering-vereiste is steeds op die werker van toepassing.",
        "USCIS newsroom alert describing the online change-of-address tool and clarifying that USPS forwarding does not change a USCIS record.": "USCIS-nuuskamer-waarskuwing wat die aanlyn-adresverandering-instrument beskryf en verklaar dat USPS-aanstuur nie 'n USCIS-rekord verander nie.",
        "USCIS umbrella page on the federal change-of-address requirement, including the online change-of-address tool.": "USCIS-sambreelblad oor die federale adresverandering-vereiste, insluitend die aanlyn-adresverandering-instrument.",
        "USPS mail-forwarding page; referenced to clarify that USPS change-of-address does not substitute for federal AR-11 filing per USCIS guidance.": "USPS-pos-aanstuur-bladsy; verwys om te verduidelik dat USPS-adresverandering nie federale AR-11-indiening volgens USCIS-leiding vervang nie.",
        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "Onder 22 CFR Deel 62 onderhou J-1-programborge die SEVIS-rekord en monitor die aktiwiteitsplek vir elke uitruilbesoeker. 'n Trek wat verblyf, aktiwiteitsplek of gasheer-organisasie verander aktiveer oor die algemeen 'n uitruilbesoeker-rapporteringsverpligting aan die borg en 'n borg-opdatering aan SEVIS.",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "Onder USCIS-leiding na Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015) is 'n H-1B-werker se trek na 'n werksplek buite die metropolitaanse statistiese gebied (MSA) of gebied van voorgenome indiensneming wat op die huidige Labor Condition Application (LCA) gelys is, oor die algemeen 'n wesenlike verandering wat 'n nuwe LCA en 'n gewysigde H-1B-petisie verg.",
        "Understand how the destination state defines residency": "Verstaan hoe die bestemmingstaat inwonerskap definieer",
        "University of California admissions page on the AB 540 nonresident tuition exemption, noting that most nonimmigrant visa holders such as F-1 or J-1 generally cannot establish California residency for tuition purposes.": "University of California-toelatingsbladsy oor die AB 540 nie-inwoner-klasgeld-vrystelling, en noem dat die meeste nie-immigrant-visumhouers soos F-1 of J-1 oor die algemeen nie California-inwonerskap vir klasgelddoeleindes kan vestig nie.",
        "Update employment paperwork and state tax forms": "Werk werkspapierwerk en staatsbelastingvorms by",
        "Use do not assume language. Do not state that USPS or DMV updates can substitute for AR-11 (USCIS guidance says they generally do not). Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "Gebruik 'moenie aanneem nie'-taal. Moenie verklaar dat USPS- of DMV-opdaterings AR-11 kan vervang nie (USCIS-leiding sê dat dit oor die algemeen nie doen nie). Vermy die iOS SafeCopy-vermy-lys (regsgevolgtrekking-formulering en boete-vermyding-formulering).",
        "Vaccination, licensing, breed restrictions, housing pet policies.": "Inenting, lisensiëring, ras-beperkings, behuising-troeteldierbeleide.",
        "Vaccination, local licensing, breed restrictions, and landlord pet policies can vary across destination states and cities.": "Inenting, plaaslike lisensiëring, rasbeperkings en verhuurder-troeteldierbeleide kan verskil oor bestemmingstate en stede heen.",
        "Vehicle registration": "Voertuigregistrasie",
        "Vehicle registration rules can change after a state-to-state move, especially if the destination state treats you as a new resident.": "Voertuigregistrasiereëls kan verander na 'n trek tussen state, veral as die bestemmingstaat u as 'n nuwe inwoner hanteer.",
        "Verification progress": "Verifikasievordering",
        "Verified: %1$d of %2$d": "Geverifieer: %1$d uit %2$d",
        "Verify ACA marketplace categories described as lawfully present for nonimmigrants": "Verifieer ACA-mark-kategorieë wat as wettig teenwoordig vir nie-immigrante beskryf word",
        "Verify F-1 SEVIS school-transfer steps if the move is to a different school": "Verifieer F-1 SEVIS-skooloordrag-stappe indien die trek na 'n ander skool is",
        "Verify FICA (Social Security and Medicare) handling for F-1 and J-1 nonresident aliens": "Verifieer FICA (Social Security en Medicare)-hantering vir F-1- en J-1-nie-inwonende vreemdelinge",
        "Verify H-1B portability and address handling for a move within the same MSA": "Verifieer H-1B-oordraagbaarheid en adres-hantering vir 'n trek binne dieselfde MSA",
        "Verify J-1 program sponsor reporting for site-of-activity or host-organization changes": "Verifieer J-1-programborg-rapportering vir aktiwiteitsplek- of gasheer-organisasie-veranderings",
        "Verify L-1 or O-1 worksite change handling against the approved petition": "Verifieer L-1- of O-1-werksplek-verandering-hantering teen die goedgekeurde petisie",
        "Verify Medicare and Medicaid eligibility rules that may apply to nonimmigrants after a move": "Verifieer Medicare- en Medicaid-kwalifikasiereëls wat op nie-immigrante na 'n trek van toepassing kan wees",
        "Verify SEVP Portal updates for address, employer, and unemployment-day tracking on OPT or STEM OPT": "Verifieer SEVP Portal-opdaterings vir adres, werkgewer en werkloosheidsdag-opvolging op OPT of STEM OPT",
        "Verify destination Board of Nursing documentation for non-citizen applicants": "Verifieer bestemming Board of Nursing-dokumentasie vir nie-burger-aansoekers",
        "Verify destination-state DMV documents for non-citizen applicants": "Verifieer bestemmingstaat-DMV-dokumente vir nie-burger-aansoekers",
        "Verify destination-state DMV documents for nonimmigrant visa applicants": "Verifieer bestemmingstaat-DMV-dokumente vir nie-immigrant-visum-aansoekers",
        "Verify destination-state financial aid eligibility rules for non-citizens": "Verifieer bestemmingstaat se finansiële-hulp-kwalifikasiereëls vir nie-burgers",
        "Verify destination-state professional licensing documentation rules for visa or OPT applicants": "Verifieer bestemmingstaat se professionele lisensiëring-dokumentasiereëls vir visum- of OPT-aansoekers",
        "Verify destination-state tuition classification rules for non-citizen students": "Verifieer bestemmingstaat se klasgeld-klassifikasiereëls vir nie-burger-studente",
        "Verify destination-state tuition classification rules for nonimmigrant visa students": "Verifieer bestemmingstaat se klasgeld-klassifikasiereëls vir nie-immigrant-visum-studente",
        "Verify documentation a destination-state licensing board requires for non-citizens": "Verifieer dokumentasie wat 'n bestemmingstaat-lisensiëringsraad vir nie-burgers vereis",
