        "Whether the destination state has elected the CHIPRA option to cover lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals without a federal waiting period": "Of die bestemmingstaat die CHIPRA-opsie gekies het om wettig wonende kinders en swanger individue sonder 'n federale wagtydperk te dek",
