        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace with separate documentation rules": "Of die bestemmingstaat HealthCare.gov gebruik of sy eie staatsgebaseerde mark met afsonderlike dokumentasiereëls bestuur",
        "Whether the destination state uses the CHIPRA/ICHIA option to remove the waiting period for children, pregnant people, or both": "Of die bestemmingstaat die CHIPRA/ICHIA-opsie gebruik om die wagtydperk vir kinders, swanger persone of beide te verwyder",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV asks all applicants about voter registration, including non-citizens": "Of die bestemmingstaat se DMV alle aansoekers oor kieserregistrasie vra, insluitend nie-burgers",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV record reflects the new address on its own timeline": "Of die bestemmingstaat se DMV-rekord die nuwe adres volgens sy eie tydlyn weergee",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV typically issues a credential to your visa category for the standard multi-year cycle or for a shortened cycle keyed to the I-94 or another federal document": "Of die bestemmingstaat se DMV tipies 'n geloofsbrief aan u visumkategorie vir die standaard-meerjarige siklus uitreik, of vir 'n verkorte siklus gekoppel aan die I-94 of 'n ander federale dokument",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV will issue a REAL ID to your specific visa category and which federal documents it requires": "Of die bestemmingstaat se DMV 'n REAL ID aan u spesifieke visumkategorie sal uitreik en watter federale dokumente dit vereis",
        "Whether the destination-state board for your profession lists DACA recipients or lawful permanent residents in its documentation guidance": "Of die bestemmingstaat se raad vir u beroep DACA-ontvangers of wettige permanente inwoners in sy dokumentasie-leiding lys",
        "Whether the destination-state board for your profession lists nonimmigrant visa categories or OPT or academic training in its documentation guidance": "Of die bestemmingstaat se raad vir u beroep nie-immigrant-visumkategorieë of OPT of akademiese opleiding in sy dokumentasie-leiding lys",
        "Whether the destination-state license or ID application automatically initiates Selective Service registration": "Of die bestemmingstaat se lisensie- of ID-aansoek outomaties Selective Service-registrasie inisieer",
        "Whether the employer is filing a new LCA and an amended Form I-129 before or shortly after the worker reports to the new worksite": "Of die werkgewer 'n nuwe LCA en 'n gewysigde Vorm I-129 indien voor of kort nadat die werker by die nuwe werksplek aanmeld",
        "Whether the employer or petitioner is filing an amended Form I-129 before the worker reports to the new location": "Of die werkgewer of petisionaris 'n gewysigde Vorm I-129 indien voor die werker by die nuwe ligging aanmeld",
        "Whether the exception covers a specific person depends on age, current status, and continuity of valid nonimmigrant status, and a later transition to LPR or naturalization can revive a registration question relevant to federal benefits and naturalization.": "Of die uitsondering 'n spesifieke persoon dek hang af van ouderdom, huidige status en kontinuïteit van geldige nie-immigrant-status, en 'n latere oorgang na LPR of naturalisering kan 'n registrasievraag herleef wat relevant is vir federale voordele en naturalisering.",
        "Whether the existing LCA needs to be posted at the new worksite for the required period": "Of die bestaande LCA by die nuwe werksplek vir die vereiste tydperk geplaas moet word",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 address change has been filed within 10 days of the residential move": "Of die federale AR-11-adresverandering binne 10 dae na die woonadres-trek ingedien is",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 filing is also needed as a separate step": "Of die federale AR-11-indiening ook as 'n afsonderlike stap benodig word",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 filing is also needed in addition to sponsor notification": "Of die federale AR-11-indiening ook benewens borg-kennisgewing benodig word",
        "Whether the institution you plan to attend sets its own classification rules in addition to any state policy": "Of die instelling wat u beplan om by te woon sy eie klassifikasiereëls instel benewens enige staatsbeleid",
        "Whether the item is regulated by state law": "Of die item deur staatswet gereguleer word",
        "Whether the license expiration is tied to the federal document expiration date": "Of die lisensie-vervaldatum gekoppel is aan die federale dokument se vervaldatum",
        "Whether the medication is a controlled substance under federal or state law": "Of die medikasie 'n beheerde stof onder federale of staatswet is",
        "Whether the move triggers a special enrollment period and the documentation needed to verify status": "Of die trek 'n spesiale inskrywingstydperk aktiveer en die dokumentasie wat benodig word om status te verifieer",
        "Whether the new employer's payroll setup reflects the exemption": "Of die nuwe werkgewer se betaalstaat-opstelling die vrystelling weergee",
        "Whether the new physical and mailing address has been entered in the SEVP Portal or reported to the DSO within 10 days": "Of die nuwe fisiese en posadres binne 10 dae in die SEVP Portal ingevoer is of aan die DSO gerapporteer is",
        "Whether the new worksite falls inside the MSA or area of intended employment listed on the current LCA": "Of die nuwe werksplek binne die MSA of gebied van voorgenome indiensneming val wat op die huidige LCA gelys is",
        "Whether the new worksite is inside the same MSA or area of intended employment as the current LCA, or in a new MSA": "Of die nuwe werksplek binne dieselfde MSA of gebied van voorgenome indiensneming as die huidige LCA is, of in 'n nuwe MSA",
        "Whether the online change-of-address tool in a USCIS online account is the right path, or whether a paper Form AR-11 is needed": "Of die aanlyn-adresverandering-instrument in 'n USCIS-aanlynrekening die regte pad is, of dat 'n papier-Vorm AR-11 benodig word",
        "Whether the original L-1 or O-1 petition listed a specific worksite, employer location, or itinerary that the move changes": "Of die oorspronklike L-1- of O-1-petisie 'n spesifieke werksplek, werkgewer-ligging of reisplan gelys het wat die trek verander",
        "Whether the person is within the age range to which the federal requirement may apply": "Of die persoon binne die ouderdomsreeks val waarop die federale vereiste van toepassing kan wees",
        "Whether the program start date and on-campus reporting deadline at the new school have been confirmed": "Of die programbegin-datum en op-kampus-rapporteringsperdatum by die nuwe skool bevestig is",
        "Whether the tax year of the move includes both nonresident and resident periods for federal tax purposes": "Of die belastingjaar van die trek beide nie-inwoner- en inwoner-tydperke vir federale belastingdoeleindes insluit",
        "Whether the waiting period applies, whether a state option removes it for children or pregnancy, and which documents are accepted can change between origin and destination states and affect coverage continuity.": "Of die wagtydperk van toepassing is, of 'n staatsopsie dit vir kinders of swangerskap verwyder, en watter dokumente aanvaar word kan verander tussen oorsprong- en bestemmingstate en dekkingskontinuïteit beïnvloed.",
        "Whether the worker still meets the IRS conditions for the F-1, J-1, M-1, or Q FICA exemption (status type, primary purpose, and federal tax residency)": "Of die werker nog aan die IRS-voorwaardes vir die F-1-, J-1-, M-1- of Q FICA-vrystelling voldoen (statustipe, primêre doel en federale belasting-inwonerskap)",
        "Whether their current nonimmigrant status is on the list described by the Selective Service System as covered by the exception": "Of hul huidige nie-immigrant-status op die lys is wat deur die Selective Service System beskryf word as gedek deur die uitsondering",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney about how AR-11 interacts with a specific status": "Of u 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg oor hoe AR-11 met 'n spesifieke status saamwerk",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney about how registration history may interact with later filings": "Of u 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg oor hoe registrasie-geskiedenis met latere indienings kan saamwerk",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney before submitting status documentation to the marketplace": "Of u 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor u statusdokumentasie aan die mark indien",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer familiar with non-citizen federal tax issues before relying on a particular residency conclusion": "Of u 'n belastingvoorbereider moet raadpleeg wat met nie-burger federale belastingkwessies vertroud is voor u op 'n bepaalde inwonerskap-gevolgtrekking staatmaak",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer or the employer's payroll team to verify FICA setup after the move": "Of u 'n belastingvoorbereider of die werkgewer se betaalstaat-span moet raadpleeg om FICA-opstelling na die trek te verifieer",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer who handles dual-status filings": "Of u 'n belastingvoorbereider moet raadpleeg wat dubbel-status-indienings hanteer",
        "Whether to consult employer counsel and a licensed immigration attorney before the worker starts at the new location": "Of u werkgewer-raadgewer en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor die werker by die nuwe ligging begin",
        "Whether to consult employer counsel before relying on intra-MSA treatment": "Of u werkgewer-raadgewer moet raadpleeg voor u op intra-MSA-hantering staatmaak",
        "Whether to consult petitioner counsel and a licensed immigration attorney before the worker starts at the new location": "Of u petisionaris-raadgewer en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor die werker by die nuwe ligging begin",
        "Whether to consult the DSO and a licensed immigration attorney before changing employers around an interstate move": "Of u die DSO en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor u werkgewers rondom 'n trek tussen state verander",
        "Whether to consult the DSO and a licensed immigration attorney before making decisions that affect the transfer timeline": "Of u die DSO en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor u besluite neem wat die oordrag-tydlyn beïnvloed",
        "Whether to consult the destination-state Medicaid agency for current eligibility categories": "Of u die bestemmingstaat se Medicaid-agentskap moet raadpleeg vir huidige kwalifikasie-kategorieë",
        "Whether to consult the responsible officer or alternate responsible officer at the sponsor and a licensed immigration attorney for category-specific guidance": "Of u die verantwoordelike beampte of alternatiewe verantwoordelike beampte by die borg en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg vir kategorie-spesifieke leiding",
        "Whether to keep dated confirmations of each address update in case a later filing relies on it": "Of u gedateerde bevestigings van elke adres-opdatering moet hou ingeval 'n latere indiening daarop staatmaak",
        "Whether translations or originals are required, and whether copies are accepted": "Of vertalings of oorspronklikes vereis word, en of kopieë aanvaar word",
        "Whether you fall within a federal exception (for example, qualifying work history, certain humanitarian categories, or specific military-connected categories)": "Of u binne 'n federale uitsondering val (byvoorbeeld kwalifiserende werkgeskiedenis, sekere humanitêre kategorieë of spesifieke militêr-verbonde kategorieë)",
        "Whether you fall within a federal exception to the five-year waiting period (for example, certain humanitarian categories, military-connected status, or qualifying work history)": "Of u binne 'n federale uitsondering tot die vyfjaar-wagtydperk val (byvoorbeeld sekere humanitêre kategorieë, militêr-verbonde status, of kwalifiserende werkgeskiedenis)",
        "Whether you fall within the federal age range and category that must register": "Of u binne die federale ouderdomsreeks en kategorie val wat moet registreer",
        "Whether you may owe a part-year return in the origin state and another in the destination state for the year of the move": "Of u 'n deeljaarstaat in die oorsprongstaat en 'n ander in die bestemmingstaat vir die jaar van die trek verskuldig mag wees",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney about how Selective Service registration interacts with your specific status": "Of u 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg oor hoe Selective Service-registrasie met u spesifieke status saamwerk",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before signing any voter-related paperwork": "Of u 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor u enige stem-verwante papierwerk onderteken",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before signing licensing attestations": "Of u 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor u lisensiëring-bekragtigings onderteken",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before submitting any marketplace documents related to status": "Of u 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor u enige mark-dokumente met betrekking tot status indien",
        "Whether you should consult a tax preparer familiar with nonresident alien filers in the destination state": "Of u 'n belastingvoorbereider moet raadpleeg wat met nie-inwonende-vreemdeling-indieners in die bestemmingstaat vertroud is",
        "Whether you should consult a tax preparer who is familiar with non-citizen filers in the destination state": "Of u 'n belastingvoorbereider moet raadpleeg wat met nie-burger-indieners in die bestemmingstaat vertroud is",
        "Whether you should consult both the board and a licensed immigration attorney before signing licensing attestations": "Of u beide die raad en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor u lisensiëring-bekragtigings onderteken",
        "Whether you should consult both the financial-aid office and a licensed immigration attorney about how your status documentation will be used": "Of u beide die finansiële-hulp-kantoor en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg oor hoe u statusdokumentasie gebruik sal word",
        "Whether you should consult both the registrar and a licensed immigration attorney about how your documentation may interact with classification": "Of u beide die registrateur en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg oor hoe u dokumentasie met klassifikasie kan saamwerk",
        "Whether you should consult the registrar, your designated school official, and a licensed immigration attorney about how your documentation interacts with classification": "Of u die registrateur, u aangewese skoolbeampte en 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg oor hoe u dokumentasie met klassifikasie saamwerk",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing a DMV renewal around a pending federal filing": "Of u u aangewese skoolbeampte, werkgewer-immigrasiekontak, of 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg oor die tydsberekening van 'n DMV-hernuwing rondom 'n hangende federale indiening",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing renewals around an extension or change of status": "Of u u aangewese skoolbeampte, werkgewer-immigrasiekontak, of 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg oor tydsberekening van hernuwings rondom 'n verlenging of verandering van status",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney before applying": "Of u u aangewese skoolbeampte, werkgewer-immigrasiekontak, of 'n gelisensieerde immigrasieprokureur moet raadpleeg voor u aansoek doen",
        "Whether you should speak with your prescriber or pharmacist": "Of u met u voorskrywer of apteker moet praat",
        "Whether your EAD or permanent resident card is on the accepted-documents list": "Of u EAD of permanente-inwoner-kaart op die aanvaarde-dokumente-lys is",
        "Whether your EAD or permanent resident card is on the board's current accepted-documents list": "Of u EAD of permanente-inwoner-kaart op die raad se huidige aanvaarde-dokumente-lys is",
        "Whether your current immigration status is on the marketplace's current 'lawfully present' list": "Of u huidige immigrasiestatus op die mark se huidige 'wettig teenwoordig'-lys is",
        "Whether your current license remains usable during a transition period": "Of u huidige lisensie bruikbaar bly tydens 'n oorgangstydperk",
        "Whether your current policy covers driving in the destination state": "Of u huidige polis bestuur in die bestemmingstaat dek",
        "Whether your employer needs an updated address": "Of u werkgewer 'n bygewerkte adres benodig",
        "Whether your employer needs updated state tax forms": "Of u werkgewer bygewerkte staatsbelastingvorms benodig",
        "Whether your employer's state tax withholding should be updated after the move": "Of u werkgewer se staatsbelastingafhouding na die trek opgedateer behoort te word",
        "Whether your employer's state tax withholding should be updated after the move and which form is used": "Of u werkgewer se staatsbelastingafhouding na die trek opgedateer behoort te word en watter vorm gebruik word",
        "Whether your federal status document is on the destination-state DMV's accepted list for REAL ID": "Of u federale statusdokument op die bestemmingstaat se DMV se aanvaarde lys vir REAL ID is",
        "Whether your health insurance network covers the destination state": "Of u gesondheidsversekering-netwerk die bestemmingstaat dek",
        "Whether your insurer requires you to update your policy address": "Of u versekeraar vereis dat u u polisadres opdateer",
        "Whether your license transfers via endorsement or reciprocity": "Of u lisensie via onderskrywing of wedersydsheid oorgedra word",
        "Whether your pharmacy can transfer the prescription": "Of u apteek die voorskrif kan oordra",
        "Whether your specific school sets its own tuition-classification rules in addition to any state policy": "Of u spesifieke skool sy eie klasgeld-klassifikasiereëls instel benewens enige staatsbeleid",
        "Whether your visa documents (passport with visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, EAD) are on the accepted-documents list": "Of u visumdokumente (paspoort met visum, I-94, I-20 of DS-2019, I-797, EAD) op die aanvaarde-dokumente-lys is",
        "Which documents the destination state Medicaid agency uses to verify status": "Watter dokumente die bestemmingstaat se Medicaid-agentskap gebruik om status te verifieer",
        "Which documents the destination-state agency uses to verify status": "Watter dokumente die bestemmingstaat se agentskap gebruik om status te verifieer",
        "Which factors apply (lease, employment, vehicle registration, voting, tax filing)": "Watter faktore van toepassing is (huurkontrak, indiensneming, voertuigregistrasie, stem, belastingindiening)",
        "Which federal immigration documents (for example, EAD, permanent resident card, USCIS notices) the destination-state DMV currently lists as acceptable": "Watter federale immigrasiedokumente (byvoorbeeld EAD, permanente-inwoner-kaart, USCIS-kennisgewings) die bestemmingstaat se DMV tans as aanvaarbaar lys",
        "Which federal immigration documents the destination-state DMV currently lists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (for example, passport with visa stamp, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, employer support letter)": "Watter federale immigrasiedokumente die bestemmingstaat se DMV tans lys vir nie-immigrant-visum-aansoekers (byvoorbeeld paspoort met visumstempel, I-94, I-20 of DS-2019, I-797, werkgewer-ondersteuningsbrief)",
        "Which forms (1040, 1040-NR, and supporting statements) apply for a dual-status year": "Watter vorms (1040, 1040-NR en ondersteunende verklarings) vir 'n dubbel-status-jaar van toepassing is",
        "Withholding the wrong state's taxes can lead to filing complications and unexpected balances.": "Om die verkeerde staat se belasting af te hou kan tot indieningskomplikasies en onverwagte saldo's lei.",
        "Working in a licensed profession before completing the destination state's licensing process may have regulatory consequences.": "Om in 'n gelisensieerde beroep te werk voor die bestemmingstaat se lisensiëring-proses voltooi is, kan regulatoriese gevolge hê.",
        "Worth knowing about. Usually administrative or low-stakes to verify.": "Werd om van bewus te wees. Gewoonlik administratief of met lae belang om te verifieer.",
        "YOUR CHECKLIST": "U KONTROLELYS",
        "Your selections aren't saved or shared. The checklist is generated locally.": "U keuses word nie gestoor of gedeel nie. Die kontrolelys word plaaslik gegenereer.",
        "eCFR Part 62 covers J-1 Exchange Visitor Program regulations. Curl returned 200 but with an unblock.federalregister.gov redirect, consistent with an anti-bot challenge on a long-standing .gov resource; the canonical eCFR URL still resolves in a browser.": "eCFR Deel 62 dek J-1 Exchange Visitor Program-regulasies. Curl het 200 geretourneer maar met 'n unblock.federalregister.gov-herleiding, in lyn met 'n anti-bot-uitdaging op 'n langdurige .gov-hulpbron; die kanonieke eCFR-URL los nog steeds in 'n blaaier op.",
        "eCFR section that describes J-1 sponsor and exchange-visitor notification obligations. Same eCFR anti-bot redirect observed.": "eCFR-afdeling wat J-1-borg- en uitruilbesoeker-kennisgewing-verpligtings beskryf. Dieselfde eCFR anti-bot-herleiding waargeneem.",
    ]

    /// Somali (Soomaali) - formal register.
    /// Generated 2026-05-19 / 2026-05-21.
    static let somali: [String: String] = [
        "%1$@: %2$d topics": "%1$@: %2$d mowduucyo",
        "%1$d of %2$d items verified": "%1$d ka mid ah %2$d cinwaano la xaqiijiyay",
        "%d item": "%d cinwaan",
        "%d items": "%d cinwaano",
        "%d topic to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "%d mowduuc oo la hubinayo ka hor guuritaanka. Liiskan hubintu ma aha gunaanad sharci.",
        "%d topics to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "%d mowduucyo oo la hubinayo ka hor guuritaanka. Liiskan hubintu ma aha gunaanad sharci.",
        "A first or last year in the United States, or a year that includes adjustment to LPR status, can involve different forms, allowable deductions, and treatment of foreign income than a standard resident or nonresident return.": "Sannadka koowaad ama dambe ee Mareykanka, ama sannad ay ku jirto hagaajinta xaaladda LPR, waxay yeelan kartaa foomamka kala duwan, qaadid loo oggol yahay, iyo qaab loola dhaqmo dakhliga shisheeye kaga duwan soo celin resident ama nonresident oo caadi ah.",
        "A health plan that works at home may have limited in-network access in the destination state.": "Qorshe caafimaad oo ku shaqeeya gurigaaga ayaa laga yaabaa inuu yeesho helitaan shabakad oo xaddidan gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "A household that was covered by a state-funded program in the origin state may not find an equivalent program at the destination, which can affect a move plan.": "Qoys oo lagu daboolay barnaamij lacag-gobol leh oo gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid waxa ay yeelan kartaa inaanu ka heli karin barnaamij u dhigma halka loo socdo, taas oo saamayn ku yeelan karta qorshaha guuritaanka.",
        "A missed AR-11 filing can disrupt USCIS notice delivery for any pending or future case, and may create a question of status maintenance that compounds with employer and school records that also need updating.": "Gudbinta AR-11 ee la seegay waxay carqaladayn kartaa gaarsiinta ogeysiiska USCIS ee kiis kasta oo sugaya ama mustaqbal, waxayna abuuri kartaa su'aal sii-haynta xaaladda oo iskugu darsanta diiwaanada shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada iyo dugsiga ee sidoo kale loo baahan yahay in la cusboonaysiiyo.",
        "A move part-way through a tax year can lead to part-year filings, multiple state filings, or unexpected withholding, and rules for non-citizens generally follow the same state framework as for citizens but documentation can differ.": "U guuritaanka qayb ka mid ah sannad canshuureed waxay horseedi kartaa gudbinno qayb-sano ah, gudbinno gobol oo badan, ama hayid aan la sii sheegin, qawaaniinta aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn guud ahaan waxay raacaan qaab gobol oo isku mid ah sida muwaadiniinta laakiin dukumentiyadu way kala duwanaan karaan.",
        "A move part-way through a tax year may produce part-year filings, multiple state filings, or unexpected withholding, and the interaction between federal nonresident alien treatment and state residency rules can change between origin and destination.": "U guuritaanka qayb ka mid ah sannad canshuureed waxay soo saari kartaa gudbinno qayb-sano ah, gudbinno gobol oo badan, ama hayid aan la sii sheegin, falgalka u dhaxeeyo qaabilaadda nonresident alien ee federaalka iyo qawaaniinta degenaanshaha gobolku waxay isbeddeli kartaa u dhaxeeyo gobollada aad ka soo kacaysid iyo aad u socotid.",
        "A move that triggers a fresh application in the destination state may produce a credential with a different renewal cycle than the prior state used, and timing renewal around an I-94 or visa extension can affect work, study, and travel logistics.": "U guuritaan kicinaya codsi cusub gobolka aad u socotid waxay soo saari kartaa aqoonsi leh wareeg cusboonaysiin oo ka duwan kii uu gobolka hore isticmaalay, wakhtiga cusboonaysiinta agagaarka kordhinta I-94 ama fiisaha ayaa saamayn ku yeelan kara nidaamka shaqada, waxbarashada, iyo safarka.",
        "A move that triggers loss of prior coverage may open a marketplace special enrollment period, and the eligibility framework for nonimmigrants can differ from Medicaid waiting-period rules. Federal rules in this area have been changing.": "U guuritaan kicinaya luminta caymiska hore wuxuu furi karaa muddada isdiiwaangelinta gaarka ah ee suuqa, qaab-dhismeedka u qalmitaanka aan-socdaal-doon ahna wuu ka duwanaan karaa qawaaniinta muddada sugitaanka Medicaid. Qawaaniinta federaalka ee aagga ayaa isbeddelay.",
        "AB 540 nonresident tuition exemption": "AB 540 ka-saaridda kharashka waxbarashada nonresident",
        "About": "Ku saabsan",
        "About Dreamer status": "Ku saabsan xaaladda Dreamer",
        "About green card holder status": "Ku saabsan xaaladda hayste kaadhka cagaaran",
        "About visa-holder status": "Ku saabsan xaaladda hayste fiisaha",
        "Administrative guidance only. Not medical advice.": "Hagid maamul oo keliya. Ma aha talo caafimaad.",
        "Administrative requirement": "Shuruud maamul",
        "After a move that involves a new employer, payroll systems may default to withholding FICA, and a misclassification can take time to correct through the employer or via an IRS refund claim.": "Ka dib guuritaan ay ku jiraan shaqaale cusub oo bixiya shaqada, nidaamyada mushaharku waxay si toos ah u haystaan FICA, qalad-kala-saaridna way qaadan kartaa wakhti in lagu saxo iyada oo loo marayo shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada ama codsi soo celin IRS.",
        "Agency rule": "Qaanuunka hay'adda",
        "All": "Dhammaan",
        "An F-1 student moving to another SEVP-certified school generally goes through a SEVIS record transfer between the current school's DSO and the new school's DSO, with a transfer release date, an initial reporting requirement at the new school, and a new Form I-20.": "Arday F-1 ah oo u guuraya dugsi kale oo SEVP shahaadeysan guud ahaan wuxuu maraa u wareejinta diiwaanka SEVIS u dhaxeeyo DSO-ga dugsiga hadda iyo DSO-ga dugsiga cusub, oo leh taariikh sii-deyn u wareejin, shuruud warbixin bilaw ah dugsiga cusub, iyo Foomka I-20 cusub.",
        "An interstate move during OPT or STEM OPT often coincides with an employer change, and missed reporting can affect both SEVIS standing and the running count of unemployment days, which is tracked at the federal level rather than by the destination state.": "U guuritaanka gobol-dhaafka ah inta lagu jiro OPT ama STEM OPT inta badan waxa la falgasha isbeddelka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, warbixinta la seegay waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa labadaba xaaladda SEVIS iyo tirinta maalmaha shaqo-la'aanta socota, taas oo lagu raadiyo heerka federaalka halkii uu gobolka aad u socotid raadin lahaa.",
        "An outdated SEVIS address can interfere with notice delivery from SEVP or the program sponsor, and uncorrected records can place a SEVIS record at risk of termination, which can have downstream effects on status, work authorization, and travel.": "Cinwaanka SEVIS ee duugay wuxuu carqaladayn karaa gaarsiinta ogeysiiska ka soo socda SEVP ama kafiilka barnaamijka, diiwaanada aan la saxin waxay diiwaanka SEVIS gelin karaan khatarta joojinta, taas oo cawaaqib hoosaadyo ku yeelan karta xaaladda, oggolaanshaha shaqada, iyo safarka.",
        "Apartment or landlord pet policies": "Siyaasadaha xayawaanka guriga ee guriga la kireysto ama mulkiilaha guriga",
        "Applicant Frequently Asked Questions - California Board of Registered Nursing": "Su'aalaha Inta Badan La Iwedyiiyo Codsade - California Board of Registered Nursing",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements.": "Dib-u-dhac codsiga, diidmada, ama dib-u-qaadidda farahaha ayaa raaci karta haddii dukumentiyada aad gudbisid aanay la mid noqon qawaaniinta hadda ee guddiga gobolka aad u socotid, gaar ahaan marka laga guurayo gobol leh shuruudo kala duwan.",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements. Boards of Nursing also vary in how they treat the Nurse Licensure Compact for non-citizen primary state of residency.": "Dib-u-dhac codsiga, diidmada, ama dib-u-qaadidda farahaha ayaa raaci karta haddii dukumentiyada aad gudbisid aanay la mid noqon qawaaniinta hadda ee guddiga gobolka aad u socotid, gaar ahaan marka laga guurayo gobol leh shuruudo kala duwan. Guddiyada Kalkaalisada sidoo kale way ka kala duwanaan karaan sida ay ula dhaqmaan Nurse Licensure Compact aan-muwaadinka gobolka aasaasiga ah ee degenaanshaha.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance and other tasks that rely on a state ID after a move.": "Imaanshaha aan la haynin isku-darka dukumentiyada ee uu sugayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid waxay dib u dhigi kartaa bixinta shatiga iyo waxqabadyada kale ee ku tiirsan aqoonsiga gobolka ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance, which then delays other tasks that rely on a state credential after a move, including rental, employer onboarding, and school registration.": "Imaanshaha aan la haynin isku-darka dukumentiyada ee uu sugayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid waxay dib u dhigi kartaa bixinta shatiga, taas oo dib u dhig karta waxqabadyada kale ee ku tiirsan aqoonsiga gobolka ka dib guuritaanka, oo ay ku jiraan kiraysiga, gelinta shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, iyo diiwaangelinta dugsiga.",
        "Arriving without the right documents can delay your license and other tasks that depend on it.": "Imaanshaha aan la haynin dukumentiyada saxda ah waxay dib u dhigi kartaa shatigaaga iyo waxqabadyada kale ee ku tiirsan.",
        "Assuming H-1B-style MSA logic for L-1 or O-1 can lead to a missed amendment when the original petition described a specific worksite or itinerary that no longer matches.": "Is-malaynta caqliga MSA ee qaab H-1B leh ee L-1 ama O-1 waxay horseedi kartaa beddel la seegay marka codsiga asalka ahi sheegay goob shaqo oo gaar ah ama jadwal aan dib u-mid ahayn.",
        "Auto insurance": "Caymiska baabuurka",
        "Auto insurance minimums and rules differ by state. Insurers may need to update your policy after a move.": "Heerarka ugu hooseeya iyo qawaaniinta caymiska baabuurka way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta. Hay'adaha caymisku waxay u baahan karaan inay cusboonaysiiyaan caymiskaaga ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "Auto-detected: %@": "Si toos ah loo aqoonsaday: %@",
        "Awareness item": "Cinwaan wacyigelin",
        "Back to builder": "Ku noqo sameeyaha",
        "Back to home": "Ku noqo bogga hore",
        "Background check and fingerprinting requirements": "Shuruudaha baaritaanka asalka iyo qaadidda farahaha",
        "Background check or fingerprinting requirements": "Shuruudaha baaritaanka asalka ama qaadidda farahaha",
        "Based on your selected states and purpose, here are topics to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "Iyada oo ku saleysan gobolladaada la doortay iyo ujeeddadaada, halkan waxa ku jira mowduucyo aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso ka hor guuritaanka. Liiskan hubintu ma aha gunaanad sharci.",
        "Because the J-1 sponsor (not USCIS) controls the SEVIS record and may need Department of State approval for certain changes, a move can affect program compliance differently from H-1B or F-1 scenarios.": "Sababtoo ah kafiilka J-1 (ee aan ahayn USCIS) waxa uu xakameeyaa diiwaanka SEVIS waxa uu u baahan karaa oggolaanshaha Waaxda Gobolka isbeddel gaar ah, u guuritaanku wuxuu si kala duwan u saamayn karaa u-hoggaansanaanta barnaamijka kaga duwan xaaladaha H-1B ama F-1.",
        "Beneficiary-facing CMS site on Medicare basics.": "Bogga CMS ee jeedha ka-faa'iidaystaha ee aasaaska Medicare.",
        "Board of nursing requirements, compact licenses, clinical placement.": "Shuruudaha guddiga kalkaalisada, shatiyada heshiiska, meelaynta isbitaalka.",
        "Boards of Nursing may have specific guidance about documentation for non-citizen applicants, including whether an SSN is required, whether an ITIN or attestation is accepted, how foreign education is evaluated, and how license endorsement works when moving from another state.": "Guddiyada Kalkaalisadu waxay yeelan karaan hagid gaar ah oo ku saabsan dukumentiyada codsadayaasha aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn, oo ay ku jiraan inay SSN loo baahan yahay, inay ITIN ama caddayn la aqbalayo, sida waxbarashada shisheeye loo qiimeeyo, iyo sida aqoonsiga shatigu u shaqeeyo marka laga guurayo gobol kale.",
        "Breed or species restrictions (state, local, or housing-level)": "Xayiraadaha nooca ama jinsiga (heerka gobolka, deegaanka, ama guriga)",
        "BridgeUSA J-1 Program Categories": "BridgeUSA J-1 Qaybaha Barnaamijka",
        "Build a state-to-state checklist for licenses, vehicles, housing, pets, work, school, healthcare licensure, and other rules that may change when you move.": "Samee liis hubin oo gobol-ka-gobol oo ku saabsan shatiyada, gawaarida, guryaha, xayawaanka guriga, shaqada, dugsiga, shatiga daryeelka caafimaadka, iyo qawaaniin kale oo laga yaabo inay isbeddelaan markaad guurto.",
        "Build checklist": "Samee liis hubinta",
        "Build my checklist": "Samee liiskayga hubinta",
        "Build your relocation checklist": "Samee liiskaaga hubinta guuritaanka",
        "Builder options": "Doorashooyinka sameeyaha",
        "CBP I-94 Official Site": "Bogga Rasmiga ah ee CBP I-94",
        "CBP I-94 site for retrieving the most recent admission record.": "Bogga CBP I-94 oo loo isticmaalo soo helitaanka diiwaanka soo dhoweynta ugu dambeyey.",
        "CHECKLIST BUILDER": "SAMEEYAHA LIISKA HUBINTA",
        "CMS Marketplace Overview of Exchanges": "CMS Dulmar Suuqa ee Is-weydaarsiyada",
        "CMS Original Medicare (Part A and B) Eligibility and Enrollment": "CMS Original Medicare (Qaybta A iyo B) U Qalmitaanka iyo Isdiiwaangelinta",
        "CMS Press Release on Federal Medicaid and CHIP Funding Limits for Certain Noncitizens": "CMS Saxaafadda ee Xayiraadaha Maalgelinta Medicaid iyo CHIP ee Federaalka ee Aan-Muwaadiniinta-Ahayn Qaarkood",
        "CMS landing page on the federal and state marketplaces. Redirected from a cciio URL.": "Bogga aasaasiga ah ee CMS ee suuqyada federaalka iyo gobolka. Waxa laga wareejiyay URL cciio.",
        "CMS page summarizing Original Medicare eligibility, including the five-year continuous residency provision for lawfully admitted permanent residents.": "Bogga CMS oo kooba u qalmitaanka Original Medicare, oo ay ku jirto qodobka degenaansho joogto ah ee shanta sano ee deganayaasha joogto ah ee si sharci ah loo soo dhoweeyay.",
        "CMS press release on April 2026 guidance to implement statutory limits on federal Medicaid and CHIP funding for certain noncitizens, taking effect October 1, 2026, and noting the carve-out for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "Saxaafadda CMS ee hagidda Abriil 2026 si loo hirgeliyo xayiraadaha xeer ah ee maalgelinta Medicaid iyo CHIP ee federaalka ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn qaarkood, oo dhaqan-gali doonta Oktoobar 1, 2026, oo lagu xusi doono ka-saaridda carruurta iyo dadka uurka leh ee si sharci ah u degan.",
        "CPR / BLS certification": "Shahaadada CPR / BLS",
        "CROSS-STATE RELOCATION CHECKLIST": "LIISKA HUBINTA U GUURISTA GOBOL KALE",
        "CUNY tuition and fee manual chapter on residency, covering nonimmigrant visa categories that may establish New York domicile and high-school-attendance provisions.": "Cutubka manual-ka kharashka waxbarashada iyo lacagaha CUNY ee ku saabsan degenaanshaha, oo daboolaya qaybaha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah ee laga yaabo inay aasaasaan domicile New York iyo qodobada ka qaybgalka dugsiga sare.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing applicant FAQ page covering documentation, SSN, and immigration-status questions.": "Bogga FAQ ee codsade California Board of Registered Nursing oo daboolaya su'aalaha dukumentiyada, SSN, iyo xaaladda socdaalka.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing page on international endorsement requirements, including credentials evaluation.": "Bogga California Board of Registered Nursing ee shuruudaha aqoonsiga caalamiga ah, oo ay ku jirto qiimaynta aqoonsiga.",
        "California DMV REAL ID page covering documentation for non-U.S. citizens, including how the credential expiration may track the underlying federal document.": "Bogga REAL ID ee California DMV oo daboolaya dukumentiyada aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn, oo ay ku jirto sida dhicitaanka aqoonsigu uu uga raaci karo dukumentiga federaalka ee hoosta yaal.",
        "California FTB page on part-year and nonresident filers, including a note that California does not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "Bogga California FTB ee filerada qayb-sano ah iyo nonresident, oo ay ku jirto qoraal sheegaya in California aanay raacin marka laga reebay heshiiska canshuurta dakhliga federaalka.",
        "California Franchise Tax Board page on residency, nonresidency, and part-year status for state income tax purposes.": "Bogga California Franchise Tax Board ee degenaanshaha, aan-degenaanshaha, iyo xaaladda qayb-sano ah ee ujeeddooyinka canshuurta dakhliga gobolka.",
        "Can cause inconvenience, fees, or compliance problems if ignored.": "Waxay sababi kartaa dhibaato, kharashyo, ama dhibaatooyin u hoggaansanaan haddii la iska indhatiro.",
        "Categories": "Qaybaha",
        "Categories where rules vary substantially. Verify directly with official sources.": "Qaybaha qawaaniintu si weyn ugu kala duwan yihiin. Si toos ah uga hubi ilaha rasmiga ah.",
        "Check insurance networks, student health, and prescription transfer": "Hubi shabakadaha caymiska, caafimaadka ardayda, iyo u wareejinta dawooyinka",
        "Check pet vaccination, licensing, and housing rules": "Hubi qawaaniinta tallaalka, shatiga, iyo guryaha xayawaanka",
        "Check the destination state board of nursing requirements": "Hubi shuruudaha guddiga kalkaalisada ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Check whether a destination-state license application triggers Selective Service registration": "Hubi inay codsiga shatiga gobolka aad u socotid uu kicinayo diiwaangelinta Selective Service",
        "Check whether moving creates a state tax filing requirement": "Hubi inay guuritaanku abuuro shuruudda gudbinta canshuurta gobolka",
        "Check whether your professional license transfers": "Hubi inay shatigaaga xirfadda u wareego",
        "Checklist": "Liiska hubinta",
        "Checklist builder": "Sameeyaha liiska hubinta",
        "Choose your origin and destination state.": "Dooro gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid iyo gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Choose your origin and destination, your purpose, and the categories that apply. MoveSafe will generate a list of topics to verify before moving.": "Dooro gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid iyo kan aad u socotid, ujeeddadaada, iyo qaybaha khusayso. MoveSafe wuxuu abuuri doonaa liis mowduucyo aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso ka hor guuritaanka.",
        "Choose your states, purpose, and categories. MoveSafe will assemble a source-linked checklist with risk badges.": "Dooro gobolladaada, ujeeddadaada, iyo qaybahaaga. MoveSafe wuxuu isu keenayaa liis hubin oo ilo ku xiran oo leh calaamado khatar.",
        "Choosing the wrong credential type at the destination-state DMV can mean reapplying later, and document expiration may shorten the validity of a REAL ID issued to non-citizens.": "Doorashada nooca aqoonsiga khaldan DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid waxay macnaheedu noqon karaa dib-u-codsasho goor dambe, dhicitaanka dukumentigu waxa uu gaaban karaa muddo-ansax ah ee REAL ID-ga loo bixiyay aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn.",
        "Clears the verified state on items currently shown.": "Nadiifiya xaaladda hubinta ee cinwaanada hadda muujinaya.",
        "Clinical placement": "Meelaynta isbitaalka",
        "Clinical sites and schools may require immunizations, drug screens, CPR/BLS, background checks, and other clearances separate from board licensure.": "Goobaha isbitaalka iyo dugsiyadu waxay u baahnaan karaan tallaal, baaritaan daroogo, CPR/BLS, baaritaan asal, iyo nadiifin kale oo gaar ka ah shatiga guddiga.",
        "Confirm clinical placement and school onboarding requirements": "Xaqiiji shuruudaha meelaynta isbitaalka iyo gelinta dugsiga",
        "Confirm required documents for a destination-state license": "Xaqiiji dukumentiyada loo baahan yahay shatiga gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Confirm school residency, insurance, and immunization rules": "Xaqiiji qawaaniinta degenaanshaha dugsiga, caymiska, iyo tallaalka",
        "Confirm your auto insurance covers the destination state": "Xaqiiji in caymiskaaga baabuurka uu daboolayo gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Continue my checklist": "Sii wad liiskayga hubinta",
        "Continuing education requirements": "Shuruudaha waxbarashada sii socota",
        "Continuity of coverage after a move depends on whether the destination state operates its own marketplace, which categories of non-citizens it considers, and whether state-funded coverage is offered to people who are not eligible for the federal marketplace.": "Sii-socoshada caymiska ka dib guuritaanka waxay ku xirantahay inay gobolka aad u socotid uu maamulayo suuqiisa, qaybaha aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee uu tixgaliyo, iyo inay caymis lacag-gobol leh loo bixiyo dadka aan u qalmin suuqa federaalka.",
        "Could not generate checklist": "Lama abuuri karin liiska hubinta",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page covering personal information updates.": "Bogga xarunta kaalmada SEVIS ee DHS Study in the States oo daboolaya cusboonaysiinada macluumaadka shakhsiga.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on F-1 SEVIS transfer mechanics.": "Bogga xarunta kaalmada SEVIS ee DHS Study in the States oo ku saabsan farsamada u wareejinta F-1 SEVIS.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on STEM OPT.": "Bogga xarunta kaalmada SEVIS ee DHS Study in the States oo ku saabsan STEM OPT.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVP Portal help page describing OPT reporting.": "Bogga kaalmada SEVP Portal ee DHS Study in the States oo qeexaya warbixinta OPT.",
        "DHS Study in the States blog post on the 10-day DSO reporting expectation.": "Qoraal-bilog DHS Study in the States oo ku saabsan rajada warbixinta DSO ee 10-maalmood.",
        "DHS Study in the States guidance for F-1 and M-1 students on reporting address changes to the designated school official within 10 days.": "Hagidda DHS Study in the States ee ardayda F-1 iyo M-1 ee warbixinta isbeddelka cinwaanka sarkaalka dugsiga ee loo magacaabay 10 maalmood gudahood.",
        "DHS Study in the States post on SEVIS address-of-record.": "Qoraalka DHS Study in the States ku saabsan cinwaanka-diiwaanka ee SEVIS.",
        "DOL FLAG (Office of Foreign Labor Certification) Portal": "Bogga DOL FLAG (Office of Foreign Labor Certification)",
        "DOL FLAG portal that handles LCA and other foreign-labor filings. The dol.gov subpages returned 403 to curl with Mozilla user-agent, consistent with anti-bot behavior on a long-standing .gov domain, so this canonical FLAG portal URL is used.": "Bogga DOL FLAG oo qabta gudbinta LCA iyo gudbinta kale ee shaqaalaha shisheeye. Bogagga hoose ee dol.gov waxay soo celiyeen 403 marka loo isticmaalo curl iyada oo loo isticmaalayo Mozilla user-agent, taas oo la mid ah dabeecadda ka-hortagga botka ee domain .gov ah, sidaas darteed URL-kan caanka ah ee FLAG ayaa la isticmaalay.",
        "Decide your residency, eligibility, or tax status": "Go'aaminta degenaanshahaaga, u qalmitaankaaga, ama xaaladdaada canshuurta",
        "Department of Homeland Security guidance for F-1 and M-1 students, and Department of State regulations for J-1 exchange visitors, generally require reporting an address change to a designated school official (DSO) or program sponsor within 10 days so the SEVIS record can be updated.": "Hagidda Waaxda Amniga Dalka ee ardayda F-1 iyo M-1, iyo qawaaniinta Waaxda Gobolka ee booqdayaasha is-weydaarsiga J-1, guud ahaan waxay u baahan yihiin in la soo sheego isbeddelka cinwaanka sarkaal dugsi oo loo magacaabay (DSO) ama kafiilka barnaamijka 10 maalmood gudahood si diiwaanka SEVIS loo cusboonaysiiyo.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA categories overview.": "Dulmar BridgeUSA Department of State oo ku saabsan qaybaha.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA landing page for the J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.": "Bogga aasaasiga ah ee Department of State BridgeUSA ee J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.",
        "Destination state": "Gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state DMV / MVA": "DMV / MVA gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state attorney general": "Xeer-ilaaliyaha guud ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state board of nursing": "Guddiga kalkaalisada ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state department of agriculture": "Waaxda beeraha ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state department of health": "Waaxda caafimaadka ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state department of labor": "Waaxda shaqaalaha ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state professional licensing": "Shatiga xirfadda ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state tax agency": "Hay'adda canshuurta ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination-state minimum coverage requirements": "Shuruudaha caymiska ugu hooseeya ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination:": "Loo socdo:",
        "Determine whether a specific act is lawful": "Go'aaminta in fal gaar ah uu raacayo sharciga iyo in kale",
        "Different agencies may apply different residency tests. The same person can be a resident for one purpose and not another.": "Hay'ado kala duwan ayaa khusayn kara tijaabooyin degenaansho oo kala duwan. Qof isku mid ah ayaa noqon kara degane ujeedo gaar ah ee ma ahan mid kale.",
        "Direct users to confirm coverage with their insurer. Do not state whether coverage applies.": "U tilmaan isticmaalayaasha inay caymiska ku xaqiijiyaan hay'adda caymiskooda. Ha sheegin in caymisku khusayo.",
        "Disclaimer. %@": "Af-celin. %@",
        "Do not assert that any group is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID rules involve both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only.": "Ha sheegin in koox kasta u qalanto ama aanay u qalmin REAL ID-da gobol gaar ah. Qawaaniinta REAL ID waxay ku lug yeeshaan heerarka ugu yar ee federaalka iyo hirgelinta gobolka oo isbeddeli kara. U isticmaal kaliya luqadda 'hubi' iyo 'waxay kala duwanaan kartaa'.",
        "Do not assert that any specific state always uses a shortened renewal cycle for a given visa category. Frame as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in gobol gaar ah uu had iyo jeer isticmaalo wareeg cusboonaysiin oo gaaban qaybta fiisaha. U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not assert that any visa category is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID involves both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in qayb fiise kasta ay u qalanto ama aanay u qalmin REAL ID gobol gaar ah. REAL ID waxay ku lug yeeshaa labadaba heerarka ugu yar ee federaalka iyo hirgelinta gobolka oo isbeddeli karta. U isticmaal kaliya luqadda 'hubi' iyo 'waxay kala duwanaan kartaa' oo raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not assume": "Ha is malayn",
        "Do not assume a USPS or DMV address update satisfies the federal AR-11 step": "Ha is malayn in cusboonaysiinta cinwaanka USPS ama DMV ay buuxiso tallaabada AR-11 ee federaalka",
        "Do not assume regulated items follow the same rules across state lines": "Ha is malayn in cinwaanada la nidaamiyey ay raacaan qawaaniin isku mid ah xudduudaha gobollada dhexdooda",
        "Do not assume rules from your origin state apply. Rules vary across state, local, and federal jurisdictions. Verify directly with official sources.": "Ha is malayn in sharciyada gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid ay khusayaan. Sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunada gobolka, deegaanka, iyo federaalka. Si toos ah uga hubi ilaha rasmiga ah.",
        "Do not characterize voter registration by non-citizens using legal-conclusion or accusatory language. Use neutral framing such as 'generally not eligible' and 'may create immigration complications'. Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney. Do not give procedural advice for any specific state.": "Ha ku tilmaamin diiwaangelinta codbixinta ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn luqad gunaanad sharci ah ama eedeyn ah. U isticmaal qaabaynta dhexdhexaadka ah sida 'guud ahaan ma qalmaan' iyo 'waxay abuuri karaan dhibaatooyin socdaal'. U tilmaan akhristayaasha inay la tashadaan qareen socdaal oo shati haysta. Ha bixin talo nidaameed gobol gaar ah.",
        "Do not characterize whether any visa category can establish residency in a specific state as a determination. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha ku tilmaamin inay qayb fiise kasta uu aasaasi karo degenaansho gobol gaar ah sida go'aan. U qaab dheh qawaaniin kala saarid lagu hubinayo diiwaangeluhu dugsiga iyo hay'adda waxbarashada sare ee gobolka. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not determine residency. List factors to verify. Direct to the relevant agency or school.": "Ha go'aamin degenaanshaha. Liis ka samee arrimaha la hubinayo. U tilmaan hay'adda ama dugsiga la xiriira.",
        "Do not determine that a household 'is' or 'is not' eligible for Medicaid. Frame as items to verify with the state Medicaid agency. Use 'may apply' and 'rules differ by jurisdiction'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha go'aamin in qoys 'u qalmo' ama 'aanu u qalmin' Medicaid. U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo hay'adda Medicaid ee gobolka. U isticmaal 'waxaa laga yaabaa inay khusayso' iyo 'sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not list which states grant in-state tuition for DACA recipients. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency.": "Ha liisin gobollada bixiya kharashka waxbarashada gobol-gudaha ee DACA-hayayaasha. U qaab dheh qawaaniin kala saarid lagu hubinayo diiwaangeluhu dugsiga iyo hay'adda waxbarashada sare ee gobolka.",
        "Do not provide a public-charge determination or say that using benefits 'will' or 'will not' affect immigration. Frame as 'may interact' and recommend consulting a licensed immigration attorney. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha bixin go'aan ku saabsan culayska dadweynaha ama ha sheegin in isticmaalka manaafacaadku 'saamayn doono' ama 'aanu saamayn doonin' socdaalka. U qaab dheh 'waxay la falgalan kartaa' oo kula tali la tashashada qareen socdaal oo shati haysta. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not provide medical or transport instructions for controlled substances.": "Ha bixin tilmaamo caafimaad ama gaadiid oo loogu talagalay walxaha la nidaamiyo.",
        "Do not provide tactical instructions for transporting, possessing, hiding, storing, modifying, or avoiding enforcement for regulated items.": "Ha bixin tilmaamo qaab-fulin oo loogu talagalay gaadiidka, haysashada, qarinta, kaydinta, beddelka, ama looga gudbinta fulinta sharciga ee cinwaanada la nidaamiyey.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to official tax agency and qualified professionals.": "Ha bixin talo canshuur. U tilmaan hay'adda canshuurta rasmiga ah iyo xirfadlayaasha aqoonsan.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to state tax agency or qualified tax professional.": "Ha bixin talo canshuur. U tilmaan hay'adda canshuurta gobolka ama xirfadle canshuur oo aqoonsan.",
        "Do not say a Board of Nursing in a particular state grants or refuses an applicant's NCLEX path. Use 'verify with the destination Board of Nursing'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in Guddiga Kalkaalisada gobol gaar ah uu siiyo ama diido jidka NCLEX ee codsade. U isticmaal 'ku hubi Guddiga Kalkaalisada ee aad u socotid'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not say a particular aid program 'is open to' or 'is closed to' DACA recipients or LPRs. Use 'verify with the state aid agency and the school financial-aid office'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in barnaamij kaalmo gaar ah 'u furan yahay' ama 'u xidhan yahay' DACA-hayayaasha ama LPR-yada. U isticmaal 'ku hubi hay'adda kaalmada gobolka iyo xafiiska kaalmada maaliyadeed ee dugsiga'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not say a person 'can' or 'cannot' enroll. Use 'verify current eligibility categories with the marketplace operator' since federal rules have changed. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin qof 'wuu' ama 'ma' isdiiwaangelin karo. U isticmaal 'ku hubi qaybaha u qalmitaanka hadda ee maamulaha suuqa' maaddaama qawaaniinta federaalku isbeddelay. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency for a given visa category or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin sida gobol gaar ah uu u qeexo degenaanshaha qaybta fiisaha ama in qof 'yahay' degane. U qaab dheh 'sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta' iyo 'ku hubi hay'adda canshuurta gobolka aad u socotid'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin sida gobol gaar ah uu u qeexo degenaanshaha ama in qof 'yahay' degane. U qaab dheh 'sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta' iyo 'ku hubi hay'adda canshuurta gobolka aad u socotid'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license a given visa category. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in guddi gaar ah uu shatiyeeyo ama aanu shatiyaynayn qaybta fiisaha. U qaab dheh wax kasta sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo guddiga gobolka aad u socotid. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license non-citizens. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in guddi gaar ah uu shatiyeeyo ama aanu shatiyaynayn aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn. U qaab dheh wax kasta sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo guddiga gobolka aad u socotid. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Frame as a federal requirement that 'may apply' depending on age and sex, with state implementation details to verify. Use neutral language and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in qof gaar ah ay tahay ama aanay ahayn in la diiwaangeliyo. U qaab dheh shuruud federaal oo 'laga yaabo inay khusayso' iyada oo loo eegayo da'da iyo jinsiga, iyada oo faahfaahinta hirgelinta gobolka la hubinayo. U isticmaal luqad dhexdhexaad ah oo raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state whether the user is eligible for licensure. Only identify requirements to verify.": "Ha sheegin inay isticmaaluhu u qalmo shatiga. Kaliya aqoonso shuruudaha la hubinayo.",
        "Do not state which states do or do not issue licenses to a given group, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV.": "Ha sheegin gobollada bixiya ama aan bixinin shatiyada koox la bixiyay, hana liisin dukumentiyo la aqbalay oo gaar ah. U qaab dheh wax kasta sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Do not state which states issue or do not issue licenses to a given visa category, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin gobollada bixiya ama aan bixinin shatiyo qaybta fiisuhu, hana liisin dukumentiyo gaar ah oo la aqbalo. U qaab dheh wax kasta sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Document lists accepted by state DMVs for non-citizen license or state-ID applicants can differ from those accepted for U.S. citizens, and accepted combinations may vary by jurisdiction.": "Liisaska dukumentiyada ee ay aqbalaan DMV-yada gobolka ee codsadayaasha shati ama aqoonsi gobol ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn way ka kala duwanaan karaan kuwa loo aqbalo muwaadiniinta U.S., isku-darka la aqbalayaana way ka kala duwanaan karaan xukunka kasta.",
        "Documents for proof of identity": "Dukumentiyada caddaynta aqoonsiga",
        "Done": "La sameeyay",
        "Driver's license": "Shatiga darawalnimada",
        "Driving across one or more state lines for travel.": "Wadidda hal ama in ka badan oo xudduud gobol ah socdaal awgeed.",
        "Driving with coverage that does not meet destination-state minimums can create compliance and financial problems.": "Wadidda baabuur leh caymis aan oolin heerarka ugu hooseeya ee gobolka aad u socotid waxay abuuri kartaa dhibaatooyin u hoggaansanaan iyo dhaqaale.",
        "Drug screen requirements": "Shuruudaha baaritaanka daroogada",
        "Edit selections": "Wax ka beddel doorashooyinka",
        "Emissions testing requirement": "Shuruudda tijaabinta qiiqa",
        "Employer policy": "Siyaasadda shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada",
        "Employment Authorization": "Oggolaanshaha Shaqada",
        "Employment paperwork": "Waraaqaha shaqada",
        "Endorsement requirements if already licensed": "Shuruudaha aqoonsiga haddii horay shati lagu haysto",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary permits, and continuing education requirements vary by state and profession.": "Aqoonsiga, isweydaarsiga, oggolaanshooyinka ku meel gaarka ah, iyo shuruudaha waxbarashada sii socota way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka iyo xirfadda kasta.",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary practice, and continuing education.": "Aqoonsiga, isweydaarsiga, dhaqanka ku meel gaarka ah, iyo waxbarashada sii socota.",
        "Enhanced or REAL ID": "Enhanced ama REAL ID",
        "Establishing a new permanent residence in the destination state.": "Aasaaska guri joogto ah oo cusub gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Eviction and late-fee rules": "Qawaaniinta saaridda iyo dib-u-dhaca lacagta",
        "Example checklist categories": "Tusaalooyin qaybaha liiska hubinta",
        "Exploring options. Receive a broad overview checklist.": "Sahaminta doorashooyinka. Hel liis hubin oo dulmar ballaaran.",
        "F-1 OPT and STEM OPT specific. Use verify with the DSO and SEVP Portal guidance. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Do not advise on a specific status outcome.": "F-1 OPT iyo STEM OPT si gaar ah. U isticmaal 'ku hubi DSO-ga iyo hagidda SEVP Portal'. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado (luqadda gunaanad sharci iyo luqadda ka fogaanshaha ciqaabta). Ha bixin talo natiijo xaalad gaar ah.",
        "F-1 specific. Frame as verify with both DSOs and reference Study in the States or ICE materials. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1 si gaar ah. U qaab dheh ku hubi labada DSO oo tixraac qalabka Study in the States ama ICE. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "F-1 students on post-completion OPT or a STEM OPT extension generally use the SEVP Portal or work with their DSO to update physical and mailing address, employer information, and other personal data, typically within 10 days of a change. Unemployment-day limits during OPT continue to apply during and after a move.": "Ardayda F-1 ee ku jira OPT ka dib-dhammaystirka ama kordhinta STEM OPT guud ahaan waxay isticmaalaan SEVP Portal ama waxay la shaqeeyaan DSO-gooda si ay u cusboonaysiiyaan cinwaanka jirka iyo boostada, macluumaadka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, iyo xog kale oo shakhsi ah, sida caadiga ah 10 maalmood gudahood isbeddelka. Xayiraadaha maalmaha shaqo-la'aanta inta lagu jiro OPT waxay sii khusayaan inta iyo ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q specific. Frame as items to verify with IRS guidance and the employer. Do not state that a particular worker is exempt from FICA. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1, J-1, M-1, iyo Q si gaar ah. U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo hagidda IRS iyo shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada. Ha sheegin shaqaale gaar ah uu ka madax-bannan yahay FICA. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Factors that may affect residency for tuition, taxes, licensing, benefits.": "Arrimaha laga yaabo inay saamayn ku yeeshaan degenaanshaha kharashka waxbarashada, canshuuraha, shatiga, manaafacaadyada.",
        "Failing to register on time may affect eligibility for federal benefits, federal jobs, and naturalization later, even though the requirement is federal. State DMV workflows can also trigger automatic registration, which applicants should understand before applying.": "Diidmada diiwaangelinta wakhtigeeda waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa u qalmitaanka manaafacaadyada federaalka, shaqooyinka federaalka, iyo dhalashada goor dambe, in kasta oo shuruuddu ay tahay federaal. Shaqada DMV-da gobolka ayaa sidoo kale kicin karta diiwaangelin toos ah, taas oo codsadayaashu ay tahay inay fahmaan ka hor codsiga.",
        "Family move": "Guuritaanka qoyska",
        "Federal HealthCare.gov guidance describes a list of immigration statuses considered lawfully present for purposes of the Affordable Care Act marketplace, which includes many common nonimmigrant categories. These categories can purchase coverage without a five-year waiting period that applies in many Medicaid contexts.": "Hagidda HealthCare.gov ee federaalka waxay qeexaysaa liis xaaladaha socdaalka ee loo tixgaliyo joogitaan sharci ah ujeeddooyinka suuqa Affordable Care Act, oo ay ku jiraan qaybo aan-socdaal-doon oo caadi ah. Qaybahaani waxay iibsan karaan caymis iyada oon la sugin muddada shanta sano ee khusaysa xaalado Medicaid badan.",
        "Federal Medicaid and CHIP rules generally include a five-year waiting period for many qualified non-citizens after obtaining qualified status, with several federal exceptions. States may use an option that removes the waiting period for children and pregnant people, and some states cover certain groups with state funds.": "Qawaaniinta Medicaid iyo CHIP ee federaalka guud ahaan waxay ku jiraan muddada sugitaanka shanta sano ee qaar badan oo aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn oo u qalma ka dib markay helaan xaalad u qalanta, oo leh dhowr marka laga reebo ee federaalka. Gobolladu waxay isticmaali karaan ikhtiyaar ka saara muddada sugitaanka carruurta iyo dadka uurka leh, qaar ka mid ah gobolladuna waxay ku daboolaan kooxo gaar ah lacag gobol.",
        "Federal Medicare guidance generally describes eligibility for non-citizens who are lawfully admitted for permanent residence and have lived in the United States for five continuous years. Federal Medicaid rules for most nonimmigrants are narrower than for LPRs, with state-specific options for emergency Medicaid and for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "Hagidda Medicare federaalka guud ahaan waxay qeexaysaa u qalmitaanka aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee si sharci ah loogu soo dhoweeyay degenaansho joogto ah oo ku noolaaday Mareykanka shan sano oo isku xiga. Qawaaniinta Medicaid federaalka ee inta badan aan-socdaal-doon ah way ka cidhiidhi yihiin kuwa LPR, oo leh doorashooyin gobol gaar ah ee Medicaid degdeg ah iyo carruurta iyo dadka uurka leh ee sida sharci ah u degan.",
        "Federal REAL ID rules require evidence of lawful status, and many states issue a REAL ID to nonimmigrant visa holders only with an expiration date that does not extend past the I-94, the visa, or another underlying federal document. Implementation differs between states, and standard (non-REAL-ID) options may or may not be offered.": "Qawaaniinta REAL ID ee federaalku waxay u baahan yihiin caddaynta xaaladda sharciga, gobollo badan ayaa siiya REAL ID haystayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah keliya taariikh dhicitaan ah oo aan ka bixin I-94, fiisaha, ama dukumenti federaal kale oo hoosta yaal. Hirgelintu way ka kala duwan tahay gobollada, doorashooyinka caadiga ah (aan-REAL-ID ahayn)na laga yaabaa in la bixiyo iyo in kale.",
        "Federal SNAP, TANF, and similar programs apply a waiting period to many qualified non-citizens. Some states use state funds to operate replacement or supplemental programs that cover groups not eligible for the federal program, with differing rules.": "SNAP, TANF, iyo barnaamijyada la mid ah federaalku waxay khusayaan muddada sugitaanka qaar badan oo aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn oo u qalma. Gobollo qaar waxay lacagta gobolka u isticmaalaan inay maamulaan barnaamijyo beddel ama dheeri ah oo dabool kooxaha aan u qalmin barnaamijka federaalka, oo leh qawaaniin kala duwan.",
        "Federal law": "Sharciga federaalka",
        "Federal law (INA section 265) generally directs non-citizens to report a change of address to USCIS within 10 days of moving, typically through Form AR-11 or the USCIS online change-of-address tool. The federal filing is separate from updating a state DMV record, an employer, a school, or the U.S. Postal Service.": "Sharciga federaalka (INA qaybta 265) wuxuu guud ahaan u tilmaamayaa aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn inay USCIS u soo sheegaan isbeddelka cinwaanka 10 maalmood gudahood guuritaanka, sida caadiga ah iyada oo loo marayo Foomka AR-11 ama qalabka cinwaan-bedelka onlaynka ee USCIS. Gudbinta federaalku waa ka gooni cusboonaysiinta diiwaanka DMV-da gobolka, shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, dugsiga, ama Adeegga Boostada Mareykanka.",
        "Federal law generally requires motor vehicle offices to offer voter registration to applicants, and forms are screened for citizenship attestations. Non-citizens generally are not eligible to register for federal elections, and a registration record can later create immigration complications.": "Sharciga federaalku guud ahaan wuxuu u baahan yahay xafiisyada gawaarida inay codsadayaasha bixiyaan diiwaangelinta codbixinta, foomamkana waxa loo eegaa caddaynta muwaadinimada. Aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn guud ahaan uma qalmaan inay isdiiwaangeliyaan doorashooyinka federaalka, diiwaan diiwaangelin ah ayaa goor dambe abuuri kara dhibaatooyin socdaal.",
        "Federal residency for tax purposes determines whether worldwide income is reported, which IRS forms apply, and how an interstate move's first and last year are filed at the federal level, separately from state residency rules.": "Degenaanshaha federaalka ee ujeeddooyinka canshuurta wuxuu go'aamiyaa inay la soo sheego dakhliga adduunka, foomamka IRS ee khusayaa, iyo sida sannadka koowaad iyo dambe ee u guuritaanka gobol-dhaafka ah loogu gudbiyo heerka federaalka, oo ka gooni ah qawaaniinta degenaanshaha gobolka.",
        "Federal rules govern which immigration statuses can purchase coverage and receive financial help through the Affordable Care Act marketplace, and those rules have changed. State-based marketplaces and state-funded programs add another layer that can differ between origin and destination.": "Qawaaniinta federaalku waxay maamulayaan xaaladaha socdaalka ee iibsan karaan caymiska oo helsi kaalmada maaliyadeed iyada oo loo marayo suuqa Affordable Care Act, qawaaniintaasna way isbeddeleen. Suuqyada gobolka iyo barnaamijyada lacag gobol-leh waxay ku daraan lakab kale oo u kala duwanaan kara u dhaxeeyo gobollada aad ka soo kacaysid iyo aad u socotid.",
        "Federal tax authority": "Maamulka canshuurta federaalka",
        "Federal tax authority general guidance": "Hagid guud oo maamulka canshuurta federaalka",
        "Filing Requirements, Residency, and Telecommuting FAQs": "Shuruudaha Gudbinta, Degenaanshaha, iyo Su'aalaha Inta Badan La Iwedyiiyo ee Telecommuting",
        "Flags risk levels so you know where to focus": "Wuxuu calaamadiyaa heerarka khatarta si aad u ogaato meesha aad diiradda saari karto",
        "Florida Board of Governors page on residency for tuition purposes for the State University System. flbog.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Bogga Florida Board of Governors ee degenaanshaha ujeeddooyinka kharashka waxbarashada ee State University System. flbog.edu wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan.",
        "Florida FLHSMV documentation page for nonimmigrant applicants for driver licenses and identification cards.": "Bogga dukumentiyada Florida FLHSMV ee codsadayaasha aan-socdaal-doon ah ee shatiyada darawalnimada iyo kaadhadhka aqoonsiga.",
        "Follow device language": "Raac luuqadda qalabka",
        "For L-1, whether the new worksite is the same qualifying U.S. office described in the petition or a different one": "Xaaladda L-1, inay goobta shaqada ee cusub ay tahay xafiis Mareykan oo u qalma oo isku mid ah kii lagu sheegay codsiga ama mid kale",
        "For L-1A, L-1B, and O-1 status, USCIS treats a move to a new worksite as a material change in some fact patterns and not others, depending on what the original petition described and whether the new location is consistent with the approved terms. The analysis follows the underlying petition, not LCA-based MSA rules.": "Xaaladda L-1A, L-1B, iyo O-1, USCIS waxay u qaadaa u guuritaanka goob shaqo oo cusub sida isbeddel muhiim ah qaab xaalado qaar ka mid ah, ee ma ahan kuwa kale, iyada oo ku xiran waxa codsiga asalka ah uu sheegay iyo inay goobta cusub ay la mid tahay shuruudaha la oggolaaday. Falanqaynta waxay raacaa codsiga hoosta yaal, ee ma ahan qawaaniinta MSA ee LCA-saleysan.",
        "For O-1, whether the new venue, event, engagement, or agent arrangement falls within the approved petition scope": "Xaaladda O-1, inay goob, dhacdo, ka qaybgal, ama heshiis wakiil oo cusub ku dhaco baaxadda codsiga la oggolaaday",
        "For federal tax purposes, a non-citizen is generally treated as a resident alien if they meet the Substantial Presence Test or hold lawful permanent resident status, with separate rules in IRS Publication 519 for exempt individuals (such as certain F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q students and scholars) whose days of presence may not count.": "Ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka, aan-muwaadin guud ahaan waxa loola dhaqmaa sida resident alien haddii ay buuxiyaan Substantial Presence Test ama ay haystaan xaaladda degane joogto ah oo sharci ah, oo leh qawaaniin gooni ah Daabacaadda IRS 519 ee shakhsiyaadka laga reebay (sida ardayda F-1, J-1, M-1, iyo Q-da qaarkood) oo aanay maalmaha joogitaankooda lagu tirinin.",
        "For nursing specifically, how the destination state treats primary state of residency under the Nurse Licensure Compact for a non-citizen who declares either the country of origin or the compact state, and any credentials-evaluation requirement (for example, CGFNS) for internationally educated applicants": "Si gaar ah kalkaalisada, sida gobolka aad u socotid uu ula dhaqmo gobolka aasaasiga ah ee degenaanshaha hoos imanaysa Nurse Licensure Compact aan-muwaadin ku dhawaaqaya labadaba dalka aasaaska ama gobolka heshiiska, iyo shuruud qiimaynta-aqoonsiga (tusaale, CGFNS) codsadayaasha caalami ah waxbarashada laga qaaday",
        "Form AR-11 paper version posted on uscis.gov.": "Nooca warqada ee Foomka AR-11 oo lagu dhejiyay uscis.gov.",
        "Frame AR-11 as a federal reporting step to verify, not a guarantee of status. Do not state that any specific status category is or is not covered without source. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing such as the i-word, the p-words, and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney for status-specific guidance.": "U qaab dheh AR-11 sida tallaabo warbixin federaal oo la hubinayo, ee ma aha damaanad xaaladda. Ha sheegin in qayb xaaladeed gaar ah la daboolay ama aan la daboolin iyada oon isha la haynin. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado (luqadda gunaanad sharci sida 'i-word', 'p-words', iyo luqadda ka fogaanshaha ciqaabta). U tilmaan akhristayaasha inay la tashadaan qareen socdaal oo shati haysta hagid xaalad gaar ah.",
        "Frame as a federal requirement that may apply, with a nonimmigrant exception that may apply based on continuous valid status. Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida shuruud federaal oo laga yaabo inay khusayso, oo leh marka aan-socdaal-doon ah oo laga reebay oo laga yaabo inay khusayso oo ku saleysan xaalad ansax ah oo sii socota. Ha sheegin in qof gaar ah loo baahan yahay ama loo baahnayn in la diiwaangaliyo. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Frame as items to verify in IRS Publication 519 and with a qualified tax preparer. Do not state a person is a dual-status filer for a particular year. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo Daabacaadda IRS 519 iyo diyaariye canshuur oo aqoonsan. Ha sheegin qof yahay file xaalad labanlaha ah sannad gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Frame as items to verify with CMS and the destination-state Medicaid agency. Federal rules have changed and may continue to change. Do not state a person is or is not eligible. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo CMS iyo hay'adda Medicaid ee gobolka aad u socotid. Qawaaniinta federaalku way isbeddeleen waxayna sii isbeddeli karaan. Ha sheegin qof yahay ama aanu ahayn mid u qalma. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Frame as items to verify with IRS Publication 519 and a tax preparer. Do not state a person is or is not a resident alien for federal tax purposes. Use may apply and rules differ by jurisdiction. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo Daabacaadda IRS 519 iyo diyaariye canshuur. Ha sheegin qof yahay ama aanu ahayn resident alien ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka. U isticmaal 'waxaa laga yaabaa inay khusayso' iyo 'sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta'. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Frame as items to verify with the DSO or J-1 sponsor and Study in the States or ICE guidance. This item is specific to F-1, M-1, and J-1 status. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo DSO ama kafiilka J-1 iyo hagidda Study in the States ama ICE. Cinwaankan waxa loogu talagalay xaaladda F-1, M-1, iyo J-1. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado (luqadda gunaanad sharci iyo luqadda ka fogaanshaha ciqaabta).",
        "Frame as items to verify with the current HealthCare.gov or state-based marketplace lists. Do not state any specific category is or is not on the lawfully present list, since federal rules have changed. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo liisaska hadda ee HealthCare.gov ama suuqa gobol-saleysan. Ha sheegin in qayb gaar ah ay ku jirto ama aanay ku jirin liiska joogitaanka sharciga, maaddaama qawaaniinta federaalku isbedeleen. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Full disclaimer:": "Af-celinta dhammaystiran:",
        "General information only. Not legal advice. Verify with official sources.": "Macluumaad guud oo keliya. Ma aha talo sharci. Ku hubi ilaha rasmiga ah.",
        "General information only. Verify with the relevant official source. Not legal advice.": "Macluumaad guud oo keliya. Ku hubi isha rasmiga ah ee la xiriira. Ma aha talo sharci.",
        "Generate checklist": "Abuur liis hubinta",
        "Generated:": "La sameeyay:",
        "Generates a checklist of topics to verify before moving": "Wuxuu abuuraa liis hubin oo mowduucyo aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso ka hor guuritaanka",
        "Georgia Department of Driver Services page for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including a 30-day rule for establishing Georgia residency.": "Bogga Georgia Department of Driver Services ee codsadayaasha aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn, oo ay ku jirto qaanuun 30-maalmood ah oo aasaaska degenaanshaha Georgia.",
        "Get a grouped checklist with risk badges and links to official sources.": "Hel liis hubin oo kooxaysan oo leh calaamado khatar iyo xiriiriyeyaal isaha rasmiga ah.",
        "H-1B specific. Frame as verify with employer counsel and USCIS or DOL guidance. Do not state that an amendment is or is not required in a particular fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "H-1B si gaar ah. U qaab dheh ku hubi qareenka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada iyo hagidda USCIS ama DOL. Ha sheegin in beddelku la baahan yahay ama aan loo baahnayn qaab xaalado gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "H-1B specific. Use verify whether MSA boundaries cover the new worksite. Do not assert that no amendment is needed in any specific fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "H-1B si gaar ah. U isticmaal 'hubi inay xudduudaha MSA daboolaan goobta shaqada cusub'. Ha sheegin in beddel loo baahnayn xaalad gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "HOW IT WORKS": "SIDUU U SHAQEEYO",
        "Health clearance documentation": "Dukumentiyada nadiifinta caafimaadka",
        "HealthCare.gov Coverage for Immigrants": "HealthCare.gov Caymiska Soogalootiga",
        "HealthCare.gov Health Coverage for Lawfully Present Immigrants": "HealthCare.gov Caymiska Caafimaadka ee Soogalootiga Joogitaan Sharci Leh",
        "HealthCare.gov Immigration Status and the Marketplace": "HealthCare.gov Xaaladda Socdaalka iyo Suuqa",
        "HealthCare.gov general page on immigrant coverage options.": "Bogga guud ee HealthCare.gov ee doorashooyinka caymiska soogalootiga.",
        "HealthCare.gov list and explanation of lawfully present categories for ACA marketplace coverage.": "Liiska HealthCare.gov iyo sharaxaadda qaybaha joogitaan sharci leh ee caymiska suuqa ACA.",
        "HealthCare.gov page on which statuses qualify for marketplace coverage.": "Bogga HealthCare.gov oo ku saabsan xaaladaha u qalma caymiska suuqa.",
        "Healthcare access / insurance": "Helitaanka daryeelka caafimaadka / caymiska",
        "Help avoid enforcement or recommend workarounds": "Kaalmayn si looga fogaado fulinta sharciga ama soo jeedinta dariiqyo dhaaf-ah",
        "Helps tailor the checklist. None of these flags create legal conclusions.": "Wuxuu caawiyaa habayntu liiska hubinta. Midkoodna calaamadahani ma abuurayaan gunaanad sharci.",
        "High risk only": "Khatar sare oo keliya",
        "High-risk categories require separate verification.": "Qaybaha khatar-sare leh waxay u baahan yihiin xaqiijin gaar ah.",
        "High-risk categories require separate verification. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use of regulated items is lawful.": "Qaybaha khatar-sare leh waxay u baahan yihiin xaqiijin gaar ah. MoveSafe ma go'aamiyo in haysashada, gaadiidka, ama isticmaalka cinwaanada la nidaamiyey ay raacayaan sharciga.",
        "High-risk items to verify separately": "Cinwaanada khatar-sare leh ee la hubinayo si gaar ah",
        "High-risk only": "Khatar-sare oo keliya",
        "High-risk warning. High-risk categories require separate verification.": "Digniin khatar-sare. Qaybaha khatar-sare leh waxay u baahan yihiin xaqiijin gaar ah.",
        "Highlights stale or placeholder sources": "Wuxuu iftiimiyaa ilaha duugay ama kuwa boos-haye ah",
        "Housing / renter basics": "Aasaaska guryaha / kireystaha",
        "How CHIP coverage rules in the destination state interact with the waiting period for your household": "Sida qawaaniinta caymiska CHIP ee gobolka aad u socotid ay ula falgashan karto muddada sugitaanka qoyskaaga",
        "How OPT or STEM OPT employment is treated for FICA while the worker remains a nonresident alien": "Sida loola dhaqmo shaqada OPT ama STEM OPT ee FICA halka shaqaaluhu weli yahay nonresident alien",
        "How a future change to LPR status before age 26 may affect the registration question": "Sida isbeddelka mustaqbalka ee xaaladda LPR ka hor da'da 26 uu u saamayn karo su'aasha diiwaangelinta",
        "How a mid-year move between states may affect aid-application deadlines": "Sida u guuritaanka bartamaha sano ee u dhaxeeyo gobollada uu u saamayn karo kama dambaysta codsiga kaalmada",
        "How a move mid-coverage may affect the reasonable opportunity period for documentation": "Sida u guuritaanka bartamaha caymiska uu u saamayn karo muddada fursadda macquulka ah ee dukumentiyada",
        "How a transfer interacts with current employment authorization, on-campus work, and any pending OPT": "Sida u wareejintu ula falgasho oggolaanshaha shaqada hadda, shaqada kambaska, iyo OPT kasta oo sugaya",
        "How a year of arrival to or departure from the United States interacts with the test": "Sida sannadka imaanshaha ama bixitaanka Mareykanka uu ula falgasho tijaabada",
        "How an in-progress extension of status (for example, an H-1B amendment or an F-1 transfer) interacts with renewing or replacing the credential": "Sida kordhinta xaaladda ee horumarsan (tusaale, beddel H-1B ama u wareejin F-1) ay ula falgasho cusboonaysiinta ama beddelka aqoonsiga",
        "How clinical-placement and background-check requirements interact with your immigration status": "Sida shuruudaha meelaynta isbitaalka iyo baaritaanka asalku ay ula falgasho xaaladdaada socdaalka",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification": "Muddada aad u baahan tahay inaad degenaansho ka haysato gobolka aad u socotid ka hor inta aan lagu tixgalin kala saaridda gobol-gudaha",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification, and whether time on a nonimmigrant visa counts": "Muddada aad u baahan tahay inaad degenaansho ka haysato gobolka aad u socotid ka hor inta aan lagu tixgalin kala saaridda gobol-gudaha, iyo inay wakhtiga aad ku jirtay fiise aan-socdaal-doon ah la tirinayo",
        "How temporary stay is treated differently from permanent relocation": "Sida joogitaanka ku meel gaarka ah si kala duwan loogu qaado guuritaanka joogtada ah",
        "How the destination state defines residency": "Sida gobolka aad u socotid uu u qeexo degenaanshaha",
        "How the destination state's DMV or other application workflows interact with Selective Service screening": "Sida DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid ama shaqada codsiga kale ay ula falgasho baaritaanka Selective Service",
        "How the move affects any STEM OPT Form I-983 training plan and the destination employer's E-Verify status": "Sida guuritaanku uu u saamayn karo qorshe tababar Foomka I-983 ee STEM OPT iyo xaaladda E-Verify ee shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada ee aad u socotid",
        "How the move and any change in employer-sponsored coverage interact with marketplace special enrollment timing": "Sida guuritaanku iyo isbeddel kasta oo caymis-kafiilkaagu uu bixiyo ay ula falgashan karaan wakhtiga isdiiwaangelinta gaarka ah ee suuqa",
        "How the move interacts with H-4 dependent status and any pending I-485 or I-140": "Sida guuritaanku ula falgasho xaaladda ku-tiirsanaan H-4 iyo I-485 ama I-140 kasta oo sugaya",
        "How to confirm a registration after applying for a license": "Sida loo xaqiijiyo diiwaangelin ka dib codsiga shatiga",
        "How to correct the record if a non-citizen registration was submitted in error": "Sida loo saxo diiwaanka haddii diiwaangelin aan-muwaadin ah si khalad ah loo gudbiyo",
        "How to decline voter registration when offered at the DMV in that state": "Sida loo diido diiwaangelinta codbixinta marka lagu bixiyo DMV-da gobolkaas",
        "How to obtain or replace a Selective Service registration record if needed for future immigration or federal-benefit filings": "Sida loo helo ama loo beddelo diiwaanka diiwaangelinta Selective Service haddii loo baahdo gudbinta socdaalka ama manaafacaadka federaalka ee mustaqbalka",
        "How unemployment days are counted during a gap between employers around a move": "Sida maalmaha shaqo-la'aanta lagu tiriyo inta lagu jiro farqi u dhexeeyo shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada agagaarka guuritaanka",
        "I am a nursing or healthcare student": "Waxaan ahay arday kalkaaliye caafimaad ama daryeel caafimaad",
        "I am moving for school": "Waxaan u guurayaa dugsi awgeed",
        "I am moving for work": "Waxaan u guurayaa shaqo awgeed",
        "I have a car": "Waxaan leeyahay baabuur",
        "I hold or need a professional license": "Waxaan haystaa ama u baahanahay shati xirfadeed",
        "I may stay temporarily": "Waxaa laga yaabaa inaan si ku meel gaar ah u joogo",
        "I may work in the destination state": "Waxaa laga yaabaa inaan ka shaqeeyo gobolka aan u socdo",
        "I own a pet": "Waxaan leeyahay xayawaan guri",
        "I plan to relocate permanently": "Waxaan qorshaynayaa inaan si joogto ah u guuro",
        "I rent housing": "Waxaan kireystaa guri",
        "I understand": "Waan fahmay",
        "I understand that MoveSafe provides general information and source links, not legal advice.": "Waan fahmayaa in MoveSafe uu bixiyo macluumaad guud iyo xiriiriyeyaal isa, ee uusan ahayn talo sharci.",
        "I'm a Dreamer (DACA / similar)": "Waxaan ahay Dreamer (DACA / kuwa la mid ah)",
        "I'm a green card holder (LPR)": "Waxaan ahay hayste kaadhka cagaaran (LPR)",
        "I'm on a nonimmigrant visa (F-1, H-1B, J-1, etc.)": "Waxaan ku jiraa fiise aan-socdaal-doon ah (F-1, H-1B, J-1, iwm.)",
        "ICE SEVIS landing page.": "Bogga aasaasiga ah ee ICE SEVIS.",
        "ICE SEVIS overview page for background context on F, M, and J record management.": "Bogga dulmar ICE SEVIS oo bixiya macluumaad asal ah oo ku saabsan maaraynta diiwaanka F, M, iyo J.",
        "ICE Student and Exchange Visitor Program (SEVIS) Landing Page": "Bogga Aasaasiga ah ee ICE Student and Exchange Visitor Program (SEVIS)",
        "ICE Transfers for F-1 Students": "ICE U Wareejinta Ardayda F-1",
        "ICE page describing F-1 SEVIS transfers.": "Bogga ICE oo qeexaya u wareejinta F-1 SEVIS.",
        "IRS Aliens Employed in the U.S. Social Security Taxes": "IRS Aliens-ka Shaqaalaha U.S. Canshuurta Social Security",
        "IRS Determining an Individuals Tax Residency Status": "IRS Go'aaminta Xaaladda Degenaanshaha Canshuurta Shakhsiga",
        "IRS Foreign Student Liability for Social Security and Medicare Taxes": "IRS Mas'uuliyadda Ardayga Shisheeye ee Canshuurta Social Security iyo Medicare",
        "IRS Publication 519 U.S. Tax Guide for Aliens": "IRS Daabacaadda 519 U.S. Hagidda Canshuurta ee Aliens",
        "IRS Publication 519 describes a dual-status tax year for non-citizens who are both a nonresident and a resident for federal tax purposes during the same year, which can apply to many arrival, departure, and adjustment-of-status fact patterns rather than interstate moves alone.": "Daabacaadda IRS 519 waxay qeexaysaa sannad canshuureed xaalad labanlaha ah ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee labadaba nonresident iyo resident ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka inta lagu jiro sannadka isku mid ah, taas oo khusayn karta xaalado badan oo imaanshaha, bixitaanka, iyo hagaajinta-xaaladda halkii ay khusayn lahayd guuritaanka gobol-dhaafka ah keligeed.",
        "IRS Publication 519 main page.": "Bogga ugu weyn ee Daabacaadda IRS 519.",
        "IRS Taxation of Dual-Status Individuals": "IRS Canshuurta Shakhsiyaadka Xaaladda Labanlaha ah",
        "IRS Taxation of Nonresident Aliens": "IRS Canshuurta Nonresident Aliens",
        "IRS dual-status filer page. Final redirected URL uses the dual-status-individuals slug.": "Bogga filerada xaaladda labanlaha ah ee IRS. URL-ka kama dambaysta loo wareejiyo wuxuu isticmaalaa slug dual-status-individuals.",
        "IRS general page on taxation of nonresident aliens.": "Bogga guud ee IRS ee canshuurta nonresident aliens.",
        "IRS guidance generally describes an exemption from FICA tax for wages paid for services performed by F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q nonresident-alien students, scholars, teachers, researchers, and trainees, when the work is part of the activity for which they were admitted and they remain nonresident aliens for federal tax purposes.": "Hagidda IRS guud ahaan waxay qeexaysaa marka laga reebay canshuurta FICA mushaharka loo bixiyo adeegyada ay qabtaan ardayda, cilmi-baarayaasha, macallimiinta, iyo tababaranayaasha F-1, J-1, M-1, iyo Q ee nonresident-alien, marka shaqadu ay qayb ka tahay howsha loo soo dhoweeyay ay weli yihiin nonresident aliens ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka.",
        "IRS overview page for non-citizen tax residency status.": "Bogga dulmar IRS oo ku saabsan xaaladda degenaanshaha canshuurta ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn.",
        "IRS page describing the Substantial Presence Test for federal tax residency.": "Bogga IRS oo qeexaya Substantial Presence Test ee degenaanshaha canshuurta federaalka.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for F, J, M, Q nonresident-alien students and scholars.": "Bogga IRS ee qaabilaadda canshuurta FICA ee ardayda iyo cilmi-baarayaasha F, J, M, Q nonresident-alien.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for non-citizens employed in the U.S.": "Bogga IRS ee qaabilaadda canshuurta FICA ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee shaqaaleeysiiyay U.S.",
        "IV. Residency - The City University of New York Tuition and Fee Manual": "IV. Degenaanshaha - The City University of New York Tuition and Fee Manual",
        "Identification Requirements": "Shuruudaha Aqoonsiga",
        "Identity and residency documents accepted by the destination state": "Dukumentiyada aqoonsi iyo degenaansho ee uu aqbalo gobolka aad u socotid",
        "If a credential is issued with an unexpected short term tied to a federal document, the timing of renewal can affect domestic flights, federal building access, and other tasks that may rely on a REAL ID after a move.": "Haddii aqoonsi la bixiyo oo leh muddo gaaban oo aan la fileyn oo ku xidhan dukumenti federaal, wakhtiga cusboonaysiintu waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa duulimaadyada gudaha, gelitaanka dhismaha federaalka, iyo waxqabadyada kale ee laga yaabo inay ku tiirsanaadaan REAL ID ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "Illinois Board of Higher Education directory page on campus liaisons supporting students under state tuition-equity provisions.": "Bogga buug-tilmaameedka Illinois Board of Higher Education ee xidhiidhiyeyaasha kambaska oo taageeraya ardayda hoos imanaysa qodobada sinaanta kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka.",
        "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL) page. ilsos.gov returns a 302 redirect to its own page for curl HEAD requests, which is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov domain; the URL was confirmed via the Secretary of State's own search index.": "Bogga Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL). ilsos.gov wuxuu soo celiyaa wareejin 302 ee bogiisa codsiyada curl HEAD, taas oo la yaqaan oo been ah oo taban oo domain .gov ah; URL-ka waxa lagu xaqiijiyay diiwaanka raadinta ee Secretary of State-ka.",
        "Illinois Student Assistance Commission resources page for non-U.S. citizen students including RISE Act and Alternative Application context. isac.org returns 403 to non-browser requests (anti-bot); this is a known false negative.": "Bogga khayraadka Illinois Student Assistance Commission ee ardayda aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn oo ay ku jiraan RISE Act iyo Alternative Application. isac.org wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (ka-hortagga botka); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan.",
        "Immigration status - including Dreamer / DACA status - can significantly affect driver's licenses and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing and healthcare), in-state tuition, SSN-related requirements, and state tax filing. Rules vary by state and federal law and change frequently.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney before relying on any state-by-state summary.": "Xaaladda socdaalka - oo ay ku jirto xaaladda Dreamer / DACA - waxay si weyn u saamayn kartaa shatiyada darawalnimada iyo REAL ID, shatiga xirfadda (gaar ahaan kalkaalisada iyo daryeelka caafimaadka), kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka, shuruudaha la xiriira SSN, iyo gudbinta canshuurta gobolka. Sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta iyo sharciga federaalka, waxayna isbeddelaan si joogto ah.\n\nMoveSafe ma aha bedel u ah talada sharci. Ka fiirso inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan koobid gobol-ka-gobol.",
        "Immunization requirements": "Shuruudaha tallaalka",
        "Important to verify": "Muhiim in la hubiyo",
        "Information for Non-US Citizens": "Macluumaadka Aan-Muwaadiniinta US-Ahayn",
        "Inspection requirement": "Shuruudda kormeerka",
        "Insurance networks, Medicaid and marketplace rules, and prescription transfer processes vary by state.": "Shabakadaha caymiska, qawaaniinta Medicaid iyo suuqa, iyo hababka u wareejinta dawooyinku way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta.",
        "Insurance networks, student health, prescriptions, primary care access.": "Shabakadaha caymiska, caafimaadka ardayga, dawooyinka, helitaanka daryeelka aasaasiga ah.",
        "Internship": "Tababarka shaqo",
        "J-1 specific. Frame as verify with the program sponsor and reference 22 CFR Part 62. Do not state that any specific category does or does not require sponsor pre-approval for a particular change. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "J-1 si gaar ah. U qaab dheh ku hubi kafiilka barnaamijka oo tixraac 22 CFR Qaybta 62. Ha sheegin in qayb gaar ah ay u baahan tahay ama aanay u baahnayn oggolaansho hore oo kafiil isbeddel gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Jurisdiction: %@": "Xukunka: %@",
        "Know how to respond if asked to register to vote at the DMV": "Ogow sida looga jawaabo haddii laguu sheego inaad isdiiwaangeliso codbixin DMV-da",
        "L-1 and O-1 specific. Frame as verify against the approved petition and consult petitioner counsel. Do not state that an amendment is or is not needed for any specific scenario. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "L-1 iyo O-1 si gaar ah. U qaab dheh ku hubi codsiga la oggolaaday oo la tasho qareenka codsadaha. Ha sheegin in beddel loo baahan yahay ama loo baahnayn xaalad gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Language": "Luuqadda",
        "Last verified:": "Hubinta u dambeysay:",
        "Last verified: %@": "Hubinta u dambeysay: %@",
        "Lawful permanent residents (LPRs / green card holders) can face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing - foreign credentials evaluation may apply), Medicaid and state-marketplace eligibility (the federal 5-year bar interacts with state programs), state tax filing, and how DMVs handle voter-registration prompts (LPRs are not eligible to vote in federal or most state elections).\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney for status-affecting questions and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Degane joogto ah oo sharci ah (LPR / haystayaasha kaadhka cagaaran) waxay la kulmi karaan kala duwanaansho gobol-ka-gobol oo ku saabsan dukumentiyada shatiga darawalnimada iyo REAL ID, shatiga xirfadda (gaar ahaan kalkaalisada - qiimaynta aqoonsiga shisheeye laga yaabo inay khusayso), u qalmitaanka Medicaid iyo suuqa gobolka (xayiraadda 5-sano ee federaalka ayaa la falgashada barnaamijyada gobolka), gudbinta canshuurta gobolka, iyo sida DMV-yadu u qabtaan codsiyada diiwaangelinta codbixiyaha (LPR-yada uma qalmayaan inay ka codeeyaan doorashooyinka federaalka iyo inta badan kuwa gobolka).\n\nMoveSafe ma aha bedel u ah talada sharci. Ka fiirso inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ee su'aalaha saamaynta ku leh xaaladda, iyo xirfadle canshuur oo aqoonsan ee gudbinta gobol-dhaafka ah.",
        "Lease decisions made based on origin-state assumptions may not match destination-state rules.": "Go'aamada heshiiska kirada ee lagu saleeyo malaha gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid laga yaabaa inaanay la mid noqon qawaaniinta gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Lease terms, security deposits, notice periods, and tenant protections.": "Shuruudaha kirada, deebaajiga ammaanka, muddooyinka ogeysiiska, iyo ilaalinta kireystaha.",
        "Legal aid (general info)": "Kaalmo sharci (macluumaad guud)",
        "License transfer, deadlines, documents, and REAL ID awareness.": "U wareejinta shatiga, kama dambaysta, dukumentiyada, iyo wacyigelinta REAL ID.",
        "Licensure Compacts - NCSBN": "Heshiisyada Shatiga - NCSBN",
        "Licensure requirements can affect clinical placement, NCLEX eligibility, endorsement, and employment timing.": "Shuruudaha shatigu waxay saamayn ku yeelan karaan meelaynta isbitaalka, u qalmitaanka NCLEX, aqoonsiga, iyo wakhtiga shaqada.",
        "Links to official state agency sources": "Wuxuu ku xirayaa ilaha hay'adaha rasmiga ah ee gobolka",
        "Load example": "Soo geli tusaalaha",
        "Local city/county rules may add protections. Review lease language directly.": "Qawaaniinta magaalada/gobolka deegaanka ayaa laga yaabaa inay ku darto ilaalin. Si toos ah u eeg luqadda heshiiska kirada.",
        "Local ordinance": "Qaanuunka deegaanka",
        "Local pet licensing requirements": "Shuruudaha shatiga xayawaanka guriga ee deegaanka",
        "Main USCIS page for H-1B specialty occupations classification.": "Bogga ugu weyn ee USCIS ee kala saaridda shaqooyinka takhasuska H-1B.",
        "Many nonimmigrant visa holders are not within the standard Medicare or Medicaid eligibility groups, and federal rules in this area have been changing. Destination-state Medicaid rules add another layer that may differ from origin-state rules.": "Haystayaal badan oo fiise aan-socdaal-doon ah ah ma ku jiraan kooxaha u qalmitaanka caadiga ah ee Medicare ama Medicaid, qawaaniinta federaalka ee aaggana way isbeddeleen. Qawaaniinta Medicaid ee gobolka aad u socotid waxay ku daraan lakab kale oo u kala duwanaan kara qawaaniinta gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid.",
        "Many states require new residents to obtain a state driver's license within a specific period after becoming a resident.": "Gobollo badan waxay u baahan yihiin in degane cusub helo shatiga darawalnimada ee gobolka muddo gaar ah ka dib markay noqdaan degane.",
        "Mark as not verified": "Calaamadi inaan la xaqiijinin",
        "Mark as verified": "Calaamadi inay la xaqiijiyay",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for nonresidents using Form 1-NR/PY. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Hagidda Massachusetts Department of Revenue ee canshuurta dakhliga shakhsiga ee nonresidents iyada oo la isticmaalayo Foomka 1-NR/PY. mass.gov wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan.",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for part-year residents. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Hagidda Massachusetts Department of Revenue ee canshuurta dakhliga shakhsiga ee deganayaasha qayb-sano ah. mass.gov wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan.",
        "Massachusetts RMV identification requirements page covering REAL ID, standard licenses, and lawful presence documentation. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov-hosted state portal.": "Bogga shuruudaha aqoonsiga Massachusetts RMV oo daboolaya REAL ID, shatiyada caadiga ah, iyo dukumentiyada joogitaanka sharciga. mass.gov wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan oo bog gobol ah oo .gov-hoy-yaha ah.",
        "Massachusetts identification (ID) requirements": "Shuruudaha aqoonsiga (ID) Massachusetts",
        "May involve penalties or licensing consequences.": "Waxaa laga yaabaa inay ku lug yeesho ciqaabyo ama cawaaqib shati.",
        "Medicare.gov Get Started with Medicare": "Medicare.gov La Bilow Medicare",
        "Minimum coverage, state-specific rules, and policy address updates.": "Daboolida ugu yar, qawaaniinta gobolka u gaarka ah, iyo cusboonaysiinta cinwaanka caymiska.",
        "Missing a school or hospital onboarding requirement can delay clinical hours and graduation timing.": "Seegista shuruudda gelinta dugsiga ama isbitaalka waxay dib u dhigi kartaa saacadaha isbitaalka iyo wakhtiga qalin-jabinta.",
        "Missing a state motor vehicle deadline can create administrative or driving-related problems after relocation.": "Seegista kama dambaysta hay'adda gawaarida ee gobolka waxay abuuri kartaa dhibaatooyin maamul ama wadid la xiriira ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "Missing source": "Isha maqan",
        "Missing the transfer reporting steps at the new school, or letting the transfer release date and program start fall out of sync, can affect status maintenance and access to on-campus work.": "Seegista tallaabooyinka warbixinta u wareejinta dugsiga cusub, ama u oggolaanshaha taariikhda sii-deynta u wareejinta iyo bilaabista barnaamijka inay ka jajaban yihiin, waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa sii-haynta xaaladda iyo helitaanka shaqada kambaska.",
        "Mixed jurisdiction": "Xukun isku dhafan",
        "MoveSafe checklist": "Liiska hubinta MoveSafe",
        "MoveSafe is a source-first checklist tool. It links you to official resources and highlights topics to verify. It does not provide legal advice.": "MoveSafe waa qalab liis hubin oo isha rasmiga ah marka hore u dhigta. Wuxuu kugu xirayaa ilaha rasmiga ah wuxuuna iftiimiyaa mowduucyada aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso. Ma siiyo talooyin sharci.",
        "MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves. You can still build a checklist, but some items may not apply.": "MoveSafe waxaa loogu talagalay guuritaanka gobol-ka-gobol. Weli waad samayn kartaa liis hubin, laakiin qaar ka mid ah cinwaanada laga yaabo inaanay khusayn.",
        "MoveSafe prefers official agency sources. Placeholder entries should be replaced with verified URLs before production use.": "MoveSafe waxa uu door biday ilaha hay'adaha rasmiga ah. Galitaannada boos-haye waa in lagu beddelaa URL-yo la hubiyay ka hor isticmaalka soosaarka.",
        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "MoveSafe wuxuu bixiyaa macluumaad guud oo sharci iyo maamul oo ku saleysan ilo dadweynaha la heli karo. Ma bixiyo talooyin sharci, ma abuuro xiriir qareen-macmiil, mana aha in loo isticmaalo bedel u ah talo qareen shati haysta xukunkaaga. Sharciyada iyo qawaaniinta hay'aduhu way isbeddelaan si joogto ah. Mar walba ku hubi macluumaadka ilaha rasmiga ah ka hor inta aadan go'aan gaarin.",
        "Moving across state lines? Know what to verify before you go.": "Ma u guuraysaa gobol kale? Ogow waxa aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso ka hor inta aadan tegin.",
        "Moving for school": "U guuritaan dugsi awgeed",
        "Moving for work": "U guuritaan shaqo awgeed",
        "Moving from %1$@ to %2$@": "Ka guuritaanka %1$@ una guuritaanka %2$@",
        "Moving from one state's aid program to another's may change which aid applications to consider and which documents to gather, and this can affect how to plan tuition and living costs at the destination.": "Ka guuritaanka barnaamijka kaalmada gobol qiyaastiis ee kale waxa uu bedeli karaa codsiyada kaalmada la tixgelinayo iyo dukumentiyada la soo aruurinayo, taasna waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa sida loo qorsheeyo kharashka waxbarashada iyo nolosha ee halka loo socdo.",
        "Moving may change which state tax withholding forms apply, and remote work can create cross-state payroll questions.": "Guuritaanku wuxuu bedeli karaa foomamka hayidda canshuurta gobolka ee khusayaa, shaqada fogna waxay abuuri kartaa su'aalo mushaharka gobol-dhaaf ah.",
        "Moving to another state for clinical rotations, externships, or supervised practice.": "U guuritaan gobol kale wareegyada isbitaalka, ku tababarka, ama dhaqanka la kormeerayo.",
        "NCLEX and license-by-endorsement steps can stall when documentation does not match a destination board's current rules, which can delay clinical placement, hire dates, and compact-state recognition.": "Tallaabooyinka NCLEX iyo shatiga-aqoonsiga ayaa joogsan kara marka dukumentiyadu aanay la mid noqon qawaaniinta hadda ee guddiga aad u socotid, taas oo dib u dhigi karta meelaynta isbitaalka, taariikhaha shaqo qaadashada, iyo aqoonsiga gobolka heshiiska.",
        "NCLEX eligibility requirements": "Shuruudaha u qalmitaanka NCLEX",
        "NCSBN Licensure Compacts overview, including Nurse Licensure Compact context for non-citizen primary state of residency declarations.": "Dulmar Heshiisyada Shatiga NCSBN, oo ay ku jirto macluumaadka Nurse Licensure Compact ee ku dhawaaqida gobolka aasaasiga ah ee degenaanshaha ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn.",
        "National Council of State Boards of Nursing licensure guidance page for background context across boards.": "Bogga hagidda shatiga National Council of State Boards of Nursing ee macluumaadka asalka guddiyada dhammaantood.",
        "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education page summarizing the Tuition Equality Act and the 2020 statute affecting dependent students of H-1B holders.": "Bogga New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education oo kooba Tuition Equality Act iyo xeerka 2020 ee saamayn ku leh ardayda ku-tiirsanaha ee haystayaasha H-1B.",
        "New York DMV REAL ID page noting that an Enhanced ID is for U.S. citizens only and that REAL ID issued to applicants with temporary lawful status may expire with the federal document.": "Bogga REAL ID ee New York DMV oo tilmaamaya in Enhanced ID uu yahay kaliya ee muwaadiniinta U.S. iyo in REAL ID-ga loo bixiyo codsadayaasha xaalad sharci ku meel gaar ah haysta uu dhici karo dukumentiga federaalka.",
        "New York DMV documentation guidance for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including REAL ID and standard credentials.": "Hagidda dukumentiyada New York DMV ee codsadayaasha aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn, oo ay ku jiraan REAL ID iyo aqoonsiyada caadiga ah.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance FAQ on residency, nonresident filing, and telecommuting.": "FAQ New York Department of Taxation and Finance ee degenaanshaha, gudbinta nonresident, iyo telecommuting.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance page on nonresident and part-year filing using Form IT-203.": "Bogga New York Department of Taxation and Finance ee gudbinta nonresident iyo qayb-sano ah iyada oo la isticmaalayo Foomka IT-203.",
        "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN licensure requirements page, which administers nursing licensure for New York.": "Bogga shuruudaha shatiga RN ee New York State Education Department Office of the Professions, oo maamula shatiga kalkaalisada ee New York.",
        "No items match your filters": "Wax cinwaanno ah uma waafaqsana sifeeyayaashaada",
        "No source has been added yet for this item. Add an official source before relying on it.": "Wax isha ah weli looma diirin cinwaankan. Ku dar isha rasmiga ah ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan.",
        "No sources are attached to the items in this view.": "Ma jiraan ilo ku lifaaqan cinwaanada muuqaalkan.",
        "Non-Immigrant - Florida Department of Highway Safety and Motor Vehicles": "Aan-Socdaal-Doon ah - Florida Department of Highway Safety and Motor Vehicles",
        "Nonimmigrant visa holders (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, and others) face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID (often tied to I-94 / visa dates), in-state tuition (most public universities classify F-1 students as out-of-state), professional licensure documentation, tax residency rules, and health-insurance options. USCIS also requires reporting any address change within 10 days via Form AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney, your school's DSO if on F-1, employer HR or immigration counsel if on a work visa, and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Haystayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doonka ahayn (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, iyo kuwa kale) waxay la kulmaan kala duwanaansho gobol-ka-gobol oo ku saabsan dukumentiyada shatiga darawalnimada iyo REAL ID (badanaa waxay xidhan yihiin taariikhaha I-94 / fiisaha), kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka (jaamacadaha dadweynaha intooda badan waxay arday F-1 u tixgeliyaan in ay yihiin kuwo aan-gobolka-ahayn), dukumentiyada shatiga xirfadda, sharciyada degenaanshaha canshuurta, iyo doorashooyinka caymiska caafimaadka. USCIS sidoo kale waxa loo baahan yahay in la soo sheego isbeddel kasta oo cinwaan ah 10 maalmood gudahood iyada oo loo marayo Foomka AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe ma aha bedel u ah talada sharci. Ka fiirso inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta, DSO-ga dugsigaaga haddii aad ku jirto F-1, HR-ka shaqaalaha ama qareenka socdaalka haddii aad ku jirto fiisaha shaqada, iyo xirfadle canshuur oo aqoonsan ee gudbinta gobol-dhaafka ah.",
        "Nonresident and part-year resident forms and instructions": "Foomamka iyo tilmaamaha nonresident iyo degane qayb-sano ah",
        "Not sure yet": "Wali ma hubo",
        "Note for editors: %@": "Qoraal loogu talagalay tafatirayaasha: %@",
        "Notes:": "Qoraallada:",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact FAQs": "Su'aalaha Inta Badan La Iwedyiiyo ee Nurse Licensure Compact",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact general information": "Macluumaad guud oo ku saabsan Nurse Licensure Compact",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact participation": "Ka qaybgalka Nurse Licensure Compact",
        "Nurse Licensure Compact public FAQ page including the rule that a non-citizen applicant may declare either country of origin or the compact state as primary state of residency.": "Bogga FAQ dadweynaha ee Nurse Licensure Compact oo ay ku jirto qaanuunka uu codsade aan-muwaadin ah uu ku dhawaaqi karo labadaba dalka aasaaska ama gobolka heshiiska sida gobolka aasaasiga ah ee degenaanshaha.",
        "Nurse Licensure Guidance - NCSBN": "Hagidda Shatiga Kalkaalisada - NCSBN",
        "Nursing / healthcare licensure": "Shatiga kalkaalisada / daryeelka caafimaadka",
        "Nursing education, licensure, endorsement, temporary permits, and compact license rules are handled by state boards of nursing and may differ by state.": "Waxbarashada kalkaalisada, shatiga, aqoonsiga, oggolaanshooyinka ku meel gaarka ah, iyo qawaaniinta shatiga heshiiska waxaa qabta guddiyada kalkaalisada ee gobolka waxayna kala duwanaan karaan xukunka kasta.",
        "Nursing school / healthcare training": "Dugsiga kalkaalisada / tababarka daryeelka caafimaadka",
