        "Official source needed before relying on this item.": "Isha rasmiga ah ayaa loo baahan yahay ka hor intaadan ku tiirsanaan cinwaankan.",
        "Official state agency": "Hay'adda rasmiga ah ee gobolka",
        "Open official source": "Fur isha rasmiga ah",
        "Optional profile": "Profile ikhtiyaari ah",
        "Origin and destination are the same. MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves - some items may not apply.": "Asalka iyo halka loo socdo waa isku mid. MoveSafe waxa loogu talagalay guuritaanka gobol-ka-gobol. Cinwaannada qaarkood laga yaabo inaanay khusayn.",
        "Origin state": "Gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid",
